Comment: Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 800M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 750M, saved ground on turn, not enough room until final 100M, finished off well to take a place.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, found rail near 850M, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 2-1/2L back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Began fairly, taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, steadied near 750M, raced behind midfield on turn, kept on same pace in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped well from a wide draw, took the lead but trapped wide, headed approaching 800M, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped at start before getting lovely run in fifth away from the rail. Charged to the lead at the 150m mark & went clear to win impressively.

Bumped & unbalanced at start before racing just worse than midfield along the rail. Stayed nearer the rail on straightening when nearly 5L from lead before closing well to move to second at 75m without challenging winner.
Showed early speed to lead. Raced over a length clear on straightening, continued in lead until passed by winner at 150m, passed for second at 75m, held well beaten third on line.

Strode forward to race second at the leaders quarters. Slipped back to be 1.5L from the lead on straightening as leader skipped clear, battled on in last 300m but ultimately gave ground to be well beaten in 4th.

Jumped awkwardly before drifting back after the start & racing worse than midfield away from the rail. Shifted outwards to be the widest runner on straightening when about 6L from lead & held that deficit on the line.

Crowded soon after start before getting position in midfield along rail after improving after first 100m. Was held up around bend, shifted outwards at 350m before finishing off only one paced between rivals in final stages.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Only battled in last 300m & ultimately weakening to be beaten 7.5L into midfield.
Began ok but didn't drive for lead & instead raced in midfield away from rail. Was ridden along passing the 500m, was 5L from lead entering last section but only weakened a few lengths, no threat.

Crowded on jumping, bumped & got back to race at the tail. Shifted out wider on the track on straightening when last & nearly 9L from the lead before passing only a few tiring rivals without ever looking to be in a threat.
Had a nice run fourth on the rail for the majority. Was ridden along before straightening, weakened meekly to be beaten nearly 9L.
Bumped at the start before racing a clear third last the start. Continued rearward & over 8L from the lead on straightening before failing to improve in the straight, second last.
Jumped awkwardly & lost ground before being shifted across behind runners to race at the tail. Continued rearward on straightening when nearly 9L from lead & failed to make any headway, last.
Sat behind midfield, traveled nicely, obtained clear running inside 350M, made good progress over the final 200M.
Sat rear, traveled okay, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, responded well when asked, stayed on well to grab 2nd.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, closed off nicely.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened entering the Straight, ran on evenly.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, one pace to the line.
Settled towards rear, lay in in the Straight, finished off fairly (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, slightly dropped back passing the 700M, no clear run in the early Straight (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, ridden along to sit handy, weakened inside 250M, could not be ridden out.
Settled handy 2 wide, improved rounding the Turn, limited response when placed under pressure, weakened and faded quickly inside 150M.
Sat midfield 3 wide, traveled fairly, eased down in the Straight (Roarer, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Ridden forward after the start & came across from widest gate to race outside the leader. Moved up to share the lead at the 100m, just held off late closer in final stages to win narrowly.

Raced just worse than midfield between runners for the majority. Eased wider passing 600m, was about 5L from lead on straightening when still tenth before finishing strongly down the outside to be narrowly beaten into second.
Began fast & came across from second widest gate to lead. Raced over a length clear on straightening, held the lead until joined by winner at 100m, battled hard late, only beaten 1.5L.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Commenced to race keenly passing the 800m, stayed along rail on straightening when 4.5L from lead, made continual ground along rail to steal 4th late.

Jumped only fairly & then raced near the rail when galloping between runners. Was next to last & nearly 7L from lead on straightening before making good late ground down the outside in final furlong to be beaten under 2L.

Knuckled on jumping before getting a nice run on the leaders back. Continued not far from the lead at the furlong mark, shifted out at 150m (rider suspended) before finishing only evenly in final stages.

Raced in midfield along the rail, steadied away from heals near the 800m. Moved away from rail near 600m, about 3L from lead on straightening, checked when having no room near the 100m but was only going fairly at that stage.
Had a lovely run 1,1 for the majority. Continued in third place until near the 300m mark before peaking on effort & weakening a few lengths to midfield.

Slow to begin & was a clear last after the start. Continued rearward on straightening, shifted outward after 400m mark, passed a couple late, never likely (substantial blood in trachea, reluctant to stretch out early â€“rider).

Raced in midfield, three wide but with cover throughout. Entered final section 4L from lead, lay inwards passing 200m when finishing off ok before slightly ungenerous late when already beaten (substantial blood in trachea).

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Straightened under 3L from the lead, dashed well in early part of straight until peaking on run near the 200m & weakening late after wide passage.

Had a soft run in midfield between runners throughout. Was just over 4L from the lead on straightening, didn't have much room when between runners passing the 150m mark but was already beaten at that point.
Bumped on jumping before being taken back to race worse than midfield when three deep with cover. Continued back & wide throughout, weakened a further few lengths in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly before being taken back to race at the tail. Was a clear last on straightening when taken outwards to be the widest runner but did nothing in the run to the line, long last.

Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 4 lengths back, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, showed very good response, hit the front 50M, won by 1/2L.
Jumped awkwardly and shifted in on jumping, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, took the lead 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, commenced move 500M, finished off well to take a place.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.

Began awkwardly and crowded, raced behind midfield on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, unable to obtain clear run until well inside final furlong, made some progress final 100M.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 10, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority of the race, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at tail, lost touch from halfway, unacceptable performance.
Jumped well, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on strongly. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Settled towards the rear, had trouble finding clear running early in the Straight, made good ground when have clear running.
Jumped okay, ridden along early to be prominent, kept on okay in the Straight.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, ran on fairly. (Roarer)
Settled just behind the leader, made some progress early in the Straight, and finished off only one pace after 250M.
Settled at the rear on the rail, stayed on okay.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, made some late ground. (Lame right hind next morning)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, made little impression.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, unable to quicken in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, settled midfield 2 wide, never a factor.
Jumped well and hard ridden early to take the lead, weakened and faded at 250M.

Placing: PU
Comment: Crowded at the start, pulled up soon after. (Performance unacceptable, must trial) (See Incident Report)
Settled in 6th about 4L off the pace, gained slightly closer to 5th passing the 1000 metres, quickened well inside final 350 metres to assert authority 150 metres out.
Pressed forward from a poor gate to join the leaders, disputed lead rounding home bend before gaining narrow advantage into home straight, found winner too strong when headed 150 metres out.
Settled one from last in 7th of small field, came under pressure upon straightening and fought on steadily to reach 3rd inside final 100 metres.

Settled in 5th on rail some 3L off the pace, lost position passing 1000 metres dropping to 6th onto home bend, saved ground turning in and fought on under pressure inside final 200 metres to narrowly miss a placing.
Settled in last of the strung-out small field of eight trailing the field until the 150 metres, produced good impression for best work late.
Broke well in front before taken back to 3rd one-out-one-back, kept on on straightening until finding no extra under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Began fairly, recovered steadily along the rail to take slender lead 1200 metres out, narrowly headed into straight and lay in under pressure, crowded 200 metres out and yielded ground.
Jumped fairly settling not far off the pace in 4th, travelled keenly on the rail behind leaders coming onto home bend, kept on in straight until finding no extra 200 metres out and tightened.
Slow to begin from draw 1, given a patient ride towards the rear, plenty to do top of the straight, brought to outside and finished off strongly to get up close home. Impressive win.
Held up behind midfield, raced wide no cover from 800M, widest turning home, let down well to lead near 150M, no match for the fast finishing favourite in latter stages and was overrun close home.
Settled near last, made nice inroads in the run home, briefly challenged for the lead mid-straight before flattening late.
5th on settling, stayed close enough to leaders throughout, kept battling from 400M but lacked the dash to launch a serious bid.
Given a waiting ride at the rear, brought wide top of straight, ran on without threatening first few.
Obtained a 3-wide position ahead of midfield, responded well early straight to lead inside 300M, run ended mid-straight, faded to finish 6th.

Restrained behind mid-division along the inside, got held up 400M-250M but only got home fairly once obtaining clear running. (Jockey : not suited by the middle stages of the event being run outside of standard time.)
Jumped on terms and soon took up running, caught by rivals inside 300M, weakened away.
Settled in mid-division 3Ls back along the fence, was badly held up from 400M to 100M behind weakening rivals and lost all chance. (Roarer.)
Jumped awkwardly, settled in a midfield position 8th along the 2-path, unable to obtain clear running until 350M but couldn't pick up speed when required.
Chased leader along the inside, lacked a kick in the straight, soon out of contention.
From draw 11 worked forward to be tracking leader on outside, had no extra passing 300M, weakened towards the line.
Sat in behind midfield 5Ls off the pace on settling, couldn't make any headway over final 400M.
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders, went 2nd 400M, hung in under pressure in the straight and proved very difficult to ride, swamped by rivals passing 300M.

Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, not enough room early in straight, cleared 250M, took the lead 200M, kept on well to the line, just able to hold off the challenger late.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly, just denied in a ding-dong battle.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, angled out 450M, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, still 7 lengths behind the leader turning in, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, very wide into straight, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, easy run to turn, hit the front 300M, kept on well to hold off the challengers.
Slowly away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, closed off well to take a place.
Away well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, made good progress there. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 14, raced at rear on the outside, there to turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 350M, kept on well until approaching 150M, weakened gradually final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight.
Jumped only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on outer, no cover for the majority of the race, showed limited response early in straight, no clear run 100M, eased thereafter.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Bled.)

Horse No: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Horse Name: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Jockey: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Comment: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Average to begin, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, closer on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on strongly to the line.
Fast into stride, raced better than midfield on the inside, left in 2nd from 950M, 2-1/2L back on turn, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, kept on same pace to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield on the outside early, inconvenienced and dropped to rear near 1000M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2-1/2L on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, inconvenienced and dropped position 1000M, 4 lengths back turning in, emptied early in straight, eased thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently, commenced to buck near 1000M, dropped to tail-end 900M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame right front leg next day.)
Settled in rear of midfield, commenced move rounding home bend, quickened well under pressure from 5th into straight to gain upper hand over 50 metres out.
Began well settling over 2L back in 4th, commenced move on top of home bend to hit the front narrowly upon straightening, swamped over 50 metres out.
Broke well from the widest draw to soon lead, narrowly headed under pressure 200 metres out, just held on for 3rd.
Settled in last few from a poor draw, commenced move rounding home bend, sustained good progress in straight to narrowly miss 3rd.
Soon dropped to last few despite ridden along, gained slightly closer to 7th passing the 700 metres, saved ground turning in, produced good late impression inside final 100 metres.
Began well from the one draw settling one back in 3rd on rail, baulked behind runners upon straightening, unable to quicken to threaten inside final 150 metres.
Settled in 5th 3-wide without cover, became 6th rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Settled well back, saved ground turning for home, ran on past well-beaten horses in straight.
Away slowly from a poor draw, quickly recovered towards rear in 7th or 8th, commenced move very wide approaching home turn, one-paced in straight. (Lame next day)
Ridden forward 3-wide before settling in 2nd just outside race leader, dropped away quickly from a similar position into straight.
Ridden along to sit in front of midfield, traveled smoothly, responded nicely when asked.
Sat rear, angled out rounding the turn, showed some dash inside 200M, closed off nicely.
Sat behind midfield, was bumped near 150M, made some progress thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards rear on the rail, traveled okay, crowded for clear running inside 200M, closed off okay.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in front of midfield, traveled fairly, one pace to the finish.
Jumped awkwardly, settled worse than midfield on the rail, ran on fairly.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Settled towards rear 2 wide, slightly weakened rounding the turn, made no impression.
Settled handy, weakened entering the Straight, never a threat.
Sat midfield initially, made a forward move inside 1100M, weakened and faded in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Jumped okay, ridden along to lead until 1000M, weakened and fade inside 150M.
Sat midfield, raced wide throughout, did not be ridden out to the finish (Disappointing performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Improved after the start, raced prominently before being steadied near the 1500m & then racing 1,1, thereafter. Closed well to take the lead at 150m, won by 0.75L.

Raced in midfield along the rail for the majority. Was 3.5L from lead entering last section, moved off the rail on straightening, shifted outwards & had difficulty getting clear until near 100m, charged to second late.

Had a soft run along the rail just behind the leaders throughout. Improved to race on the leaders back from the 500m, stayed close to the rail in the straight, finished well to only be beaten 1.25L into third.

Raced third last along the rail in early & middle stages. Stayed near the inside at the 400m when about 6L from lead, improved into tight run near 200m, was making ground when struck on nose at 150m, closed to just miss 3rd.

Was wide out of straight first time before improving to share lead at 1050m. Led momentarily before again racing outside leader from 850m. Obtained outright lead on straightening, passed by winner 150m, fought well late.
Raced in midfield way from the rail throughout. Was just under 3L from the lead entering last section, finished off fairly to the line to finish in a bunch in midfield only beaten around 1.5L.

Pushed forward to lead, challenged in the lead near the 1050m, shared lead until regaining narrow outright lead near the 850m. Was immediately headed on straightening, battled away, and ultimately weakened into seventh.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was 4L from the lead at the 400m mark, moved three wide at that stage, finished off only one paced to the line, no threat.

Shifted across behind runners & raced just worse than midfield away from rail. Steadied just before straightening when there was no run between rivals, was then held up until 150m, only tested final 100m, had some excuse.

Crowded after the start & then raced just worse than midfield along the rail. Moved off the rail approaching the 400m mark when 4.5L from the lead, did little in the straight & could only hold deficit to the line.

Drifted back after start & raced second last away from the rail. Was relegated to last near 600m, moved three wide with cover from 550m, the widest runner on straightening when next to last, failed to improve in straight.
From the outside gate was shifted back to last. Moved wider on the track near the 700m & was left without cover, improved to midfield near the 400m when 4L from lead, weakened in straight to be last.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on the inside, there to turn, showed good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well to take a place.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the inside, shared lead turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Awkward leaving stalls and started very slowly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider from 450M, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (Lost right front plate.)
Began well, sent forward to take the lead but trapped 3 wide, shared the lead with rivals turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear throughout, eased final 350M, unacceptable performance.
Steadied early from a wide barrier to obtain cover towards the rear, angle out rounding the Turn, closed off strongly to score.
Broke well, ridden along early to be prominent, sat just behind the leader, improved nicely into the Straight, kept on well, just got caught near the line.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, made good progress, never threatened top 2.
Settled midfield 2 wide, began his run 3 wide at the 500M, got taken wider, run peaked inside 150M.
Settled in a handy position 2 wide, only one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, switched out to 3 wide to improve at 500M, ran on evenly.
Sat at the rear, under pressured at 600M, took time to respond, made some late ground.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, never a threat (See Incident Report)
Ridden along early and showed good early speed to lead, weakened inside 200M.
Settled midfield on the rail, never in contention.
Settled in last few in 9th on rail, obtained clear passage over 250 metres out, finished off the race strongly to snatch victory final strides.
Began moderately before travelling keenly early one back in 2nd on rail, 2L off the lead rounding home bend and into straight, fought on dourly only to find winner too strong.
Attempted to make all setting a sound pace and kicking 2L clear onto home bend, unable to sustain tempo and swamped close to home.
Began moderately, made steady headway along the rail to reach midfield 800 metres out, in similar position into straight, ran on steadily to narrowly miss a placing.
Began fairly from a poor draw, improved steadily wide without cover to reach 3rd some 3L back inside the 700 metres, kept on one pace from similar position into straight.
Jumped best from the widest draw before taken back towards rear in 8th, commenced move passing the 400 metres and widest into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled at the back, saved ground turning in, ran on steadily past well-beaten horses in straight.
Crowded at start before settling well behind, only ran past well-beaten horses in home straight.
Jumped fairly before settling in midfield in 6th or 7th some 4L off the pace, slightly further off the speed rounding home bend, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Close up early, shifted back to some 3L back in 4th early in back straight, slightly further off the speed rounding home bend, kept on before weakening inside final 150 metres.
Prominent early before taken back to midfield, remained wide without cover to straight, dropped away quickly.
Positively ridden, tracked leader on settling, challenged down center of track and hit lead near 200M, dug deep late under pressure to just prevail. Game effort.
Fast into stride, held position just off leaders on settling, fought on well for much of the straight, gave everything but just came up short.
Travelled well in midfield before moving closer to leaders 500M, loomed up mid-straight and fought hard to the line for a close 3rd.
Dropped back and trailed the field, 8Ls to make up 400M, finished decently and came from well back to claim 4th. Too much to do. (Jockey questioned re his riding.)
Away with them, maintained a midfield position 5Ls off the pace, ran on steadily passing 300M without threatening first 3.
From draw 12 driven to find the lead, caught nearing 200M, no extra late and faded to finish 6th.
Settled in the back half of the field, 9th at mid-way, brought wide into straight but only worked home fairly.
Jumped on terms, settled down behind midfield, 6Ls to make up 400M but was just fair throughout the home straight.
Reserved towards the rear, swung widest into straight but gave very little in the run home. Never threatened.
In midfield early stages, struggled to maintain position 600M, already beaten top of straight. (Jockey reported his horse is still somewhat immature.)
Held up near last, had plenty to do 400M but failed to respond under pressure, never in it.
From draw 11 caught wide no cover early stages, moved closer to leaders making home turn, didn't go on with it passing 300M, weakened to last.

Fast into stride, took the early lead, headed near 1000M, 2nd on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well to hold off the challengers.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Began smartly, raced prominently, took the lead near 1000M, led by 2-1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside, there to turn, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide towards rear, 8 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began well from gate 1, raced in 3rd, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Quickly into stride, led uncontested into straight, kept responding to pressure passing 300M, held on well from pursuing rivals at the line.

From wide draw settled at the rear further back than intended, closed off well when asked on straightening, got 2nd near line in an eye-catching effort. (Lay in final 200M / Jockey questioned re riding tactics.)
Restrained to a position ahead of midfield, 3-wide making the home turn, battled steadily home to claim 3rd in a busy finish.
Dropped back from wide draw and adopted a rearward position 7Ls back, worked into it nicely from 350M, made up good ground in the run home to get up for 4th late.
Crowded on jumping, raced in midfield along the fence, stayed on moderately over final 300M, lacked a kick and was safely held in the end.
Chased leaders along the inside, moved up to 2nd early straight, tried hard to get to leader but succumbed late, lost several places close home.

Caught 4-wide without cover from outside draw, maintained a position just ahead of midfield home turn, kept battling until no extra inside 100M. (Jockey was advised his ride in early stages lacked initiative.)
Always in touch, raced keenly in early stages, had every chance turning home, improved to 3rd mid-straight but couldn't sustain effort final 150M.
Jumped well, taken back to a midfield position, was commencing to finish off the race when disappointed for running 200M and had difficulty obtaining clear running after. Inconclusive run.
Jumped fairly, settled near last 5Ls off the pace, offered very little on straightening, never posed a serious threat.
Tracked leader, checked 200M when already beaten, no extra late stages.
Caught wide in a position behind midfield from draw 11, struggled to keep up 550M, never dangerous.
Settled at the back of midfield, held up for clear running until 200M, made no impression after.
Ridden hard to lead, traveled nicely, responded well when asked inside 200M, kept on well to win.
Sat handy, traveled smoothly, made some ground over the concluding stages, closed off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, sat worse than midfield, showed some dash over the final 150M, stayed on well.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, commenced to improve entering the Straight, ran on evenly to the finish.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, traveled okay, no clear run in the early Straight, closed off okay.
Sat handy, traveled fairly, weakened over the final 75M (Substantial blood in trachea).
Sat worse than midfield, made minor progress in the Straight, closed off fairly.
Settled midfield, steadied passing 400M, one pace to the line.
Settled towards rear 2 wide, switched out in the Straight, never a factor.
Sat towards rear, limited when asked, never a threat
Sat rear, raced rear throughout, no impression made.
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, angled out rounding the turn, weakened notably in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield, weakened and faded inside 150M.
Chased the leader on the rail, slightly weakened rounding the turn, further weakened and faded entering the Straight.

Improved after the start to stride to the lead after 200m & then raced with about a 2L advantage in middle stages. Was joined in the lead near the furlong marker but dug deep all the way to the line to win narrowly.

Led momentarily after start before racing on the rail in third place from the 1300m. Moved over the heels of the leader on straightening, moved up to share lead at 200m but couldn't passed, just beaten into second.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was just over 2L from the lead entering last section, finished steadily all the way to the line to hold third.

Raced in midfield along the rail early. Moved off the rail near the 700m, was 3L from the lead on straightening, shifted back inwards near 400m but raced tight before getting clear in final 300m & finishing steadily.

Had a soft run in midfield along rail. Came under hard ridding near the 500m, just under 3L from the lead entering last section, raced tight & bumped with rival runner approaching 350m before only holding margin last furlong.

Jumped awkwardly & bumped before racing worse than midfield along the rail early before improving to midfield passing the 1000m mark. Was 5L from the lead on straightening before finishing only steadily to line.

Jumped awkwardly & raced worse than midfield away from the rail. Continued third last, shifted wider passing 500m & wider again on straightening, just under 8L behind at 400m before making some late headway to midfield.

Shifted across behind runners from a wide draw & raced rearward along rail. Moved away off rail just before straightening, was over 6L from lead entering last section before passing a few tiring runners without threatening.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Eased wider just before straightening, was 5.5L from the lead entering final section & could only maintain that margin all the way to the line.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Came under riding passing the 550m mark to hold position, was 4L from the lead entering final section but weakening a few lengths to finish tenth.

Was shifted back behind runners from the outside draw to race at the tail. Continued rearward, shifted wider at the 500m, steadied away from heels on straightening when the widest runner before never challenging in straight.

Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Came under pressure near the 550m & began losing ground, was over 7L from the lead entering last section & was beaten a similar margin on line when finishing third last.

Drifted back after start to race rearward before being relegated to last passing 1100m. Was ridden along passing the 600m mark, was 9.5L from the lead on straightening when still last & could only pass one tiring rival.

Raced forward from gate 12, obtained position two-wide without cover in second place after 500m. Continued close to lead on straightening, peaked on run at 350m before weakening badly to finish a long last (mucus in trachea).
Away well, raced better than midfield on the stands' side, hard ridden 250M, took the lead approaching 50M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Out in line, raced in midfield on the stands' rail, commenced move 200M, not enough room 150M to 50M, finished off well to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3 lengths at 400M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, hard ridden 300M, made some progress thereafter to make frame without threatening.
Taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths or so back at 400M, switched to the middle of the track after passing 350M and made good progress thereafter.
Made contact with the left side of its barrier and lost ground on jumping, raced at rear on the stands' rail, 7 lengths back at 400M, finished off well without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the stands' rail, made some progress after passing 400M, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped only fairly, raced towards rear, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden 300M, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden 350M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 away from the stands' rail, unable to maintain position after passing 500M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped nicely, ridden along to hold a forward position, ran on strongly to score, won comfortably.
Broke a step slow, settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made good progress, best stride late.
Jumped with the field, showed very good early speed to lead, kept on nicely until weakened inside final 50M. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, under pressured near 700M, ran on evenly.
Jumped okay, settled behind midfield 2 wide, showed some dash inside 250M, run peaked at 50M.
Settled towards the rear, stayed on fairly.
Settled midfield, one pace when asked.
Tracked leader, weakened inside 250M.
Hard ridden early but was beaten for the early lead, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Raced 3 wide midfield, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Got crowded at the start, sat towards the rear, never a factor.
Got hampered at the start, sat last, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Well there from a low draw, soon came to join race leader near stands side eventually taking over 500 metres out, drew clear inside final 200 metres.
In rear early improving steadily to 1L 3rd 700 metres out near the centre of the track, came to tackle eventual winner inside final 200 metres but found him too strong.

Settled over 2L back early stages, tightened and dropped to last over 600 metres out, renewed effort coming onto course proper and quickened well inside final 150 metres, snatched distant 3rd final strides.

Slightly slow out settling well behind of small field, recovered steadily to 6th some 2L back approaching half-way mark down the centre of the track, fought on under pressure only to be pipped for a placing late.
Niggled along from moderate start settling just over 1L back in 4th, one-paced in closing stages.
Well there on the stands rail, soon drifted some 2L back inside the 700 metres, shared 5th coming onto course proper, faded gradually.
Soon took up running, held narrow lead until headed half-way out, weakened noticeably inside final 250 metres.
Jumped awkwardly settling in worse than midfield, found nothing under pressure inside final 400 metres.
Settled over 2L back behind midfield, inconvenienced and lost position 600 metres out, made no further impression.
Jumped only fairly, recovered to race behind midfield, picked up nicely on straightening, made up good ground in the run home to win going away in the end.

Caught wide early stages before improving to race outside leader, took narrow lead near 200M, tried hard but couldn't hold off winner late. (Jockey fined for using the whip forward of the saddle on numerous occasions.)
From wide draw driven forward to find the lead, pressed by rival home turn, kept to the task on straightening, headed near 200M, rallied to hold 3rd late stages.
Guided to a rail position in midfield, cut the corner home turn and moved up to 3rd early straight, battled on evenly and just missed a minor placing in a tight finish.
Jumped only fairly from draw 1, reserved towards the rear, kept to inside on straightening, ran on mildly and was held by leaders final stages in a busy finish.
Stalked the speed on inside, switched away from fence 500M, battled on evenly to the line and was not far away at the finish. (Bled.)
Away well, restrained to race just off the pace, poised to strike at 400M, fought on steadily to line.
Dropped back to 2nd last, 5Ls to make up top of straight, made some ground without ever threatening.
Jumped only fairly, held up behind midfield, gave limited response turning home, never going the pace to challenge.
Settled in mid-division along the 3-path, couldn't finish off when the race got serious, never a winning hope.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, got too far back straightening, lacked finishing effort.

Jumped awkwardly, caught wide no cover chasing leaders, struggled to hold his position passing 550M, soon beaten and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance / Jockey reported his horse lay out on the turn.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, a bit closer on turn, angled out 450M, finished off strongly, led close home.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead 650M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 550M, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to make frame, not quite able to challenge.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover, a length or so back, 2 wide from 750M, found rail 600M, sat right behind the leader turning in, kept on same pace in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, steadied off heels 600M, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 650M, 2nd turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Away with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, tracked leaders on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.

Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, angled out 350M, cleared 250M, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line, won comfortably.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside early, moved a bit closer after 1100M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader from 550M, took the lead 450M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until 200M, made little progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, unable to obtain clear run in straight, stumbled near 125M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on outer, moved a bit closer on turn, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, inconvenienced 250M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 6 lengths back, a bit clear on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, crowded 300M, weakened final furlong.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival from 550M, peaked and headed 450M, weakened final furlong.

Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, moved closer in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, hit the front 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, closed off well to take a place.

Bumped start, took the early lead, headed after passing 800M, taken back to race 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight. (Had an epiglottic entrapment.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, took the lead after passing 800M, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight.

Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail 400M, 5 lengths back turning in, made some headway early in straight, no clear run and snatched up near 75M, eased thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently on the inside, 1/4L behind the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, made no progress in straight.

Raced slightly wide leaving the straight first time before improving to race outside the leader from the 1100m. Shared the lead on straightening, bumped at the 300m before pulling away in the final furlong to win easily.

Shared lead early before racing on the leaders back from the 1100m.Stayed near to the inside on straightening when 2L from lead, closed to second place near the furlong marker, was beaten 2L by winner, 2L clear of third.

Improved after start to share the lead passing the winning-post first time before crossing to the rail when leading near 1100m. Joined in the lead on straightening, bumped with winner at 300m, battled to hold well beaten 3rd.

Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was just under 3L from the lead entering final section, couldn't go with the first three in the straight, weakening a few lengths but managing to hold fourth place on line.

Jumped only fairly before racing third last away from the rail for the majority. Was just over 5L from the lead entering last section, came wider on straightening before holding deficit in the run to the line.

Drifted back after the start & raced rearward throughout. Was relegated to last near the 500m, continued last & over 6L from the lead entering last section before passing a few rivals when making up a length to midfield late.

Jumped awkwardly & lost ground before improving along the rail after the start to race in midfield in middle stages. Entered last section just under 4L from the lead, stayed near the inside but weakened a further few lengths.

Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was just over 4L from the lead entering final section, came wider on straightening but did very little in the straight, weakening to be beaten 6.5L on line.

Was shifted behind runners after the start & raced at the tail. Shifted wider at the 500m, was the widest runner on straightening when about 6L from lead before failing to make any headway into margin.
Jumped only fairly before racing just worse than midfield along the rail throughout . Came under pressure before straightening and then weakened very poorly in the straight to finish a long last.
Jumped okay, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, switched out rounding the Turn, well responded when asked inside 150M, kept on well to win.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, traveled smoothly, made good progress near the 100M, finished off nicely.
Sat midfield 2 wide, traveled okay, slightly improved from 500M, closed off okay.
Sat handy on the rail, angled out at the Turn, ran on evenly.
Slow to jump, settled midfield, commenced to improve inside 650M, one pace to the line.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened inside 500M, ran on fairly (Substantial mucus in trachea).
Sat towards rear on the rail, commenced to make ground near 450M, made minor progress in the Straight.
Settled behind midfield, traveled fairly, limited response when placed under pressure (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, ridden along to chase the lead, was taken wide at the Turn, weakened notably inside 200M (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear 2 wide, one pace throughout, no impression.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, no contention.

Had superior early speed to cross the field from gate 11 to lead. Momentarily joined in lead near 750m before again moving a few lengths clear passing 600m. Was over 2L clear on straightening, dug deep in late stages to win.

Raced in a bunch behind easy leader at first bend before having a nice run in third on rail in the middle stages. Continued second and 2.5L from lead entering last section, closed well late but was unable to get to leader.

Raced keenly early when maintaining position in midfield along rail. Was 4.5L from lead entering last section, stayed nearer the inside on straightening before making good late ground to be beaten under a length into third.

Jumped only fairly & then was shifted back from wide gate to race rearward. Continued to race three wide line with cover around bend, was the widest runner on straightening before making good late ground down the outside.

Jumped awkwardly & crowded and consequently raced last early. Improved along the rail after first bend to race worse than midfield. Was over 6L from the lead entering last section before making late ground to midfield.

Crowded & checked shortly after start & raced rearward throughout. Was relegated to last approaching the final corner, stayed nearer the rail on straightening before making late ground to finish in a bunch in midfield.

Raced worse than midfield away from the rail. Raced keenly & got head up near 600m when being steadied between rivals. Was third last & over 7L behind on straightening before making some late headway to finish midfield.

Steadied from widest gate & taken back to last. Continued rearward when 7.5L from the lead entering final section, shifted inwards for clear running passing the 300m before closing steadily to finish in a bunch in midfield.

Raced in a bunch behind easy leader early before improving position to momentarily share lead near 750m but then dropping a few lengths behind. Was around 3L from lead on straightening, weakened slightly when over-run late.

Raced in a bunch vying for second position at first bend before being crossed & getting 1,1 position from 800m. Was ridden along from 450m, 4L from lead entering last section before being over-run, weakening to third last.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Continued in midfield and 5.5L from the lead entering final section, had clear running on straightening but did little in the straight & finished second last.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Continued wide around bend, was 5L from lead entering last section, was beaten early in the straight & tired out to finish last after a tough trip.
Out with rest, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 50M.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well and settled in front of midfield on the rail, switched out rounding the Home Turn, closed off strongly.
Settled midfield on the rail, made the Home Turn awkwardly, made good progress near the rail, ran on nicely.
Showed good early speed to be prominent, sat just behind the leaders, kept on okay.
Tracked leader, under pressured at 500M, kept on and hung on for 4th.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made decent progress late, closest finish.
Ridden along early but showed no early speed, settled towards the rear, stayed on fairly.
Broke nicely and led, weakened inside 200M.
Settled midfield 2 wide, limited response when asked.
Sat last, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Settled behind the lead 2 wide, switched out to 3 wide at 700M to improve, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, hung in at the top of the Straight, then soon after held up for clearing and weakened. (See Incident Report)
Sat near the rear, never a threat (See Incident Report)
Settled in last few on rail, commenced move rounding home bend, ran on well under pressure to just get up on line.
Settled some 4L back in 5th on rail, became 4th in similar position 850 metres out, saved ground turning in for home, ran on resolutely under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
Soon took up running obtaining rails run passing the winning post the first time, attempted to make all setting a steady pace, held every chance in straight only to be pipped at post.
Settled some 3L back in 3rd in back straight, commenced move rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.

Settled in last few from a poor draw travelling keenly in back straight, dropped to second last into home straight but saved ground turning in, produced good late impression inside final 100 metres, never nearer.
Pressed forward from the widest draw reaching 2-wide 2nd onto first bend, over 2L off the pace in back straight, kept on under pressure until finding no extra 50 metres out.
Settled just worse than midfield from moderate start, switched off rail for a run entering home straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Held up at the back after beginning from a poor draw, trailed the field into home straight hugging the rail, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in midfield after moderate start, became slightly further behind passing the 700 metres, kept on at the same pace in home straight.
Travelled in 4th mainly 4L off the pace, lost position rounding home bend carried wide into straight, ran home one-paced.
Settled in rear from a poor draw, made steady headway 4-wide from 600 metres out, wideset of all into straight, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Began moderately, travelled wide without cover in midfield, very wide making home turn, soon weakened.
Jumped on terms and maintained a midfield position just over 4Ls back, let down strongly final 200M, stretched clear late for comfortable win.
From wide draw fast into stride and took up the running led by 1L on settling, kept battling away passing 300M but couldn't hold off the determined winner inside 100M.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards the rear, maintained his spot to the bend 6-7Ls off the pace, closed off nicely to go 3rd near 50M.
Restrained to a midfield position 5Ls off leader, brought wide into straight making solid inroads, got up for 4th close home.
Stalked the leader into the straight, fought hard to stay in contention from 300M, tired 150M and was overwhelmed in closing stages.
Dropped back to race towards the rear, had big task at 400M 8Ls to make up, passed a few but never likely to feature.
Jumped well from inside draw to be tracking leaders, in touch as they turned for home but couldn't go with it, weakened 200M.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up behind midfield 6Ls away , found little from 300M when it mattered.
Made some use early stages to hold a forward position just off leaders, chased fairly early straight, kept on one pace over the final 150M. Ran below expectations.
Settled down behind mid-division along the inside, couldn't quicken enough passing 300M,. Never a threat to leaders.
From wide draw switched off to race in last, lacked a kick in the straight, never a winning hope.
Began well, restrained to race ahead of midfield, failed to run on in the straight, dropped out. (Lame next day.)

Out in line, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, took the lead approaching 250M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 800M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.
Jumped well from gate 12, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, no clear run and checked approaching 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, hard ridden early in straight but only showed limited response, weakened final 150M.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide with cover slightly better than midfield, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Slow to begin, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, wider turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1200M, a length back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1200M, led by a length turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, tracked leaders on the outside, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Broke well, restrained to 5th some 3L off the pace, saved ground turning for home, quickened well under pressure to hit the front 200 metres out, hung on well.
Quickly improved to prominent position, joint 4th over 2L back 500 metres out, obtained clear run entering straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly travelling towards rear, switched 4-wide entering home straight, finished off well down the centre of the track, did best work late.
Began moderately, settled in 7th in rear of midfield on rail, obtained clear run after shifting out inside the 300 metres, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Taken well back from a poor draw, trailed the field to the 500 metres, obtained clear run on straightening, ran on steadily despite inconvenienced 150 metres out.
Amongst leaders 2-wide, taken over 1L back to 2nd rounding home bend, kept on in straight until finding no extra 150 metres out.
Restrained towards rear 3-wide from a poor draw, 4-wide without cover rounding home bend and widest into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Pressed forward from the widest draw before gradually taken back to 4L 6th in midfield, niggled along rounding home bend and into straight, kept on one pace without quickening.
Settled in last few from a wide draw, came under pressure down the centre of track after straightening, produced good late impression inside final 100 metres.
Ridden forward to take up running on the rail 950 metres out, kicked over 1L clear after straightening but soon flattered and swamped over 150 metres out.
Among leaders 3-wide early stages, taken back to 3rd remaining wide without cover rounding home bend, kept on before weakening badly inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly and soon dropped to last few, saved ground turning for home, found nothing.
Hard ridden after the start to assume the lead, responded well in the Straight, won comfortably.
Jumped well, ridden along early, tracked leader, kept on nicely for 2nd.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, switched out in the Straight, quickened very well final furlong, stayed on very well.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, responded fairly well in the early part of the Straight, run peaked final 100M, lost 3rd on the line.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Jumped slowly, settled towards the rear, made ground along the rail.
Jumped nicely, settled just behind the leaders, limited response in the Straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide, raced very freely, lay in the Straight, did ran on fairly when into the clear.
Settled midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Sat last, blundered in the Straight when crowded up badly inside 200M, eased up thereafter.
Settled in a prominent position, raced greenly and gave ground. (See Incident Report)
Settled near the rear, never a factor. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Showed customary early speed to lead easily after start. Was never headed when leading along the stand side rail all of the way to line.

Raced in midfield between runners in early stages before improving to share second place from the 400m mark. Looked a winning chance passing the 200m mark but ultimately couldn't get to the leader who won by a length.
Stumbled badly at the start before recovering & improving to second place. Was joined in second place near the 400m when 2L from the lead, finished well to be beaten just over a length.
Raced in midfield when galloping between runners throughout when one horse off the stand side rail. Was 4L from the lead entering final section before closing well to halve deficit on the line.

Steadied & raced rearward. Continued rearward when over 5L from the lead entering last section, shifted inwards passing 250m mark when making ground before closing eye-catchingly late despite drifting inwards.
Raced in midfield along the stand side rail throughout. Was 4L from the lead entering last section, effectively maintained that deficit all the way to the line.

Drifted back to race just off of midfield in early stages. Was ridden along from the 400m when 5L from lead before being held up for a clear run from the 300m to the 200m before finishing fairly thereafter, well beaten.

Drifted back to last place after the start. Was second last and hard ridden passing the 400m mark when nearly 7L from the lead before passing only one or two tiring rivals when being well beaten into midfield.
Bumped at the start before racing in midfield when closer to the center of the track. Was only 3.5L from the lead entering final section but weakened out poorly in the final 300m to be well beaten.
Drifted back to race worse than midfield when galloping in the clear nearer to the center of the track. Came under heavy pressure at half-way before weakening poorly to be well beaten.
Raced in midfield between runners for the majority. Was just under 4L from the lead entering last section but was soon beaten & weakened out poorly in concluding stages to be long second last.

Bumped at the start before racing in midfield between runners nearer to the center of the track. Was only about 3L from the lead at half-way but emptied out near 300m & weakened very poorly in final stages to finish last.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly, led last stride.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, no clear run until 200M, took the lead 50M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 50M, finished 3rd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Began smartly from gate 13, raced prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader from 600M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, passed some tired runners in the run home.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, sent forward after passing 1050M, positioned 3rd in the middle stages, 3 wide, peaked on run 300M, weakened thereafter.
Out in line, raced 3 wide in midfield, wider turning in, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on outer, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, showed no response early in straight, weakened 300M, eased thereafter.
Jumped nicely, showed good early speed and settled just behind the leaders, angled out at 250M, closed off nicely after getting balance, won cozily.
Niggled along early and led, kept on well for 2nd.
Settled in a prominent position 2 wide, held up for the majority of the Straight, ran on once into the clear. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield 2 wide, raced keenly in the middle stages, made good progress in the Straight.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, over-raced throughout, switched to 3 wide at 900M, closed off okay.
Steadied after the start and settled worse than midfield, stride forward at 1000M but was taken to 4 wide, made his run at the 700M and peaked at 350M, one pace thereafter.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, stayed on fairly well, closest finish.
Caught 3 wide no cover early, pushed forward at 900M, made heavy contact with a runner at in the early part of the Straight, limited response soon after. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Tracked leader, weakened in the Straight.
Settled last 2 wide, made minor progress in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, never a factor.
Settled midfield 3 wide, raced keenly, under pressured at 650M, weakened and faded.
Got crowded badly at the start, settled towards the rear, raced keenly, never a threat.

Began moderately settling in 6th some 4L back on the rail, travelled keenly passing 900 metres, saved ground turning for home and commenced move upon straightening, quickened well to assert authority 100 metres out, won readily.

Began moderately, recovered steadily to just over 2L back in 5th in midfield of small field, travelled keenly gaining 4th rounding home bend, fought on steadily to hit the front 200 metres out only to be outsprinted shortly afterwards.
Began well from a wide draw and soon taken just over 2L back to joint 4th, 3-wide in 5th rounding home bend, fought on late to snatch remote 3rd final strides.
Soon recovered from moderate start to close-up 2nd 2-wide, quickened to hit the front briefly 300 metres out, soon faded.
Soon took up running 3-wide, obtained rails run in front coming onto home bend, led until headed inside the final 300 metres, soon weakened.
Ridden along in first few on the rail before settling about 1L off the pace in 3rd, found nothing shortly after straightening.
Began fairly, travelled in last few on the rail, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run to the line.
Settled well back, commenced move 600 metres out on top of home bend, went wide into straight but unable to quicken to threaten.
Began well from the widest draw and gradually taken back to last few wide without cover, one of the widest at the back turning for home, made no further impression.
Found the lead as expected, held 1L advantage 300M, kept going strongly to give nothing else a chance. Won 6 of his 7 starts this season.
Jumped on terms and restrained to race in midfield, 3-4Ls to make up on leader at 400M, stayed on well to go 2nd close home, not reach winner.
Positively ridden, in 2nd place following winner into the straight, tried hard but couldn't get near, lost 2nd close home.
From draw 1 had a ground saving trip in mid-division, ran on mildly until 100M when held up for clear running. Not fully tested late. (RF tendon injury after racing.)
Jumped awkwardly, reserved behind midfield along the inside, made some ground from the 300M but wasn't charging to the line. Never dangerous.
Caught racing 3-wide in midfield, couldn't accelerate enough when driven nearing 400M, never a threat to leaders.
Chased leaders, got boxed in top of straight and held up from 400M to 300M, wilted passing mid-straight. (Bled.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled at the rear 8Ls back, maintained his position over the bend, gave limited response passing 400M. Never near to challenge.
From wide draw settled back in the field, brought wide into straight, finished the race off only fairly. Never a winning hope.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, responded fairly to pressure on straightening, never looked likely.
Jumped only fairly, held up near last 7-8Ls away, couldn't finish it off on straightening. Made no impression on debut.

Caught wide early on jumping from draw 10, pushed up to track leaders passing 1000M, gave very little in the run home, gone from 200M. (Jockey concerned action of his mount when under pressure in home straight.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, a bit closer on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide on turn, finished off strongly to take a place, no threat to the winner.

Bumped on jumping, took the early lead, 2 wide, headed 1300M, 3 wide from 800M, a length or so back in the middle stages, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail near 800M, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until 150M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Away well, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead after passing 1000M, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, no clear run early in straight, made some progress final 200M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, very wide into straight, passed some tired runners in the run home.
Taken back from gate 13, raced behind midfield on outer, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slowly away, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, no clear run early in straight, failed to make any progress thereafter.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1250M, headed 1000M, 2nd on turn, 1/2L back, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well from a wide draw, tracked leaders on the outside, no cover from 1000M, challenged the leaders on turn, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running until 200M, finished off very strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take a place, always just held.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, finished off well to make frame, not quite able to challenge.
Moderately away, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run until 150M, made some progress thereafter.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, made some progress in straight.
Taken back to race at rear on the outside, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, slightly inconvenienced 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Away with them, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
