Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly to score, won by a narrow margin.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move 400M, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame, nearest on line.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run until final 75M, finished off well without threatening.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move 450M, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 50M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail in the early stages, commenced move after passing 800M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 8, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, eased final 100M.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, unable to maintain position 450M, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Soon led, took them along slowly, had a slight advantage turning home, kept kicking to line and found enough to hold on.
Bumped at the start, stayed prominent behind leaders, poised to strike at 400M, kept closing but held by leader / winner towards the line.
Settled ahead of midfield, in 5th place ridden along 450M, did well under pressure to grab a placing, nearest at the line.
Dropped back to race in the 2nd half of the field, pushed along inside 500M, made up a lot of ground in the run home to claim 4th, nearest finish.
Prominently ridden, followed leader on outside, vied for lead 400M, no match for leader mid-straight, no extra and lost several places final stages.
From wide draw taken back, settled in the back half of the field, 6Ls to make up 400M and closed off well, still in contention for a minor placing when not able to be ridden out late.
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, under the pump 450M, kept on without threatening in the straight.

Tracked leader, handy enough turning home but wasn't able to get into the finish, weakened mid-straight. (Jockey : raced keenly early and middle stages with the race being run outside of standard time.)
Adopted a rearward position, plenty to do turning for home, failed to make any real progress.
Bumped on jumping, obtained a midfield position 4-5Ls off the pace, failed to finish off in the straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Switched off to race at the rear, couldn't keep up home turn, soon beaten.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, made good progress inside 150M, showed some dash over the concluding stages, closed off strongly.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield 2 wide, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, finished off nicely.
Sat handy, traveled smoothly, responded okay when asked in the Straight.
Settled towards rear on the rail, angled out rounding the Turn, no clear run inside 150M, ran on evenly.
Settled handy, traveled okay, crowded in the early Straight, ran on fairly.
Sat towards rear, switched out making the Turn, one pace to the line.
Sat midfield, raced wide throughout, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, but weakened inside 150M.
Settled midfield on the rail, unable to quicken in the Straight, just one pace when asked.
Sat rear, limited when asked in the Straight, no impression made.
Jumped only fairly, sat midfield 2 wide, no clear run in the Straight, could not be ridden out.
Settled in front of midfield, was checked near the 150M, could not be ridden out when crowded to the finish.
Ridden along to lead, weakened notably passing 100M (See Incident Report).
Showed speed at start, raced second away from the rail for the majority. Moved to the lead at the 200m, drew away to win by over a length carrying 2lb over-weight.

Raced in midfield away from the rail. Was slightly wide around the first bend when hanging outwards. Came wider on straightening before making good ground down the outside in late stages to steal second on line.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was just under 4L from the lead on straightening, drifted outwards mid-straight when hitting the line well to be third beaten just over a length.

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout early & middle stages. Came away from the inside on straightening, before closing well all the way to the line to be in a line of three all beaten just over a length.

Jumped fairly & then shifted across to the rail & raced second last. Raced third last along the rail from the 600m, was just under 7L from the lead entering final section before making good late ground from a long way back.
Showed customary early speed to come across from gate 9 and lead. Was joined by the winner near the 200m mark, over-run for a minor placing in final 50m & was only beaten 2L into midfield.

Bumped at the start & got back to race just worse than midfield away from the rail. Was just over 6L from the lead at 400m, shifted outwards to be the widest runner on straightening before making some late ground out wide.

Ridden along to improve position after the start before settling in third along the inside from about the 700m. Was only 2.5L from the lead entering last section, peaked on effort near the 150m, weakened a few lengths late.

Raced wide in early stages before steadying approaching the 650m bend & getting back to second last. Was over 7L from the lead entering last section, halved deficit in the run to the line but only beat one rival home.

Drifted back from the outside gate & was a clear last after the first 50m. Continued last & nearly 9L from the lead entering last section before failing to pass a rival in the straight & being beaten 7.5L on line.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 50M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Commenced well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always just held.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 50M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 350M, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on outer, no cover for the majority of the race, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress early in straight, weakened final 100M.

Made contact at start, taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer 800M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly from the widest draw, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped well and ridden along early, settled in front of midfield, ran on strongly when in the clear, won nicely.
Steadied after the start and shifted in from the outside barrier, sat last, under pressure the whole way, stayed on well for 2nd. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield 2 wide, closed off okay despite laying in. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind the leaders, only one pace when asked.
Settled midfield on the rail, made some minor progress late.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide between horses, travelled a bit ungenerous throughout, took time to respond in the Straight, made some late progress.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, made little impression.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Jumped nicely and showed good early speed to lead, weakened inside 150M.
Hard ridden early and sat outside the lead, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Caught 3 wide no cover behind midfield, never a threat.
Slightly slow out settling towards the rear, commenced move wide rounding home bend, quickened well to hit the front over 200 metres out, just held on from runner-up's strong late burst of speed.
Held up in rear and waited with, commenced move on top of home bend going very wide into straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to just fail to get up on line.

Bumped and unbalanced at start settling in midfield in 8th on rail, commenced move entering home straight, did not find much room after straightening, finished off well once into the clear inside final 200 metres.
Settled well behind from a poor draw, widest of all entering home straight, ran on well under pressure down the centre of the track and did work late.
Broke well amongst leaders early, settled some 4L back in 6th and slightly closer in 5th in back straight, switched for a run over 200 metres out to produce moderate progress closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly, restrained some 4L back in 5th or 6th , saving ground in similar position turning into home straight, kept on at the same pace under pressure without quickening.
Jumped well from the one draw, restrained 2L back in 4th into back straight, chased leaders most of the way to home straight, kept on at the one pace without quickening under pressure.

Pressed forward from a poor draw going 4-wide vying for lead around first bend, obtained rails run in front over 1150 metres out holding narrow advantage to the 300 metres, soon weakened. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped awkwardly, settled 2-wide in midfield switching wider entering home straight, found nothing.
Began fairly from the widest draw, pressed forward around first bend to join race leader into back straight, soon weakened out of contention inside final 350 metres.
Ridden positively to vie for lead early, settled for one-out-one-back position entering back straight, came to challenge turning into home straight, soon weakened. (Blood in trachea)
Crowded at start and soon dropped to last few on the rail, saved ground turning for home but soon dropped out of contention.
Away well, sat in behind the leaders, 4th at 200M, worked home strongly to get up near line.
Bumped at the start, prominently ridden, moved up to 2nd 600M, responded well on straightening and wrestled the lead nearing 200M, just failed to hold off winner late stages.
From draw 1 well into stride, shared early lead before taking a sit behind leader, fought hard to the line but no match for first two late stages. (inconvenienced near 200M.).
Jumped on terms, raced keenly in the middle stages, close up behind leaders making home turn, kept on steadily over final 300M, couldn't get closer to first few.
Jumped cleanly and moved up quickly to lead, shifted in under pressure mid-straight and got run down soon after, faded out of the placings.
Maintained a midfield position 4Ls off the lead on settling, driven wide into straight before keeping on moderately to the line, never a genuine threat.
Not hurried after the jump, settled down behind mid-division, brought wide 350M, lacked a strong response and laid in when placed under pressure. Failed to threaten.
Restrained to a rearward position, widest straightening and came home only fairly, never likely to feature.
Jumped awkwardly, recovered to settle in midfield, had 4Ls to make up 400M but didn't finish it off on straightening.
From wide draw ridden along after the start, caught wide no cover chasing leaders for the majority of the event, only battled in the straight, no extra 200M.
Given a waiting ride, 6Ls off the pace making home turn, steadied 450M, was making progress when checked near 100M, lost all chance. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back to last 8-9Ls off the pace, had job ahead on straightening, gave no response and was never in the picture.

Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, bumped near 650M, a bit closer on turn, finished off very strongly, won by a narrow margin.
Commenced well, raced in 3rd, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed very good response in straight, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, a length behind the leader, there to turn, hit the front 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, still 7 lengths behind the leader turning in, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail after passing 700M, 7 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on same pace in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, bumped near 650M, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Had a nice run in midfield along rail. Avoided the trouble at the 500m, came off the rail on straightening, bumped at 400m when improving between runners, dashed well to lead 150m, pulled away to win with something in hand.

Showed speed after the start to lead. Continued in lead until being joined by the winner near the 150m, bounded the track close to line when holding down second, over a length clear of third but no match for winner.
Got back to race worse than midfield along the rail. Had clear running on straightening, was 4L from the lead entering last section before finishing well, closing to third in final 50m.

Steadied after start & got back to race three wide with cover near the rear. Came wider to avoid incident on straightening, was 6L from lead entering last section before making eye-catching late ground to just miss third.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout early & middle stages. Was hampered & lost ground near 500m when rival horse went amiss, was nearly 6L from the lead entering last section before making eye-catching late ground.
Had a soft run on the leaders back throughout. Was in second place and only 1.5L from the lead entering final section before giving some ground in the run to the line to be well held in midfield.

Pushed forward but was caught racing three wide without cover outside the leaders. Hung out rounding the home turn, bumped with winner near the 400m when 2L from lead but weakened to midfield in straight.

Shifted behind runners after start & raced third last between rivals. Had clear running on straightening when many rivals were forced wider due to incident, was just over 4L from lead at the 400m & held that deficit to line.

Drifted back & raced at the tail after the start. Shifted wider just before 500m, shifted outwards abruptly near 500m to avoid injured rival, was over 7L from the lead at 400m, passed a couple late but was never likely.

Raced three wide with cover in midfield early. Was checked & veered outwards near the 550m, was extremely wide entering straight, shifted back inwards & bumped near 400m before weaking in last furlong. Had some excuse.

Began awkwardly & lost ground before sifting behind runners to the rail where he settled second last. Continued near the tail and was over 6L from the lead on straightening before doing little in the straight.

Raced three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Was badly hampered & taken outwards sharply near the 550m following incident, was just over 5L from the lead on straightening but weakened to be beaten over 10L on line.

Had a nice run 1,1 in early & middle stages before being hampered & checked near the 500m when rival in front went amiss. Was just under 5L from lead at 400m when still in 7th place but weakened badly, beaten a big margin.

Placing: PU
Comment: Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Went amiss near the 550m mark & dropped out quickly through the field before being dismounted at the top of the straight.
Ridden along to chase the leader on the rail, switched out rounding the turn, made good progress in the Straight, closed off strongly.
Ridden hard to lead, traveled strongly, responded well when asked, just miss.
Sat midfield, traveled smoothly, ran on evenly to the line.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, no clear run in the early Straight, slightly weakened approaching 150M.
Sat rear on the rail, traveled okay, one pace when asked.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, minor progress made in the Straight, ran on fairly.
Settled towards rear, traveled fairly, switched out rounding the turn, limited response when placed under pressure.
Sat rear, always rear, never a factor.
Settled in front of midfield, switched out rounding the turn, weakened notably inside 300M.
Sat handy, raced wide until near the 600M, weakened and faded entering the Straight, no contention.

Raced worse than midfield after the start. Was briefly held up behind runners approaching the 200m mark, got a gap and dashed strongly between runners passing the 150m before charging to lead in final few strides.

Raced in midfield, one horses away from the stand side rail. Shifted inwards passing the 400m, was held up approaching 250m mark, dashed between runners near 150m & closed strongly to the line but couldn't hold out winner.

Raced just forward of midfield when galloping close to the stand side rail. Shifted inwards near the 350m when just under 3L from lead, moved to the lead momentarily near the 150m, over-run in final stages but held third.

Raced in midfield between runners in early & middle stages. Was 5L from the lead entering final section, shifted inwards after the 250m mark before closing strongly nearer the inside of the track to be beaten only 1L on line.

Got back to race just worse than midfield after the start when nearer to center of track. Was ridden along from half-way, was over 6L from lead in final section before halving deficit when making late ground in final furlong.

Lifted feet at start & consequently lost ground before improving position in the middle stages to get to midfield between rivals. Was under a length behind at the 200m mark before peaking & then weakening in last 100m.
Raced in midfield in a bunch in early & middle stages when positioned nearer to the center of the track. Weakened a few lengths in final 150m & was beaten 4L on line.

Bumped on jumping (rider losing iron momentarily) before mustering normal early speed to improve and then share the lead from the 700m. Continued to share lead until about the 200m mark before giving ground in last 100m.

Drifted back after the start & raced third last early. Was second last from about the 600m, was 7L from the lead entering last section, shifted inwards near the 250m before running up behind runners in last 100m.

Raced in midfield along stand side rail. Was crowded & checked near 700m & again at 500m. Was just under 5L from lead at 400m before again being badly checked when having something to offer near 100m mark. Forgive run.
Raced in third place, about a length behind the leading pair in the middle stages. Was still close to the lead at the furlong mark before peaking & giving ground thereafter.

Blundered badly on jumping & then bumped heavily consequently losing ground & racing a clear last. Was last and 10L from the lead entering last section & failed to make any noteworthy head-way in final stages.

Showed customary early speed to charge across the face of the field to stand side rail when leading. Was joined in lead near 700m, peaked on effort passing furlong pole, was giving ground before being checked at the 75m mark.

Raced worse than midfield nearer to the center of the track in early stages. Was relegated back to second last near half-way, was over 8L from the lead entering last section & weakened further to finish a long last.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to score.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.

Began well from gate 1, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 450M, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened final 50M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 300M but only showed limited response, ran on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run final 100M.
Began well, raced in 3rd, right behind the leader turning in, raced tight early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 100M. (Bled.)
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, raced tight early in straight, peaked on run 300M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped nicely, settled in front of midfield, closed off nicely to score.
Jumped with the field, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, angled out at the 600M, showed good dash early in the Straight, run peaked at 100M.
Restrained after the start, settled worse than midfield on the rail, held up in the early part of the Straight, stayed on strongly to the line, nearest finish. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide no cover near midfield, ran on okay despite the tough run.
Sat midfield 2 wide between horses, made some progress in the Straight.
Raced at midfield on the rail, closed off only fairly.
Showed no early speed, settled last, under pressure for the majority of the race, stayed on okay.
Sat just behind the leaders, weakened inside 250M.
Settled in a prominent position 2 wide, weakened inside 300M.
Sat towards the rear, made no impression.
Sat outside the lead, limited response in the Straight.
Jumped well and led, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never a factor.
Broke well before settling one back in 3rd before becoming 2L off the pace over 1200 metres out, commenced move 3-wide 700 metres out and asserted authority 350 metres out, won cozily.

Pressed forward from a wide draw before settling one back in 2nd, commenced move passing the 600 metres gaining slender advantage briefly on straightening, had no more to give inside final 150 metres.

Inconvenienced at start and trailed the small field some 7L off the pace, gained closer when pace slackened rounding home bend, switched out to challenge entering straight and fought on dourly under pressure to reach 3rd late.
Soon took up running and led until headed into straight, faded gradually under pressure.
Began moderately settling in 6th some 3L off the pace, became closer when pace slackened around home bend coming within 2L of pace into straight, kept on well to the line.

Recovered steadily from moderate start to reach 4th just over 3L back 1200 metres out, joined before passed by two others coming onto home bend, came under pressure entering home straight but ran home one-paced.
Settled one from last of the small field, in last when tight between runners entering home straight, fought on steadily to do best work late over this apparently insufficient trip.

Close up early before settling just over 3L back in 4th, lost ground dropping to 5th approaching home bend while travelling wide without cover, folded up quickly shortly after straightening. (Blood in trachea)
Settled behind midfield, waited with on the inside turning home, into clear 300M, drove hard final stages to get up near line in a game effort.
Maintained a position just off leaders, worked into the race nicely passing 500M, kept battling to the line, just couldn't hold off winner in concluding stages.
Reserved behind midfield 5Ls back on settling , swung wide passing 500M, picked up well when asked, lay in under pressure final 300M, dug deep to get up for joint 3rd at the line.
Soon prominent and sat in behind leader, fought on well to hit lead 150M, tried hard late stages but was collared close home.
From draw 1 jumped on terms, maintained a midfield spot 3-4Ls off the pace, responded well early straight and looked a threat, wilted in the chase late stages.
Crossed to the lead nearing 1600M, led at good pace before slowing down the tempo middle stages, fought on under top weight early straight, headed inside 200M and had no extra late.
Soon taken across to the fence, behind midfield early before falling back to a rearward position, came with an even run from well back but never looked a winning hope.
Switched off to race at the rear, long way off the pace early stages, moved closer home turn but still had task in hand 400M, stayed on without really threatening.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, in a 3-wide position entering back straight, couldn't pick up well enough passing 400M, never reach leaders.
Away well enough, restrained to race in midfield, swung wide for home but couldn't quicken as required and was never a real threat.
Dropped back from wide draw, settled near last, bustled along 550M but couldn't muster any sort of challenge in the straight.
From draw 7 ended up racing 3-wide in midfield, widest turning into straight but offered little and was easily accounted for.
In the group chasing leaders, caught wide no cover until near 1200M then stalked the leader into straight, failed to finish the job and weakened rapidly passing 400M.
Held up 3-wide in midfield, left with no cover from 1200M, pressed leaders entering home turn, run ended 300M, dropped away to finish last.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, hard ridden after passing 350M, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 50M, just held 2nd.
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out after passing 450M, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearly snatched 2nd.

Slightly slow out, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, short of room near 150M, kept on well thereafter, no threat to the first few.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Inconvenienced start, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made good progress early in straight, no further impression final furlong.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 800M, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 800M, 2nd on turn, challenged the leader early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened gradually final 150M.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Slightly slow out and inconvenienced, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll. (Mucus.)
Began smartly from gate 12, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (Irregular heart rhythm.)

Placing: TNP
Comment: Stood in the barriers and refused to jump. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 11, raced prominently on the outside, a length back turning in, took the lead approaching 250M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.

Commenced well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover in the middle stages, 4 wide turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide towards rear, there to turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened final 50M.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, easy run on turn, no clear run early in straight, found daylight near 250M, peaked 200M, weakened inside final furlong.
Began smartly from the widest draw, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Out with rest, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed approaching 250M, weakened final furlong. (Irregular heart rhythm.) (See Racing Incidents.)

Horse Name: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Jockey: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Comment: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, took the lead 250M, headed 100M, kept on well to win narrowly in a ding-dong battle.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out 500M, showed good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Made contact shortly after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.

Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle in the early stages, sent forward after passing 1250M, took the lead 1100M, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened final 100M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move 700M, 3 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Made contact at start, raced prominently on the outside early, raced in 3rd after entering the back straight, 1/2L back on turn, peaked 300M, weakened inside final furlong.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 1100M, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Blood in trachea.)
Broke well to lead on rails setting a sedate pace to make all, hung on well under pressure.
Restrained behind steady pacemaker eventual winner, unable to quicken to pose real threat throughout final stretch.
Settled in 3rd becoming 4th rounding home bend, in similar position into straight, unable to quicken to challenge.
Travelled keenly in 2L 4th in the slowly-run early to middle stages, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend but never able to quicken to threaten.
Soon taken back to rear of small field and waited with, made steady progress under pressure in home straight but never threatening.
Travelled keenly behind midfield in 6th, commenced move gaining 5th rounding home bend, one-paced in straight.
Settled in 5th on rail within 4L of pace, became 6th rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Always well behind and never seen with a chance. (Lame next day)
Ridden along to lead, traveled comfortably, kept on well to win.
Slow to begin, settled rear, commenced to improve approaching 900M, angled out rounding the Turn, made good ground, closed off strongly.
Settled midfield 2 wide, was held up rounding the Turn and in the early Straight, showed some dash over the concluding stages.
Sat handy on the rail, traveled smoothly, responded okay when asked, closed off nicely.
Settled behind midfield, switched out rounding the Turn, one pace to the line.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Chased the leader 2 wide, traveled fairly, weakened inside 300M.
Settled midfield on the rail, traveled one pace, limited response when asked.
Settled handy 2 wide, weakened inside 200M, no impression made.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, switched out inside 500M, weakened notably near 150M.
Sat towards rear, yielded ground steadily entering the Straight, never a factor.
Sat towards rear, very limited response when asked, faded in the Straight, no contention.
Sat handy, raced wide throughout, dropped back and faded quickly after 400M.
Settled worse than midfield, never traveled (Unacceptable performance, Must BT).

Crowded at start & then raced at the rear. Moved wider at the 550m, was the widest runner on straightening when 5.5L from lead before closing off very strongly down the middle of the track to charge to lead inside last 50m.

Had a nice run in third in the clear throughout. Moved up to take lead early in the straight, raced a couple of lengths clear at the 200m mark before being charged down by the winner inside the last 50m.

Raced in midfield along the rail. Was just over 3L from the lead on straightening, had clear running in the straight before closing off well to move to third near the 100m & hold that placing on line.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Came wider passing the 500m & wider again on straightening when 3.5L from the lead before closing off steadily all the way to the line to finish 4th.

Led soon after the start before being headed near the 1250m mark & then racing on the leaders back thereafter. Continued not far from the lead on straightening before only battling onto midfield in the straight.

Pushed forward from widest gate, raced wide out of straight the first time before improving to lead near 1250m & crossing to rail soon after. Joined & headed by the runner-up early in straight, only battled to midfield late.
Raced just worse than midfield in early stages before improving to midfield when racing a touch wide but with cover approaching half-way. Straightened 5.5L from the lead, only battled to line.

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Was ridden along before straightening, was just over 2L from the lead entering last section, stayed near the rail in straight but weakened to be beaten over 5L.

Drifted back after the start to race last. Continued rearward approaching turn, shifted back towards rail near the 500m, was making steady ground before being cut out for room near 250m but then finished only one paced.

Jumped awkwardly, shifted back to race worse than midfield between runners. Came wider approaching corner, was held up between runners near the 400m when over 6L from lead but made no headway to line (blood in trachea).

Drifted back after start & raced second last early. Shifted wider & commenced mid-race move around runners to get forward of midfield from the 650m. Bumped at 400m before Was beaten off on straightening, weakened in last 300m.

Raced in fourth place away from the rail in the early & middle stages. Raced tight with rival passing the 500m, was only 2.5L from the lead on straightening but did nothing in the lane, weakening poorly to be well beaten.

Ridden along after start to get position in midfield away from the rail. Was shuffled slightly further back after the 700m mark, began losing further ground passing 500m mark before weakening badly to be long second last.

Ridden along after the start but couldn't hold position & raced worse than midfield along the rail in middle stages. Came under hard ridding passing 700m, yielded ground & was last from 550m, weakened badly to distant last.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the outside, 3 lengths or so back turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on very strongly to the line, won by 2 lengths.
Away with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight, snatched 3rd close home. (See Racing Incidents.)

Made contact shortly after start, unable to slot in, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, closer on turn, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, no threat to the first few.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced prominently on the outside, took the lead 650M, headed 400M, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced behind midfield on the outside, carried wider 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M.
Bumped on the hindquarters on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 650M, retook the lead near 400M, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final 150M.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped a bit slow, settled last, switched out rounding the Home Turn, stayed on strongly to score, won going away.
Settled behind the leader, hit the front at 150M, kept on but can't hold off the winner.
Settled midfield on the rail, had trouble obtaining clear running in the Straight, ran on nicely when in the clear. (abrasion to the right front leg)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, closed off only fairly.
Showed very good early speed to lead, kept on until weakened quickly at the 150M.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Jumped awkwardly, caught 3 wide no cover in front of midfield throughout, weakened in the Straight.
Settled towards the rear, made some progress along the rail.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no impression. (lame left front leg)
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, limited response when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield 3 wide, never a threat.
Sat on pace 2 wide, under pressured at 500M, weakened and faded in the Straight. (Performance disappointing, must trial)
Began well from a low draw settling within striking distance in 4th or 5th, hit the front under pressure just inside the 200 metres.
Settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning for home, did not find much room over 200 metres out, improved well between runners to reach 2nd late but never able to threaten the winner.

Niggled along after moderate start before settling in 9th behind midfield, made further headway rounding home bend reaching joint 7th 4-wide into straight, sustained progress under pressure but never threatening.
Amongst leaders, taken back to 3rd coming onto home bend, remained 2-wide sharing lead into straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Taken back to last few from a wide draw, switched out off heels for a run over 300 metres out, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Jumped awkwardly from the widest draw, gradually recovered to take up running 800 metres out and rails run shortly after, led until joined into straight, weakened under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Ridden along in last few after moderate start before settling in 10th on the rail, did not find much room early in straight, produced some late impression closing stages.
Settled 3-wide without cover in 6th in forward of midfield, gained closer rounding home bend and 3-wide in 5th into straight, kept on before fading under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Settled just worse than midfield wide without cover, inconvenienced approaching first bend, one of the widest entering home straight, one-paced under pressure.
Travelled in 5th within 4L of pace early stages, hung and lost considerable ground rounding home bend inside the 700 metres, never recovered.
Soon dropped well behind despite ridden along, never seen with a chance.
Ridden to lead early, ceded advantage passing the 800 metres for one-back position on rails rounding home bend, baulked for a run entering straight, soon weakened. (Blood in trachea)
Reserved behind mid-division, had a ground saving trip, switched out into clear 300M then finished off determinedly to win going away in the end.
Settled in 2nd half of the field about 6-7Ls off the pace, held up for clear running 500-400M before closing off strongly to get up for 2nd near line.
Took up running from 1500M, travelled well to the home turn, kept on nicely and still had 2Ls lead inside 200M, caught by first 2 final stages.
Jumped only fairly and then was crowded, raced at the rear 8-9Ls off the pace, held up on home turn along the fence, ran on steadily to go 4th close home.
Stalked the pace on inside, poised to strike at 400M, came with an even run, held 2nd until inside 150M, faded to 5th close home.
From wide draw positively ridden to chase leader, tried hard to stay in contention passing 400M, no extra final 150M.
Chased leaders, raced keenly in early stages and lay out, not far off the pace home turn, battled on one paced over final 400M, well held by leaders.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, given a waiting ride near the rear, made limited progress final 400M and unable to trouble leaders.
Held up in mid-division, shifted out 500M to continue, responded fairly passing 400M and wasn't able to get into the finish.
Caught racing 3-wide towards the rear early stages, dropped back to last passing 650M, had many lengths to make up top of straight but failed to pick up.
Jumped on terms from draw 1, maintained a midfield position along the fence, came under pressure 600M, soon beaten on straightening.
Crowded at the start, gradually moved up to chase leaders, caught wide no cover for the majority of event, struggled to keep up 500M, finished tailed out on the 2nd consecutive occasion.
From wide draw chased leaders early, caught wide no cover until 700M then dropped back to midfield, gave ground rapidly 400M, finished tailed out. Unacceptable Performance.

Placing: FE
Comment: Jumped awkwardly, settled down 3-wide in midfield, driven along 550M, fell 450M. (Lame RF and RH legs.)

Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide after passing 1300M, commenced move 600M, very wide turning in, hit the front 250M, kept on very strongly to the line, easily scored.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away with them, raced in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Slow to begin, raced at tail, 11 lengths back in the middle stages, still 8 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight to make frame.

Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, hard ridden after passing 800M, closer on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened inside final furlong.

Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened 250M, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, peaked 500M, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened 300M, eased final furlong.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled at the back of the field, checked near 300M, rebalanced and picked up sharply final 200M, arrived just in time for maiden win.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, restrained in mid-division, wide into straight, closed off well to claim 2nd in a photo.
From draw 11 settled 3-wide just ahead of midfield, no cover in middle stages, responded well to lead 200M, caught by first 2 closing stages. (Jockey had been asked to hold a more forward position.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, at rear entering home turn, wide into straight and picked up nicely in the run home to get 4th.
Settled behind midfield, 5-6Ls off the pace home turn, stayed on to get pretty close in the end. (Jockey: his mount hung in and proved difficult to ride out.)
Tracked leaders along the 2-path, hit lead briefly 300M, fought hard to the line, faded late and lost several places close home.
Jumped on fairly, waited with in a rearward position, steadied 300M to avoid a rival who had gone amiss, made ground late but not enough.
Bumped on jumping, maintained a position just ahead of midfield, responded fairly early straight, couldn't go on with it passing 200M and was outsprinted.
Driven forward to be racing outside the leader, joined by rivals early straight, weakened from 300M and gave way.
Positively ridden, led from 1200M, held a slender lead early straight, caught 300M and faded away.
Settled ahead of midfield, held up along the inside after 400M and didn't obtain clear running until 150M, failed to pick up over the final stages.
Pressed forward, up with early pace before taking a sit behind leaders, fought hard to stay in contention early straight but run ended near 200M, weakened rapidly.
Raced in midfield early stages before dropping back to near the rear, pushed along 500M, badly checked near 300M and eased.

Placing: UR
Comment: Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield, shifted out 300M to obtain clear running but struck heels of rival and dislodged rider.
Ridden hard to lead 2 wide, traveled nicely, kept on well to win.
Chased the lead on the rail, made some ground entering the Home Straight, slightly weakened over the concluding stages, closed off nicely.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, made some progress over the final 200M, just missed 2nd.
Settled towards rear on the rail, responded nicely when asked inside 100M, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear 2 wide, angled out rounding the Turn, made some progress in the early Straight.
Settled towards rear, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, ran on okay.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, traveled fairly, one pace to the line.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide throughout, minor progress made in the Straight, closed off fairly.
Chased the lead 2 wide, raced keenly in the early stages, no impression made in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly, settled rear, limited response when place under pressure.
Sat midfield 3 wide, crowded and steadied passing the 50M, weakened thereafter (Lost right front plate).
Settled in front of midfield, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Sat midfield 2 wide, weakened and faded quickly passing 200M.
Sat behind midfield, traveled fairly in the early stages, did not respond when asked.
Had an economical run in midfield between runners. Was 3L from the lead on straightening, shifted outwards soon after before closing well to take the lead inside the final 50m to win.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Improved to be only about 2L from the lead on straightening, dashed up to take narrow lead near the 150m, caught by winner inside last 50m.

Slow to begin before racing worse than midfield along the rail. Was held up for clear running on straightening when about 5L behind, held up again 150m, veered outwards sharply at 100m before closing well to steal third late.

Led early before being crossed & racing on the leaders back from about the 900m. Stayed near the inside on straight, closed off steadily along the rail before being caught for third place in final strides.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was under 2L from the lead entering last section, raced tight between runners from 250m until inside last 75m but was finishing only fairly to line.
Pushed forward, galloped close to the lead when racing outside the leader for the majority. Moved to lead near the 350m mark, joined by the runner-up near the 150m, battled on to be beaten only 2L.

Drifted back & raced near the tail throughout. Moved into three wide line passing 700m, continued rearward & 5.5L from the lead entering final section, made up a few lengths when running into midfield but was never a threat.

Raced on leaders back early before a pair further back from the 900m. Came off the rail on straightening, under 3L from lead entering last section, didn't have much room between rivals in final furlong but was only fair late.

Drifted back after the start to race near the tail. Shifted wider passing the 500m mark, shared last place on straightening when nearly 7L from the lead, made some late ground when running on out wide without threatening.

Had no speed despite being ridden at the start & got back to race at the rear. Continued rearward, forced very wide passing the 500m, was last and 7L from the lead on straightening, passed only a few tiring rivals late.

Began awkwardly & lost a few lengths at start before improving along rail to race in midfield. Was 4.5L from lead entering last section, was finishing off only steadily, held up passing 200m, only moderate in final 100m.

Raced just worse than midfield between runners in the early stages. Drifted further back after the 900m mark, was ridden along passing the 700m, was third last on straightening before making no headway & being well held.

Steadied in the first furlong & got back to race worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Continued wide around bend, was wider again from 550m, was just over 4L from the lead on straightening but weakened further.

Pushed forward from gate 13, continued to improve to take the lead passing the 1100m and then crossing to the rail near the 900m. Was headed in the lead passing the 350m before weakening quickly in last furlong to be last.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, very wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 500M, took the lead 300M, headed 150M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress in the run home.

Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 900M, 3rd on turn, angled out 500M, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 300M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 850M, 2nd on turn, challenged the leader early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened final furlong.

Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, a bit closer on turn, 2 wide from 500M, no clear run early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead near 850M, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, no clear run 350M to 250M, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Reared leaving stalls and started very slowly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, showed no early speed, raced at tail, detached from 1000M , virtually pulled up. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped nicely, settled behind the leaders, hit the front at 250M and kept on nicely to the line.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide with cover, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Jumped with the field, settled behind midfield on the rail, stayed on okay, no threat to top 2.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, took some time to respond, closed off fairly.
Broke well and quickly assumed the lead, kept on until weakened inside 150M.
Settled towards the rear, made some progress in the Straight.
Raced behind the pace, limited response in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, one pace when asked.
Settled near the rear 3 wide, showed some dash early in the Straight, soon one pace.
Sat outside the lead, weakened inside 200M.
Jumped slowly, settled at the rear, raced greenly and never tested. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 3 wide no cover, weakened in the Straight.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Sat last, never in contention.

Jumped fairly settling over 3L back in 4th, slightly closer when pace slackened rounding home bend switching 3-wide into straight, loomed up to hold every chance 200 metres out eventually asserted authority 50 metres out.

Ridden forward before settling one back on rail in 3rd, obtained run shortly after the 400 metres, quickened under pressure to hold every chance inside final 200 metres only to be overshadowed 50 metres out.
Jumped best to lead attempting to make all, found no extra inside final 200 metres and overhauled.
Settled in last few from a poor draw, commenced move shortly after straightening and ran on steadily under pressure down the centre of the track for remote 4th.
Soon recovered to midfield along the rail from awkward start, improved further to over 3L 6th onto home bend, obtained clear passage passing the 350 metres, ran home one-paced.
Niggled along in mid-division of strung-out field, snuck up on rails rounding home bend reaching joint 5th into straight, unable to sustain inside final 150 metres.
Soon taken well behind from a poor draw, baulked for a run in home straight until the 150 metres, made modest progress closing stages.
Settled well behind from a poor draw, widest runner into home straight, produced moderate progress down the centre of the track.
Settled at the back and waited with, made good ground between 250 and 50 metres, made no further impression thereafter.
Settled in mid-division of strung-out field, travelled 3-wide around home bend and in similar position into straight, found nothing.
Began fairly settling 3-wide without cover in 5th within 3L of pace, slightly wider into home straight, ran home one-paced.
Soon taken back from the widest draw settling in rear of midfield in 9th wide without cover, baulked for a run in straight until the 200 metres, one-paced in the run to the line.
Settled towards rear, obtained rails run 600 metres out, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Driven forward from a poor draw to vie for lead, settled for 2nd just outside race leader passing the 1000 metres, dropped quickly out of contention inside final 350 metres.
Soon led after a good start, took them along slowly before quickening up the pace 450M, kept on strongly to line gave nothing else a chance.
Maintained a midfield position 4Ls off the lead on settling, quickened well to go 2nd 300M out, fought hard final 200M but couldn't get closer to winner.
Held up behind midfield, caught wide no cover after 850M, worked into the race well 500M, kept battling over final 300m but couldn't reach winner.
Settled in 4th spot always In touch, held up for clear running after 350M, stuck on well over final 200M for a creditable 4th against higher rated rivals.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, raced keenly early stages, kept on steadily passing 400M but couldn't get closer to first few.
Failed to show early pace, raced keenly in 2nd half of the field further back than intended, no clear run until passing 250M, passed a few late and never looked like winning. (Lame next day.)
Slow to begin, recovered to race behind midfield, shifted away from fence 500M, disappointed for running mid-straight before closing off well final stages. Could do better.
Chased leader on outside, urged along passing 350M but couldn't finish well enough, weakened over final 200M.
Began only fairly, not bustled, settled in mid-division further back than intended, failed to improve on straightening.
Jumped only fairly, soon taken back to the last spot from a wide draw, had plenty to do top of straight, failed to finish the job.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled near last racing keenly early and middle stages, had a lot of ground to make up 400M but gave very little, never a factor.
Jumped awkwardly, urged along to be tracking leader, out-finished from 250M, steadied 100M when giving ground.
From draw 1 obtained a position ahead of midfield, couldn't quicken passing 400M, dropped away to finish last. (Jockey reported his horse made a respiratory noise during race.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly, won by a narrow margin.
Away well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1150M, 2nd on turn, took the lead 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.

Began well, raced prominently early, slightly taken back after passing 1100M, raced 2 wide better than midfield in the middle stages, commenced move 450M, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide on turn, no clear run early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1150M, led by 1-1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run 200M to 50M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Away with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, hung left and hampered entering final furlong, soon weakened. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover in the middle stages, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the outside early, raced in 3rd in the middle stages, 2 wide, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, hampered shortly after passing 200M, eased final 150M.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 8 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, commenced move 500M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, closed off well to take a place, always just held.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, commenced move 700M, 3 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the inside, there to turn, unable to obtain clear run in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made some progress in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Bumped on jumping, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 1/2L back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped only fairly, raced towards rear, 6 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced better than midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (Bled.)
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, angled out 500M, 6 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced at rear on the inside, hampered by loose horse near 1100M, still well back on turn, made no impression in straight.

Placing: UR
Comment: Stumbled and unseated rider soon after start.
