Made contact shortly after start, raced in 3rd, 1-1/2L back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, hard ridden 450M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Moderately away, raced in 2nd, travelled well to turn, took the lead near 400M, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two late.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest finish.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground to turn, no clear run early in straight, raced tight near 200M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home without threatening.
Away well, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began well from gate 11, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, a bit closer on turn, raced tight early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 450M, 4 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, headed near 400M, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Got back to second last from widest gate before improving position in middle stage when galloping three wide. Was the second widest on straightening before dashing to the lead near the 75m mark, held off late challenger.

Drifted back to race at the tail. Shifted wider passing the 450m, was last and the widest runner on straightening before closing strongly down the outside to charge to a fast finishing second, just beaten on line.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Came off the rail passing the 500m, closed off well all the way to the line to move to third in the final 50m & was only beaten half a length on line.

Raced in midfield away from the rail for the majority. Eased three wide passing the 500m, dashed well & hung inwards but took the lead momentarily near 150m before being over-run in concluding stages.

Drifted back to race just worse than midfield between runners. Was third last approaching corner, held up near momentarily 200m when galloping between runners, came to the outside & made up a length late (blood in trachea).
Pushed forward as normal, raced outside the leader early before being crossed near the 700m & racing a length from lead. Took lead momentarily near 200m, over-run in final 100m.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was only just behind leaders passing 200m, finished off only moderately in last 100m.
Raced on the leaders back early before a pair further back from the 750m. Was held up on straightening when continuing along rail, got clear near 175m, finished off fairly late.

Bumped heavily soon after the start before being hard ridden to improve, was three wide outside leaders before improving to lead near 850m and then crossing to rail passing 700m. Was headed early in straight & weakened out.
Bumped heavily soon after the start & lost ground before shifting behind runners to the rail & racing rearward. Was last on straightening, shifted outwards passing 250m, did little in last furlong.
Took the lead early before being headed near the 850m & then racing on the leaders back from about the 700m. Stayed near the inside on straightening but did little & was well beaten.

Raced just forward of midfield when three wide before improving to be three wide outside the leaders from the 500m. Peaked on run early in the straight before weakening out to last after a wide trip throughout.
Jumped nicely, settled midfield 2 wide, angled out at the Turn, responded well when asked, closed off strongly.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards rear, made good progress over the final 150M, finished off nicely.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, traveled smoothly, stayed on okay for 3rd.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide throughout, ran on evenly.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, slightly steadied rounding the Turn, closed off okay.
Shared the lead throughout, weakened entering the Straight, one pace thereafter.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, slightly held up in the early Straight, weakened notably inside 150M (Substantial blood in horse's trachea).
Settled towards rear, traveled fairly, limited response when asked (Rider concerned horse's action, See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, very minor progress made in the Straight, never a factor.
Shared the lead throughout, weakened and faded in the early Straight, no impression.
Sat midfield on the rail, never responded despite ridden along, no contention.

Placing: UR
Comment: Clipped heels at 1000M, blundered and dislodged rider (Racing Manners Unacceptable, must trial) (Blood In Trachea)

Raced in midfield along the rail for the majority. Shifted away from the inside on straightening, shifted back inwards mid-straight when making ground before sticking head out in final stride to steal lead right on the line.
Pushed forward to lead. Was joined at the 150m but dug deep all the way to the line & was only caught in final stride to be beaten a head.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Moved up to share the lead at the 150m, looked the winner & tried hard all the way to only be beaten a narrow margin into third on line.
Raced on the leaders back for the majority. Stayed along the rail in the straight, closed well all the way to the line to be beaten only a half length.

Pushed forward from gate 10 and raced in second place from the 700m when at the leaders flanks. Continued close to the lead all the way to the line and was only beaten 0.75L on the line in a bunched finish.

Drifted back after start, raced a clear last from the 750m. Was over 6L from lead entering last section, was bumped on straightening when shifting wider into clear running before making some late ground down the outside late.

Bumped at the start before being steadied & racing three wide in midfield. Continued wide around bend, was 3L from lead entering last section before closing off steadily all the way to be beaten 2.25L into midfield.
Slightly crowded after the start & raced just worse than midfield along the rail. Continued rearward on straightening, made up a length when passing only one or two tiring rivals to line.

Steadied & taken back from outside draw to race rearward. Moved wider after the 500m, was hampered when bumped between runners near the 400m when shifting wider, only battled to the line in final stages.
Raced between runners in midfield but raced tended to over-race in middle stages when becoming keen. Was 3.5L from the lead entering last section, had clear running but weakened to be third last.

Wasn't fast away, positioned worse than midfield between runners before racing keenly in the middle stages & steadying off heels near the 600m. Continued keen when shifting out & bumping near 500m, did little in straight.

Bumped & then crowded at the start & got back to race rearward when three wide with cover. Forced wider after the 500m, was bumped multiple times & taken very wide on cornering before weakening sharply in last 200m. Last.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, hard ridden approaching 200M, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 450M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Away well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, challenged the leader approaching 400M, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the inside, moved a little bit closer 700M, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Jumped well, sat right behind the leader on the inside, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began well, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Commenced well, raced behind midfield on the inside, 7 lengths back, 2 wide from 700M, 6 lengths back on turn, angled out 350M, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, produced good late finish but had too much to do.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 700M, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, showed no response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Out with rest, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with the field, raced keenly early, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely to score on the line.
Broke well and ridden along to be on the lead, kept on well, just got caught on the line.
Settled just behind the leaders, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Jumped slow, settled towards the rear, held up early in the Straight, angled out and stayed on. (See Incident Report)
Steadied after the start, sat last, swung wide into the Straight, made good late progress.
Jumped okay, settled worse than midfield 2 wide, only one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Tracked leader, limited response in the Straight.
Settled behind the pace 2 wide, made no impression.
Settled midfield 3 wide no cover, raced ungenerously throughout, made no ground.
Settled midfield on the rail, never a threat.
Settled towards the rear, never in contention. (See Incident Report) (Racing Manners Unacceptable, must trial around a bend in HK)

Placing: TNP
Comment: (See Incident Report)
Settled in midfield on rails or slightly worse, commenced move rounding home bend going 4-wide into straight, quickened well to duel with runner-up only to prevail by a narrow margin.

Settled 2L back in 2nd early stages, raced keenly briefly when 4th in similar position early into back straight, angled out for a run holding every chance inside final 200 metres only to be denied by a small margin.
Slowly away and lacked pace despite ridden along, detached from the main body of the field until the 300 metres, finished off the race strongly down the apparent fast strip of the track.

Gradually settled wide in last few, gained slightly closer approaching home bend and further closer by saving ground into straight, quickening under pressure when baulked 150 metres out, made no further impression.
Ridden along in first few before settling some 3L back in 5th passing the 900 metres, carried wide into home straight, made moderate progress without threatening.
Prominent early stages before dropping gradually to one from last, came under pressure from the 700 metres, did not find much room between runners in home straight but fought on to the line.
Soon dropped to last few despite niggling along on rails, saved ground turning for home and quickened well upon straightening, unable to sustain effort inside final 50 metres.
Travelled wide in rear from a poor draw, ridden forward to 8th passing the 950 metres, remained 3-wide into straight, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Settled wide in midfield, lost ground for going wider into straight, made no further impression.
Soon took up running from the one draw setting a smart pace, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Pressed forward from a wide draw to travel just outside race leader from the 900 metres, dropped quickly out of contention shortly after straightening.
Pressed forward from the widest draw reaching 3rd 3-wide early in back straight, gained 2nd briefly coming onto home bend, drifted very wide into straight and never recovered. (Tactic questioned)
From wide draw settled close up in 4th, responded strongly under top weight, led nearing 100M and extended to win comfortably.
Sped to the front, led uncontested setting steady pace in middle stages, kept on well turning for home but no match for winner final 150M, held on for 2nd.
Settled behind midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, found the line well to claim 3rd near line.
Dropped back to race towards the rear, driven along 500M, ran on nicely down the outside, just missed 3rd.
Settled in 5th spot never far off leaders, briefly went 3rd mid-straight, caught by pursuers late.
Bumped on jumping, settled ahead of midfield, came with an even run but never looked a winning hope.
From draw 1 obtained a midfield position along the fence, lacked the dash to launch a serious bid. No threat to leaders.
Crowded after the start, chased leaders, gave nothing when asked 400M and fell back through the field. (Jockey - raced flat.)
Held up behind midfield, driven along 450M but couldn't master any sort of challenge in the straight.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, raced near last and failed to finish off. (Jockey concerned with his mount's action when it was racing on the wrong lead leg early stages.)
Raced ungenerously after 1000M, was a long way last at the turn, made no impression on his Happy Valley debut. (Jockey : raced greenly throughout the race.)
Settled just off the pace, under pressure to maintain its position from halfway, faded out in the straight to finish last.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the outside, 3-1/2L back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross 850M, 2 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd.

Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, 3 wide after entering the back straight, commenced move approaching 400M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.

Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 1100M, moved closer after entering the back straight, took the lead 550M, led by 1L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened close home.

Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the outside early, moved closer after passing 1000M, shared lead from 900M, headed 550M, a length back turning in, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer after passing 1000M, 2 wide turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 1000M, wider turning in, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made no progress early in straight, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival from 850M, headed 550M, peaked 400M, weakened final 250M.
Slowly away, raced better than midfield on the inside, unable to maintain position 500M, weakened thereafter, eased final furlong, unacceptable performance.

Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Jumped only fairly, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest finish.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off well to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced prominently but 3 wide, 2 wide from 700M, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the outside, 6-1/2L back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Blundered on jumping, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Shifted out at start, positioned 1-3/4L behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (Blood in trachea.)
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, found rail 700M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened 250M, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled some 2L off the pace near on stands rails, came to challenge under pressure inside the 300 metres, responded well to hit the front 50 metres out.
Settled behind midfield within 3L of pace, baulked 300 metres out, finished off the race strongly inside final 150 metres to snatch 2nd near the line.
Well there settling one back on the stands rails, came to challenge under pressure inside final 300 metres, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled not far off the pace mainly in 5th, quickened passing the 400 metres to hit the front shortly after, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 50 metres.
Broke well settling some 2L off the pace, obtained clear passage over 200 metres out, ran on without threatening.
Settled some 2L off the pace, tight between runners 300 metres out, fought on steadily without threatening.
Ridden from the one draw to lead obtaining stand rails run 600 metres out, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 200 metres.
Began moderately and bumped, soon dropped to last few, came under pressure onto course proper, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in midfield some 3L off the pace near the centre of the track, kept on same pace without threatening.
Gradually settled at the back, tailed off approaching course proper, ran on well under pressure past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Soon dropped to last few down the centre of the track, came under pressure from the 300 metres, found nothing.
Close up, gave ground steadily inside final 250 metres.
Close up, gave ground from the 300 metres, beaten when checked 200 metres out.
Began moderately soon dropped to last few, never seen with a chance. (Mucus in trachea)
Slow to jump, settled rear on the rail, traveled strongly, was slightly held up in the early Straight, responded well over the final 100M, finished off nicely.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, traveled comfortably, made good progress inside 150M.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, traveled one pace, closed off okay.
Ridden hard to lead, traveled okay, slightly weakened inside 200M, ran on evenly.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, traveled fairly, minor progress made in the Straight.
Slow to begin, settled towards rear, limited response when asked.
Sat in front of midfield, was steadied entering the Straight, weakened over the final 150M.
Sat handy, traveled okay, eased passing the 200M (Rider concerned his mount's action, See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, angled out rounding the Turn, failed to respond when placed under pressure (See Incident Report).
Sat midfield, raced wide throughout, weakened and faded in the Straight.

Prominent after start, raced wide before improving to take the lead near the 950m and then crossing to rail soon after. Raced a couple of lengths clear of nearest rival half-way down the straight & went on to win by 0.75L.

Raced three wide in midfield and was then left in that position without cover from about the 900m. Moved closer to the lead approaching corner, was 2.5L from lead at the 400m before making late closing ground for second.

Bumped at start & then caught racing four wide without cover in midfield throughout. Wide on straightening, 3.5L from the lead entering last section before making continual steady ground down the outside to steal third late.

Drifted back after the start & raced three wide with cover worse than midfield. Was then four wide with cover from 700m, was 5L from lead on straightening when the widest runner before making good late ground from the back.

Bumped at start before ridden along to improve to midfield. Steadied & shifted outwards passing 750m to avoid rival, was 3.5L from lead on straightening before making up a length or so when finishing steadily between runners.

Raced prominently after the start before settling third away from the rail around first bend. Moved up to the leaders' quarters from the 700m, only 1L from lead entering last section but gave a few lengths late to midfield.

Raced in midfield in the three wide line with cover but did have a runner on his outside in middle stages. Came wider passing 600m, was just under 3L from lead entering last section but found little, weakening to midfield.

Raced 1,1 early before racing keenly near the 900m & steadying off heels. Was 3L from the lead on straightening, shifted back inwards & stayed near the rail in straight, gave a length to line (substantial blood in trachea).

Got back after the start & raced third last between runners. Shifted wider on the track passing 700m, was hard ridden before straightening, was 5L from lead entering last section, finished off only one paced (Bled).

Got back to race worse than midfield along the rail. Was third last when coming off the rail near the 650m to avoid rival, was just under 6L from lead on straightening, finished only one paced, no threat (mucus in trachea).

Improved to the lead after first 100m when wide, crossed to rail near the 1100m before being headed & racing on the leaders back near 850m. Just over a length from the lead on straightening but weakened to finish rearward.

Bumped at the start before getting back to race at the tail. Continued rearward, came wider on the track from the 600m, was 6.5L from the lead entering last section, did little in the straight, finishing towards the rear.

Bumped at the start before getting back from wide gate to race at the tail. Taken wider on the track from 600m, very wide on straightening when nearly 7L from lead, weakened poorly in the straight & was beaten a big margin.

Raced in a prominent position along the rail early before drifting back to midfield from the 850m. Hung outwards around bend before dropping back through the field quickly from the 750m & was eased out of the race by rider.
Began fairly, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover from 1300M, commenced move 600M, hit the front 200M, kept on well to hold off the challenger.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, finished off well to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 13 lengths back, still 8 to 9 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Made contact at start, raced in 3rd, 5 lengths or so back, moved closer on turn, made some progress early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly and made contact, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, made some progress early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Mucus.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped well, sat handy, ran on strongly to the line, always doing enough.
Broke nicely, settled midfield on the stands' rail, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Settled at the rear, switched in towards midfield, stayed on well.
Settled midfield 4 from the stands' rail, kept on nicely.
Crowded at the start, settled towards the rear near the stands' side, had some trouble finding clear running, ran on once in the clear.
Settled worse than midfield one off the stands' rail, made good progress.
Settled at the rear 3 off the stands' side, only one pace when asked.
Settled in front of midfield one off the stands' rail, hampered near 250M, never fully tested.
Jumped well and led on the stands' rail, weakened inside 250M. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield two off the stands' side, limited response final two furlongs.
Showed good early speed to share lead, weakened inside 300M.
Settled near the rear 2 off the stands' side, never impress.
Broke nicely and raced prominent near the middle of the track, weakened and faded at 350M
Sat at the rear, never in contention.

Settled just off the pace obtaining rails run about 1400 metres out pulling hard in the slackened tempo approaching and rounding home bend, quickened to assert authority inside the 200 metres, won cosily.

Broke well settling just outside race leader, came to dispute lead from the 800 metres eventually hitting the front under pressure about 250 metres out but only to be swamped by the winner shortly after.

Settled in 7th some 6L off the pace from moderate start, came under pressure 700 metres out and given reminders passing the 500 metres, ran on well down the inside of the straight to be nearest at finish.

Soon recovered to 5th within 4L of pace after moderate start, gained steadily closer to pace rounding home bend, baulked early in straight and checked over 200 metres out, fought on dourly to the line.

Broke well from a low draw before settling in midfield, pulled hard in 3L 5th between the 1300 and 1000 metres, came to challenge under pressure entering home straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, soon ridden forward to take up running, joined by eventual runner-up approaching home turn near the 500 metres and narrowly headed over 250 metres out, swamped 100 metres out.
Settled well back from slow start, last and one of the widest into straight, made modest progress past well-beaten horses in the run to the line.

Broke well from the widest draw but soon taken well behind travelling keenly throughout back straight, made no impression in home straight from wide in last few turning in. (Questioned for disappointing performance)

Began well from a wide draw before restraining one-out-one-back in 4th and travelling keenly at about the 1000 metres, made short-lived effort entering home straight but unable to sustain effort inside 250 metres.
Jumped on terms, held a position behind midfield, responded well to pressure passing 400M, led inside 150M and drove hard late to just get the verdict from the fast finishing 2nd.
Settled behind midfield along the inside, had to switch out for clear running early straight, picked up in great style passing 200M, worked home well to be just denied.
Switched off to race at the rear on jumping, had difficulty obtaining clear running from 400M-200M before working home hard under top weight to claim 3rd.
Jumped in line and maintained a midfield position along the 3-path, pushed along 550M, came home well under pressure and briefly went 2nd inside 100M, edged out to 4th near line.
Caught wide early, moved up to 2nd before home turn, loomed large top of the straight, responded well to lead 200M before giving way to first few in closing stages.
Up with early pace before taken back to race in midfield, worked home steadily from 400M, run ended 100M and faded towards the line.
Settled down in midfield, had ground saving trip along inside but was badly held up for clear running from 350M until 100M. Got out too late.
Jumped well to be tracking the early pace before settling back in midfield home turn, badly held up for clear running from 400M-50M. Luckless.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, 6-7Ls to make up 400M, worked home steadily without seriously threatening.
Stalked the lead in 3rd, came with an even effort early straight, couldn't go on passing 150M and weakened out of contention.
Dropped back to race towards the rear, no closer than 3-wide throughout, had plenty to make up 400M and was just fair through the run home.
Jumped awkwardly, in midfield early stages before improving to 4th at 800M, loomed a threat top of straight, in contention until 150M then lost momentum inside 100M when steadied.
Slow to begin and settled at the rear, no change in position making home turn, had the job ahead top of the straight and couldn't make any headway.
Bumped at the start, sent forward to lead setting a good pace to straight, hard driven to hold lead passing 400M, was gone after 200M and weakened right away.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on strongly to the line.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.

Began well from a wide draw, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 100M, finished off strongly to make frame.

Slowly away and made contact, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, found rail after passing 800M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually close home.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover, slightly better than midfield, 2 wide on turn, angled out 450M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider 500M, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight, made contact near 100M.

Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide after passing 600M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, showed some response early in straight, made contact 100M, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced prominently on the outside, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final 100M.
Crowded shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.

Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, no cover from 800M, carried wider 500M, hard ridden from 350M but only showed limited response, weakened inside final furlong, short of room and snatched up 125M.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, no clear run in straight, not able to be properly tested. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped well from a wide draw, tracked leaders on the outside, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened 300M, eased final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1-1/2L back turning in, made little progress in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 4 wide behind midfield, no cover from 700M, 3-1/2L back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield early, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Jumped with them, trapped very wide in midfield, taken back after passing 750M, showed no response 500M, weakened and eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began smartly, raced in midfield on the inside, 3-1/2L back, saved ground on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front near 150M, kept on very well to the line.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 700M, made contact near 550M, 6 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide from 700M, bumped near 550M, slightly improved on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run 200M to 100M, finished off well to make frame.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, kept on same pace to the line.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, led by 2 lengths turning in, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.

Began fairly from a wide draw, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, difficult to settle in the early stages, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, raced towards rear on the outside, found rail approaching 800M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made no impression in straight.
Blundered shortly after the start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 600M, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 700M, carried wider 600M, peaked on turn, weakened final furlong.
Crowded start, raced in midfield on the outside early, sent forward after passing 1250M, raced in 2nd after passing 1100M, weakened from 500M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Led without having to be pressured, took them along steadily, urged 450M and kept responding in the run home, just held on from pursuers in a busy finish.
Settled down midfield, laid in 300M resulting in its rider having to take corrective measure, finished off the race well and was just held by a short head in a blanket finish.
Restrained behind mid-division, pressed along 500M, stuck to task well to get 3rd in a photo finish.
Stalked leader on settling, no change in position entering final turn, fought hard from 300M trying to get past leader, edged out to 4th last stride in a desperately close finish.
Dropped back and raced towards the rear, 8Ls off leader in middle stages, moved closer home turn before staying on well to claim 5th, narrowly beaten in a busy finish.
Tracked leader on outside, poised to strike 300M, fought on evenly to the 100M before weakening.
Restrained in 4th spot, never far off from leaders but battled on one paced in the straight, out of contention passing 150M.
Jumped awkwardly, raced in mid-division, lacked a response when driven along top of straight, soon outstayed by rivals.
Shifted across from wide draw, held up in last 10Ls off on settling, wide into straight before closing off only fairly, never a winning hope.
Slow to begin, settled near last early stages, taken wide 800M and covered more ground than rivals, failed to run on in the straight. (Jockey questioned regarding his riding tactics.)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, traveled smoothly, made some progress over the final 200M, closed off nicely.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, commenced to improve from 400M, stayed on well to grab 2nd.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, traveled okay, nearest to the line.
Settled towards rear on the rail, traveled okay, closed off fairly.
Jumped only fairly, settled midfield, slightly steadied entering the Straight, made minor progress over the concluding stages.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled fairly, ran on evenly.
Sat midfield on the rail, traveled okay, could not be quickened over the concluding stages.
Ridden along to sit handy, raced wide, one pace throughout.
Sat towards rear, traveled fairly, very limited when asked.
Jumped fairly, settled worse than midfield 2 wide, weakened rounding the Turn, no impression made (See Incident Report).
Ridden hard to lead, (Lost right hind plate, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Chased the lead throughout, weakened notably from 550M, faded gradually entering the Straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 600M, a length back turning in, retook the lead 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to take a place.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide from 500M, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out 350M, finished off evenly.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced towards rear on the outside, 8 lengths back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.

Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 600M, led by a length turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Clean jump, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, hit the front 200M, kept on well to hold off the challengers.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail approaching 500M, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame, always held.
Commenced well, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, very wide into straight, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made good progress early in straight, no clear run inside final 100M.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 350M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced behind midfield on outer, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced at rear on the inside, still 9 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped nicely, settled in front of midfield on the rail, ran on strongly to score.
Broke alertly, ridden along early to be prominent, sat just behind the leader on the rail, kept on for 2nd.
Caught 3 wide no cover near midfield, closed off okay despite the tough trip.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, angled out rounding the Home Turn before switching back in, stayed on reasonably well.
Settled close to the pace 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Showed good early speed to lead, kept on nicely until weakened final 75M.
Jumped with the field, settled midfield on the rail, made little progress.
Settled at the rear on the rail, made no impression.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Sat last, never a threat.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, no response in the Straight.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, never in contention.
Vied for early lead before settling one back around first bend, became 3rd 650 metres out, commenced move entering home straight and hit the front despite hanging over 200 metres out, won readily.
Took up running on the rail coming onto first bend, led until headed passing the 800 metres, just held on under pressure for 2nd.from strong late challenges.
Settled in last few after moderate start from a wide draw, came under pressure inside the 700 metres going 3-wide around home bend, ran on to narrowly miss 2nd.
Soon taken across for rails run in last few, commenced move under pressure rounding home bend, ran on to narrowly miss a placing.
Pressed forward from the widest draw travelling 3-wide without cover, came under pressure when some 2L back in 4th rounding home bend, went wider into straight and ran home one-paced.

Soon taken back to midfield travelling 3-wide without cover in 6th, became 7th in similar position passing the 800 metres, very wide rounding home bend and into straight, fought on nicely to be nearest at finish.
Settled in 5th within 3L of pace, became 6th in similar position inside the 600 metres, kept on same pace without quickening in home straight.
Very slowly away, tailed off to home straight, saved ground making home turn, ran past well-beaten horses.
Never better than midfield, commenced move rounding home bend and wide into straight, found nothing under pressure.
Restrained in worse than midfield 3-wide without cover, made swift headway passing 800 metres to take up running 550 metres out, led until finding no extra 200 metres out.
Broke well taken some 2L back with rails run, became 5th when pace quickened around home bend, saved ground turning in, weakened under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Jumped fairly settling in midfield on rail, came under pressure from the 600 metres, saved ground turning for home, soon faded after straightening.
Jumped well then restrained to race behind the lead, worked into the race well and loomed at the 250M, delivered a strong challenge to get up last stride. Determined victory.
Emerged as leader passing 900M, held narrow lead on straightening, fought hard when challenged by eventual winner final 150M, just beaten in a photo.
Began well and maintained position just off the lead on settling, stuck to task well passing 300M, couldn't go with first 2 near 150M but kept trying right to the line. Good effort.
Not hurried after the start, reserved behind midfield 5Ls away, worked home solidly from 300M to claim 4th. Nearest finish.
Taken back from wide draw and settled at the tail of the field 7Ls away, stayed on final 300M but failed to trouble leaders.
Jumped on terms, settled ahead of midfield along the fence, poised to strike turning home and was only fair to the line.
Bumped shortly after the start, held up 2-wide in midfield, battled on fairly passing 300M. Not reach leaders.
Fractious in stalls and began awkwardly, settled behind midfield along the inside, failed to finish off leaving the bend. (Jockey: hung in in the home straight and proved difficult to ride out.)
From draw 10 ended up racing wide no cover behind leading trio, couldn't go on passing 300M, soon no threat.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M but lacked the dash under 135lb, failed to finish off. (Jockey : not suited by the pace being run outside of standard time.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled at the back 7Ls off the pace, had the job ahead passing 400M but couldn't muster any sort of challenge in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly, ended up racing 3-wide in midfield, came under pressure home turn and faded out in the straight. (Jockey : didn't appreciate racing around Happy Valley circuit.)
Away with them, raced 2 to 3 wide slightly behind midfield, found rail near 850M, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.
Out with rest, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, angled out 400M, finished off well to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move 400M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place on line.
Began well from the widest draw, raced prominently on the outside, a length back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened gradually close home.
Began awkwardly from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 500M, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress in straight, no clear run and snatched up close home.
Jumped well, raced in 3rd, 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 800M, moved closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased inside final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, trapped very wide in midfield, moved a bit closer after passing 750M, hung out from 550M, very wide turning in, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Jumped awkwardly, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest finish.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, 3 lengths back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made little progress in straight.
Crowded start, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently on the outside, 3/4L back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, one-paced in straight.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, raced towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Had a nice run on the leaders back for the majority. Was held up along the rail behind the leader for the first half of the straight, switched over heels at the 150m mark before charging to take lead in final three strides.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Moved up to take lead near the 150m, looked the winner before being run down in the final few strides.
Drifted back after the start & raced a clear second last. Was over 5L from the lead entering last section, stayed nearer the rail in the straight & closed well to charge to fast finishing third late.
Pushed forward to lead. Headed by the runner-up near the 150m mark, gave a few lengths in late stages but still held 4th on line.

Raced in midfield along the rail. Had clear running on straightening when moving off rail, was just over 3L from the lead entering last section, finished off steadily to be beaten a similar margin into midfield.

Crowded & lost ground after the start before shifting down to rail & improving to midfield. Stayed along rail on straightening when over 4L from lead, moved to 4th near the 250m but finished only moderately in last furlong.

Drifted back after start & raced third last in the clear. Travelled strongly near 600m when continuing rearward, shifted inwards on straightening when 6L behind, was making ground before being checked near 50m mark, ok late.

Raced in midfield away from the rail & was then between runners around the bend. Had clear running on straightening when just under 5L from lead, finished off only fairly to the line to be beaten a similar margin.
Had a nice run 1,1 in the middle stages. Was ridden along before straightening, was 3.5L from the lead entering last section, peaked on effort mid-straight & gave a few lengths thereafter.
Was trapped racing three wide, but with cover in midfield throughout. Eased wider just before straightening, was 5L from the lead entering last section but did little, weakening to be beaten over 7L.
Taken back from wide gate & raced a clear last after the start. Moved four wide with cover near the 600m, was last & the widest runner on straightening when over 7L behind, made no headway.

Raced just worse than midfield between runners in the early & middle stages. Clipped a heel, dipped & lost ground near the 700m, shifted outwards & bumped heavily on straightening, weakened badly in straight.

Raced three wide with cover when worse than midfield before drifting further back after the 1000m. Was then four wide no cover from about the 550m, was bumped heavily on straightening but then weakened very poorly thereafter.

Pushed forward but was left racing three wide outside the leaders early before coming a pair further back after the 1000m mark. Began losing ground before straightening & weakened badly, distant last (irregular heart rhythm).
Ridden along to lead, traveled smoothly, made some progress, kept on nicely.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, showed some dash over the final 200M (See Incident Report).
Settled handy 2 wide, traveled nicely, nearest finish.
Sat midfield 2 wide, traveled okay, responded nicely when asked inside 100M.
Settled midfield on the rail, lay out slightly over the concluding stages, ran on evenly.
Sat in front of midfield, slightly weakened passing 150M, closed off okay.
Sat rear, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, closed off fairly.
Sat worse than midfield, hung out making the Turn, limited response when asked (Racing Manners Unacceptable, Bled, Must BT).
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, slightly weakened passing 200M.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear 2 wide, minor progress made in the Straight.
Settled midfield, raced wide throughout, never a threat.
Sat midfield, making the Turn wide, never a danger.
Settled worse than midfield, blundered and was steadied passing 1000M, dropped back thereafter.
Sat rear 2 wide, always rear, no contention.

Had a nice run on the leaders back from the 850m. Was held up for clear running in the heels of the leader from the 400m, dashed through between runners passing the 150m mark, charged to lead at 100m & went on to win stylishly.

Had a nice run 1,1 in the middle stages. Had clear running on straightening when only 1.25L from lead, dashed up to be within half a length at 150m, tried hard but couldn't match winner late, narrowly held second.

Had no early speed & was ridden to hold position third last. Was galloping between runners near corner, was badly held up for clear running from on straightening until shifting inwards at 250m & then flying home late.

Was trapped very wide in midfield before being used up to improve & race three wide outside the leaders from the 800m. Moved up to share lead at 350m, was passed by winner at 100m mark, battled bravely to hold fourth.

Blundered on jumping & lost ground & then raced worse than midfield along the rail. Came away from the rail near the 400m mark when just over 3L from the lead, finished steadily in final stages to finish in midfield.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail throughout. Was held up for clear running from the 400m until the 350m before finishing off only moderately in the concluding stages to finish midfield.
Raced three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Was only 1.5L from the lead entering last section, continued close to the lead until peaking near the 150m, weakening a length or two late.

Ridden forward at the start, worked hard to get to lead near the 1000m before crossing to the rail near the 850m. Was joined & headed passing the 350m mark, weakened in last furlong to be beaten over 5L into midfield.

Began only fairly & was then shifted across behind runners from wide gate & raced at the rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening when continuing second last, passed a couple of tiring rivals late but was never a chance.

Raced three deep with cover in midfield for the majority before becoming a touch keen in the middle stages. Was just over 3L from the lead entering last section, battled on until the furlong mark, gave ground thereafter.

Bumped on jumping, raced in midfield away from the rail before being steadied away from heels near 950m when racing keenly. Continued between runners around bend, was 3L behind on straightening but weakened in last furlong.

Steadied after the start & taken back to race at the tail. Came wider on the track from the 500m, was last & nearly 6L from the lead on straightening, did nothing in the run to the line & was well beaten.

Raced wide in midfield early before shifting outwards away from rival runner near the 900m & then drifting further back around bend. Was third last entering last section when 4.5L from lead but did nothing in straight.
Ridden forward at start, shared lead momentarily before racing second away from the rail. Was beaten on straightening before weakening very badly in the final section to finish a distant last.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, a length or so back, there to turn, hit the front 350M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, closed off well to take 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, angled out 450M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 650M, 4-1/2L back turning in, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter to make frame.
Taken back from gate 13, raced towards rear on the outside, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, no threat to the first few.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, hard ridden after passing 600M, 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until final 100M, made no impression thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, peaked and headed 350M, weakened final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, no cover on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well, showed good early speed to lead, kept on nicely to score.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, settled last, switched out in the Straight, stayed on fairly.
Sat towards the rear, navigated through traffic early in the Straight, showed some dash from 300M to 100M, but run peaked soon final 75M.
Broke nicely, settled in front of midfield 3 wide no cover, kept on only fairly.
Sat box seat, only one pace when asked.
Tracked leader, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, made little progress in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, had trouble finding clear running, never seriously tested.
Sat one pace 2 wide, weakened in the Straight.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression
Caught 4 wide no cover near midfield, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield 3 wide, never a threat.

Began moderately but soon picked up to 2L 4th, gained closer off the rail when pace slackened rounding home bend, quickened well under pressure inside final 150 metres to snatch victory final strides.
Began well from a wide draw holding narrow advantage until joined approaching final turn, fought on dourly the length of home straight but winner too good.

Broke well but gradually settling just over 2L back in 5th, gained closer 3-wide in slackened pace passing the 800 metres to join the leaders 600 metres out holding slender advantage briefly on straightening, winner too strong.
Soon taken back towards rear travelling 3-wide without cover, gained slightly closer rounding home bend and one of the widest into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled wide in midfield in 7th, commenced move approaching home turn reaching 5th over 300 metres out, made no further impression thereafter.
Settled in 6th near mid-division on rail, in similar position into home straight, fought on steadily to the line.
Never better than midfield, crowded and lost position 900 metres out, kept on well to the line.
Badly crowded at start, recovered under pressure to just worse than midfield on rail in 9th or 10th, saved ground turning for home but could only keep on at the same pace inside final 150 metres.
Settled in last few, kept on at the same pace in home straight.
Pressed forward from the widest draw travelling 3-wide with leaders, 2-wide sharing the pace rounding home bend, gave ground noticeably inside final 300 metres.
Soon dropped well back and never seen with a chance.
Soon dropped to last few and never seen with a chance.
Ridden forward to prominent 3rd on rail, carried backward and lost about a length dropping to 5th over 700 metres out, weakened out of contention inside final 300 metres.
Broke well, ridden along but soon dropped to last few, wide rounding home bend and widest into straight, found nothing.

Restrained to race behind leaders, 4th entering home turn, quickened up smoothly to lead 300M, pressed by the odds on favourite passing 200M, kept finding and maintained the advantage. First two drew 8Ls clear.
Held up near last in a 6 runner race, finished off strongly from 400M, pushed winner all the way to the line. Spaced the rest.
Raced keenly early stages, allowed to stride forward and lead, headed near 300M and soon left behind by first 2, finished distant 3rd beaten 8.5L.
Crowded after the start, settled in 3rd, outsprinted passing 400M, well beaten.
Jumped only fairly, held up at the rear but not far off from leader going into final 400M, failed to pick up under pressure.
Tracked leader, gave ground rapidly passing 350M. (Roarer.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 125M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide approaching 650M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, tracked leaders on the inside, angled out 550M, took the lead 300M, headed near 125M, kept on same pace to take a place.
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, there to turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 300M, kept on evenly to 50M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, raced tight approaching 200M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide towards rear early, found rail near 1100M, moved closer along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter, nearest finish.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start, tracked leaders, 2 wide, carried wider 550M, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, commenced move 550M, 4 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield on the outside, commenced move 600M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened 300M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 800M, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, shifted out 900M, a bit closer turning in, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began well from a wide draw, tracked leaders, 3 wide, no cover for the majority of the race, took the lead 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival from 600M, peaked and headed near 350M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly and made contact, taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, wider turning in, made some progress in straight.
Started slowly, raced in midfield on the inside, made contact near 850M, 2 wide turning in, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, challenged the leader from 600M, took the lead 350M, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final 100M.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the outside, carried wider 900M, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, checked and made contact near 850M, angled out 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.

Drifted back to race just worse than midfield away from the rail. Was over 3L from the lead on straightening, shifted wider at the 300m before closing strongly to take lead at the 50m mark & win well.

Drifted back to race third last away from the rail. Came wider on the track passing the 600m, continued rearward and over 4L from the lead entering last section before strong late ground down the outside to steal second late.

Raced in midfield away from the rail. Moved wider on the track near the 700m & then forced very wide from the 600m. Was the widest on straightening when only 2.5L from lead, moved to lead near 200m, collared in final 50m.

Raced just forward of midfield, was checked near the 1100m before racing three wide without cover thereafter. Continued wide around bend, dashed well to take lead momentarily near 225m, battled bravely to finish fourth.

Raced in midfield between rivals in the middle stages & was slightly keen around bend. Eased wider passing the 650m, was just under 2L from the lead entering last section, finished steadily all the way to the line.
Crowded soon after start and got back to race forth from last along the rail. Continued rearward on straightening, made continual steady ground to be beaten under 2L in eye-catching debut.

Raced in midfield away from the rail before shifting down to the rail near the 1000m mark. Came off the rail again near the 600m, finished off steadily between runners all the way to the line to be beaten just over 2L.

Drifted back after the start to share last place. Continued last & over 6L from the lead on straightening, came wider on the track before finishing making late ground to halve deficit when finishing midfield.

Had no early speed before improving along the rail to race in midfield. Was badly held up along the rail for majority of straight, shifted outwards at the 150m to get clear, finished ok in dying stages but had clear excuse.
Had a nice run 1,1 throughout the middle stages. Didn't have much room in the first half of the straight before weakening in last furlong.
Had a soft run in third on the rail for the majority. Battled on until the furlong mark before weakening late.
Pushed forward after start, raced outside leader for the majority. Was beaten approaching the 200m mark & weakened out late.
Showed customary early speed to lead from gate 12. Was headed in the lead passing the 250m mark & weakened badly in late stages.
Taken back to share last place after beginning from widest gate. Was over 5L from the lead on straightening but did nothing in the straight & weakened to be beaten 9L when finishing last.
