Shifted out at start and bumped, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off very strongly to score.

Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 50M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped with them, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, kept on well early in straight, took the lead 100M, peaked and headed 50M, weakened gradually close home.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, made minor progress early in straight, not enough room near 175M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 200M, cleared 100M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced in 3rd, 2 lengths behind the leader, saved ground throughout, kept on same pace in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began well from the widest draw, trapped very wide in midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, blocked approaching 100M, eased thereafter.
Settled well back after moderate start, commenced move passing the 500 metres and widest into straight, ran on well down the centre of the track to just get up on line.
Amongst leaders early stages, gained half a length advantage into back straight and set a steady tempo, kicked 2L clear under pressure after straightening only to be caught final strides.

Prominent without cover early before taken back to 7th in midfield 2-wide onto first bend, travelled keenly in slightly worse position in back straight, renewed effort 4-wide rounding home bend, ran on steadily.
Settled at the back from a poor draw, commenced move on rail rounding home bend, ran on steadily in straight without threatening.
Settled well back, commenced move 3-wide over 550 metres out, second last into straight, ran on well under pressure down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Close up early before settling one back on rail in 4th or 3rd travelling keenly early in back straight, gained 2nd briefly after home turn but soon weakened.
Settled in forward of midfield on rail travelling keenly early in back straight in 5th, shifted out for a run entering home straight, found nothing under pressure.
Sluggish at start settling behind midfield on rail, saved ground on the inside turning for home, baulked for a run until the 200 metres, made no further impression.
Amongst leaders after beginning from a wide draw, before settling one-out-one-back in 4th, came under pressure rounding home bend, found nothing in straight.
Used early pressing forward from the widest draw to join race leader rounding first bend, travelled keenly early in back straight, dropped quickly out of contention after home turn.
Broke well before taken back to midfield, inconvenienced onto first bend and lost position and steadied again passing the 1100 metres, bumped and lost balance 550 metres out and never recovered.
Close up early before settling over 3L back in 5th, became 6th in similar position passing the 900 metres, came under pressure rounding home bend and soon weakened after straightening. (Bled)
Ridden along to lead, traveled smoothly, show some dash over the final 100M, closed off nicely.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, made good progress inside 200M, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, commenced to improve passing 900M, finished off strongly.
Sat handy, traveled okay, slightly weakened in the Straight, ran on evenly.
Settled midfield on the rail, weakened entering the Straight, ran on fairly (See Incident Report).
Sat midfield, traveled fairly, one pace to the line (See Incident Report).
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, switched outrounding the Turn, minor progress made over the concluding stages.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, limited response when asked.
Settled in front of midfield, raced wide, weakened passing 100M.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, raced rear throughout, no contention (Performance unacceptable, Must BT, See Incident Report).

Ridden after the start before obtaining position 1,1 in middle stages. Only a couple of lengths from lead on straightening, closed strongly in late stages to charge to lead in final 50m to score overdue win.
Pushed forward before improving to race at the leaders quarters from the 900m. Moved up to take lead at 150m before being over-run by winner in final 50m.

Raced in midfield away from the rail, was contacted at the 700m with rider reporting saddle shifted. Was just under 4L from lead on straightening, following winner, was eventually shifted outwards before closing well late.
Had a soft run on the leaders back for the majority. Stayed nearer the inside on straightening, finished off steadily to be beaten under 2L.

Improved after first corner to race in midfield on rail. Became keen & had to be steadied off heels near the 800m when continuing along rail. Was just under 5L from lead at 400m, made a few late lengths without threatening.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening when about 2.5L from the lead, finished only evenly, maintaining margin in the last section when finishing midfield.
Jumped awkwardly & then shifted behind runners to the rail & raced third last. Was over 6L from the lead entering last section, made some ground when finishing off to finish midfield from the back.

Drifted back after first bend to race worse than midfield away from rail. Was 5.5L from lead entering last section, came wider on straightening, made up a few lengths relative to lead but couldn't improve placing in straight.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined & headed by the runner-up near the 150m mark before weakening a few lengths late.
Slow to begin & was then shifted back from widest gate to race second last away from the rail. Was over 7L from the lead entering last section, failed to improve in straight & was well beaten.
Steadied from second widest gate & taken back to last. Was about 9L from the lead entering last section, failed to improve in straight & was well beaten last.
Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score by a head.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out approaching 350M, finished off strongly, just beaten by a head.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off well to make frame, always just held.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Away well, raced in 2nd, a length or so back, same position on turn, kept on well in straight, checked close home.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Away with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, showed some response early in straight, no clear run final 150M.
Shifted out at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Slow to begin, ended up racing at the rear, under the pump 450M, ran on fairly without troubling leaders.
Reared and missed break, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Broke well and showed good early speed to lead, kicked clear top of the Straight and ran on.
Sat prominent, 3 wide no cover the trip, kept on nicely for 2nd.
Settled just behind the pace, closed off okay for 3rd.
Settled at the rear on the rail, made some late progress.
Caught 3 wide midfield, raced greenly in the Straight, showed some dash late. (See Incident Report)
Tracked leader, unable to quicken in the Straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide, raced ungenerously throughout, limited response when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled towards the rear, made no impression.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no ground.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Settled at the rear 2 wide, never involved.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Performance disappointing, must trial)

Travelled 4-wide in midfield early stages, made steady headway around runners from 800 metres to join race leader entering home straight, gained upper hand over 200 metres out and just held on to the line.
Settled in midfield on rail, angled out for a run 400 metres out, ran on steadily under pressure down the centre of straight to just fail to get up on line.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, dropped to last few despite ridden along, gained 8th 800 metres out, saved ground on the inside turning for home, fought on dourly under pressure despite bumped over 100 metres out.
Soon taken well back from a wide draw and waited with, came to challenge upon straightening obtaining a tight run over 100 metres out but never threatening.
Began well from a poor draw gradually settling wide in last few, came under pressure rounding home bend and one of the widest into straight, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in last few, very wide rounding home bend and wider into straight, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start, travelled about 2L off the pace in 4th or 5th, inconvenienced and lost position 550 metres out, kept on at the same pace from wide into straight.
Ridden positively to take up running 2-wide, obtained rails run in lead over 800 metres out, led until finding no extra over 200 metres out.

Lost considerable ground at start, soon recovered to rear of field by 1000M bend, snuck up on rail turning for home coming within 2L of pace early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 80 metres.
Ridden to be up with the pace early, settled for one back position in 3rd early in back straight, in similar position in 4th on rail making home bend, swamped under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Moderate start, pulled forward to 2L 4th briefly early stages, drifted backward to midfield 7th about 700 metres out, wide without cover rounding final bend and wider into straight, soon weakened.
Well there to 400 metres, gradually weakened.
Broke alertly and swiftly crossed to the fence, sat back from 800M and tracked leaders entering home turn, sprinted quickly early straight to an emphatic win.
Jumped with them, maintained a position in midfield, made nice inroads in the home run to take 2nd close home, not reach winner.
Away well, stalked leaders in 4th on settling, fought hard to the line but couldn't get closer to winner.
Jumped only fairly, restrained to race in a rearward position, had job ahead on straightening, stayed on well to go 4th near line.
Tracked the pace early before moving up to take lead 650M, headed inside 300M, maintained 2nd until closing stages, swamped before line.
Jumped on terms, raced in mid-division along the 2-path, steadied 600M and got shuffled back, worked home moderately over final 300M, safely held by leaders.
Commenced only fairly, maintained a position behind midfield 4-5Ls off the lead, came with an even effort final 300M and never a serious threat. (Lame next day.)
Held up in midfield 3Ls off the pace, saved ground on inside, failed to run on in the straight.
Raced keenly, 3-wide and no cover early stages, allowed to stride forward to race outside leader, commenced to give ground passing 250M.weakened away.
Jumped fairly from a wide draw then shifted across behind runners, last turning for home, closed off fairly from 300M, struck heels of rival near 50M and blundered badly.
Slow to begin, raced towards the rear, under the pump home turn, soon left behind by rivals passing 300M and out of contention.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 800M, 3/4L back turning in, took the lead 200M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 2 wide on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 700M, 2 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 800M, wider on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the outside, moved closer after entering the back straight, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide after passing 800M, 3 wide on turn, made no impression in straight.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, angled out 500M, 3 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 550M, finished off well to take a place.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line. (Lost right front plate.)
Bumped on jumping, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 500M, unable to obtain clear run until approaching 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Bumped start, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on same pace to the line.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 550M, very wide into straight, made no impression in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, raced tight early in straight, peaked approaching 200M, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider 550M, peaked 450M, weakened final furlong.
From wide draw moved up to sit just behind the leading trio, loomed large top of the straight, quickened up smartly to lead inside 200M, kept on well final stages for a promising debut win.
Away well, not bustled and held his position in midfield, worked into the race nicely from 400M, ran on well enough to claim 2nd, nearest finish.
Settled towards the rear, 6Ls to make up top of straight, responded well and fought hard to the line only beaten by two newcomers.
Moved up to track the lead on outside, lay in under pressure in the home straight, peaked on run 200M and just held ground.
Began well, restrained to race in midfield, fought hard passing 400M, wasn't up to it and always held by leaders.
Jumped on terms, soon led and crossed to the fence before home turn, under full pressure from 300M, caught by rival inside 200M before fading away.
Urged along to hold a prominent position behind the lead, battled on one paced passing 400M, had difficulty obtaining clear running from 200M to 50M but already no threat to leaders.
Jumped only fairly and then blundered, adopted a rearward position along the fence, over 8Ls to make up 400M, ran past beaten horses only.
From wide draw caught racing raced wide no cover in a rearward position, had the job ahead passing 400M but couldn't muster any sort of challenge in the straight.
Bumped at the start, maintained a midfield position 4Ls back on settling, couldn't finish it off in the straight.
Settled behind midfield along the fence 5-6Ls back, lacked a finishing response passing 400M. (Jockey : his mount not comfortable racing inside other horses.)
Jumped awkwardly from wide draw, raced in last 8-9Ls off the pace, had some ground to make up 400M but failed to respond. (Jockey could offer no explanation for the disappointing run / Roarer.)
Jumped awkwardly, sat worse than midfield, switched out to the center of the track entering the Straight, made good progress over the final 75M.
Settled midfield, traveled smoothly, no clear run until 200M, closed off nicely.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, responded well when asked passing 250M, stayed on well to grab 3rd.
Ridden hard to sit handy, slightly weakened in the early Straight, picked up again passing 200M, ran on evenly.
Ridden along to lead on the rail, weakened entering the Straight, ran on fairly to the line.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, traveled fairly, responded okay when asked.
Chased the leader, weakened passing the 200M, one pace thereafter (See Incident Report).
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, traveled fairly, minor progress made in the Straight.
Sat towards rear, lay in in the Straight, weakened and faded gradually.
Sat rear, switched out rounding the Turn, no impression made.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, gave ground when asked, never a danger.
Sat worse than midfield, could not be ridden out, never a threat.
Settled in front of midfield, raced wide, weakened notably near the 250M (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear on the rail, no contention.
Had a nice run on the leaders back. Was held up momentarily at the top of the straight, improved between runners at furlong marker, moved to lead at 150m, went on to win with something in hand.
Steadied & taken back to race at the tail. Eased wider approaching corner, was 5.5L from the lead entering last section, made good late ground down the outside to move to second at the 75m.

Steadied from outside gate & taken back to race second last away from rail. Eased wider passing the 550m, was the widest on straightening when over 5L from lead, made good late ground down the outside to move to third late.

Taken back to race 4th last away from the rail. Moved into the three wide line with cover near the 750m when pace steadied, was 4L from the lead entering last section before making steady ground despite racing greenly to finish 4th.
Got a nice position 1,1 throughout. Had clear running on straightening when 3L from lead, raced a little tight between runners approaching 100m and battled on to maintain margin to line.
Ridden forward at the start to lead before crossing to rail approaching the 900m. Continued in lead until being joined by winner approaching the 150m, gave a few length in final stages.

Was slow to begin before improving along the rail to race in midfield after first furlong. Steadied away from heels near the 750m when pace steadied. Stayed near rail entering last section when just over 3L from lead, held margin.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Was held up on straightening when 4L from the lead & galloping between runners, shifted outwards over heels at 200m to get clear running, finished fairly late.

Was slow to begin before racing third last along the rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening when about 4.5L from lead, momentarily held up near 350m, could only hold margin in final stages & was never a threat.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Continued in second passing the 250m mark but peaked soon after & weakened poorly in last furlong.
Raced three wide in midfield before improving after the 750m mark & racing three deep outside the leaders. Emptied near the 300m & stopped quickly in final 150m.
Raced three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Was 3.5L from the lead on straightening, did zero in the straight, weakening to a well beaten last.
Made contact shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, a bit closer on turn, 2 wide turning in, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, always held.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.

Taken back from the widest draw, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on the outside, 2 wide from 800M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from gate 10, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back turning in, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from 1200M, allowed rival to cross near 750M, angled out 600M, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 550M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, no clear run until 200M, failed to make any progress thereafter.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, angled out 600M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, trapped wide in midfield, sent forward 1150M, raced in 2nd on turn, weakened from 500M.
Jumped awkwardly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, crowded near 450M, weakened early in straight. (Distressed.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, dropped to midfield on turn, severely checked near 450M, eased early in straight.
Jumped nicely, settled in a prominent position 3 wide with cover, closed off nicely to score, won comfortably.
Jumped well but was taken back from the wide barrier, settled towards the rear, stayed on well.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, made good progress early in the Straight, run peaked final 100M.
Settled midfield 2 wide, closed off fairly between horses.
Caught 3 wide up in the speed, kept on quite okay despite the tough run. (See Incident Report)
Sat at the rear, made some late ground.
Settled last on the rail, angled out in the Straight, ran on okay.
Broke a step slow, hard ridden early but showed no early speed, sat worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Showed good early speed to sit on pace, weakened final 150M.
Jumped with the field, ridden aggressively for the lead, found the front at 900M, kept on fairly until weakened final furlong.
Sat just behind the leader, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Disappointing Performance, must trial)
Settle midfield on the rail, never a threat.
Broke well from a poor draw, travelled wide without cover in prominent positions, quickened to hit the front over 200 metres out and soon drew clear.
Began well from a wide draw settling 3-wide with cover in midfield, widest around home bend and into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Began well from the widest draw, remained wide without cover most of the way despite taken back towards rear, ran on steadily inside final 250 metres.
Settled well behind and waited with, steadied for a run 200 metres out, finished off the race well.
Trailed the field most of the way to the 700 metres, gained closer rounding home bend, fought on steadily between runners without threatening.
Broke well from a middle draw, shared pace 3-wide early stages and 2-wide just outside race leader rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 200 metres. (Lame next day)
Began moderately and ridden forward to lead 900 metres out, held narrow lead to the 300 metres and weakened under pressure.
Broke well from a poor draw settling about 2L off the pace in 5th, travelled keenly and steadied and lost position about 700 metres out, gave ground under pressure in straight.
Gradually improved to midfield along the rail after moderate start, saved ground turning for home coming to within 3L of pace, faded inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly from the one draw and soon picked up to close up 4th on rail, taken over 1L back onto home bend, gradually faded in straight.
Settled behind midfield, gained closer to midfield rounding home bend, faded steadily in straight.
Always in last few, dropping to last over 700 metres out.
Jumped on terms, sat ahead of midfield, squeezed through a narrow gap 200M, knuckled down really well to grab the lead close home.
In a handy spot behind leaders, poised to strike 400M, gave good response when asked, wrestled the lead inside 150M, couldn't hold off winner late.
From draw 1 led as expected, continued on well early straight, caught passing 150M, couldn't go with first two late.
Settled in mid-division, hard driven 400M, responded well early straight but peaked on its run 150M.
Taken back to a position behind midfield, 5-6Ls to make up 400M, stayed on mildly without troubling first 3.
Held up behind midfield along the fence, only battled in the straight and got home fairly. No threat to leaders.
Shifted across from wide draw and settled near last, swung widest 500M before finishing off moderately. Never a winning hope.
Prominently ridden to be racing outside leader, fought on one paced early straight, crowded for room 200M, no extra late.
Jumped only fairly, settled at the back of the field 7-8Ls away, plenty to do at 400M but failed to run on.
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders, wasn't able to finish the race off from 400M.
Crowded after the start, chased leaders 2-wide, had nothing left passing 300M and dropped out sharply.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Refused to jump and took no part in the event. (Entries in races and barrier trials will be refused until a final determination in respect to the racing future of the horse has been made.)

Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line, won by 2 lengths. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)

Jumped well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield but trapped wide, moved closer after passing 1400M, 2nd in the middle stages, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened close home, just held second.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off well to take a place, nearest on line.

Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle in the early stages, commenced move 650M, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 8, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back turning in, made minor progress early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at tail, 10 lengths back, still 7 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after the start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L in the middle stages, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out approaching 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Bumped shortly after start, tracked leaders, 2 wide, hard ridden 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Blundered start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide towards rear, weakened and eased 500M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Away well, raced 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, 4 wide turning in, finished off well to take a place without threatening.

Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle in the early stages, 3 wide from 1250M, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, 3rd in the middle stages, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length or so back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, 3 wide from 550M, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.

Slowly away, raced towards rear on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 1100M, 5 to 6 lengths back in the middle stages, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Placing: PU
Comment: Towards rear of midfield, stumbled and went wrong near 450M, quickly pulled up.

Began smartly from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, travelled keenly in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest finish. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, closed off well without threatening.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 50M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, 3 wide after passing 500M, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight, checked close home.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, no clear run early in straight, made no progress thereafter.
Raced outside the leader. Took lead on straightening, dashed away to win by over a length.
Race third last along rail in the small field. Came away from rail just before straightening, closed well to move to second in final stages.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail. Lay inwards early in the straight, slightly difficult to ride out late when closing off ok to finish third when beaten over 2L.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined & headed by the winner on straightening, gave a few length late.
Was crowded soon after the start & got back to last. Stayed nearer the rail in the straight but only battled to the line.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was ridden along from the 500m, shifted ground on straightening but weakened a length to finish second last.

Taken back to race second last away from rail. Ridden along from the 500m, was the widest on straightening when still near tail, failed to run on in the straight & finished last (unable to quicken when pace increased â€“rider).
Jumped nicely, led in the race, made good progress inside 200M, closed off strongly.
Settled midfield, no clear run until near the 200M, responded well when asked.
Ridden hard to chase the leader, traveled smoothly, kept on well to hold 3rd.
Was slow to jump, raced rear, slightly held up making the Turn, ran on evenly.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, traveled okay, switched out entering the Straight, made minor progress inside 150M.
Settled behind midfield, was steadied and no clear run in the early Straight, ran on okay.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards rear on the inside, closed off fairly.
Sat handy, slightly weakened inside 150M, ran on fairly.
Sat towards rear, no clear run in the early Straight until near the 200M, could not be quicken thereafter.
Settled in front of midfield, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, no impression in the Straight (Substantial mucus, Roarer previously reported).
Settled in front of midfield, traveled only fairly, never a threat (See Incident Report).
Sat handy, raced wide throughout, weakened and faded notably entering the Straight (Lost right hind plate).
Raced outside the leader early and then 1,1 from about the 900m. Moved up to take narrow lead near 150m before digging deep in final stages to cling on and win by the narrowest possible margin.

Raced in midfield away from the rail. Came wider from the 400m, closed strongly down the outside to share lead passing the 150m mark, tried hard but missed on the bob, beaten by the narrowest of margins on line.

Got back to race worse than midfield. Began closing strongly between runners passing 200m before being badly crowded & checked near 150m, regathered himself & charged to line to only be beaten half-length, should have won.

Got back to race second last away from the rail. Came wider on straightening when sharing last place before closing strongly down the outside to be beaten only half a length into fourth in bunched finish.

Raced on the leaders back in middle stages. Bumped heavily near the 250m when held up for clear running on leaders heels & checked, got clear inside last furlong, closed off well, beaten just over a length in bunched finish.

Raced second away from rail. Shifted inwards on straightening & bumped heavily with rival, shifted outwards near the 150m hampering rival (rider suspended) before finishing steadily late, not be beaten far.

Taken back to last after the start. Shifted out to be the widest runner on straightening when sharing last place, made ground down the outside in the final stages but could only beat one rival home despite beaten only 1.5L.
Showed customary early speed to lead. Joined 7 Headed by the winner near the 150m mark, weakened a few lengths to finish last albeit beaten only 3L.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned in midfield on the inside, 3-1/2L back, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move 400M, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Made contact at start, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, saved ground throughout, 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out 450M, 6-1/2L back turning in, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lost left front plate.)
Jumped well, pushed along early to hold the box seat, angled out in the Straight and ran on strongly, score comfortably.
Broke nicely and quickly assumed the lead, kept on okay.
Steadied after the start from a wide barrier, settled towards the rear, dashed home late final 100M.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on fairly.
Sat last, made some progress along the rail.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide with cover, switched out rounding the Home Turn, showed some dash in the early part of the Straight, run peaked final 150M.
Broke alertly, settled midfield 2 wide, got shuffled back rounding the turn, held up early part of the Straight, stayed on once into the clear.
Settled midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Roarer)
Ridden along early to be on pace, sat outside leader at 1100M, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide no cover near midfield, never a factor.
Settled on rail 6th in midfield, gained some 1L closer leaving the Rock and saved ground turning for home, ran on under pressure to prevail in the bobbing of heads in a 3-way finish.
Began well settling about 2L off the pace in 3rd turning into back straight, came to challenge upon straightening gaining slender advantage inside final 500 metres only to be pipped at the finish.
Jumped well from a low draw but soon taken back to 5th some 4L off the pace in back straight, hung very wide making final turn, ran on resolutely to just fail to get up on line.
Settled in 7th in midfield, commenced move rounding home bend but did not find much room behind runners in straight until about 200 metres out, unable to quicken to challenge closing stages.
Soon dropped to last few despite ridden early stages, commenced move approaching home turn swinging wide into straight, ran on well between runners, tightened on the line.
Travelled 3-wide in last few early stages before settling in 9th 2-wide in back straight, one of the widest turning for home, made up good ground under pressure despite inconvenienced 250 metres out.
Settled towards rear on rail after moderate start, commenced move over 800 metres out and snuck within 2L of pace early in straight, had no more to give inside final 200 metres.
Pressed forward from a poor draw to take up running on the rail rounding first bend setting a sound pace, led until unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 200 metres.
Midfield early, pulled forward rounding first bend before settling in 4th about 2L off the pace into back straight, unable to sustain inside final 400 metres.
Jumped awkwardly from the widest draw before settling at the back, remained in last into straight, only ran past well-beaten horses.
Began well from the one draw settling just off the pace, came under pressure rounding home bend, weakened noticeably after straightening.
Taken well behind from a poor draw, never seen with a chance.
From draw 1 maintained a midfield position along the fence, worked into the race well 400M, led inside 100M to win in good style.
Away well, restrained to race ahead of mid-division 4Ls back, wide into straight, worked home strongly to claim 2nd near line without troubling the winner.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, held up 300M-250M then came with a decent finish to go 3rd near line.
Emerged as leader passing 900M and set decent pace to straight, all out final 250M, caught by winner inside 100M, edged out to 4th near line.
Jumped on terms, tracked leaders in a race ran at good pace, moved up to 2nd 400M, fought hard under top weight but peaked on its run mid-straight.
Crowded after the start and soon towards rear, had the job ahead 400M, closed off moderately but was held up inside 100M and not ridden out to the line.
Crowded after the start, settled in 2nd half of the field 5Ls off leader, little change at the turn but lacked a kick on straightening. Comfortably held by leaders final 200M.
Taken back from wide draw, settled near last 7Ls off the pace, ran on mildly when asked, steadied passing 100M and not ridden out to the line.
Switched off to race at the rear, 8Ls off leader on settling, had to make up a lot of ground at the 400M but ran past beaten horses only.
Maintained position just off the lead, 4th at 600M, failed to pick up under pressure ,checked after 200M but was already beaten then.
From draw 10 worked through to sit just off the pace, there to pounce 300M but failed to get into the finish.
From draw 11 caught racing wide without cover in mid-division, dragged further back making the home turn, not able to finish the race off on straightening.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 350M, very wide into straight, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2-1/2L back turning in, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Fast into stride, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually approaching final 50M.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, 2 wide from 450M, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Crowded shortly after start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Average to begin, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, steadied near 350M, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after the start, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide entering straight and lost place, weakened final furlong.

Began awkwardly and made contact, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, finished off strongly to score. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced in midfield on outer, commenced move 550M, showed good response in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 750M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Slow to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out approaching 450M, closed off well to make frame, nearest finish.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced towards rear on the outside, sent forward after passing 700M, 2 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, made no progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 9, tracked leaders, 3 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 150M.
Jumped well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked 450M, weakened early in straight.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, trailed the small field for the first 400 metres, became 5th some 3L back from 1200 metres out, quickened well inside final 150 metres to snatch victory near the line.
Disputed lead, gained slender advantage on straightening only to be outsprinted by winner close to home.
Attempted to make all only to be swamped close to finish.
Settled one-out-one-back in 4th, left flat-footed on straightening but produced good late impression inside final 100 metres.
Broke well, soon taken backward to last of the small field just over 3L off the pace, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend, ran on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Broke well before settling one back in 3rd on rail, soon came to challenge on straightening but unable to quicken to threaten.
Settled worse than midfield, responded well when asked inside 250M, finished off strongly.
Jumped okay, chased the leader, traveled nicely, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Sat towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, made good progress passing 150M, stayed on well to grab 3rd.
Sat towards rear, traveled okay, ran on evenly to the finish.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, one pace to the line.
Settled behind midfield, held up for clear running in the early Straight until 200M, closed off fairly.
Sat midfield, traveled fairly, steadied in the early Straight and crowded over the concluding stages, could not be fully ridden out.
Sat worse than midfield, minor progress made when under pressure (See Incident Report).
Crowded on jumping, sat towards rear 2 wide, no impression made (Rider dropped whip).
Settled rear, always rear, never a danger.
Ridden hard to lead, weakened passing 250M, gradually faded.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, eased down over the concluding stages (Disappointing performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Sat handy on the rail, weakened notably inside 350M, no contention.
Strode forward to race outside the leader. Moved to the lead near the 300m mark, pulled away to win by over a length.

Steadied after the start & taken back to race just worse than midfield. Improved to race three wide with cover passing 700m, shifted out to be the widest runner at 400m before making late ground to close to second final 50m.
Had a nice run on the leaders back in the middle stages. Was slightly hampered when going for a run between runners at 150m before finishing off well to not be beaten far into third.

Improved after the start but was caught racing three wide outside the leaders in middle stages. Continued close to the lead all of the way before being over-run for a minor place late, ran well considering wide passage.

Steadied & got back to race worse than midfield away from the rail. Continued rearward on straightening, was 5L from the lead entering last section before making some late headway down the outside to not be beaten far.

Was hampered by rival runner on jumping before racing three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Was just under 3L from the lead on straightening, battled on late to hold midfield finish without threatening.
Ridden hard at start to improve to lead. Was joined & headed by the winner near the 300m mark, gave a few lengths in concluding stages to be beaten just under 4L into midfield.

Veered inwards at the start before improving to be prominent and then getting position 1,1 in middle stages. Shifted outwards into clear running on straightening when only 2L from lead but weakened a few lengths late.

Began only fairly before improving between runners after the start to race in midfield. Continued between rivals on straightening when just under 4L from lead but failed to improve, weakening a few lengths in final section.

Began awkwardly & was then hampered & lost ground before racing worse than midfield along the rail. Had clear running on straightening when just under 5L from lead, weakened a further few lengths, never a factor.

Allowed to get back from the outside draw to race towards to rear with only the poor beginner behind early. Was third last and 7L from the lead entering last section, made no headway & was never a factor.

Had no speed after the start & got back to race second last along the rail with only the poor beginner behind. Continued second last on straightening when over 7L from the lead, did nothing in last section & was well beaten.

Began fairly, improve along the rail to race in midfield. Was a touch keen near approaching and passing the 800m mark, was under 4L from the lead on straightening, weakened poorly to be long second last.

Began extremely slowly and lost considerable ground at the start. Tacked onto the back of the field before half-way, was 8L behind on straightening but weakened to be long last but had excuse after blowing the start badly.
Crowded start, took the early lead, headed 900M, 2nd in the middle stages, hit the front 350M, kept on very well to the line, won by 2 lengths.

Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off strongly to take 2nd without threatening the winner. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run until 100M, made good progress thereafter to take a place.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced better than midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 250M, made some progress until approaching 50M, weakened gradually.
Began well from the widest draw, raced better than midfield but trapped very wide, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 600M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 900M, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 350M, weakened final furlong.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, bumped 300M, one-paced thereafter.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Away with them, raced 3 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, bumped 300M, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped well and showed very good early speed to lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked on in the Straight, won with plenty in hand.
Jumped nicely and settled in a prominent position on the rail, raced a bit greenly throughout, had some trouble finding clear running early in the Straight, ran on nicely once in the clear.
Settled 3 wide no cover behind midfield, closed off okay for 3rd.
Ridden along early and sat just behind the leaders on the rail, showed some dash early but soon become one pace
Sat on pace 2 wide, only one pace to the line.
Slow to begin, sat towards the rear, stayed on only fairly.
Settled midfield on the rail, limited response in the Straight.
Sat towards the rear 2 wide, made no impression.
Settled midfield 2 wide, made no ground in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat outside the leader, weakened inside final 250M.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, didn't run on.
Sat last on the rail, never a threat.
Jumped a step slow, settled towards the rear on the rail, raced keenly throughout, weakened in the Straight. (Blood in mouth)
Settled behind midfield on the rail, never in contention.

Raced wide prominently from the widest draw, obtained rails run in 3rd some 4L back over 1500 metres out, 4th when closer to steadied pace middle stages, quickened well on straightening to gain upper hand over 100 metres out.

Settled over 5L off the pace in 4th tracking eventual winner, shifted 3-wide in midfield when pace slackened middle stages, commenced move 4-wide entering home straight to soon hit the front only to be caught over 100 metres out.
Settled mainly in midfield on rail, some 3L back in 6th entering home straight, fought on under pressure to reach 3rd over 200 metre out but never troubled first two.
Jumped fairly, gradually taken back towards rear causing interference turning into back straight, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Travelled in rear pushing along from over 800 metres out, saved ground on rail making final turn, switched off heels over 200 metres out, ran on steadily without threatening.

Taken well behind from a poor draw and detached from the main body of the field, commenced move rounding home bend to be back in contention, ran on past well-beaten horses in home straight but never threatening.
Broke well before taken back to midfield, in similar position turning into home straight, one-paced.

Settled in last few after moderate start, made steady headway in back straight to reach 3rd within 2L of pace half-way out, gained further closer briefly entering straight but soon weakened under pressure.
Soon took up running setting a sound early pace, steadied up the tempo in back straight before renewing effort around home bend, unable to sustain and swamped inside final 300 metres.
Towards rear early, hampered, unbalanced and lost ground entering back straight, made no impression thereafter.
Pressed forward from a poor draw to soon chase behind race leader, unable to sustain effort upon straightening for home and weakened noticeably.
Tracked leaders in a race with genuine pace, 4th at 400M, closed off willingly when asked, got up late to prevail in a busy finish.
Jumped well, restrained midfield in a race with genuine pace, over-raced middle stages, responded well 400M and kept giving to the line, just missed in a pulsating finish.
Slow to begin, improved to sit in midfield passing 1400M, driven and ran on well over final 300M, just denied in a blanket finish involving first 7 horses.
Began awkwardly, soon towards the rear, travelled well with little change to the turn, finished off steadily down the outside, just missed out top 3 finish in a photo.

Jumped on terms, maintained position just off the lead 2Ls away, responded well early straight, 2nd at 200M and kept battling under pressure, joined by 5 other rivals in a blanket finish. Just missed.
Positioned ahead of midfield, in touch behind leaders turning for home, kept going soundly to the line, just missed out on first five in a blanket finish.
Soon led and set good pace, still going fine early straight, tried hard final 200M but was claimed late by pursuing rivals in a blanket finish.
Reserved near last 10Ls off the pace middle stages, still plenty to do top of straight, closed off final 400M fastest, finished 8th but beaten 1L only in a busy finish.
Chased leaders, 3rd at 500M and close enough to launch a challenge straightening, kept on evenly, run ended 100M and swamped by rivals.
Not hurried after the start, dropped back to race in 2nd half of the field, lacked a finishing kick on straightening, never reach contention.
Jumped only fairly, settled down along the fence in mid-division, ran on one paced and couldn't go on with rivals final 200M.
From wide draw switched off early stages to race in last, plenty to do 500M, failed to close off under top weight.
Bumped at the start, taken back from wide draw, settled near last over 10Ls off leader, found nothing from 500M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 650M, moved closer turning in, took the lead 350M, kept on well to hold off the challengers.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 550M, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Commenced well, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, moved a bit closer on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 550M, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, no clear run 300M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked and raced tight early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed near 350M, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 11, unable to slot in, trapped wide behind midfield, moved closer in the middle stages, a length or so back turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Commenced well, raced in 4th, 2 wide, there to turn, hit the front 250M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the outside, angled out 500M, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest finish.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, took the lead near 950M, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed 250M, kept on same pace to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped only fairly and crowded, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, angled out 500M, 6 lengths or so back turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Began well from a wide draw, took the early lead, headed near 950M, 2nd on turn, peaked 300M, weakened final furlong.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, no clear run early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 12, raced behind midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.

Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 800M, 5 lengths back on turn, not enough room early in straight, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 1, tracked leaders on the inside, unable to maintain position in the middle stages, made minor progress early in straight, no clear run near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Began awkwardly and bumped, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, dropped towards rear in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, kept on same pace thereafter.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 700M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, commenced move 700M but only showed limited response, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 800M, no cover in the middle stages, weakened early in straight.
Only fair on jumping, maintained a midfield position on inside, picked up well from 300M, drove hard to get up close home.
Well away and tracked the pace, took over nearing 400M, kicked on well when asked, fought hard only to concede close home.
Fast into stride, raced keenly when being crossed by rival 800M, fought hard from 300M to the finish, held by first two final stages.
Not hurried after the start, reined in and raced wide no cover towards the rear, widest into straight, made up some ground to finish 4th without troubling first three.
Away with them, maintained a 3-wide position towards the rear, wide into straight, closed off moderately although never a winning hope.
Bumped at the start, soon taken across behind runners, settled towards the rear 4-5Ls on inside, just battled away on straightening and couldn't get close to first three.
Stayed close behind leaders, poised to strike turning for home, just battled home steadily, no extra late.
Pushed along after start, crowded 1000M and lost position, behind midfield 4Ls off the pace going into home turn and was just fair to the line, steadied 100M.
Taken back from wide draw and raced keenly in last, had the job in hand top of straight, held up near 250M, was making some late progress but was held up again final 50M.
Bustled along after the start, held his position midfield on outside, was crowded between rivals 300M and did not obtain clear running until after 200M, failed to get into the finish.
Jumped only fairly, pressed forward to lead, under the pressure 400M, soon weakened. (Jockey : raced "flat" / Irregular Heart Rhythm.)
Unable to slot in from draw 11, caught wide no cover chasing leaders, gave ground passing 400M, well beaten.
Sat midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, show some dash inside 50M, closed off strongly.
Sat towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, made good progress in the Straight, finished off nicely.
Chased the lead throughout, slightly weakened inside 150M, kept on okay to hold 3rd.
Sat midfield 2 wide, traveled okay, responded nicely passing 200M.
Jumped nicely, sat midfield 3 wide, raced wide throughout, finished off fairly.
Jumped only fairly, settled worse than midfield, was crowded and checked rounding the Turn, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, settled rear, was held up in the early Straight, no clear run over the concluding stages.
Sat in front of midfield, was bumped inside 200M, minor progress made when asked.
Ridden hard to lead, weakened passing 100M, gradually faded.
Sat worse than midfield, was steadied in the early Straight, no impression.
Sat worse than midfield, failed to respond, never a threat (Must Stalls test).
Sat in front of midfield, weakened and faded notably after near the 100M, never a factor.
Had a nice run on the leaders back throughout. Had to wait behind heels in the first part of straight, got through passing 200m, closed well to take lead in final 75m.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Pealed three wide just before straightening, moved to share lead 150m, passed by winner final 75m.
Pushed forward to race outside leader. Moved to lead approaching 200m, joined 150m, battled on ok to only be beaten a length into third.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined near the 200m mark, battled to hold fourth but was no match for the first three.

Got back & raced worse than midfield three wide without cover. Got some cover from the 600m after improving to midfield, was the widest runner on straightening, closed off steadily down the outside to hold midfield finish.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Finished off only moderately in the straight to finish in midfield without threatening.

Steadied from outside gate & taken back towards to rear. Was second last and nearly 7L from the lead entering last section, passed a few tiring rivals in concluding stages when making up a length or two to midfield late.

Got back to race worse third last after the start. Moved into the three wide line with cover down back straight, was 5L from the lead entering last section, finished off only one paced & was beaten the same margin on line.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Was only 3L from the lead on straightening, stayed nearer the inside but weakened a few lengths. Plain.
Got back to race just worse than midfield between runners after the start. Was 5L from the lead entering last section when third last, stayed along rail in straight but did little in the finish.

Raced keenly when being steadied after the start & taken to the rear. Moved four wide & commenced to improve around the field down back straight, was forward of midfield from the 600m but weakened to second last in straight.

Steadied at the start & shifted back to race worse than midfield along the rail after the start. Was relegated to last near the 550m mark when being hard ridden before weakening out poorly to be a long last.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, a length or so back on turn, angled out 400M, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Away well, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 400M, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, angled out approaching 400M, 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.

Jumped awkwardly and made contact with the left side of its barrier, raced in 2nd, travelled keenly in the middle stages, hard ridden 300M, every chance entering final furlong, peaked 150M, weakened final 50M.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Jumped only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced better than midfield, a length or so back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced at rear on outer, very wide turning in, showed no response early in straight, eased final furlong.
Broke well and quickly assumed the lead, travelled keenly early, kicked on in the Straight, always doing enough.
Tracked leader, kept on nicely to the line for 2nd.
Sat on pace 3 wide no cover, ran on okay for 3rd, no threat to the top 2.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, closed off fairly.
Sat just behind the leaders on the rail, unable to quicken in the Straight.
Sat towards the rear, raced keenly in the early stages, stayed on okay.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, had some trouble finding clear running early in the Straight, closed off fairly when in the clear.
Settled towards the rear, made no impression.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never ran on.
Settled midfield 2 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Sat midfield on the rail, under pressure throughout, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Disappointing Performance, must trial)
Settled on rail in 4L 6th in rear of midfield, commenced move under pressure about 550 metres out, snuck up on rail turning for home, sustain effort to gain upper hand final strides.
Soon took up running on rail setting a sound pace, kicked 2L clear rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort and collared close to home.
Settled in rear on rail after slow out, came under pressure home bend and switched out for a run entering straight, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Settled one-out-one-back in 4th, came under pressure about 550 metres out, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled one back in 3rd on rail, chased quickening race leader in 2L 2nd rounding home bend, found no extra under pressure after straightening.
Travelled near midfield in 5th over 3L back, became 6th in similar position about 550 metres out, hung in from being one of the widest turning into straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled at the back and waited with, widest into home straight, ran on to be nearest finish.

Travelled 3-wide without cover for the first 600 metres after awkward start, remained in last few despite niggling along from 600 metres out, made no further impression in straight. (Tactic questioned)
Travelled keenly in worse than midfield passing the winning post the first time, remained towards rear throughout back straight and around home bend, made no further in the run to the line.
Pressed forward from the widest draw before settling outside race leader, weakened under pressure from over 550 metres out.
From wide draw slotted into a 2-wide position behind leaders, showed a quick turn of foot early straight, led near 200M and came away for strong win.
Taken across from wide draw to be racing at the rear early stages, steadied 250M and shifted to the fence for clear running, came with a decent finish but was held by the determined winner.
Slow to begin, settled in the second half of the field, finished off well to go 3rd close home.
Off to a good start, soon restrained to a midfield position, raced keenly middle stages, briefly held up after 300M then closed off the race moderately.
Well away from draw 1 and held his position just off leader, closed just fairly over final 300M, no threat from mid-straight.
Reserved near the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, kept battling away down the outside but posed little threat to leaders.

Away on terms, sat in behind midfield 3-4Ls on settling, maintained his spot to the bend but found less than expected in the finish. (Jockey : travelled satisfactorily but did not quicken as anticipated.)
Out with the line, soon restrained to race at the rear, 6-7Ls to make up 400M but only gave limited response.
Pushed up and settled 2nd of 10, under the pump 500M, nothing more to offer passing 250M.
Jumped awkwardly, kicked up to lead on settling, headed near 200M, no extra and dropped out rapidly to last. (Jockey reported his mount made a respiratory noise during the race.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, took the lead 200M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 900M, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, angled out 350M, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead near 800M, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weekend gradually final 100M.
Average to begin, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 350M, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, no clear run and coasted final 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly
Began only fairly and crowded, raced 2 wide towards rear, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, weakened early in straight.
