Blundered shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, finished off strongly to take 2nd without threatening the winner.

Pushed forward to race on the leaders back after the first bend. Came off the rail passing the 600m, moved to the lead approaching the 300m mark, joined & passed quickly by winner at 125m, battled on to hold well beaten 3rd.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5Ls or so back, awkwardly placed 700M, 2 wide from 500M, checked 450M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, hard ridden from 450M, 5 lengths back turning in, closed off well without threatening.
Bumped start, positioned slightly better than midfield on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Blundered start and bumped, raced better than midfield on the outside, commenced move 550M, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, hard ridden from 550M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed 350M, weakened final 300M. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight, finished tailed out. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, tracked leaders on the outside, raced in 2nd after entering the back straight, unable to maintain position approaching 500M, emptied early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced outside the leader. Engaged in a two-horse battle with the leader all the way down the straight, before proving too strong in final stages to win by a head.
Pushed forward to lead. Engaged in two horse battle down the straight but was just overcome close to the line to be beaten a head.

Was caught racing three wide in midfield throughout. Was 3.5L from the lead on straightening, slightly hampered when close to heels passing 400m, before closing strongly in the last furlong to charge to fast finishing 3rd.
Had a nice run in midfield on rail. Was 3L from the lead on straightening where he had clear running before closing steadily all the way to be beaten 2.5L into 4th.

Got head down just before start & was consequently slow to begin before crossing to rail & improving along the inside to race in midfield. Came away from inside on straightening, shifted wider at 200m & closed well late.

Raced in midfield away from the rail. Lay outwards around 850m turn & was momentarily wide. Was checked away from heels near the 400m when about 4.5L from lead before closing steadily down the outside to hold midfield finish.

Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was a touch keen approaching the 850m. Was hampered when close to heels at the 300m mark & threw head before finishing only evenly in last furlong to hold midfield finish.

Steadied from outside gate & taken back to second last. Continued rearward and 7.5L from the lead on straightening before passing a few tiring rivals when making up a few lengths when running onto midfield out wide.

Got back to race worse than midfield away from the rail. Was just under 6L from the lead on straightening, shifted outwards at the 400m to be the widest runner before passing a couple but never getting near the leaders.

Began fairly before mustering speed to improve & race forward, checked at 900m when crossed, raced on leaders back thereafter. Came off the rail on straightening shifted ground near the 400m before weakening in last furlong.
Got a nice position 1,1 after the start. Was ridden along to hold place before straightening, weakened out in last 300m to be beaten over 6L.

Was slightly slow to begin & was then shifted behind runners to race worse than midfield along the rail. Came away from the inside on straightening, was 5.5L from lead entering last section but failed to improve.
Got back after the start & raced third last along the rail. Was ridden along from the 500m, stayed nearer the inside in the straight but weakened a further few lengths & finished a long second last.

Had no speed at the start & was hard ridden to hold his position when racing a clear last. Dropped further behind approaching corner, was 13L behind on straightening before weakening further to finished a distant last.
Sat in front of midfield, responded well when placed under pressure inside 200M, closed off strongly.
Ridden along to lead, traveled nicely, made good progress in the Straight, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, responded nicely when asked near the 100M.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, ran on evenly.
Chased the leader, slightly weakened in the Straight, ran on fairly (Dropped rein, See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, making the Turn wide, closed off okay (See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, minor progress made in the Straight, not much impression made.
Sat rear, raced keenly in the early stages, limited response when asked, never a threat.
Sat towards rear, not much ground made in the Straight, never a danger.
Sat in front of midfield, weakened quickly inside 200M, gradually faded (See Incident Report).

Raced just worse than midfield between runners. Shifted into clear running on straightening when just over 4L from lead before finishing strongly down the outside to charge to lead at the 200m mark & go on to win well.

Was bumped at the start & lost ground before improving along the rail to race in midfield in middle stages. Shifted back to rail in straight, closed well to move to second 150m, finished over a length clear of third.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Entered last section just over 3L from the lead, closed off steadily to move to third place inside final 75m but was no match for winner.

Bumped at the start before racing just worse than midfield away from the rail. Was ridden along passing the 600m, was bumped outwards near the 500m, was the second widest on straightening before making late ground to 4th.

Began fairly before getting back to race second last. Was bumped near the 550m when going between runners, entered last section with only one runner behind before making late headway for non-threatening fifth.

Got back after the start to race worse than midfield along the rail. Stayed along the inside on straightening when just over 5L from lead, passed a handful of rivals when finishing steadily near the inside in final stages.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Continued close to lead at furlong marker before peaking in effort & weakening out in last 100m.
Raced in midfield along the rail for the majority. Didn't have clear running and raced tight from on straightening until about the 250m but finished off only moderately thereafter.

Steadied at the start & taken back to race third last away from the rail. Moved into the three wide line near 650m, bumped near 500m, was the widest runner on straightening when 5L from lead, finished only evenly to midfield.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield for the majority. Was ridden along before cornering, was 4.5L from the lead on straightening but gave a few lengths in the straight & was no factor.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined 7 Headed by the winner near the furlong marker, weakened out poorly in final 150m
Obtained a nice position 1,1 after start. Raced tight from the 350m until the 200m but was already beaten & then gave ground in final stages.
Had a nice run on the leaders back. Came off the rail on straightening, peaked on run at the 250m before weakening out poorly in the concluding stages.
Steadied & taken back to a clear last after the start. Never improved, was 8.5L behind on straightening before weakening further to be a long last.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Shifted out at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, a bit closer on turn, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, moved closer on turn, hard ridden after passing 350M but only showed limited response, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after the start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 800M, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after the start, raced in midfield on outer, bumped 900M, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on same pace to the line.

Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the early lead, headed approaching 800M, sat right behind the leader on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, bumped and unbalanced near 900M, 2-1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced towards rear on the inside, save ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Broke smartly and ridden for the lead, sat just outside the leader, kept on well to score. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, raced greenly in the Straight, took some time to find clear run, ran on okay once in the clear. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield on the rail, began to improve near the 700M, angled out in the Straight, stayed on fairly.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, showed some dash early in the Straight, but one pace after the 250M.
Raced on pace 3 wide no cover, kept on fairly despite the tough run.
Broke slowly, sat towards the rear and niggled along throughout the early stages, made some progress along the rail, never seriously tested. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, took some time to respond, made some late ground.
Sat midfield on the rail, held up early in the Straight, made little impression. (Blood in Trachea)
Raced towards the rear, switched out in the Straight, made minor progress.
Settled midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Jumped well and showed good early speed to lead, weakened inside 350M.
Sat just behind the leaders, weakened in the Straight.
Always at rear, never in contention.

Restrained in 3L 6th on rail, travelled keenly in similar position when 8th rounding home bend, snuck up to joint 5th on the inside turning in, held up for a run until 200 metres, quickened well to assert authority final strides.
Jumped best from a poor draw to lead off the rail, ceded advantage on the rail for 2nd spot coming onto home bend, renewed effort to hit the front 250 metres out only to be pipped at post.
Pressed forward after moderate start from a wide draw, 1L back in 3rd coming onto home bend becoming 2nd 700 metres out, kept on same pace under pressure without threatening in the run to the line.

Began moderately setting well behind and waited with off the rail, commenced move passing the 700 metres and one of the widest turning for home, finished off the race strongly inside final 250 metres.
Ridden positively after moderate start obtaining lead 2-wide approaching home bend, led until narrowly headed 200 metres and swamped for a placing inside final 100 metres. (Tactic questioned)

Pressed forward early stages, restrained and travelled keenly some 2L back in 4th rounding home bend, baulked for a run for about 100 metres early in straight, fought on steadily without threatening final 200 metres.
Taken back for cover from a poor draw reaching last about 1200 metres out, remained well behind into straight, produced strong late finish inside final 200 metres.
Settled mainly 3-wide without cover in midfield, gained closer but wider rounding home bend, kept on well to the line.

Hampered and settled in last few, travelled keenly gaining slightly closer 3-wide 1100 metres out, gained further closer 5-wide rounding home bend, made modest progress in straight until finding no extra 150 metres out.
Allowed to drift backward to last few, improved steadily on rail to be just worse than midfield over 1300 metres out, lost position again rounding home bend, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Settled about 2L back in 5th gaining 4th 3-wide rounding home bend, held some chance early in straight but dropped out tamely inside final 250 metres.
Settled in midfield after reasonable start, tightened 400 metres out after straightening, ran home one-paced.
Travelled keenly towards rear after moderate start, hampered upon straightening, made no impression in the run to the line.
Began well but gradually taken well behind, remained wide in last few and the widest into straight, made no further impression.
Soon led, had uncontested lead along the fence, opened up 2L lead 200M, kept kicking away to win comfortably.
Settled down midfield, held up from 300M and didn't obtain clear running until near 100M, ran on to claim 2nd near line without troubling winner.
Held up towards the rear, finished off quite well down the stand's rail, pinched 3rd spot close home. Not reach winner.
Close up tracking leader, boxed on well to hold 2nd until near 50M, headed by 2nd and 3rd late.
Jumped awkwardly, reserved behind midfield 4Ls off the pace, finished off reasonably well and just missed out on a top four finish.
Shifted across behind runner early stages, given a waiting ride 5Ls off leader, worked home steadily passing 400M, safely held by leaders final stages.
Settled behind midfield, ran on mildly final 400M, raced tight 200M, never on terms with leaders.
Never far off from leaders, raced keenly middle stages, lacked a kick when asked and was safely held in the end. (Roarer)
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced as the back-marker 6-7Ls off the pace, failed to progress passing 400M. Never in the hunt.
Maintained a midfield position, tried hard passing 400M but wasn't good enough. Never dangerous.
Raced in the group chasing leader, 4th at 400M, battled on to hold his position until 200M when no extra, steadied 150M and weakened away.
Chased leaders, 3rd at 400M but soon came under pressure, gave ground passing 200M, eased down near 100M when crowded between rivals.

Moderately away, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 1100M, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 300M, kept on strongly, easy late.

Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, no clear run after passing 300M, cleared 150M, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Out in line, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 300M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority of the race, 4 wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 450M, 5-1/2L back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, passed some tired runners in the run home.
Out with rest, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 500M, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 1000M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped well, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 1100M, 3rd on turn, a length or so back, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, weakened final 300M, eased thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, peaked 500M, weakened early in straight, eased final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Began fairly and made contact, raced in midfield on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, angled out 500M, hit the front 300M, kept on well, just able to hold off the challenger late.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, finished off strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Average to begin, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 1000M, commenced move 550M, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, no clear run 300M, cleared 250M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail approaching 700M, saved ground on turn, no clear run 300M to 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run near 250M, kept on same pace thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, carried wider 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped only fairly, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, raced in 2nd, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (Lame right front and right hind legs next day.)
Began smartly from gate 13, raced prominently on the outside, 1-1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened 300M, eased final 150M.

Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight, won by a narrow margin.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Jumped with them, raced in 2nd, 1-1/2L back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always just held.
Commenced well, raced in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, closed off well to make frame, nearest on line.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, still well back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 10 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began awkwardly losing ground, travelled over 4L back in 4th early in back stages, gained 3rd and closer to race leader when pace slackened in back straight, responded well to assert authority 100 metres out.
Settled well behind and waited with, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, shifted out for a run inside final 200 metres and finished off the race strongly.
Restrained just off the pace in 2nd jointly or outright within 2L of pace, closer to leader when pace slackened rounding home bend, hit the front briefly 200 metres out but lost 2nd late.

Gradually settled in midfield some 5L off the pace, dropped to 8th onto home bend before coming under pressure to challenge, snuck up on rail into straight reaching within 1L of leaders but unable to sustain effort close to home.
Settled in mid-division of strung-out field, commenced move passing the 600 metres and went wide for a run into straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.

Soon took up running setting a cracking pace around first bend, steadied up the pace in back straight coming back to within 1.5L of the main body of the field, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 200 metres.
Settled towards rear from a poor draw, produced short-lived effort on rail rounding home bend gaining 5L 5th into straight, made no further impression.
Taken back to last few from a poor draw, commenced move rounding home bend sneaking closer on rail on final turn, made no impression in the run to the line.
Ridden early before settling in midfield or just worse, given reminders early in back straight, dropped further back out of contention rounding home bend.

Pressed forward from a poor draw reaching within 2.5L in 2nd on first bend against strong pace, drafted slightly backward to 3rd 950 metres out, gave ground noticeably from 4th inside final 600 metres.
Broke well from a low draw settling in remote 4th or 5th, gave ground steadily from about 600 metres out. (Blood in trachea)
Travelled in last few on rail after moderate start, came under pressure from half-way out before dropping to tail-end rounding home bend.
Chased the leader 2 wide, traveled comfortably, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, closed off nicely.
Settled rear, switched out rounding the Turn, made good progress over the final 75M.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled smoothly, angled out at the Turn, finished off okay.
Sat handy on the rail, dropped back inside 650M, picked up again in the Straight, ran on fairly.
Sat midfield, steadied in the early Straight when crowded, one pace to the line.
Sat towards rear, weakened slightly near the 550M, minor progress made when asked.
Sat handy, raced wide throughout, weakened notably inside 100M.
Settled behind midfield, limited response when asked, could not be ridden out (See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, no impression made.
Sat towards rear, always rear 3 wide, no contention.
Ridden along to lead, weakened notably inside 150M, gradually faded.

Led after start before being joined near the 950m mark & raced outside the leader thereafter. Improved to regain lead near 200m, was challenged inside last furlong but was just too strong in final 50m to win.

Raced in fourth along the rail. Raced tight on straightening when moving into clear running, moved close to lead at 200m, tried very hard, overcome by leader in final 50m but finished well clear of third.
Improved to share lead near 950m & then take outright lead soon after. Joined & headed by winner near 200m, battled on to hold well beaten third.

Got back to race second last away from the rail. Bumped, unbalanced & lost a length near the 450m, continued rearward on straightening, made some headway down the outside late, laid inwards near line when closing to 4th.

Improved around the first bend when racing wide before moving closer to rail and getting 1,1 position from about the 700m. Was only 2L from the lead entering last section, finished off only one paced in last furlong.
Obtained position in midfield away from the rail after the start. Eased wider entering last section when 3.5L from the lead, finished off only steadily down the outside & made no impression.

Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Was just over 3L from the lead entering last section, stayed along the rail in straight until shifting outwards passing 200m, finished off only moderately in concluding stages.

Slow & crowded at start & then shifted back to the rear. Was last and 6.5L from the lead entering last section, stayed near the inside in last furlong, not ridden out fully in final strides but was no factor at that stage.

Slow to begin before improving along rail after first bend to race third last. Was just under 5L from the lead entering last section, blundered on straightening, shifted out passing 150m but never challenged & finished last.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide with no cover, 3-1/2L back, a bit closer on turn, closed off well to score by a neck.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Made contact at start, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer after passing 650M, 3 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, closed off well to take a place.
Out in line, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few in the closing stages. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Began only fairly and made contact, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run approaching 200M, cleared 100M, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped with the field, settled midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely to score.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, made good progress center of the track, got 2nd final stride.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, angled out in the Straight, showed some dash early but only one pace after 150M.
A bit slow into stride, ridden along early to be handy on the rail, held up early in the Straight, closed off fairly.
Raced in a midfield position on the rail, made minor headway.
Jumped okay and restrained early to sit towards the rear 2 wide, stayed on okay, made some late ground.
Steadied after the start and moved across towards the rail, saved ground and made its run on the rail, run peaked final 150M.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, one pace to the finish.
Not the quickest out, showed good early to be prominent, weakened final furlong.
Showed good early pace to lead, weakened and faded final 150M.
Sat at the rear, never a factor.
Raced ungenerously early, settled last, never in contention. (See Incident Report) (Lost right front plate)
Pressed forward from a poor draw gaining narrow advantage off the rail, led until headed about 600 metres out, renewed effort from close 2nd into straight to gain upper hand 100 metres out.
Shared pace on rail before gaining narrow advantage 600 metres out, kicked 1L clear into straight but unable to sustain effort and swamped 100 metres out .

Broke well sharing early pace briefly before taken back for 4th over 2L back before first turn, slightly further off the pace when tempo increased 800 metres out, kept on steadily under pressure in straight without quickening.
Settled in midfield in 5th about 5L off the pace, saved ground turning in for home, fought on steadily under pressure along the rail without threatening.
Soon recovered from moderate start to 7th some 5L off the pace on rail, further away from pace when tempo increased around home bend, produced good late impression in the run to the line.
Vied for lead from a poor draw settling one back in 3rd for cover 800 metres out, came under pressure when some 3L back rounding home bend, found no extra after straightening.
Taken well back from the widest draw, gained closer to second last spot 900 metres out, wide rounding home bend and into straight, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run to the line.
Always well behind and never seen with a chance
Settled in rear of midfield, yielded ground when tempo increased 800 metres out, made no further impression.
Bumped on jumping. restrained in midfield along the 2-path in a slowly run race, remained 3L behind leader at 400M, came with a well-timed run to lead near line for maiden victory.
Soon led, allowed an easy lead early and middle stages, kept on well when driven out passing 300M, caught by winner close home.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, made his move on outside home turn, moved up to 3rd near 200M but no match for first two late stages.
From draw one moved up to track leaders, fought hard to stay in contention early straight, failed to find extra final 150M, comfortably held by leaders towards the finish.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, reserved in last off a slow pace 10Ls back on settling, pushed along 500M, ran on well in the straight but too much to do.
Slow to begin, held his position midfield, came wide home turn and was just fair to the line. No threat to leaders.

Chased leaders, little change throughout the race, lacked a turn of foot early straight, lost 3rd spot 250M and out of contention. (Jockey fined for failing to ride out to the satisfaction of the Stewards.)
Soon towards the rear, held up near last 8Ls off the slow pace, gave limited response on straightening, never in the hunt.
Jumped awkwardly and shifted across behind runners from wide draw, worse than midfield 6Ls on the turn, didn't finish it off.
Settled down midfield 4-5Ls off the slow pace, failed to respond when placed under pressure on straightening. Never dangerous.
Caught wide early stages, strode forward passing 1100M to race outside the lead, under the pump 500M before giving ground early straight.

Crowded shortly after start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, 2 wide from 400M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on strongly to the line, won by 2 lengths.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, angled out 350M, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, angled out after passing 400M, very wide into straight, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5-1/2L back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Began smartly from gate 12, took the early lead, headed 900M, retook the lead 550M, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out 350M, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead near 900M, headed 550M, 1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide, 1-1/2L back, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight. (Right front suspensory ligament injury on the day after racing.)

Jumped well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, travelled keenly in the early stages, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced in midfield on the outside, peaked on turn, weakened final 400M.
Crowded shortly after start, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight. (Irregular heart rhythm.)

Made contact shortly after start, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, took the lead 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, hard ridden approaching 300M, kept on evenly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.

Began smartly, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, taken back after passing 1350M, raced 3w slightly better than midfield in the middle stages, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, unable to obtain clear run until approaching 50M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 450M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, made no progress thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, taken back from to race at rear on the inside, angled out 600M, failed to close off in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Maintained a midfield position 3Ls away, responded well when driven near 300M, led 50M out and just held on at the line from the fast finishing 2nd and 3rd.
Jumped only fairly and settled towards the rear, charged home strongly final 250M, just missed in a desperately close finish.
Bumped after the start, soon shifted across to the outside rail 6Ls towards the rear, was badly held up for running until 50M then flew home to almost win it.
Jumped awkwardly, moved up to track leaders, loomed a strong chance 200M before outsprinted by first three close home

Chased leaders along stands' rail, showed greenness when placed under pressure 300M, still in contention going into 150M but was outsprinted late. (Jockey : his mount lay in from 250M and proved difficult to ride out.)
Soon led along the outside rail on jumping from draw 14, joined by rivals near 200M, grudgingly gave way final stages.
Bumped at the start, showed speed to be racing just off the speed, had difficulty obtaining clear running 200M-100M but always held by leaders in the run home. (Roarer).
Bounded on jumping and lost ground, restrained near the rear, made some ground final 250M but posed little threat to leaders.
Moved forward to be pressing leader, hard driven to maintain its position from 400M, no extra 150M weakened away. (Bled.)
Settled down midfield, unable to obtain clear running from 350M and couldn't be ridden out to the finish. Inconclusive run.

Bumped at the start, held up in midfield, found disappointingly little when asked and never able to challenge. (Jockey : didn't travel well amongst other runners and failed to finish to the race off.)
Shifted in at the start and was bumped, ended up at the back 5-6Ls away, never near to challenge.
Obtained a position midfield towards the center of track, failed to pick up when pushed along halfway, never dangerous.
Towards the rear, couldn't go on passing 400M. (Blood in trachea.)
Settled midfield, traveled smoothly, no clear run until 150M, closed off nicely.
Sat handy 2 wide, made good progress when asked passing 200M, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Sat midfield 3 wide, traveled nicely, responded well over the final 250M.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, no clear run in the early Straight, ran on evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear, responded okay when asked in the Straight.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, raced keenly in the early stages, slightly weakened inside 300M, closed off fairly.
Settled in front of midfield 3 wide, raced wide throughout, limited response when asked ("Roarer" previously reported, See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield 3 wide, responded only fairly, one pace to the finish.
Ridden along to lead, weakened approaching 200M, gradually faded (Lost left front plate).
Settled behind midfield, weakened in the Straight, could not be ridden out.
Sat rear, switched out entering straight, no impression made. (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, gave ground over the concluding stages, eased down thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Had a nice run-in 4th along the rail. Improved onto leaders back around bend, came off rail just before straightening, closed strongly to take lead passing the 150m, drew away to win strongly.

Raced in midfield between runners. Shifted back down to the rail entering last section when 5L from lead before making ground, shifted outwards passing the 250m before charging to second inside final 50m.
Pushed forward to obtain customary roll in the lead. Joined by challenger near 300m, passed by winner at the 150m mark, battled on ok to hold well beaten third on line.

Drifted back to last early before improving around the 850m bend to race three wide and 4th last. Was over 7L from the lead on straightening, made some late ground down the outside from a long way back.

Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Moved up to challenge for the lead at the 300m, emptied at the 150m mark & gave ground sharply in final stages to be beaten over 4L after racing handy throughout.

Raced just worse than midfield away from the rail. Improved to midfield around bend, came wider on straightening when 6L from lead, finished off only fairly to midfield in late stages & never threatened.
Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Was 4.5L from the lead on straightening but found little, weakening to be beaten 7.5L into midfield on the line.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail throughout. Was 3L from the lead on straightening, moved off the rail passing the 400m mark, weakened in last furlong & was beaten 9L on line.

Began well but was steadied & dragged back in first two furlongs & was relegated to last near the 1000m mark. Continued rearward and over 8L from the lead on straightening before passing a couple of tiring rivals late.
Was trapped racing three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Was 5.5L from the lead on straightening, found little in final 300m & weakened to be beaten just under 10L.

Began fairly, obtained position third last along the rail in middle stages. Was hard ridden before straightening, was second last and 9L from lead entering last section, made no headway, beaten a similar margin on line.

Got head up on jumping & then got back to races second last after start. Continued rearward throughout, was last and 10L from the lead entering last section, only maintained deficit to the line & was never a threat.
Raced just worse than midfield along the rail. Was ridden along passing the 600m mark, weakened out further in the straight to be beaten over 10L when finishing second last.

Ridden forward after start & improved position but was caught racing three deep without cover when forward of midfield. Was beaten off on straightening & weakened out quickly in last 300m to finish a long last.

Bumped start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, 4-5 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, showed very good response, hit the front 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Made contact at start, positioned 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 750M, same margin back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.

Made contact at start, taken back to race at tail, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, blocked near 150M, cleared 50M, finished off well to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 12, taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, found rail approaching 700M, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, no clear run approaching 150M, cleared 100M, one-paced thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 wide from 700M, 2-1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped wide in midfield, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with the field, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled smoothly throughout, switched out in the Straight, closed off strongly, won going away
Jumped nicely, showed good early speed to sit outside the lead, kept on nicely for 2nd.
Sat just behind the leaders, improved between horses rounding the Home Turn, kept on until weakened slightly final 75M.
Broke well, settled on pace 2 wide, showed some dash from the 350M to 250M then kept on once pace, no threat to the top 3.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, made some progress in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, under pressure from the 800M, one pace to the finish.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, held up in the early part of the Straight, stayed on fairly once in the clear.
Jumped well but was restrained from the outside barrier, settled at the rear 2 wide, made some late ground.
Caught 3 wide with cover behind midfield, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Sat at the rear on the rail, never a threat.
Hard ridden early to lead, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Caught 3 wide no cover near midfield, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Got hampered at the start, sat last, never in contention.
Ridden to soon take up running before setting a moderate tempo, quickened up under pressure upon straightening and hung on well to the line.

Jumped awkwardly, refused to settle and pulled forward to reach 7th 1000 metres out, continued to travel keenly in the moderate tempo rounding home bend, came to challenge strongly inside final 150 metres to snatch 2nd late.
Settled one back in 3rd on rail within 1.5L of the moderate pace, made modest progress under pressure without threatening.
In last few early, travelled keenly in slackened pace late in back straight, shifted wide for a run entering home straight, hung in under pressure and a difficult ride but kept gaining to the line.
Travelled wide without cover towards the rear, inconvenienced before dropping to last about 1050 metres out, commenced move out wide around home bend, ran on in straight without threatening.
Ridden forward from a wide draw settling in 2nd, came to challenge inside the 600 metres holding some chance in straight until finding no extra inside final 150 metres.

Taken back to last from the widest draw, travelled keenly gaining to second last briefly approaching home bend, dropped back to last about 600 metres out, only produced moderate late headway under pressure.
Jumped fairly settling mainly in 5th about 3L off the steady pace, baulked behind runners in critical stages in home straight.
Settled in midfield, made modest headway early in straight, found no extra inside final 100 metres.
Broke well settling some 3L back in 4th, kept on early in straight before faded shortly afterwards.
Away smoothly, sat in behind leader, took over nearing 300M when still under a hold, always holding on when challenged by the runner up over final 200.
Settled midfield 2Ls off pace, quickened up nicely from 400M to challenge leader, fought hard to line but always held.
In mid-division never far off from leaders, responded moderately under pressure, moved up to 3rd near 100M, comfortably held by first two.
Jumped awkwardly and then crowded for room, chased leaders along stand's side, kept on steadily over final 400M, not able to challenge first two but ran a pleasing race on debut.

Maintained a midfield position towards the stands' rail, battled on same pace passing halfway, safely held by leaders. (Jockey : his mount did not quicken under top weight on a track that had some give in it.)
Bumped with rival at the start, soon towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, made some progress final 400M but couldn't get into the finish.
Crowded at the start, maintained a position towards the rear, picked off a few final 400M but posed no serious threat to leaders.
Badly crowded at the start, held up at the rear 7Ls off the pace, had some work to do passing halfway, made up some ground but never a threat to leaders.
Bumped shortly after the start, soon took up running along the stands' rail, headed inside 400M and failed to run on.
Began awkwardly, soon took up a forward position chasing the pace, struggled to make an impression passing 500M and gave ground.
Restrained after the jump, soon towards the rear, struggled to keep up halfway, never in the hunt.
Bumped on jumping and became unbalanced, moved up to be prominent behind leader, struggled to maintain his position 400M, soon out of contention.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in midfield but never far off the pace, couldn't go on passing 400M and gave ground. (RF tendon injury reported on the day after racing.)
Settled midfield 4Ls off the pace, under the pump near 500M, emptied final 200M and weakened to last.
Out in line, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, finished off strongly, led last stride.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, angled out 800M, 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Began well, raced in 2nd, a length or so back, there to turn, kept on well to the line, always held.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 11 lengths back, closer on turn but still 7 lengths behind, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 lengths back, 2 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 900M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out approaching 500M, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out after passing 900M, 4 wide on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, one-paced in the run home.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on outer, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Taken back to race 3 wide behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 1100M, 1/2L back in the middle stages, retook the lead 500M, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Jumped only fairly, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back, 4 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place.

Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home to make frame without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well until no extra final 50M.
Out with rest, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began well from the widest draw, tracked leaders, 3 wide, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 650M, 3-1/2L back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running until approaching final 100M, made no impression thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, there to turn, made little progress early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1100M, led by 1/2L in the middle stages, headed 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted out at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd.
Made contact at start, raced in 2nd, a length or so back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.
Jumped well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, no clear run near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back to race at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, kept on same pace in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Showed speed at the start to lead early before being headed near the 850m & racing second thereafter. Regained lead near 250m mark & dug deep under hard riding to hold narrow advantage on line.

Raced on the leaders back around first bend before slightly further back in middle stages. Stayed along rail in the straight, made closing ground all the way to line but fell a Short Head behind on line when second.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover throughout. Continued to cover additional ground around bend, was the widest on straightening when 3L from lead, closed well to be beaten a length after tough passage.

Began fairly & was then bumped & consequently raced rearward. Improved slightly to be just worse than midfield between runners down back straight. Finished steadily in straight to finish 4th but well behind the first three.

Got back to race second last along the rail after the start. Shared last place around home bend, was 5L from the lead entering last section, stayed along rail in straight, past a few tiring rivals without threatening.
Taken back from the outside gate to race at the tail. Was over 5L from the lead entering last section when still last, only held margin in the straight & only beat two rivals home.

Began awkwardly, bumped rival & was consequently slow at start. Ridden forward around first bend to improve, taking lead passing 850m & crossing to rail near 600m. Surrendered lead at 250m, weakened out quickly thereafter.

Raced near the lead early before getting 1,1 momentarily down back straight. Was just over 2L from lead entering last section, asked for full effort on straightening but weakened badly in last furlong & was a distant last.
Sat towards rear 2 wide, showed some dash over the final 75M, closed off strongly.
Sat handy on the rail, traveled smoothly, made some progress inside 150M, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Sat midfield 3 wide, made up ground inside 150M, ran on evenly.
Lead throughout, responded fairly when asked, closed off fairly.
Slow to jump, sat rear, responded nicely in the Straight when asked, finished off okay.
Settled worse than midfield, traveled fairly, no clear run over the concluding stages and steadied.
Settled worse than midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, limited response when asked (Substantial blood in horse' trachea).
Ridden along to chase the lead, weakened entering the Straight, could not be ridden out thereafter (See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, failed to respond under pressure (See Incident Report).
Settled in front of midfield, improved into narrow run and made contact with a runner, crowded shortly after, no impression (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide throughout, was bumped in the early Straight and faded.

Veered outwards at start & hampered a number of rivals, improved position to be three wide outside leaders before shifting two wide outside leader from 750m. Moved to lead at 275m pulled away to win softly.

Raced on the leaders back early & continued to get soft run along rail throughout. Got clear running up the inside in straight, moved to second approaching 100m mark, finished clear of third, no match for impressive winner.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined in the lead by the winner near the 275m, battled well, continued in second until near the 100m mark, held well beaten third on the line.

Began only fairly & raced just worse than midfield along the rail. Moved slightly closer to lead approaching home corner, entered last section 4L from lead, passed a few rivals when making some late headway, well held 4th.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Was only 2.5L from the lead at the 400m mark, stayed along rail in straight, finished off only fairly to the line.

Pushed forward, raced outside the lead in the early stages before being crossed and racing 1,1 from about the 750m. Was only just behind the lead on straightening but only battled on one paced in last furlong.

Was trapped racing three wide in midfield and was then left wide & without cover from the 800m mark. Was only 2.5L from the lead entering last section, tried hard in the straight but wide run took its toll in the last 100m.

Steadied from widest gate & take back around first bend. Veered outwards near 900m when being steadied to race third last. Continued near the back on straightening before making some ground when finishing off out wide late.

Badly crowded & hampered at start before obtaining position just worse than midfield away from rail. Improved to midfield in middle stages, came wider near 400m when just under 4L from lead, failed to finish off in straight.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Was 3L from the lead entering last section, had clear running on straightening, did little in the straight and was beaten 5L into third last.

Was badly crowded & checked soon after the start, consequently losing ground & then racing second last. Raced along the rail when 6L from the lead passing 400m mark, made no headway in straight but had some excuse.

Badly crowded between runners & lost ground after start. Shifted across sharply, became extremely unbalanced, nearly dislodged rider & lost ground when striking rail 1000m mark. Never in the race after incident. See report.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well until 100M, headed approaching 50M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start, positioned 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, no clear run early in straight, raced tight near 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Knuckled over shortly after the start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, 2 wide after passing 400M, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with no cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped well, settled behind the leaders 2 wide, switched out at 400M, closed off nicely in the Straight, won cozily.
Settled near midfield 2 wide between horses, stayed on nicely for 2nd, no threat to winner.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, ran on okay despite the tough trip.
Settled midfield on the rail, slightly held up in the early part of the Straight, made some good late ground once in the clear.
Steadied after the start, sat last, made its run along the rail, just one pace. (See Incident Report)
Sat box-seat, showed some dash early on in the Straight, but weakened final 150M. (See Incident Report)
Not the quickest out, sat at the rear 2 wide, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Showed good early speed to lead, weakened in the Straight.
Raced keenly early, sat outside lead, gave ground in the Straight.
Settled mostly in 4th or 5th some 2L back, soon came to challenge in straight and hit the front 200 metres out, won readily.
Settled in worse than midfield near the rail in 9th or 8th, angled out for a run entering straight, ran on to be nearest at finish despite having to be straightened 200 metres out.
Settled in last few from a wide draw and waited with, saved ground on inside turning for home, switched out for a run on straightening, ran on without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in midfield to home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled not far off near the rail, obtained clear run on rail 250 metres out, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Travelled wide without cover in first few, pressed forward in back straight to take up running inside the 800 metres, led until finding no extra shortly after straightening.
Broke well from a poor draw, hampered 1400 metres out before travelling keenly in mid-division, wide into home straight, made no further impression.
Trailed the field most of the way after beginning from the widest draw, ran on past well-beaten horses in home straight.
Well there to the 150 metres and weakened. Jockey reported horse travelled keenly.
Never better than midfield, made no impression in home straight.
Travelled wide in last few, widest into home straight, made no further impression.
Led until headed leaving 800 metres, folded up quickly upon straightening.
Went forward under 10lb claimer, tracked leader from 1400M, took over top of straight, quickly sprinted clear and was well in control final stages.
Tracked leaders in a slowly run race, close enough turning for home, soon moved up to 2nd, tried hard but couldn't get closer to the winner.
Soon crossed to the fence, held up towards the rear in a slowly run race, 5Ls to make up 400M, ran home mildly down the inside, got up for non-threatening 3rd late.
Settled 4th, moved closer to leaders passing halfway but raced wide no cover from 650M, only battled over final 400M, no threat to the winner.
Settled down midfield and saved ground along the fence throughout, kept on evenly under top weight but couldn't quicken to challenge leaders.
Caught 3 deep early stages before slotting into a 2-wide spot in midfield, little change at the turn, ran home one paced.
Restrained after the start, held up behind midfield, wide into straight, made limited progress only.
Jumped on terms, maintained a position just ahead of midfield, inconvenienced 200M by a weakening rival, ran home one paced.
Settled near last in a slowly run race, wide into straight but failed to finish off. (Jockey : disadvantaged by settling back in the field with the early stages of the race slower than standard.)
Jumped only fairly, positioned ahead of midfield, caught wide no cover from 1200M to 800M, hard pressed home turn but couldn't go on with his challenge. (Jockey could offer no explanation.)
From wide draw taken across behind runners, raced as the back-marker over 10Ls off the pace on settling, failed to respond under pressure 500M out. Never involved.
Sent forward and enjoyed an uncontested lead, headed passing 400M, no extra and weakened to last. (Jockey : asked to take up a forward position with his mount stepping up in distance.)
Average to begin, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began smartly, raced prominently early, slightly taken back after passing 1000M, positioned in 4th, 2 wide in the middle stages, commenced move 400M, finished off well to take 2nd.

Made contact shortly after start, raced prominently on the inside, raced 1-2Ls behind the leader in the middle stages, showed good response in straight, took the lead 75M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Began well from gate 11, raced better than midfield but trapped wide early, sent forward after entering the back straight, 2nd in the middle stages, kept on well in straight, always just held.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 850M, led by 2 lengths turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 75M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield but 3 wide, 2 wide from 500M, 5 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left front leg.)
Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail 500M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made little progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, bumped 300M, made some progress in the run home.
Crowded shortly after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, bumped early in straight, ran on same pace to the line. (Bled.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
