Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to race prominently, shared lead from 850M, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, kept on well in straight, just held on.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 450M, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly, just beaten by a nose.
Bumped shortly after start, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, finished off strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well to make frame, not quite able to challenge.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, dropped towards rear after passing 500M, made some progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Away with them, raced better than midfield, 2 wide, 3Ls back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 400M, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the outside, 6-1/2L back turning in, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival from 850M, hard ridden from 400M, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened 200M, eased final 100M.
Slow into stride settling in midfield, saved ground turning in for home, responded well inside final 200 metres to snatch victory final strides.
Settled in 4th on rail, gained 3rd passing the 800 metres, ran on under pressure only to be overshadowed by the winner final strides
Soon took up running from a wide draw, obtained rails run in front passing the 800 metres, kicked over 2L clear 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort and collared final strides.
Jumped fairly settling in midfield, covered ground widest turning in for home, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Began moderately, travelled wide without cover in midfield or slightly worse, produced good late impression in the run to the line.
Inconvenienced at start, travelled wide in last few, switched near rail for a run entering home straight, made good impression inside final 200 metres.
Broke well before taking back to share early pace, shifted further back to 2L 3rd into home bend and 4th into straight, made no further impression.
Slowly away travelling well behind, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Slowly away travelling well behind, made modest progress past well-beaten horses in straight.
Well there to straight, dropped out tamely. (Blood in trachea)
Travelled wide without cover in midfield, folded up quickly inside final 300 metres.
Never better than midfield, weakened inside final 250 metres.
Chased the lead, improved to take the lead rounding the Turn, traveled nicely, kept on well to win.
Sat midfield, steadied in the early Straight, made good progress over the final 100M, closed off nicely.
Settled behind midfield, traveled strongly, switched out entering the Straight, responded well when asked.
Settled rear, commenced to improve making the turn but held up until near the 450M, made good progress after obtained clear running.
Sat handy on the rail, was bumped near the 500M, ran on evenly to the line (Dropped whip).
Settled in front of midfield, minor progress made in the Straight, ran on okay.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, switched out in the Straight, ran on fairly.
Sat midfield, traveled only fairly, did not show much response when asked (Substantial amount of mucus in trachea, Disappointing performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear on the rail, weakened in the early Straight, no impression.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards rear, steadied near the 1000M, never a danger.
Settled in front of midfield, weakened notably in the Straight, never a threat (Irregular heart rhythm, Must BT).
Ridden along to lead, weakened notably inside 200m, faded gradually.

Raced in midfield away from the rail. Moved into the three wide line with cover near 850m, was four wide with cover from 600m, dashed strongly after straightening to charge to lead at 300m mark & pulled away to win easily.

Drifted back to race 4th last away from the rail. Moved into three wide line with cover near 600m, wider again on straightening, was under 3L from the lead entering last section before closing to second place in last 100m.

Raced in midfield along the rail before improving to race on the leaders back from the 800m. Moved over the leaders heals near 350m, battled on nearer to the inside to finish third but was well behind easy winner.

Steadied after start, raced worse than midfield. Improved along the rail to midfield from the 900m. Was held up for a run for the first half of the straight before shifting out at the 250m & finishing off steadily late.

Raced 1,1 early before over-racing in the middle stages & being relegated a pair further back after 1000m mark. Lost position approaching corner, was held up from on straightening until 300m before finishing one paced late.

Steadied & taken back to share last place. Shifted very wide passing the 500m when still rearward, was the widest runner on straightening, hampered near 250m before passing a few tiring rivals when running onto midfield.

Had no early speed & was ridden along after start to hold position third last. Stayed nearer the inside on straightening, held up until 300m, checked to avoid heels near the 250m, passed a few late but was never likely.

Raced three wide in midfield early, hampered near 950m before racing four wide without cover from 800m. Close behind on straightening, dashed well to take lead 325m, hung inwards, passed by winner 300m, weakened quickly late.

Began only fairly & shifted back to share last place. Stayed close to rail on straightening when still rearward, held up until shifting outwards at 350m, continued to shift outwards mid-straight, finished very one paced late.
Raced prominently early, challenged for lead before being crowded near the 900m mark & then racing 1,1. Was ridden along before straightening, weakened out in final 300m & was beaten over 7L.
Pushed forward to narrowly hold lead throughout middle stages. Emptied at the 300m mark & weakened poorly thereafter.

Raced wide with cover in midfield early before making mid-race move to get three wide outside the leaders from the 800m. Close to lead on straightening, was checked approaching 300m & lost ground, weakened poorly thereafter.

Improved position after the start, was three wide without cover on speed before improving and crossing to be outside leader from the 1000m mark. Was beaten on straightening, weakened poorly in final section, long second last.

Raced forward from widest gate, was four wide outside leaders early before getting some cover near 800m. Began weakening through the field from the 700m, was already last on straitening before tailing out to be distanced.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, kept on very well in straight and scored. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Average to begin, positioned 4 to 5 lengths behind the leader, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide towards rear, 2 wide from 800M, 5 lengths or so back turning in, closed off well to make frame.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length or so back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, found rail near 800M, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, read at rear on the outside, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Bumped start, tracked leaders on the outside, 2 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Roarer.)
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after start, raced in midfield on the outside, dropped towards rear 600M, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened 300M, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke nicely, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled comfortably throughout, switched out in the Straight, closed off well, won decisively.
Jumped well and ridden along to hold a forward spot, kept on nicely, no match for winner.
Settled behind the leader on the rail, held up early part of the Straight, ran on nicely when in the clear.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, had trouble obtaining clear run early, stayed on well along the rail final 250M.
Settled towards the rear, held up in the Straight, made very good progress late. (See Incident Report)
Sat midfield 2 wide, made some ground early but one pace to the line.
Sat last despite being ridden along early, stayed on nicely final 150M.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, limited response in the Straight.
Hard ridden early to assume the lead, weakened in the Straight.
Settled towards the rear, made no impression.
Sat midfield on the rail, limited response when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Made all kicking over 2L clear 200 metres out, won cosily.
Settled in midfield, ran on steadily in straight without threatening.
Well there on rail, in box seat turning for home, kept on steadily for a placing but never threatening. (Lame next day)
Jumped awkwardly and jockey unbalanced, travelled wide without cover in prominent positions sharing 3rd into straight, kept on before finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Shared 1L 2nd 3-wide without cover, commenced move rounding home bend joining race leader eventual winner briefly entering home straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 150 metres
Crowded at start but soon recovered to midfield, kept on before making late impression closing stages.
Taken well back from a poor draw, fought on under pressure in the run to the line.
Settled towards rear, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Well there, shifted back to 2L 4th coming onto home bend and 5th into straight, faded gradually under pressure.
Travelled wide without cover in last few after beginning from a poor draw, made no impression in home straight.
Jumped awkwardly, always well behind and never seen with a chance. (Mucus)
Blundered and lost ground at start, travelled in last few on rail saving ground on final turn, soon faded after straightening. (Blood in trachea)
Away with them, travelled 3-wide ahead of midfield, lost cover from 900M, worked into the race well 400M, quickened to challenge for the lead mid-straight, asserted final 100M.
From draw 14 pressed forward before moving across to track leader 2-wide, went head-to head with eventual winner from 200M, fought hard but was outbattled late.
Up with early pace before sitting back in midfield passing 900M, had difficulty obtaining clear running inside 400M, closed off well under top weight after 300M. Nearest finish.
Jumped only fairly, reserved behind midfield along the fence, steadied near 300M before finishing the race nicely.
Raced keenly middle stages with blinkers applied, raced in mid-division throughout, kept on moderately over final 400M, not reach first three.
On jumping blundered then became badly unbalanced, ended up racing at the rear, brought wide into straight before closing off well down outside. (Roarer.)
Sent forward, crossed to the lead 950M, fought hard to hold off rivals early straight, headed inside 200M, weakened to 7th.
Away well enough from draw 2, settled down midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, kept on one paced final 400M and was never dangerous.
Pressed along from the start to maintain a position behind midfield, wide no cover from 800M, lacked a finishing kick when asked and was safely held in the end.
Jumped only fairly, settled near last, 5Ls to make up top of straight but didn't get the clearest of paths over final 300M. Could do better.
Up with early pace before taking a trailing spot behind leaders, failed to find more on straightening and gave ground passing 250M.
Ridden quietly near the rear, under the pump 550M but responded only fairly. Never a threat to leaders.
Moved up to race prominently behind leaders, found nothing when asked top of straight, soon out of contention. (Jockey : obliged to make early use and not able to finish the race off.)
Taken back from draw 13 to be racing towards the rear, wide on the turn, was closing off fairly when steadied 200M, eased.
Began well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 500M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Slowly away, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Commenced well, raced in 3rd, a length or so back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Taken back to race towards rear on the outside, commenced move 500M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, nearest on line.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off well without threatening.
Away well, raced in 2nd, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 400M, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, hard ridden after passing 350M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared near 200M, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, unable to obtain clear run in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (Lame left hind leg next day morning.)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened 250M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Mucus.)
Jumped well, tracked leaders, 2 wide, angled out 450M, hard ridden 350M, showed very good response in straight, finished off very strongly to score. (Lame right hind leg next day morning.)
Away well, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, hard ridden 300M, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.

Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 5 lengths back, there to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to make frame without threatening. (Lame left front leg next day.)

Slowly away, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1100M, led by 3/4L in the middle stage, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced in midfield on outer, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back to race towards rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, same margin back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths or so back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield but trapped 3 wide, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 250M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1100M, 2nd in the middle stages, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on outer, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Jumped well, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 400M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back to race at rear on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 650M, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.

Slowly away, raced in midfield on the outside, sent forward after entering the back straight, took the lead 700M, led by 1-3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 2-1/2L back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 900M, moved closer after passing 850M, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the inside, commenced move approaching 600M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, commenced move 450M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Slow to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, one-paced in the run home.

Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1300M, led by a length, headed 700M, 1-3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.

Jumped well, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, no clear run until final 100M, one-paced thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, took the early lead, headed near 1300M, positioned a length or so back in the middle stages, peaked on turn, weakened 150M, eased final 50M. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Driven forward and led uncontested, skipped away inside 300M, soon opened up a big margin on the rest, eased towards the finish
Showed customary early speed to be tracking leader (eventual winner), no match for that rival passing 250M but fought hard to hold 2nd spot.
Away only fairly, recovered to race behind midfield, on straightening ran home evenly along the fence to claim a distant 3rd.
Jumped on terms, raced along the fence in a midfield position, kept trying final 300M but never going the pace to challenge the runaway winner.
From wide draw pressed forward to be tracking the pace, close enough turning in but got home only fairly.
Soon towards the rear, quietly ridden, 7Ls to make up 400M, made up some ground final 300M, not beaten far by the minor placegetters.
Jumped only fairly, soon outpaced and detached, had the job ahead top of the straight but only ran past beaten horses.
Bumped heavily on jumping, in midfield 5Ls off the pace, gave limited response final 300M. Never threatened.
Chased leaders, unbalanced 600M and lost ground, couldn't keep up 250M, dropped away.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, couldn't go on from top of straight, weakened.
From draw 10 caught wide early stages, towards the rear and didn't travel after taken wider by rival 550M, finished off the race in a disappointing manner. (Roarer.)
Maintained a position behind midfield, hung out across the heels of rival 550M and was severely checked, fell back to last and out of contention. (Racing manners unacceptable.)
Settled in front of midfield, traveled strongly, made good progress in the Straight, closed off nicely.
Sat midfield 3 wide, responded well when asked over the final 200M, finished off nicely.
Jumped only fairly, settled worse than midfield on the rail, commenced to improve inside 700M, ran on evenly.
Sat in front of midfield, was crowded and checked near the 600M, ran on okay.
Settled worse than midfield, limited response when asked in the Straight, closed off fairly.
Crowded after the Start, settled behind midfield, was checked near the 600M, no clear run until 250M, proved difficult to ride out.
Sat handy, weakened notably near the 150M, no impression (See Incident Report).
Ridden along to lead, weakened notably in the Straight, gradually faded.
Stumbled on jumping, sat rear, raced rear, never a danger.
Settled handy, slightly weakened rounding the Turn, no clear run in the early Straight, could not be ridden out (See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, steadied when positioned close to a runner rounding the Turn, was held up and no clear running over the concluding stages.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide, hung out near the 600M, weakened notably in the Straight, no contention.
Got a nice position 1,1. Eased three wide passing the 500m, dashed strongly to lead at 200m before pulling away to win easily.
Pushed forward from widest gate to race outside the leader. Shared lead near 200m, battled on well to hold second on line but was no match for easy winner.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Came off the rail near the 400m, finished steadily to hold well beaten third.
Pushed forward to lead. Joined near the 200m, weakened slightly in late stages, was a length behind second on line.
Had a nice run on the leaders back throughout. Stayed along the rail in straight but failed to challenge, weakening a few lengths to be beaten nearly 4L in midfield.

Raced in midfield away from the rail & galloped between rivals from the 850m. Had clear running on straightening but finished off only moderately, weakening about a length to be beaten 4L into midfield.

Drifted back after first bend to race just worse than midfield between runners. Just under 5L from lead entering last section, moved into clear running on straightening, finished off fairly, holding margin in straight.

Shifted back after the start & raced at the tail. Was last and over 6L from the lead entering last section, passed a couple of weakening rivals in the straight but was never in a threatening position.

Was shifted back behind runners from gate 11 & raced third last along the rail in the middle stages. Was 5.5L from lead entering last section, stayed along the rail in the straight & despite having clear running did little.

Bumped at the start before steadying around first bend & being taken back to second last. Continued rearward, shifted out to be the widest runner on straightening, failed to run on (Blood in trachea & epiglottic entrapment).

Bumped at the start, steadied when wide around the first bend, was hampered near 900m mark before continuing to race three wide with cover in midfield. Was the second widest on straightening, weakened to be well beaten.

Checked when crowded at start, four wide around first bend, improved to midfield when 3 wide without cover. Raced slightly keen in middle stages & hung outwards around bend, was beaten on straightening & weakened to last.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, a length behind the leader, easy run to turn, took the lead 300M, kept on strongly to the line, won very comfortably, impressive.
Bumped on jumping, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 450M, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside early, found rail after passing 800M, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.

Moderately away, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, 3 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final 200M, unacceptable performance.
Jumped okay, settled midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely in the Straight, won comfortably.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, made a mid-race move at 800M, sat outside the lead at 550M, kept on nicely. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, raced a bit ungenerously down the back Straight, angled out in the Straight, ran on fairly well, closest finish.
Settled behind the leaders, showed some dash early in the Straight, one pace final furlong.
Showed good early speed to lead, being challenged on the lead throughout, kept on until weakened final 150M.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Not the quickest out, shifted in towards the rail shortly after the start, settled at the rear, made some progress along the rail, nothing impressive.
Settled midfield on the rail, limited response in the Straight.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Sat towards the rear, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Sat just behind the leaders, weakened and faded in the Straight. (Unacceptable Performance, must trial) (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide no cover early, stride forward to sit outside the lead, weakened rounding the Home Turn. (Unacceptable Performance, must trial)
Restrained in last few from a poor draw and waited with, wide most of the way and widest into straight, ran on strongly down the centre of the track to snatch victory final strides.
Jumped well before gradually settling in midfield on rail, slightly further off the lead around home bend, ran on well in straight to hit the front only to be caught final strides.
Settled well behind from a wide draw, saved ground turning in for home, inconvenienced 200 metres out, finished off the race well.
Pressed forward from a poor draw, used wide around first home bend to take up running turning into back straight, obtained rails run 600 metres out, led until swamped inside final 150 metres.

Well there on the rail early settling over 2L back in 4th on rail, slightly further off the pace at around the 800 metres, saved ground turning in for home but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Pressed forward to soon join the leaders, restrained one-out-one-back for cover turning into back straight, held every chance upon straightening but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Never better than midfield, saved ground turning in for home, briefly baulked for a run on rail 200 metres out, finished off the race nicely.
Never better than midfield, tight between runners upon straightening, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled at the back from the widest draw, went wide rounding home bend but baulked behind runners early in straight, finished off the race well inside final 100 metres.
Travelled in midfield in 5th about 4L off the pace, came under pressure rounding home bend, unable to quicken under pressure in straight.
Jumped awkwardly from a poor draw, travelled awkwardly wide in midfield around first bend, slightly worse in back straight and one of the widest on the home turn, made no further impression.
Soon took up running, ceded advantage early in back straight, badly bumped and unbalanced over 220 metres out and dropped out tamely. (Lame)
Never far off from leaders, 4th on settling, worked into the race well passing 400M, challenged strongly for the lead 200M, gamely prevailed.
Moved forward to be pressing leader, took over early straight, fought hard final 200M but couldn't hold off winner late, held on for 2nd in a photo.
Settled behind midfield 6-7Ls off a slow pace, brought wide on straightening then closed off nicely under top weight, nearest finish.
Tracked leaders in a slowly run race, held up briefly inside 400M, kept battling in the straight and was still in contention 100M from home, held by leaders late.
From wide draw switched off to race towards the rear in a slowly run race, 6Ls to make up 400M, finished off the race mildly but was always held by leaders.
Shifted out at the start and was bumped, restrained to race in midfield, driven along 450M, was staying on mildly when held up behind leaders over final 100M. Could do better.
Jumped fairly and settled at the rear further back than intended, little change at the turn, failed to make up appreciable ground in the straight. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)
From wide draw taken back to near last for cover, raced keenly due to slow pace, made some progress final 300M but never a winning hope
Emerged as leader 1200M, set slow pace to straight, headed inside 300M then faded towards the finish.
From wide draw switched off to the rear, over 9Ls off the slow pace in middle stages, big task ahead 400M, made some late progress.
Maintained a position ahead of midfield, close enough turning in but couldn't sustain run final 200M.
Jumped fairly, settled down midfield and had a ground saving trip, couldn't go on passing 300M, weakened to last.
Fast into stride, took the early lead, headed approaching 900M, 2nd in the middle stages, easy run to turn, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out 350M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, 4 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight, took 3rd on line.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to make frame, always held.
Away with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, made some headway in straight.
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after the start and became unbalanced, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide from 500M, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Out with rest, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 900M, led by 1-3/4L turning in, peaked early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened final 100M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.

Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight, won comfortably.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on same pace to the line.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.

Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, unable to obtain clear running until approaching final 100M, made some progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Began smartly, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 900M, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on outer, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 4 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority of the race, hard ridden after passing 350M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 700M, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, checked 150M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide towards rear, 2 wide from 800M, 5-1/2L back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Had a nice run third on rail, three or 4 lengths from leader who went clear in first half before improving onto leaders back from the 700m. Brushed with rival 225m before closing well to steal lead in final few strides.

Ridden forward to lead, held 2L advantage over nearest rival in middle stages before having rival at his quarters from the 650m. Was still a length clear at furlong, tried hard but just caught in final few strides.

Drifted back after the start & raced worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Was wider again from 600m, was the widest on straightening when about 6L from lead before finishing strongly down the outside late.

Raced a clear second after the start when following the leader who went clear. Improved to race at leaders' quarters from 650m, continued to hold second place until 225m where he brushed rival, battled on to be beaten 2L.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Eased wider just prior to straightening, entered last section 4.5L from the lead, closed steadily all the way to just miss 4th on the line.
Got caught racing three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Eased wider on straightening when just over 3L from lead, finished off steadily in the straight to hold midfield finish.

Got a nice position fourth away from the rail after start and then raced 1,1 from about the 900m. Bumped heavily on straightening, was 3L from the lead entering last section, battled on to finish in a bunch in midfield.

Steadied after first 100m & raced just worse than midfield between runners. Was rearward on straightening when just under 6L from the lead before finishing off fairly late to finish in a bunch in midfield.

Limited pace after start & got back to race just worse than midfield along the rail. Improved to midfield in middle stages, steadied near the 650m, moved away from rail near the 500m, finished off steadily to midfield late.

Was slow to begin, was shifted down to rail and raced third last along the inside in the middle stages. Was 5.5L from the lead entering last section, finished off only fairly nearer to the inside in the concluding stages.

Drifted back after the start & raced second last away from the rail. Moved wider on the track passing the 600m, was just under 7L from the lead on straightening, passed only one or two tiring rivals in the straight.

Was trapped racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Moved closer to lead after the 800m when continuing wide, bumped heavily on straightening when only 2.5L from the lead, emptied at 200m, over-run late.
Shifted back from the widest gate at raced at the tail. Continued last and 7L from lead on straightening, did little in the straight & was never a factor.

Shifted down to the rail soon after the start & improved after first furling to race in midfield. Was under 4L from the lead entering last section when continuing along rail but weakened poorly in final 250m & finished last.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, traveled nicely, made good ground inside 150M, kept on well to win.
Ridden along to lead on the rail, traveled comfortably, finished off nicely.
Settled midfield, raced wide from 900M, responded well inside 100M.
Chased the leader 2 wide, made some ground in the early Straight, but slightly weakened over the concluding stages.
Settled handy on the rail, traveled okay, no clear run until 200M, ran on evenly.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, responded okay when asked inside 100M (Bled, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Settled behind midfield, traveled fairly, one pace to the line.
Settled towards rear on the rail, minor progress made in the Straight, closed off fairly.
Bumped at the Start, sat midfield, weakened notably entering the Straight (Bled, Must BT).
Bumped at the Start, sat midfield 2 wide, no clear run in the Straight, could not be fully tested (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards rear 2 wide, had difficulty to obtain clear running in the early Straight, ran on fairly.
Settled midfield, traveled keenly in the early stages, limited response when asked.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, raced rear, no contention.
Sat worse than midfield, weakened passing 300M, never a threat.
Had a nice run on the leaders back from about the 1000m mark. Moved off the rail near the 600m, moved to lead approaching the furlong pole, went on to win by over a length.
Raced in midfield between runners. Was ridden along before straightening, entered last section just under 5L from lead, closed well to second passing the 150m mark, finished clear of third.

Steadied & taken back to race near the tail along the inside. Moved away from the rail near the 500m, wider again on cornering, was over 6L from the entering last section before making good late ground down the outside late.
Got back to race at the tail between runners. Shifted wider on straightened when second last and 7.5L from lead, made good late headway down the outside in final stages to finish fourth.

Had a soft run in midfield along the rail. Followed the leader on straightening when only 2L from the lead, shifted outwards approaching the 250m before weakening a length to be well held in midfield.
Had a nice run in midfield away from the rail. Eased wider just before straightening, was only 3.5L from lead entering last section, weakened in last furlong and was beaten 4L into midfield.
Was caught racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Was wider on straightening, was 4.5L from the lead entering last section and held that deficit all the way to the line.
Had a soft run-in midfield along the rail. Was just over 4L from the lead on straightening, weakened a length in the straight when finishing off nearer the rail. Never a factor.

Raced just worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Was just over 5L from the lead on straightening, raced tight approaching 250m before being crowded and steadied near 150m, should have been closer.
Was crowded soon after the start before racing worse than midfield along the rail. Was 5.5L from the lead on straightening, made no headway in final section & was well held.
Pushed forward to lead. Was 1.5L clear of nearest rival entering last section, joined by winner at the 225m, weakened quickly in the concluding stages.
Got back to race three wide near the tail. Continued back and wide around bend, was the widest on straightening when 9L from the lead before failing to make any headway.

Drifted back after start, raced just worse than midfield between runners. Was keen in the middle stages when getting head up. Relegated to third last approaching bend, pushed wide from 500m, weakened poorly, long second last.

Ridden forward at start, contested lead early before racing outside the leader from 1200m. Raced in third place off the rail from the 900m. Was hard ridden from 550m, hung outwards on cornering before weakening badly to last.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, took the lead 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Bumped and unbalanced start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed approaching 200M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 600M, wider turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Out in line, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail near 600M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Mucus.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, peaked 400M, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke well, sat next to the leader 2 wide, kicked on in the Straight, kept on well to score.
Ridden along early to lead, being challenged throughout, kept on nicely, just held 2nd.
Settled midfield on the rail, angled out at 300M, closed off strongly, just missed 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, made good progress early in the Straight, one pace final 100M.
Hampered at the start, settled towards the rear on the rail, began to improve at the 500M, took time to obtain clear running, made good ground late.
Settled at the rear on the rail, stayed on fairly near the rail. (See Incident Report)
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide., only one pace when asked.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide with cover, ran on fairly. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, under pressure at 600M, picked off weakened rivals.
Settled towards the back of the field, never impress.
Jumped nicely, aggressively ridden to be prominent, weakened 250M, hampered inside 150M.
Sat the rear, limited response in the Straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide, never a factor.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, weakened in faded in the Straight.
Held up in last few, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, obtained clear passage over 300 metres out, ran on resolutely to snatch victory final strides.
Settled at the back from the widest draw and waited with, commenced move inside final 350 metres switching out for a run 200 metres out, ran home strongly but the post came too soon.
Set strong pace attempting to make all, drew over 4L clear rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres and caught close home.
Began well from a low draw before settling in 6th in midfield, became 5th about 8L off quickened pace around home bend, fought on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground before settling in worse than midfield near the rail, came under pressure from over 500 metres out, fought on steadily past well-beaten rivals.
Pressed forward from a wide draw settling one-one-out-back, chased over 4L behind leader rounding home bend, kept on until fading under pressure inside final 150 metres.
Soon settled in last few, obtained a run shortly after straightening, fought on steadily past well-beaten rivals late.
Travelled keenly in last few, pulled forward to 10th passing the 900 metres and further closer to 8th into straight, kept on same pace without quickening.

Pressed forward from a poor draw travelling wide in 4th around first bend, further adrift from quickened pace past middle stages, made some impression early in home straight but weakened inside final 150 metres.
Began fairly from the one draw gradually settling in midfield, came under pressure when pace quickened around home bend, ran home one-paced.
Settled in 3rd on rail not far off the pace, over 4L back from leader when pace quickened around home bend, dropped tamely out of contention inside final 300 metres.

Pressed forward from a poor draw travelling very wide in forward of midfield first bend, remained without cover in 5th most of back straight, further away from lead when pace quickened home bend, made no further impression
Never better than midfield, dropped to last few over half-way out.
Refused to settle when in midfield early stages, continued to travel keenly early in back straight, lost position approaching home bend and one of the widest entering home straight, never recovered.
Reserved in midfield, travelled well to straight, coasted up to them 300M before quickening up to take the lead inside 200M, kept battling late stages and just held on.
Settled towards the rear 6Ls back, worked into the race nicely passing 500M, found the line well but was just denied in a photo finish.
Jumped well, up with early pace before easing off to sit behind leaders, responded well when asked 300M, fought hard late stages but was held by first two towards the line.
From draw 1 moved up to chase leaders on inside, was held up from 400M-300M, chased only one-paced final stages and couldn't pose any threat on first 3.
Maintained a position in midfield 5Ls off the pace, had some work to do as they headed for home and the finishing effort was just moderate, never a threat to first three.
Jumped awkwardly, taken across from wide draw to race in mid-division, kept on without threat final 400M.
Rushed forward, vied for lead 3-wide, briefly in front near 250M, run ended 200M then weakened away.
Never far off from leaders, caught 3-wide from home turn, failed to finish off on straightening. (Jockey : instructed to take up a forward position from a wide draw.)
Went forward vying for the lead early and middle stages, couldn't go on passing 250M, faded away.
Bumped after the start, pressed forward and vied for lead on inside, couldn't hold off rivals passing 300M and was gone soon after. (Jockey : not suited by taken on in the lead. / Lame next day.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, detached in last, never in the picture.
Made contact at start, taken back to race towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out approaching 500M, raced tight 450M, not enough room early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Out in line, raced better than midfield on the inside, right behind the leader on turn, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the winner.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made minor progress after passing 200M, blocked final 50M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide on turn, no clear run early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Out with rest, sent forward to race in 2nd, peaked 500M, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the inside, easy run to turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 300M, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began well from a tricky gate, raced in midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 2-1/2L back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, not quite able to challenge.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly to take a place.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to make frame.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, angled out after passing 700M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight.

Jumped well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, a length back turning in, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until finish, coasted home.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run until approaching final 100M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, weakened inside final furlong.
Moderately away, sent forward to race in 2nd, 3/4L back turning in, showed some response early in straight, crowded near 250M, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, 6-1/2L back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 800M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, checked near 800M, 2 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened 300M, eased thereafter.

Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 800M, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1/2L back turning in, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Away well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, angled out 350M, bumped early in straight, finished off well to take a place.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced in midfield on the outside, a bit closer on turn, bumped early in straight, kept on well to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 400M, 3 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 50M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, no clear run final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 400M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 400M, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move 500M, bumped early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Broke well before settling just worse than midfield, commenced move passing the 600 metres and the widest rounding home bend, sustained effort in straight to snatch victory close to home.

Settled well behind from the widest draw and waited with, commenced move leaving the 800 metres joining race leaders 3-wide 450 metres out, hit the front shortly after straightening only to be caught close to home.
Settled in last few, commenced move rounding home bend, one of the widest onto final turn, ran on well under pressure down the centre of the track.
Settled in worse than midfield on rail, saved ground turning in for home, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Began well before settling in better than midfield in 5th or 4th on rail, came to challenge under pressure on top of home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled towards rear, saved ground making final turn, obtained run shortly after straightening and ran on steadily, never nearer.

Soon took up running narrowly, obtained rails run in front passing the 1600 metres before steadying up the pace, led until joined 500 metres out and headed on straightening, soon faded under pressure.

Amongst leaders early, taken back to joint 4th some 2L back first bend, shifted further back to 6th in midfield with one lap to go, renewed effort 600 metres out, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Began well from the one draw sharing early pace, taken one back on rail passing the 1600 metres, renewed effort home bend to re-join race leader into straight, found no extra after straightening.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield, improved to 1L 2nd rounding stables bend, came to join race leader over 500 metres out hitting front briefly upon straightening, folded up quickly.
Soon dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Pressed forward from a poor draw, taken back to 3rd for cover entering home straight the first time becoming 4th shortly after, found nothing under pressure inside final 550 metres.
Sat behind midfield, traveled comfortably, made good progress over the final 200M, finished off strongly.
Sat towards rear on the rail, no clear running until 150M, stayed on well to grab 2nd.
Settled handy, traveled nicely, responded well when asked inside 200M (See Incident Report).
Ridden hard to lead on the rail, weakened in the early Straight, closed off okay.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, ran on evenly.
Settled midfield, traveled okay, one pace to the line.
Settled midfield, over raced in the early stages, ran on fairly to the finish.
Settled towards rear, limited response when asked, never a threat.
Sat in front of midfield, slightly weakened passing 700M, no impression in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Chased the leader, weakened notably entering the Straight, never a danger (See Incident Report).
Raced rear, traveled only fairly, no contention.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail. Was in fourth place and just under 4L from the lead entering last section, closed well to charge to lead at 125m & drew away to win easily.

Bumped at the start before racing in midfield along the rail. Was over 5L from the lead entering last section, had clear running on straightening, closed steadily to improve to second passing 50m mark, no match for winner.

Bumped at start before drifting back at first bend & racing second last. Continued along rail entering last section when 8L behind, was under pressure before straightening, closed steadily along rail to steal third late.

Began well before steadying at first bend & coming back to race in midfield away from rail. Was 6.5L from lead near the 400m, pushed wider, was the widest runner on straightening before closing off ok down the outside late.

Got nice cover & raced 1,1 from about the 800m before continuing in third, stalking the leading pair in middle stages. Was just over 2L from lead entering last section, only battled in the straight & finished in midfield.

Raced close to lead after the jump, was third around first bend but raced slightly keenly. Raced slightly further back after the 850m mark, was 5L behind on straightening, closed steadily to midfield without threatening.
Began well & moved to lead. Was joined & headed by the winner near the 125m, weakened three lengths in the final 100m & could only finish seventh.

Jumped inwards at start, was wide around first bend before improving position to get outside the leader from the 850m. Challenged for lead momentarily in middle stages, peaked on run at the 150m & weakened thereafter.

Bumped at the start before steadying near the 1000m mark & getting position just worse than midfield away from the rail. Was over 8L from the lead entering last section, made some ground in straight but was still ninth.

Bumped at the start before drifting back to race rearward at first bend & then relegated to second last near 550m. Nearly 10L from lead entering last section, came wider in the straight, halved margin but finished third last.

Steadied on jumping & shifted across behind runners to race third last along rail. Made some headway along rail in middle stages, shifted away from rail nearing 400m mark, did nothing in the straight & finished second last.

Veered outwards on jumping, raced wide around first bend & was steadied to come back and race at the tail. Continued at the back approaching home corner when about 10L from lead, did nothing in the straight & was last.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear, moved a bit closer after passing 550M, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, finished off well to take 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, commenced move 500M, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest finish.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside, commence move 400M, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame, nearest on line.

Away well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1100M, headed 800M, 2nd on turn, retook the lead 300M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide from 400M, made little progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide approaching 400M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, took the early lead, headed near 1100M, retook the lead 800M, led narrowly on turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final 150M. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Commence well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, 2 to 3 lengths back in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final 150M.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, unable to maintain position 600M, dropped to last on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, trapped wide in midfield, no cover throughout, weakened 400M, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, settled midfield on the rail, closed off strongly to score cozily.
Broke alertly, ridden along early, sat on pace, improved to sit outside the leader at 550M, kept on nicely. (See Incident Report)
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, angled out in the Straight, made good progress.
Not the quickest out, showed good speed to be prominent, ran on okay.
Jumped a step slow, settled towards the rear on the rail, improved between horses near the rail into the Straight, showed some dash early in the Straight, one pace final 100M. (See Incident Report)
Taken back from the start to sit at the rear, raced keenly, stayed on fairly.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Settled towards the rear, made little impression.
Sat 3 wide midfield with cover, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Jumped nicely, settled just behind the leaders, weakened in the Straight.
Showed good early speed to lead, weakened and faded in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, under pressure for the majority of the race, no response, never involved. (Performance disappointing, must trial) (See Incident Report)
Settled not far off the pace in one-out-one-back position, fought on under pressure to gain upper hand about 50 metres out.
Ridden positively from the widest draw to eventually obtain rails run in front over 700 metres out, held 1L advantage on straightening only to be collared 50 metres out.
Settled in midfield on rail, angled out for a run entering straight, shifted back to inside shortly after straightening, fought on steadily without threatening.
Travelled well there from a poor draw, in 2nd just outside race leader rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort on straightening.
Soon dropped to last few despite ridden along on rail, saved ground turning in for home, fought on steadily under pressure in closing stages without threatening.
Slowly away, soon recovered towards rear in 9th, saved ground turning in for home, produced moderate late impression inside final 100 metres.
Settled at the back and waited with, saved ground turning in for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well before settling in midfield, kept on at the one pace straight without threatening.
Travelled 3-wide without cover in 5th in better than midfield, ran home one-paced.
Travelled wide without cover in last few after beginning from a poor draw, gained midfield onto first bend, ran home one-paced down the centre of the track.
Gradually settled in in last few after beginning from a poor draw, one of the widest turning in for home, found nil.
Well there settling one back in 3rd or 4th on rail, soon weakened from a similar position turning in for home.
Chased the pace, travelled well during race and loomed large top of the straight, wrestled the lead inside 200M, kicked on strongly to win with something in hand.
Jumped awkwardly, maintained a midfield position along the fence, gave good response early straight, tried hard to close the gap on leader over final 250M but was always held.
Reserved near last 6Ls off the pace, became the back-marker passing 700M, closed off final 300M with some effect, got up for 3rd late but not reach first two.
Went forward setting a steady pace in the lead, joined by eventual winner 200M, run ended 150M, got tired towards the finish.
Taken across from wide draw early stages, settled in last until 700M, widest turning home, ran on mildly final 300M, no threat to first two
Jumped awkwardly, settled down behind mid-division, held up for clear running 300M then got to the line only fairly. Never threatened.
Moved up to track leader, under pressure 550M, lost 2nd 300M, no extra 150M and faded away.
Chased leaders in a 3-wide position without cover, couldn't go on 300M and weakened away.
Caught racing 3-wide in midfield on settling, little change to the turn, couldn't accelerate enough when driven inside 400M, never a threat to leaders.
Jumped awkwardly, soon towards the rear, driven 400m but failed to respond. (Bled.)
Positioned ahead of midfield, under the pump passing 600M, soon couldn't keep up with leaders and out of contention.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 850M, led by 2 lengths on turn, kicked clear early in straight, ran on very well to the line and scored. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced in midfield, found rail near 800M, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced better than midfield but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from 800M, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Crowded start, raced towards rear, difficult to settle in the early stages, 8 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after the start and became unbalanced, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Away with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, kept on same pace in the run home.
Taken back to race 2 wide, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Began well from gate 1, took the early lead, headed near 850M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, still well back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
