Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide after passing 700M, 2-1/2L back turning in, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Taken back from gate 12, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 3/4L back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 600M, 4-1/2L back turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, moved closer after passing 700M, 5 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Out in line, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well, taken back to race behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, weakened final 450M, eased early in straight. (Lame right front leg.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped on terms, maintained a midfield position 3Ls off the pace, responded well to riding early straight, challenged strongly for the lead 150M before gaining the upper hand final 50M.
Chased leaders, worked into the race well 400M, hit the front 200M, couldn't hold off winner final stages.
Restrained after the jump, soon towards the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, closed off final 400M fastest making up stack of ground to claim 3rd.
Not hurried after the start, taken back to near last 8Ls off the pace, little change to the turn, finished off well on straightening to take 4th but could not threaten first three.
Crowded on jumping then taken back to last from wide draw, had 8Ls to make up 400M, closed off well but too much to do.
Pressed forward, crossed over to track leader before entering the turn, briefly threatened 300M, peaked on its run 200M, lost several places towards the finish.
From draw 1 jumped only fairly, recovered to race in midfield, switched away from fence 450M, failed to pick up pace. (Jockey offered no excuse for his horse's failure to finish the race off.)
Chased leaders on inside, raced keenly early stages, lacked a finishing response passing 400M, outpaced by rivals late stages. (had some difficulty obtaining clear running 150M.)
Crossed to a 3-wide spot in midfield, no cover from 850M, failed to make up ground on leaders over final 400M. Never threatened.
Jumped awkwardly and blundered after the start, raced 3-wide behind midfield, gave limited response passing 400M, got home only fairly.
Maintained a position just ahead of midfield, closed off only fairly passing 400M, never a threat to leaders.
Settled down midfield 2-wide, held up briefly 400M but failed to quicken after. Never involved.
Hampered shortly after the start, bustled along to maintain a rearward position, couldn't go on from 400M.
Jumped awkwardly, soon moved up to lead, headed inside 250M, weakened rapidly final stages. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped nicely, ridden along to lead, traveled strongly, responded well over the final 150M to win.
Sat midfield, raced tight near the 1100M, made good progress inside 100M.
Sat towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, stayed on well to grab 3rd (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, chased the lead throughout, slightly weakened entering the Straight, ran on evenly.
Sat rear, raced rear throughout, made minor progress inside 100M, ran on fairly.
Sat in front of midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, failed to respond when asked (See Incident Report).
Settled behind midfield, traveled only fairly, weakened and faded quickly passing 150M.

Didn't have the early speed of others, got back to worse than midfield along stand side rail. Was held up until the 300m before dashing along outside rail, finished strongly in final 150m to charge to lead inside last 50m.
Bumped at the start after veering outwards before racing in midfield. Improved position between runners approaching 400m, shared lead fleetingly approaching 50m mark before over-run in late stages.

Raced just forward of midfield nearer to the center of the track. Continued close to lead near 400m, came under pressure soon after, battled on well in late stage to narrowly hold third place on line.

Raced in midfield when galloping nearest to the center of the track. Was just under 2L from the lead entering last section, finished off well all the way to be beaten a similar margin into fourth on line.

Raced a length from the lead in early stages before improving position to take a narrow lead approaching half-way. Continued to hold narrow lead until the 125m mark, battled on ok thereafter & wasn't beaten far.

Raced close to the lead after start when galloping one horse in from the outside rail. Was just over a length from lead entering last section, tried hard all the way to the line, beaten just under 2L into midfield.

Got back to race just worse than midfield after the start when galloping in the clear. Was over 3L from the lead entering last section, made up a length or so in final stages when finishing midfield (blood in trachea).

Slow to begin & raced second last. Was 4.5L from lead entering last section, shifted inwards near the 300m to improve, badly held up between rivals in final 125m when finishing strongly, was very unlucky. Rider questioned.

Badly crowded & checked between runners at start & raced a clear last. Continued last at the 400m when over 7L from lead before making good late ground along stand side rail in final stages for eye-catching midfield finish.

Bumped on jumping & unbalanced before racing in midfield. Was just over 2L from the lead entering last section, shifted inwards near the 300m mark but then did little thereafter. Rider questioned, see report.

Began well and assumed the early lead when galloping along stand side rail. Was joined & shared lead approaching 700m, was beaten off soon after entering final section & weakened pretty poorly in last furlong.
Showed speed to race close to the lead before sharing the lead from about the 700m when galloping nearer to the center of the track. Was beaten passing the 400m mark & weakened poorly thereafter.

Began moderately & got back to race third last after start when galloping closer to center of track. Was ridden along before half-way, continued to gallop in isolation before weakening very poorly to be a long second last.
Ridden forward after the start to race only a length from the lead in early stages. Began losing ground from half-way & weakened out to be a very long last. Poor.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out 450M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide on turn, 4-1/2L back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, slightly improved on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the winner.
Jumped well from gate 12, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 50M.

Moderately away from a tricky draw, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, 2 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra inside final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight. (A wound to the left front leg.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide after passing 600M, 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, no clear run 250M, cleared 150M, one-paced thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 600M, 5-1/2L back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened inside final furlong.
Commenced well, positioned 1-3/4L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, made no progress thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until 200M, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from the widest draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke well and quickly assumed the lead, kept on strongly and won going away.
Jumped nicely and sat outside the lead, quickened nicely in the Straight but no match for the winner
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, switched out rounding the Turn, made decent progress, never threaten the top 2.
Sat midfield on the rail, showed some dash after the 300M, one pace final 75M.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, stayed on fairly.
Raced behind midfield on the rail, made some progress along the rail.
Settled midfield 2 wide, raced keenly throughout, only one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind the pace 2 wide, under pressure from the 650M, weakened 250M. (Must pass Stalls test)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, made little impression. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Settled towards the rear, never a threat.
Sat handy, weakened and faded in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat at the rear, never in contention.
Broke slowly, sat last, never involved.
Settled in midfield on rail after moderate start, steadied and lost position 900 metres out, renewed effort home turn obtaining a run passing the 300 metres, asserted authority about 100 metres.
Close up early before settling in midfield alongside eventual winner, fought on steadily under pressure in straight without threatening.

Broke well from a poor draw, led or disputed lead in first 400 metres, gradually settled one back 2-wide home bend, renewed effort to lead into straight but unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 150 metres.
Settled wide behind midfield after beginning from a poor draw, widest turning in for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly from the widest draw settling at the back on rail, running into heels when steadied about 600 metres out, switched for a run inside the 300 metres and made up some late ground.

Jumped awkwardly but soon recovered to close-up 6th, gradually shifted backward before inconvenienced dropping to 3L off the lead 900 metres out, renewed effort on straightening but could find no extra.
Soon taken back from a poor draw, remained well behind into straight, made up ground past well-beaten horses inside final 250 metres.

Soon picked up to close-up 4th on rail after moderate start, gradually drifted over 2L off the pace home bend, angled out for a run entering straight reaching 2nd shortly after, found no extra 200 metres out.
Ridden positively amongst the leaders gaining narrow advantage shortly after, ceded lead for cover coming onto home bend, one-paced in straight before fading inside final 200 metres.
Amongst first few, shifted 2L back to 5th 3-wide onto home bend, wider turning for home and soon weakened.
Soon dropped to last few and showed no pace despite niggling along, made no impression.
Began moderately from a poor draw but pressed forward to eventually take up running onto home bend, led until headed approaching straight, folded up quickly.
Stumbled shortly after the start, settled down ahead of mid-division, responded strongly under the guidance of 10lb claimer, got up near 50M to score.
Sent forward, chased leaders from 800M, closed off nicely on straightening although not pace of winner final 150M.
Jumped only fairly, recovered to race behind midfield, 9th spot turning for home, closed off final 400M fastest to take 3rd just in time, nearest finish. Encouraging first start.
Blundered after the start, commenced to race keenly, would not relax in the lead when taken on by rival 900M, fought hard to hold lead on straightening, no extra and swamped final stages.
From draw 10 went forward, moved across to rail chasing leaders from 800M, kept going well on straightening, steadied 150M, held by leaders towards the line but was a pleasing debut.
Shifted out on jumping, soon bustled along to hold a midfield position on inside, made some progress final 300M but never a winning hope.
Not hurried on jumping from draw 13, dropped back to race 3-wide towards the rear, wider from 600M, failed to make up appreciable ground in the straight. No threat to leaders.
Dropped back to near the rear, checked 900M, had the job ahead on straightening, stayed on past beaten horses. Not reach leaders.
Crowded shortly after the start, soon towards the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, got home only fairly, never a threat to leaders.

Close up to leaders early, drifted back to race ahead of midfield entering home turn, hard driven to stay in contention early straight, no extra 150M. (Jockey : may not have been suited by the rain affected track.)
Obliged to make some use to take up a position outside leader, vied for lead until 350M then weakened away.
Obtained a midfield spot, raced keenly middle stages, not quickened early straight, couldn't go on passing 200M.
Bumped at the start, maintained a position behind midfield, hard driven 600M but failed to respond. (Blood in trachea / Jockey : may not have been suited by the rain affected track.)
Switched off to last from wide draw, plenty to do top of straight, brought widest to challenge but failed to go past any of his rivals.
Out with rest, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 11 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out 500M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, commenced move 550M, very wide into straight, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Began well, raced better than midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began fairly from gate 11, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, make some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced in 2nd, 4 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.) (Mucus.)
Taken back to race 3 wide with cover towards rear, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Taken back from gate 12, raced behind midfield on the inside, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, failed to close in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 500M, 8 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, hit the front 100M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 500M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly and made contact, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening. (Lost left front plate.)
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 lengths or so back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly and made contact, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Bumped on the hindquarters at the start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.

Jumped awkwardly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside early, 2 wide from 800M, commenced move after passing 550M, hit the front approaching 200M, kept on very well to the line, won by 2-1/4L.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Commenced well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, angled out and made contact near 800M, same margin back turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, one-paced thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.

Away well, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 600M, 4 wide turning in, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, passed some tired runners in the run home.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, saved ground on turn, took the lead 500M, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Jumped with them, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1250M, 2nd in the middle stages, took the lead 600M, peaked and headed 500M, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Out with rest, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1250M, found rail near 1000M, peaked and headed 600M, weakened final 400M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Was slow away by about a length before racing just worse than midfield along the rail. Improved in middle stages along the inside, came off rail passing 500m, closed strongly in final stages to steal lead & win narrowly late.

Got back after the start to race three wide with cover near the rear. Continued in second half on straightening before closing strongly down the outside in final stages to be beaten narrowly in three-way drive to line.

Had a nice run third away from the rail. Continued in the first three on straightening, improved to take narrow lead passing 150m, caught in final few strides and was narrowly beaten in three way drive to the line.
Had a soft run in midfield along the rail. Stayed along the rail in the straight & closed off well all the way to the line to be beaten only 0.75L when just behind the first three.

Drifted back from second widest gate but was caught racing three wide without cover in midfield. Continued wide around bend before closing well down the outside to be beaten under a length when just behind first three.
Ridden forward after start, raced second throughout. Was only a length from lead on straightening, peaked on effort passing 300m mark, gave a few lengths to be well held in midfield.

Showed customary early speed to lead when racing away from the rail. Crossed down to rail when continuing to lead just before first bend. Held lead until 150m mark, weakened late to be well held in midfield.

Had no early speed & raced at the tail. Moved wider on the track passing 500m when continuing rearward, passed a few tiring rivals when making up a few lengths late when finishing off down the outside to midfield.
Raced in midfield away from the rail. Was bumped on straightening, peaked on run passing the 300m mark before weakening a few lengths in last furlong.
Drifted back after the start and raced second last after the first furlong. Hung outwards approaching the 500m mark when continued near the tail, did little in the straight & finished third last.
Was steadied & taken back to race worse than midfield along the inside. Stayed along the rail on straightening when just under 5L from the lead but did nothing in the straight & finished second last.
Raced just worse than midfield between runners after the start. Began losing ground from the 650m mark, was 7L behind on straightening but was already beaten, ultimately weakening to last beaten 9L.
Settled midfield on the rail, traveled strongly, show some dash over the final 100M, closed off nicely.
Chased the leader, traveled smoothly, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Settled worse than midfield, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, made good progress inside 100M.
Sat towards rear, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Ridden along to lead, weakened entering the Straight, one pace to the line.
Sat in front of midfield, mid-race move rounding the Turn, raced wide thereafter (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, raced keenly in the early stages, raced wide until near the 800M, closed off fairly
Sat in front of midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, weakened notably inside 150M (See Incident Report).
Settled behind midfield, limited response when asked, never a threat.
Sat rear, raced rear, no contention.
Settled midfield, weakened rounding the Turn, faded entering the Straight (Unacceptable performance, Must BT).

Got back to race third last after first furlong. Moved wider passing 550m, continued rearward when about 5L from lead on straightening before finishing strongly down the outside to steal lead in final few strides.

Was niggled along to hold position after start before improving along rail to midfield in middle stages. Was 3L from lead on straightening, shifted into clear running mid-straight before closing strongly to be narrowly beaten.

Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout. Was three wide with cover around bend, under 2L from the lead entering last section, improved to lead fleetingly near 100m mark before over-run by first two late, close behind.

Challenged for lead early, headed near 1000m mark when galloping between runners. Steadied near 700m, shared lead on straightening, held outright lead until the 100m mark before over-run in final 100m, held 4th.

Showed early speed to challenge for lead, raced along the rail in a line of three sharing lead early, was crossed after the 700m & raced on the leaders back thereafter. Shifted off rail passing 300m, finished steadily late.

Raced in midfield between runners early before slightly further back around bend. Moved wider on straightening when 3.5L from the lead, finished steadily all the way to the line to hold deficit when finishing midfield.

Challenged for lead early before being steadied around first bend when racing fourth between runners. Was ridden along before straightening when about 3L from the lead, battled to midfield when weakening a length or two late.

Crowded after jumping & got back to second last but galloped four & five wide on track throughout. Continued rearward & very wide around bend, was over 6L from lead at 400m, finished ok to midfield considering passage.

Was trapped racing four wide in midfield before improving position to be three wide outside leaders from the 600m. Moved to narrow lead momentarily near 300m but emptied soon after & weakened out very quickly in final 150m.

Ridden forward from gate 11, shared lead when racing very wide on track before improving passing 800m & crossing to rail when leading near the 700m. Was beaten off at the 300m and weakened out in the final furlong.

Drifted back after the first 100m & raced just worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Was relegated to third last near the 600m, was 6L behind on straightening but weakened poorly to be beaten about 10L.

Crowded at start, consequently lost ground & raced at the tail. Struck rail at the 700m bend, became awkward & lost ground. Was last and over 6L from lead on straightening, stayed along rail but gave further ground. Last.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Out with rest, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, showed good response in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, same position on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, showed no response early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well and showed good early speed to lead, joined at 200M but found plenty to win going away, won smartly.
Settled midfield 2 wide, switched out rounding the Turn to improve, showed strong dash early in the Straight, run peaked at 200M, made no further ground on the winner.
Broke alertly and hard ridden to sit outside the lead, kept on okay and held 3rd.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, closed off fairly.
Settled towards the rear, stayed on late.
Sat at the rear, angled out in the Straight, only able to pass weakened rivals. (See Incident Report)
Raced in a prominent position 2 wide, weakened final 200M.
Sat midfield on the rail, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Jumped nicely, sat behind the leaders, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Jumped slowly, sat long way last, never travelled, eased down midway. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)

Crowded early, travelled towards rear on rail, came under pressure to challenge 500 metres out sneaking up to 5th on rail turning in for home, sustained effort down the inside to assert authority about 100 metres out.

Broke well settling in midfield on rail, keen between runners when pace slackened about 650 metres out, shifted out for a run entering straight but baulked upon straightening, responded well inside final 250 metres.
Wide in midfield, keen in middle stages, circled the field rounding home bend, ran on to hit the front over 200 metres out only to be headed by the winner over 100 metres out, lost 2nd late.

Settled worse than midfield in 9th after beginning from a poor draw, commenced move rounding home bend circling the field 6-wide, fought on under pressure to reach within 1L of pace inside the 200 metres but soon found no extra.
Settled well behind from a poor draw and waited with, saved ground on inside turning in for home, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Broke well from a low draw before settling in 6th in better than midfield, made steady headway to within 2L of pace in steadied tempo rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening.

Broke well from a poor draw and used early to lead, held back for cover in 3rd turning into back straight, renewed effort to hit the front making final turn but unable to sustain effort and swamped over 200 metres out.
Broke well before gradually settled in worse than midfield, went very wide entering straight, fought on steadily past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Settled at rear, extremely wide rounding home bend, made up good ground from near last into straight to be nearest at finish.
Pressed forward from a poor draw before settling in distant 5th in back straight, checked 650 metres out going 5-wide into home straight, weakened under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Slowly away, always at the back and never seen with a chance. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Chased leaders in 4th, drifted further off the pace to as much as 5L back in back straight, renewed effort to remain prominent into home straight, soon weakened.
Ridden positively from the one draw to be up with the leaders, gained 1L advantage leaving the 700 metres but soon headed when weakened noticeably entering straight.
Ridden forward from the wide draw to dispute lead most of the way to the 700 metres, dropped away quickly inside final 500 metres. (Blood in trachea)
From wide draw taken back to last 10Ls off the lead, had the task ahead top of straight, closed off powerfully from rear to snatch victory near line.
On jumping was badly crowded and unbalanced, raced ahead of midfield on settling, responded well early straight, struck the lead inside 100M only to be caught by the fast finishing winner near line.
Jumped on terms, fell back to a position behind midfield, ran on strongly passing 400M and was just denied in a 3-way photo finish.
Restrained to race near last 9Ls off the pace, crept closer home turn, briefly held up 250M before doing best work late to claim 4th.
Obtained a 2-wide spot ahead of midfield, had every chance turning home, briefly went 2nd mid-straight but run ended 100M from home.
Driven forward, crossed to the lead passing 1300M, kept going well early straight, caught by pursuing rivals final 100M and lost several places close home.
Settled behind mid-division 6Ls from leader, ran on mildly final 300M but rivals finished better. (had some difficulty obtaining clear running concluding stages.)
Tracked leader, bustled along 500M, soon outsprinted by rivals on straightening. (Roarer.)
Maintained a midfield position throughout the race, couldn't accelerate when asked passing 400M. Never threatened. (Jockey concern with his mount's action.)

From wide draw taken across to a rearward position, 9Ls off the pace on settling with little change to the turn, attempted an inside run, held up 200M before shifting out for clear running final stages. Could do better.
Led early before obtaining a trailing position behind the leaders, hard driven passing 500M, couldn't go on passing 300M, weakened towards the line.
Restrained after the start, soon towards the rear 9Ls off the pace, brought wide for home but failed to pick up when asked for effort.
From draw one away well enough, chased leaders in 4th, under the pump 500M, soon gave ground and out of contention.

Away with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 650M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Bumped on jumping, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Blundered on jumping and became unbalanced, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, 3 wide from 550M, finished off evenly.
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Fast into stride, raced prominently on the outside, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened final 100M.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide towards rear, very wide into straight, kept on same pace in straight.
Out in line, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, peaked on run 500M, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Settled in midfield or slightly worse, circled the field home bend and one of the widest into straight, ran on under pressure to hit the front about 150 metres out.
Travelled within 3L of the pace in 4th in back straight, gained closer to 3rd 700 metres out, obtained clear passage over 300 metres out holding every chance but found winner too good.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to midfield on rail, gained closer when pace slackened home bend, made up good ground inside final 150 metres.
Settled at the back, came under pressure home bend switching widest into home straight, ran on well inside final 250 metres to do best work late.
Broke well, ceded lead for 2nd position passing the 1700 metres, soon came to hit the front upon straightening for home but unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 200 metres.
Settled towards rear in 10th or 9th, blundered badly 500 metres out, snuck up on the inside in home straight but could make no further impression inside final 50 metres.
Broke well settling in 5th some 3L off the pace in back straight, commenced move passing the 600 metres holding some chance when bumped twice early in straight, weakened inside final 200 metres.
Travelled wide towards rear, in similar position into straight, ran home one-paced.
Settled in rear from a poor draw, badly blundered 500 metres out causing jockey to lose use of his irons, made no impression in home straight.
Settled well behind from the widest draw, came under pressure rounding final bend, ran past well-beaten horses in home straight.
Mostly in 3rd, gave ground under pressure from about 500 metres out. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in midfield mainly in 6th, weakened under pressure after turning into home straight.
Pressed forward from a wide draw, led on rail passing the 1600 metres until headed shortly after turning into home straight.
Ridden along to lead on the rail, traveled smoothly, kept on well to win.
Sat in front of midfield, responded well when asked inside 100M, closed off nicely.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, had difficulty obtaining clear running entering the Straight, ran on evenly (See Incident Report).
Chased the leader, slightly weakened passing 300M, ran on okay.
Slow to begin, sat rear, traveled fairly in the early stages, made good ground over the final 300M (See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, finished off fairly.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, weakened inside 200M, no impression (See Incident Report).
Sat midfield, traveled keenly in the middle stages, held up rounding the Turn, no clear run until 200M.
Settled midfield, raced wide, limited response when asked, faded in the Straight (Unacceptable performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).

Shifted back from widest gate and settled second last along the rail. Moved into clear running on straightening, entered last section 5L from lead before closing strongly to charge to lead in final 25m and win.

Raced in midfield away from the rail. Eased three wide with cover passing the 700m, was just over 2L from the lead on straightening, made continual closing ground to be narrowly beaten when passed in final few strides.

Raced three wide early, was two wide in middle stages when galloping in midfield. Eased into three wide line with cover again passing 600m before closing well all the way to the line to steal third in final stride.
Pushed forward to lead. Continued in front all the way until only over-run by the closing rivals in the final 25m. Beaten under a length but missed a placing.
Raced three wide without cover outside the leaders for the majority. Tried hard & was still not far behind passing 150m but wide run took its toll in final stages.

Raced in midfield along rail early. Eased off the rail approaching 600m mark, shifted wider again on straightening when just over 3L from the lead before finishing off steadily in final stages to hold midfield finish.

Drifted back after start & raced third last away from rail. Continued rearward, shifted wider passing 550m, was the widest runner on straightening when still 5.5L behind, made some late ground from a long way back.

Got back after start, raced fourth last along the rail in the middle stages. Came off the rail approaching the 600m, steadied near 500m, shifted wider on straightening, entered last section 5L behind, finished steadily late.
Obtained a nice position 1,1 in middle stages. Was only 2L from the lead entering last section but did little in the straight, weakening a few lengths to finish ninth.
Pushed forward and raced outside the leader. Continued second on straightening, under a length behind, peaked on effort at the 200m, weakened out in final furlong & was well beaten.

Raced in midfield between runners early before racing along rail in middle stages. Was niggled along passing 600m, was 4.5L from lead on straightening, shifted outwards mid-straight but did little, weakening to be beaten 7L.

Was in midfield early before drifting slightly further back after the 1000m & raced just worse than midfield thereafter. Came wider approaching home turn, was second widest on straightening but did nothing in last section.
Had a nice run on the leaders back for the majority. Was only 2.5L from the lead on straightening but was beaten at the 300m mark & weakened very poorly thereafter & finished a long second last.

Placing: PU
Comment: Had no early speed & raced a clear last throughout. Unfortunately went amiss early in the straight & failed to finish.
Began well, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide after passing 500M, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 4 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd on line, no threat to the winner.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, shared lead after passing 550M, hard ridden from 200M, peeked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line, lost 2nd last stride.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.

Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 850M, shared lead with rival from 550M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 8, raced at tail, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Commenced well, raced prominently, 2 wide, slightly taken back 850M, 2 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped on terms, showed good early speed to lead, travelled smoothly throughout, kicked clear at the top of the Straight, kept on strongly, won cozily.
Settled midfield on the rail, began to improve at 500M, closed off nicely for 2nd, no threat to winner.
Settled in a prominent position 2 wide, kept on nicely, weakened final 150M, lost second on the line. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, made some progress along the rail.
Settled towards the rear 3 wide, stayed on okay.
Raced 3 wide with cover midfield, made little impression.
Jumped well and settled behind the leaders, weakened final 250M.
Settled towards the rear, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Settled at the rear, made no progress in the Straight.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, made the Home Turn awkwardly, limited response when asked.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, one pace throughout. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide no cover throughout, weakened in the Straight. (Barrier Manners unacceptable, must passed stalls test)
Tracked leader 2 wide, under pressure from 500M, weakened and faded final 200M.
At rear, raced greenly, never involved.

Crowded at start, lacked early pace despite niggling along travelling in 9th, commenced move shortly after straightening responding well inside final 200 metres to assert authority 100 metres out. (Sustained bone fracture)
Settled one back on rail, shifted out for a run after straightening, quickened to lead over 200 metres out only to be caught by fast-finishing winner 100 metres out.
Settled well behind from the widest draw, trailed the field to the 500 metres, ran on between runners in straight without threatening first two.
Settled well back in 10th and waited with, shifted widest turning into straight, ran on well inside final 200 metres to narrowly miss 3rd.
Prominent to straight, came under pressure upon straightening and steadily faded inside final 200 metres.
Broke well before taken over 2L back to 4th 3-wide, commenced move 700 metres out disputing lead into straight, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 200 metres.

Hard ridden from a poor draw to vie for early lead obtaining rails run in front passing the 800 metres, led until joined into straight, weakened under pressure out of contention inside final 200 metres.
Niggled along in worse than midfield early stages, gained closer 3-wide rounding home bend, kept on under pressure from 6th into straight before finding no extra inside final 100 metres.
Never better than midfield, baulked for a run early in straight, one-paced afterwards. (Jockey expressed ground concern)
Niggled along in better than midfield on rail, travelled keenly behind runners coming onto home bend, kept on from close-up 6th into straight before yielding ground inside final 200 metres.

Placing: PU
Comment: Towards rear on rails, dropped away noticeably after straightening, did not finish.
Settled nicely in midfield along the fence, into clear running 400M, stayed on best final 200M to take lead close home.
Tracked leaders, driven along 500M, quickened up to lead them 200M out, just couldn't hold off winner late.
From draw 12 caught wide no cover chasing the pace, fought on well from 400M, not matched first two over final 200M but kept on determinedly to hold 3rd.
Away well enough from draw 2, held up just behind midfield on settling, ran home evenly to claim 4th, just missed out on 3rd spot.
Taken across from wide barrier, settled behind mid-division, 6Ls to make up 400M, ran on mildly for modest 5th.
Jumped on terms, obtained an inner spot tracking the pace, held up early straight and unable to obtain clear running until near 150M, got home only fairly over final stages.
Taken across from wide barrier, settled towards the rear, ran on only fairly passing 400M, never a threat to leaders.
Moved forward and emerged as leader passing 1000M, under siege 300M, driven but no extra final 150M.
Up with early pace before taking up a position outside leader, fought hard early straight trying to gain the lead, ran on empty passing 200M and weakened away.
Dropped back to race at the rear 9Ls, brought wide for home but gave limited response. Never a threat to much higher rated leaders.
Reserved near the rear 8Ls off the pace, couldn't pick up on straightening, no impression on leaders.
Settled down in midfield further back than usual, couldn't go on passing 400M, soon weakened. (Jockey expressed concern with the manner in which his horse finished the race off.)
Caught racing 3-wide in midfield, dropped away passing 350M, quickly out of contention. (Jockey : no explanation for the disappointing run / Unacceptable Performance.)
Began well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide from 600M, 1-1/2L back turning in, finished off strongly to score.

Jumped well from a wide draw, trapped wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, moved closer after passing 1250M, 2nd in the middle stages, hit the front 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on outer, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 550M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.(See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, showed some response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped heavily on jumping, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, carried wider 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.

Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the outside, sent forward after passing 1650M, took the lead 1600M, led by a length in the middle stages, challenged by rival 600M, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1600M, 2nd in the middle stages, challenged the leader 600M, kept on well in straight, always held.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4-1/2L back turning in, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Crowded shortly after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, commenced move 700M, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, a bit closer on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced in 3rd, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, dropped to midfield on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Stood flat-footed as the start was effected and lost ground, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail 550M, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score.

Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside early, 2 wide after passing 1200M, moved closer 800M, 3 wide better than midfield on turn, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival 700M, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed 200M, kept on evenly to take a place.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 1450M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Jumped well, raced better than midfield on the inside, dropped to midfield after entering the back straight, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, commenced move 500M, very wide into straight, passed some tired runners in the run home.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide after passing 800M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the outside, sent forward after entering the back straight, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 850M, 4 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Made contact at start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Showed good pace to lead, skipped away early straight opening up a sizeable lead, eased late and had his winning margin reduced to a neck. (Jockey reprimanded for failing to ride out to the line.)
Away in line, given a waiting ride near the rear, closed off strongly final 300M and was rapidly making ground on the eventual winner who had been eased final stages.
From draw 1 bustled along early to hold a midfield spot along the fence, kept on steadily final 300M for a non-threatening 3rd.
From wide draw dropped back to race in last, had the task ahead at 400M with 9Ls to make up, finished off well to take 4th.
Jumped on terms, maintained a midfield spot, 6Ls to make up 400M, held up 300M-250M before closing off the race moderately. (Jockey reported post race his horse had its tongue over the bit.)
Away quickly, tracked leaders, 4th at 400M, briefly went 2nd mid-straight but peaked on its run 150M.
Slow to begin, settled near last 8Ls off pace, stayed on without threatening over final 300M.
Began well, always stayed in touch behind leading trio, couldn't pick up pace when asked early straight, soon out of contention.

Had to make early use from a wide draw to obtain a forward position outside leader, no extra nearing 200M, weakened away. (Jockey: may be better suited being ridden more conservatively in early stages.)
Away well enough, dropped back to a midfield spot along the 3-path, couldn't go on passing 300M. No impression on leaders.
From wide draw taken across behind rivals, reserved behind midfield, failed to finish off under top weight. (Bled.)
Pressed forward to be racing just off leader, struggled to keep up nearing 400M, soon beaten on straightening. (Lame next day.)
Settled midfield, traveled keenly in the early stages, showed some dash over the concluding 75M, closed off strongly.
Sat handy, traveled nicely, made good ground inside 100M, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled smoothly, shifted out to obtain clear running in the Straight, ran on evenly.
Ridden along to lead, traveled okay, slightly weakened entering the Straight.
Jumped only fairly, sat behind midfield, shifted out to obtain clear running in the Straight, closed off fairly.
Sat rear, traveled fairly, no impression made (Tongue tie replaced on arrival at the Start).
Settled worse than midfield, traveled okay, ran on fairly to the line.
Sat rear, raced rear, could not make up ground, no contention.
Began well, raced outside the leader for the majority. Moved up to share lead approaching 200m, looked challenged but was strong in final stages & went on to win well again.

Raced in midfield along the rail before improving to race on the leaders back from 550m. Stayed along rail on straightening, moved through to share lead at 200m, battled well but winner was too strong, finished clear of 3rd.

Was a touch wide early before coming a pair further back after first bend & raced just worse than midfield. Was 4L from the lead entering last section, closed off well to move to well beaten third near 50m mark.

Drifted back after the start, was third last before being second last from the 800m. Was just under 6L from the lead entering last section, came wider on straightening before making some late headway down the outside.

Pushed forward but was caught three wide without cover outside leaders. Was steadied near 900m & came back a length, continued to cover additional ground. Was finishing steadily before being crowded in concluding stages.

Got back after start & raced rearward along the rail. Was over 6L from the lead entering last section when third last before making a couple of lengths late in the raced when running home along the rail to finish in midfield.

Obtained position in midfield away from rail early before moving to rail mid-race. Was only 2L from lead on straightening, finished off only moderately last furlong & despite being crowded in final stages was no threat.

Began awkwardly, lost ground & raced last after start. Came outwards sharply near the 400m mark when continuing last and over 7L from the lead before making up a few lengths from a long way back to finish in midfield.
Held the advantage of inside draw & improved after start to lead. Was headed in the lead near the 250m, weakened in final furlong, checked near the line when beaten & finished ninth.
Began fairly before racing in midfield along the rail. Was 4L from the lead entering last section when continuing in midfield, did little in the straight & finished third last.

Crowded & checked after start, before getting back when caught racing very wide & rearward. Shifted out to avoid rival near the 600m & raced very wide around bend. Pushed very wide again on straightening & was never a factor.
Obtained a nice position 1,1 in middle stages. Was only 2.5L from the lead entering last section, came under hard ridding before straightening and then weakened to finish last.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, commenced move 600M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 750M, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Away well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 400M, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, kept on same pace to the line.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, no clear run early in straight, made no impression thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed approaching 200M, weakened and eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Broke well, settled behind the leaders, switched towards the inside in the Straight, closed off strongly to score.
Restrained after the start from a wide barrier and settled at the rear, had some trouble finding clear running early in the Straight, stayed on strongly, closet finish.
Jumped well but caught 3 wide no cover on pace, kept on nicely until weakened final 50M.
Jumped on terms, settled midfield 2 wide, ran on okay for a non-threatening 4th. (See Incident Report)
Showed good early speed to lead, kept on until weakened final 150M.
Settled midfield on the rail, raced keenly in the early and middle stages, made some progress.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide with cover, only one pace when asked.
Settled midfield 3 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Sat at the rear on the rail, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Settled towards the rear, made no impression.
Sat outside the lead, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat on pace on the rail, began to lose ground at 400M, weakened and faded after.
Tracked leaders in 3rd or 4th on rail, came to tackle leaders upon straightening and asserted authority 50 metres out
Always thereabouts, hit the front into straight, hung on well until caught 50 metres out.
Settled in midfield on rail, saved ground turning in for home, fought on steadily for distant 3rd without threatening.
Ridden to lead attempting to make all, headed into straight and faded.
Travelled in midfield or slightly worse and keenly at times, came under pressure rounding home bend and wide into straight, ran on under pressure down the centre of the track and did best work late.
Travelled keenly at times mainly in 5th in better than midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Held up in last few from the widest draw, improved steadily around first bend to reach 1.5L 3rd 3-wide into back straight, went wider turning in for home and could find no extra under pressure.
Settled well behind, saved ground turning in for home, fought on steadily between runners after straightening, steadied close home.
Held up in last few, ran home one-paced.
Settled towards rear on rail after moderate beginning, saved ground turning in for home, found no extra after straightening.
Settled at the back, never seen with a chance.

Travelled wide in last few before improving steadily to some 3L 6th 3-wide into back straight, lost position 700 metres out before coming under pressure home bend, dropped further back from approaching straight.

Settled ahead of midfield, in touch with leaders home turn, wide into straight, saddle shifted according to rider and hung in badly causing interference to rivals over final 250M. Just held on in a photo finish.
Jumped awkwardly, reserved behind midfield 6-7Ls back, wide into straight, hit the line well, just denied in a photo finish.
Taken back to last from a wide draw, 9-10Ls off the pace on settling, had task in hand top of straight, briefly crowded for room near 200M before finishing off nicely to claim 3rd, nearest finish.
Restrained to a rearward position, 6Ls off the pace entering home turn, brought widest top of straight and closed off well to take 4th, nearest finish.

Went forward tracking leader, raced keenly 900M when pace steadied, kept going well early straight, outran by first two inside 150M, checked late stages and edged out to 5th near line. (Protest on winner overruled.)
Switched off to race near the rear 7-8Ls away, pushed along nearing 400M, stayed on well under top weight but was badly crowded for room on the inside late stages.
Chased leader on outside, badly crowded for room near 250M and lost momentum, kept on without threatening leaders late stages.
Tracked leaders early stages, 5th at 800M, was commencing to finish off the race when badly held up for clear running from 150M. Could do better.
Settled down in midfield along the 2-path, kept on mildly on straightening and was always held by leaders.
Maintained a midfield spot on the inside, kept battling away early straight, held by leaders from 150M, checked 50M losing momentum.
Crowded on jumping, soon moved up to the lead, swung to center of track on straightening, fought hard from 300M, steadied by rival 150M, no extra towards the finish.
Held up behind midfield early stages, under the pump 550M, failed to close off the race.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Clean jump, sent forward to race in 2nd, 1-1/2L behind the leader, same position on turn, finished off well without threatening the winner.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, a bit closer on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail near 500M, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider on turn, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, slightly improved on turn, angled out 350M, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, trapped wide in midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made little progress early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, weakened 500M, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
