Average to begin, raced in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed very good response, took the lead 75M, kept on strongly to the line. (A minor laceration below the left stifle.)
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, 3 away from the stands' rail, took the lead 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 75M, finished 2nd.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, hard ridden 400M, peaked and headed 250M, kept on evenly to take a place.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear, 4 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, hard ridden after passing 350M, finished off evenly.
Jumped only fairly, raced prominently on the stands' side, travelled well in the middle stages, peaked on run 250M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden 400M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently on the stands' rail, peaked 250M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Lifted front feet on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the stands' rail, peaked 500M, weakened gradually final furlong.

Shifted behind runners after start & raced just worse than midfield along the rail. Came away from the rail near the 500m, moved into clear running near the 250m before closing well to take lead in final few strides.

Raced in midfield along the rail. Was held up on straightening, bumped heavily when trying to shift into clear near the 225m, got clear inside last 150m & closed well to finish a narrowly beaten & slightly unlucky second.
Raced outside the leader. Moved to narrow lead approaching 200m, joined inside final 50m, hung outwards in concluding stages but did enough to hold third on the line only beaten a neck.

Had a nice run 1,1 for the majority. Bumped with second near the 225m, continued close to the lead for most of the straight, was bumped by third in final 25m and was beaten under a length on the line.
Shifted back to race rearward away from the rail. Was second last on straightening when 4.5L from the lead, made good late ground down the outside in concluding stages to be beaten only 1.5L on line.

Had no early speed, was ridden to hold position near the tail. Continued to race third last along the rail in middle stages, stayed only the rail on straightening before making some late ground, not be beaten far in midfield.

Had a nice run on the leaders back. Was held up for clear running along the rail for the first half of the straight, then continued to be held tight with limited room until inside the final 100m before finishing ok late.
Began fairly before mustering speed to lead. Joined at the 250m, weakened out a few lengths in the final 100m & was beaten just over 3L.

Was steadied & taken back to race at the tail. Was last and over 6L from the lead on straightening, shifted out to be the widest runner in the straight, made up a few lengths late but was no threat when finishing ninth.

Was caught racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Continued only about a length from the lead at the furlong marker before wide trip took its toll and weakened in final 100m to be third last.
Began well but drifted back to race midfield away from the rail. Was under 3L from the lead entering last section but didn't do much in the straight, weakening to finish second last.

Drifted back after the start & raced just worse than midfield away from the rail. Shifted into three wide line with cover approaching 500m, was 4L from lead entering last section but weakened in straight & finished last.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, switched out entering the Straight, show some dash over the final 200M, closed off strongly.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, traveled nicely, made good ground over the final 150M, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Sat midfield, switched out and improved rounding the Turn, responded well when placed under pressure.
Sat rear, slightly held up near 250M, raced tight over the concluding stages.
Chased the leader throughout, traveled okay, weakened passing the 300M, ran on evenly.
Settled midfield, angled out rounding the Turn, slightly weakened inside 250M, closed off fairly.
Ridden along to lead, traveled smoothly, weakened inside 250M, minor progress made when asked.
Sat in handy, raced wide throughout, limited response when asked (See Incident Report).
Settled worse than midfield, traveled fairly, no impression made.
Sat handy, raced keenly in the early stages, held up entering the Straight, could not be fully tested (Wound to left hind cannon, See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, raced keenly in the early stages, could not be ridden out, never a threat.
Sat rear, raced rear, failed to respond when asked, no contention.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear, weakened passing the 200M, faded gradually.
Settled in front of midfield, lay out at the Turn, weakened notably entering the Straight (Unacceptable performance, Must BT).
Raced second along the stand side rail, a couple of lengths behind leader in middle stages. Shifted inwards passing 300m, moved to lead near 100m mark, held off late challenger.

Raced third, followed the winner for the majority. Was 4L from the lead entering last section, shifted inwards at the 250m, tried very hard, making continual ground but only being able to get within a neck on the line.
Veered inwards at start before showing customary early speed to lead. Joined by winner near 100m, battled well to hold third, only beaten 1.5L on line.
Raced in midfield between runners. Was 5.5L from the lead passing the 400m mark, made up late ground to be beaten just over 2L into 4th.

Raced just worse than midfield nearer to the center of the track. Was ridden along passing half-way, entered last section just under 6L from lead before making up a few lengths in final stages when holding midfield finish.
Got back to race worse than midfield between runners. Was 7L from the lead entering last section, made late progress to halve deficit on the line to finish in midfield.

Was crowded at the start & lost ground and raced third last along stand side rail. Was over 7L from the lead entering last section, shifted inwards at the 200m, made up a length or two but was never close.
Was bumped at the start before racing in midfield along the stand side rail. Was over 5L from the lead entering last section when in fourth place, weakened in final furlong to finish third last.
Steadied after the start & taken back to race second last. Continued rearward when the closest to the center of the track, was over 7L from lead entering last section & made no ground.
Was slow to begin by a few lengths and raced at the tail. Continued last and 9L from the lead entering last section, made no ground and was beaten that margin on the line when finishing last.
Out with rest, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, angled out 450M, finished off very strongly to score.
Started very slowly, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, angled out 450M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced in 3rd, 3 lengths behind the leader turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Moderately away, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length or so back, there to turn, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 50M, ran on evenly to the line, lost 3rd on line.
Out in line, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, saved ground on turn, 8 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Away well, raced in midfield on outer, no cover in the middle stages, 5 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Placing: UR
Comment: Stumbled and unseated rider leaving stalls. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, showed good speed near the lead one off the stands' side, kept on nicely and just held on.
Settled midfield 4 off the stand's rail, closed off strongly, just missed.
Settled behind the leaders, switched in final 400M, made good progress, stuck on gamely, narrowly beaten for 3rd.
Settled midfield on the stand's rail, improved along the rail, stayed on, closest finish.
Dispute lead early on the far side, travelled strongly throughout, still led final 75M, weakened quickly inside 50M.
Jumped nicely and ridden aggressively early, share lead early, unable to quicken final 300M, only one pace.
Settle behind midfield 4 off the stands' rail, switched in towards center track to improve, stayed on only fairly.
Settled towards the rear, only one pace when asked.
Settled midfield 2 off the stands' rail, limited response when asked.
Settled worse than midfield 2 off the stands' rail, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield 3 off stand's rail, weakened final 350M.
Sat last, never a factor.
Settled at the rear, never in contention.
Settled at the rear, raced greenly, never involved.
Travelled outside race leader to straight, came to challenge upon straightening, gained upper hand close to home.
Attempted to make all, challenged by eventual winner after straightening only to lose advantage close to home.
Travelled in forward of midfield, crowded for room over 700 metres out, fought on steadily in straight to reach remote 3rd final strides.
Chased leaders to straight, ran home one-paced and lost remote 3rd late.
Began moderately, travelled in last few, switched wide into straight, ran on near the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, remained in last few to straight, ran on past well-beaten horses.
Travelled keenly in prominent 4th most of way to straight, unable to sustain effort.
Settled at the back from a poor draw, remained behind runners upon straightening, made modest progress past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres. (Mucus in trachea)
Travelled in midfield, inconvenienced about 350 metres out, ran home one-paced under pressure.

Broke well from a poor draw, gradually settled towards rear before renewing effort to circle the field from 900 metres and join the leaders briefly 500 metres out, folded up quickly after straightening.
Jumped awkwardly, travelled in last few, saved ground on rails turning in for home, fought nothing.
Travelled wide in midfield, beaten when tightened about 350 metres out, made no further impression.
Soon led, skipped away passing 400M, soon opened up a good lead and maintained a strong gallop to the line.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, ran on moderately over final 400M, got up for 2nd close home but no threat to runaway winner.
Tracked the pace, tried hard but couldn't get closer to the leader passing 400M, lost 2nd close home.
Jumped awkwardly, tracked leaders on inside, outsprinted by first three over final 300M.
Dropped back to last 5Ls off the pace , waited with till 350M but got to the line only fairly.
Slow to begin then shifted across from wide draw to race towards the rear, ran on one paced only passing 400M, never a threat to leaders.

Settled near the rear in a 7 runner race, failed to run on under top weight when the race developed into a sprint final 400M. (Jockey : disadvantaged by the early stages of the race being run outside of standard time.)
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, hit the front 125M, kept on strongly to the line.
Commenced well, took the early lead, headed 950M, 2nd in the middle stages, shared lead turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 125M.
Out with rest, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight.

Made contact and unbalanced shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover in the middle stages, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Jumped well from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 950M, shared lead with rival from 500M, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Began well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced slightly better than midfield, 3 wide, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back at 400M, showed no response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began smartly, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Began fairly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few final 25M.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, finished off well without threatening.
Bounded at the start and lost ground, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run final 150M.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 5-1/2L back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began well, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (Lost left hind plate.)
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 5 lengths back, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared near 150M, finished off strongly to score.
Began well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead in the middle stages, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two late.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest finish. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 8 lengths or so back, same position on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 500M, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 200M.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 lengths back in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the outside, 9 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Stood flat-footed as the start was effected and lost ground, raced at tail, still 10 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in the run home.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the outside, 9 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in 3rd, 2 wide, 3 lengths back in the middle stages, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Crowded shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)

Began smartly, took the lead easily, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight, won comfortably.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 350M, finished off well to take 2nd on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length or so back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line, missed 2nd on line.
Away with them, raced in 3rd, 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced better than midfield on the outside, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 8, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began fairly from gate 1, showed no early speed, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Settled mainly about 3L off the pace in 4th, in similar position into straight, ran on under pressure to gain upper hand close to home.
Began fairly, travelled keenly in 3rd just off the pace on rail, commenced move entering home straight and hit the front shortly after and only to be caught close to home.
Broke quickly before settling in 6th near midfield, went wide into straight, ran on dourly under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield on rail, commenced move early in straight, tightened for a run inside the 200 metres, recovered well under pressure to the line and narrowly missed 3rd.

Broke well before settling some 4L back in 5th on rail, niggled along in back straight coming under stronger pressure turning in for home, angled out for a run over 200 metres out causing interferences, found no extra late.
Settled towards rear on rail from a poor draw, saved ground turning in for home, fought on steadily in straight without quickening.
Took up running from the one draw, led the field until headed inside the 300 metres, soon weakened under pressure.
Settled in last few after beginning from a poor draw, came under pressure rounding home bend, ran past well-beaten horses down the centre of the straight.
Pressed forward from a poor draw for 1L 2nd 2-wide, unable to sustain effort inside final 400 metres.
Moderate start, niggling along when tightened on rail shortly afterwards, remained well behind throughout, found nothing under pressure in final stretch.
Settled just worse than midfield in 8th from a poor draw, came under pressure rounding home bend, made no impression in the run to the line.
Restrained well behind from the widest draw, remained at the back most of way and never seen with a chance.
Settled worse than midfield, traveled nicely, switched out and improved rounding the Turn, made good progress over the concluding stages.
Sat towards rear, raced wide throughout, showed some dash over the final 75M, stayed on well to grab 2nd.
Sat rear, traveled smoothly, responded well when asked, closed off nicely.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Sat towards rear, traveled okay, one pace to the line.
Sat handy, traveled fairly, minor progress made in the Straight.
Settled midfield, could not be ridden out over the concluding stages when close to heels, ran on fairly.
Sat in front of midfield, slightly weakened passing 400M, further weakened in the Straight.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, no impression made.
Ridden hard to lead, raced keenly, weakened approaching the 200M, faded gradually (Disappointing Performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Settled rear, raced keenly in the middle stages, weakened rounding the Turn, never a threat.
Jumped awkwardly, sat midfield, limited response when asked, never a danger.

Raced worse than midfield early when three wide without cover. Improved to midfield after 800m, continued to improve, getting outside leaders approaching home corner, moved to lead early in straight, tough in straight to win.

Shifted behind runners after start to race at the tail. Shifted wider on track approaching the 400m when still last, was the widest runner in the straight before finishing strongly down outside to steal second near line.

Lost ground at start before racing just worse than midfield between runners. Shifted three wide to follow the eventual winner from the 700m, improved around bend to be closer to lead, closed well to be beaten only 1L on line.

Got back to race last after the start. Moved three wide with cover passing half-way but continued rearward. Was the second widest on straightening when about 4L from the lead before making late ground, only beaten 1L.

Pushed forward, was challenged for the lead early before getting lead approaching winning post first time. Was headed by the winner early in the straight before battling on in final furlong to be beaten 2L.

Had no early speed & got back to race just worse than midfield along the rail. Was 4L from lead entering final section, stayed near the inside in straight & halved deficit to the line to be beaten 2L into midfield.

Raced in midfield along rail. Briefly held up approaching 400m when trying to come away from rail, was 2.5L from the lead on straightening, shifted outwards in straight when finishing steadily, maintained deficit to line.

Shifted across behind runners to race third last between horses. Continued near the rear throughout, was 4.5L from lead entering last section when second last, made up a couple of lengths late but was never in contention.

Pushed forward, was three wide challenging for lead leaving straight before shifting to two wide outside leader from the 1100m. Continued close to the lead on straightening before weakening final furlong (blood in trachea).

Pushed forward after start, challenged for lead leaving straight before coming back to race on the leaders back from 1100m. Shifted back to rail on straightening when close behind but did nothing in last furlong, weak late.
Pushed forward, raced second early before racing fourth in the clear around first bend. Improved to 1,1 near the 800m, was hard ridden before straightening, weakened out in final 250m.
Raced in midfield away from rail. Was shuffled slightly further back approaching corner, was rearward on straightening before weakening to last in the run to the line.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 4 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on strongly to the line.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, angled out 350M, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line, finished 3rd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 5-3/4L back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, nearest on line.
Average to begin, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from gate 1, raced in 3rd, a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Take back from gate 9, raced towards rear on the inside, 4-1/2L back, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened 150M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, ridden along for speed, led and travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear at the top of the Straight, kept on strongly along the rail and won.
Broke nicely, tracked leader 2 wide, switched out to center track in the Straight, closed off nicely, closest finish. (See Incident Report)
Hard ridden soon after the start, settled midfield 3 wide, made some ground center track, no match to the top 2.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, made some progress but never threaten.
Sat on pace 3 wide, limited response when asked.
Steadied after the start from the outside barrier, sat last, only able to pass weakened rivals. (See Incident Report)
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, under pressure at 500M, weakened in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, unable to improve rounding the Home Turn, made no ground in the Straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Settled towards the rear, never in contention.
Broke well to lead and make all, soon drew clear under pressure after straightening.
Chased leader to straight, hung in badly on straightening, kept on well for 2nd spot.
Jumped moderately losing ground, remained towards rear to straight, made up good ground under pressure.
Chased leader in 3rd on rail, plugged on under pressure in the run to the line.
Soon taken back from the widest draw settling at the back of the main body of the field, switched wide for a run entering home straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Began moderately, recovered to 4th about 3L off the pace turning into back straight, became 5th about 650 metres out, came under pressure rounding home bend, found nothing under pressure.
Began awkwardly losing ground, recovered steadily along the rail in back straight to reach 5L 4th coming onto home bend, made no further impression.
Broke well before dropping back to 6th about 850 metres out despite ridden along, dropped further away into straight. (Blood in trachea)
Planted at start losing considerable ground, detached from the main body of the field most of the way, never a factor. (Declared afforded a fair start after stewards' enquiry
Hard ridden but soon retired from the race shortly after start.
Jumped only fairly, held up behind midfield 3-wide, picked up nicely inside 300M, took over near 50M and kept kicking for a well-deserved maiden victory on his 28th start.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, waited with at the rear and over 7Ls to make up passing 400M, chased on solidly down outside to go 2nd close home. Nearest finish.
Reserved near last, had task ahead at 400M with 7Ls to make up, closed off well to take 3rd.
Away well enough from draw 1, travelled well behind leaders, took lead near 200M but couldn't hold off first 3 closing stages.
Unable to slot in, raced wide no cover in midfield for the majority of race, moved closer home turn and stayed in contention until final 150M.
Soon prominent and sat in behind leader, battled on mildly early straight, not pace to challenge leaders final 200M.
Not hurried on jumping from draw 12, towards the rear 5-6Ls back, chased steadily over final 300M without threatening.
Jumped only fairly, settled midfield 4Ls back in 6th position, couldn't muster any sort of challenge in the straight.
Soon led and set steady pace to straight, caught nearing 200M, no extra close home.

From wide draw shifted across to race towards the rear on inside, couldn't pick up early straight, held up 200M-100M then eased when no chance. (Jockey : didn't travel well throughout and dipped on a number of occasions.)
Chased leaders, 4th on settling, under pressure to maintain his position 600M, soon beaten top of straight. (Lame RF leg.)
Jumped on terms, held his position midfield, under the pump passing 600M, couldn't go on turning into straight.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced in midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 650M, no cover throughout, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, wider turning in, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place without threatening. (Dead-heat 3rd.)
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, peaked and headed 200M, stayed on evenly to the line. (Dead-Heat 3rd.)
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 500M, made some progress early in straight, no clear run near 150M, ran on evenly final 100M.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on outer, a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, made minor progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, made no impression in straight.
Made contact at start, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in the run home.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, broke down approaching 500M, quickly pulled up. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began smartly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, hit the front approaching 200M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 200M, finished 2nd.
Began well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, a bit closer on turn, angled out 450M, bumped near 350M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, angled out 550M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, bumped early in straight, peaked 300M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still 8 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed some response early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened and eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked near 500M, weakened final 400M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, assumed the lead without being pressured to do so, kicked strongly 300M soon holding a commanding lead, kept finding late to maintain margin and score.
Jumped awkwardly, maintained a midfield position, held up 400-300M before coming up with a decent finish to claim a distant 2nd close home.
From draw 2 soon prominent, tracked leader into straight, tried hard but couldn't close the gap on leader, lay in final 100M and proved difficult to ride out to finish, lost 2nd near line.
From wide draw took up a forward position tracking the pace, fought gamely throughout the straight to miss a placing narrowly. No threat to runaway winner.

Restrained after the jump, behind midfield and raced keenly after 1000M, steadied 300M then shifted out to center of track for his challenge, finished with some effect and not beaten far by the minor placegetters.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in mid-division, wide into straight but lacked a turn of foot to launch a serious bid. (Mucus / Lame next day.)
Jumped only fairly, in touch turning for home but failed to go on final 200M.
From wide draw dropped back to the rear early stages, moved closer to mid-division 900M, had a few ahead as they headed for home but lacked the dash.
Soon towards the rear, had task ahead top of straight 6Ls to make up, made no impression in the run home.
Caught wide early, steadied to near last for cover, came wide on the corner then came with a weak finish. Never likely to feature.
From wide draw taken across behind runners to settle behind midfield, briefly held up near 400M but finished off only fairly after.
From wide draw dragged back to race at the rear, had nothing to give final 400M.
Jumped on terms, maintained a midfield spot 3-wide, no cover from 900M, found little on straightening.
In touch behind leading trio, lay out home turn and found no extra top of straight, weakened to last.
Ridden along to chase the leader, traveled strongly, made good progress in the Straight.
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, commenced to improve passing 800M, responded well when asked in the Straight.
Ridden hard to lead, slightly weakened in the early Straight, kept on well to hold 3rd.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, traveled smoothly, switched in to obtain clear running near the 400M, closed off okay.
Sat rear 3 wide, responded okay when asked, ran on evenly.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled fairly, minor progress made in the Straight.
Sat towards rear, raced wide throughout, limited response when asked.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, no impression.
Sat midfield, lay in in the Straight, weakened and faded notably passing 200M (See Incident Report).
Raced in midfield early, momentarily crowded near the 800m before improving to second place near the 600m. Moved to the lead at the 200m, went on to win by 0.75L.
Raced in midfield for the majority. Travelled well entering last section when just under 2L from lead, made continual ground to move to second at 125m, finished 1.5L clear of third.

Got back to race in the final four after the start. Continued rearward entering last section when over 4L from lead before making good ground between rivals in the final furlong to move to third inside the final 50m.

Race just worse than midfield after the start when galloping nearer to the center of the track. Was 4L from the lead entering last section, improved between runners near the 200m before closing to 4th late.
Showed customary early speed to lead when racing along stand side rail. Joined by the winner at the 200m mark, gave a few lengths late.

Had no early speed & got back to race second last when galloping closest to the center of the track. Was last and 5.5L from the lead entering last section, passed a few rivals in final furlong when making up a few lengths late.

Bumped at start and raced in midfield thereafter. Shifted outwards over heels near the 400m mark when just over 3L from lead before finishing off steadily to midfield, maintaining deficit to the line in final section.

Was slow to begin & then bumped and raced a clear last early. Continued near the back and about 4L from the lead entering last section before passing a few when running onto midfield without making relative headway.

Couldn't go the early speed and got back to race near the rear along the stand side rail. Was second last and over 4L from lead passing 400m, blundered soon after, finished off steadily in late stages to midfield.

Raced forward of midfield after the start when galloping one horse in from stand side rail. Raced at the winner's quarters in the middle stages but couldn't go with him in final 300m, weakening to be beaten over 5L.
Raced in midfield when galloping a few horses in from the center of the track. Was just under 3L from the lead entering last section before weakening in the final 150m to finish eleventh.

Raced just worse than midfield early before improving to midfield in the middle stages when galloping closest to the center of the track. Peaked on run near the furlong marker and weakened in the concluding stages, beaten 6L.

Wasn't far from lead after start before being crowded between runners near the 800m & losing a length. Was ridden along passing half-way, was under 3L from the lead at the 400m before weakening to be well beaten second last.
Was ridden along at start to race in a prominent position. Was in second place early before beginning to lose ground just after half-way. Weakened poorly in the final section & finished a long last.

Moderately away, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, hit the front 250M, ran on well to the line and scored.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, angled out approaching 450M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest finish.

Began well from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run approaching 250M, cleared 200M, finished off well to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Away well, raced 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, similar position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Jumped with them, tracked leaders on the inside, 2 wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, kept on evenly thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 500M, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, hampered 200M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, slightly hampered near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3Ls or so back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, hampered 200M, eased final furlong.
Taken back to race at rear, 9 lengths or so back, still 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 8 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter.
Jumped well, sat outside the leader, pressed on at 450M, soon went 4 lengths clear, kept on nicely and just held on.
Sat behind the leaders on the rail, under pressured at 600M, took some time to respond, closed off strongly final 200M, just missed.
Not the quickest out, settled behind midfield 2 wide, stayed on okay, no threat to top 2.
Settled towards the rear, ridden along at 550M, swung to the outside, made good progress in the Straight.
Settled midfield 3 wide, angled out in the Straight, one pace to the line.
Hard ridden after the start, dispute lead, limited response in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, made little impression.
Sat prominent 2 wide, under the whip at 500M, no response and weakened. (Mucus in Trachea)
Sat at the rear, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Caught 3 wide no cover near the pace, weakened and gave ground in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards the rear, never a threat.
Settled mainly 3-wide in midfield from a wide draw, quickened well inside final 250 metres to gain upper hand close home.
In last few early, made steady headway from 10th onto home bend along the rail to be 4L back in 9th approaching straight, quickened well after obtaining clear passage inside final 200 metres.
Restrained in prominent position, some 2L back in 4th onto home bend gaining closer into straight, quickened to lead over 200 metres out and only to be swamped close to home.
Always thereabouts on the rail, came under pressure to hold place after straightening, swamped for a placing inside final 50 metres.
Niggled along to just over 2L off the pace in 6th, drifted back to midfield before tightened 1000 metres out, ran on between runners in straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled wide in last few to straight, ran on well under pressure down the centre of the track to nearest at finish.
Very wide without cover with leaders after beginning from a poor draw, taken some 3L back to 5th coming onto home bend, kept on before finding no extra 100 metres out.
Midfield early stages, lost position rounding home bend, came under pressure on straightening, produced some late impression closing stages.
Ridden to soon take up running, led until finding no extra inside final 300 metres.
Settled in forward of midfield, faded under pressure in straight.
Crowded at start, settled in last few on rail, failed to quicken under pressure after straightening.
Trailed the field most of the way, never seen with a chance.
Pressed forward from a poor draw, travelled outside race leader rounding home bend, dropped out of contention inside final 300 metres.
From draw 10 not hurried early stages, improved to race behind midfield going into home turn, dug deep under a vigorous ride to get up close home.
Stalked leader, took over passing 500M, fought hard vying for lead with a rival from top of straight, overran by winner late.
From wide draw caught wide tracking leaders, gave good response when driven top of straight, kept closing final 200M, just denied by first two.
Began awkwardly then went forward to contest the lead, caught wide no cover, ran on alongside the leader to hold every chance on straightening, faded final 100M.
Jumped fairly, settled at the back of the field, came from well back and made solid inroads final 300M, nearest finish.
Taken back to a rearward position, came wide 500M, finished off moderately, always held by leaders. (Blood in trachea.)
Raced keenly early stages, stayed close enough behind leaders, battled on early straight but struggled to go on with it passing 150M, faded late.
Settled down midfield, scrubbed along 600M, lacked the turn of foot and didn't finish off.
Jumped on terms from draw 1, maintained position just off leaders, couldn't go on passing 250M dropped right out of it.
Away awkwardly, tracked leaders early then dragged back to race in midfield, lacked the dash to be competitive on straightening.
Dropped back to near last, was well back top of straight and made no impression in the run home.
Went forward from wide draw, unable to cross until passing 700M, soon weakened turning home. (BLED.)

Made contact shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, angled out approaching 500M, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began awkwardly, raced in 2nd, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 400M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to take a place.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover in the middle stages, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 1000M, 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight.
Began well, raced behind midfield on the inside early, 2 wide from 1200M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress early in straight, no clear run final 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider 500M, 4 lengths back turning in, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Made contact shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, 2 wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 550M, finished off evenly.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider 550M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at rear on the outside, still well back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 400M, weakened and eased inside final furlong.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, headed 800M, retook the lead 500M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, angled out approaching 500M, very wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.

Bumped shortly after the start and became unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, kept on well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 12, raced prominently on the outside, took the lead near 800M, headed 500M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out after passing 550M, no daylight early in straight, cleared 300M, made some progress thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, angled out after passing 550M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, tracked leaders, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out approaching 500M, bumped and short of room early in straight, eased final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide better than midfield, there to turn, peaked 400M, weakened and eased final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well, tracked leaders on the outside, 2 lengths back turning in, finished off well to score by a head.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1-1/2L back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield, 2 wide, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared near 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back on turn, showed some response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, raced towards rear of midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Had a soft run on the leaders back throughout. Moved over heels and into clear running on straightening, made continual ground to share lead inside final 50m, got head down on line to win narrowly.
Raced just worse than midfield along the rail. Switched back towards the inside on straightening, made continual ground and was beaten a very short margin into second on line.
Pushed forward to lead & had a very soft time in front in the middle stages. Was joined by the winner inside last 50m, finished third beaten a short margin.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Was 3L from lead entering last section, had clear running on straightening, made steady ground to 4th, beaten under 2L.
Got back after start & raced third last in middle stages. Moved very wide on the track at the 400m mark when just under 6L from lead before making late ground down the outside in final stages.

Got back after the start & raced a clear second last in the middle stages. Was 6L from the lead entering last section, stayed along rail on straightening, made some late ground along the inside to finish in midfield.

Steadied after start & taken behind runners to race a clear last. Continued a clear last & nearly 9L from the lead entering last section before making late ground to midfield. Rider questioned regarding vigor â€“ see report.

Got head up leaving the straight first time before getting position 1,1. Was hard ridden passing the 600m mark, was held up from on straightening until about the 225m mark before finishing only moderately thereafter.
Was trapped racing three wide without cover about 2L from the lead in the middle stages. Peaked on effort soon after straightening before the wide passage took its toll in final furlong.

Began only fairly before racing just off of midfield between runners. Drifted slightly further back after 500m, was 6L from lead entering last section, did little in the straight & finished third last.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Was hard ridden passing the 600m, began weakening before straightening & then gave further ground in the straight and finished second last.
Began awkwardly before racing three wide with cover in midfield throughout. Was hard ridden from the 550m, was the second widest on straightening before weakening in the straight to finish last.
Ridden along to lead, traveled comfortably, responded nicely when asked, kept on well to win (Rider dropped whip).
Jumped awkwardly, sat in front of midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, raced wide throughout, closed off nicely.
Jumped awkwardly, sat in front of midfield, lay out in the Straight, finished off evenly.
Settled worse than midfield, traveled smoothly, made some ground in the Straight, ran on okay.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear on the rail, obtained clear running near 200M, one pace to the line.
Sat in front of midfield, slightly weakened rounding the Turn, hung in over the concluding stages, could not be ridden out.
Sat midfield on the rail, raced tight over the concluding stages, ran on fairly (Lame left fore).
Jumped nicely, chased the leader, weakened passing 200M (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, raced rear, could not make up ground, never a threat.
Sat midfield, traveled fairly, no impression made.
Sat towards rear, traveled fairly, limited response when asked (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, raced rear, no contention.
Had a nice run in midfield along the rail. Was only 2.5L from lead on straightening, came through between runners at 150m before closing to take lead inside final 50m to win.

Hard ridden from outside gate to lead when racing wide before crossing to rail approaching the first bend. Continued in the lead until being caught by winner inside last 50m & was brave late, finishing clear of third.

Pushed forward to challenge for lead before being crossed approaching the first bend & racing second away from the rail. Shared lead on straightening, tried hard but couldn't match the first two, hold third on line.

Raced in midfield away from the rail. Over-raced during the early & middle stages, drifted slightly further back around 500m bend, shifted wider on straightening, finished steadily down the outside late.

Challenged for lead early before being crossed approaching the first bend & racing on the leaders back thereafter. Had clear running on straightening when just behind lead, gave a length in the straight to finish in midfield.

Raced just worse than midfield when three wide with cover. Improved to midfield around the bend, was just over 4L from the lead entering last section, made up a few lengths late to finish in midfield without threatening.

Raced three wide with cover in midfield early, improved after the 650m mark, raced in fourth position around the bend. Was only 1.5L from the lead entering last section, gave a length or so in last furlong.

Began fairly, was last after the start. Was racing second last between runners before being steadied to avoid horses near 550m. Was third last and 6L from the lead entering last section, made some late headway well back.

Hampered after start, got back to race third last when three wide without cover. Continued wide around bend, was the widest runner on straightening when about 5L from lead, finished off ok but was never in the race.

Jumped fairly & got back to last along rail. Was checked away from heels near the 600m & lost ground. Was 7.5L from lead entering last section, came wider on straightening, unable to be ridden out last 125m when held up.

Raced just worse than midfield between runners. Shifted down to rail just after first bend, was just under 5L from lead entering last section, failed to finish off, hampered in final stages but was already beaten.

Began fairly, raced worse than midfield along rail. Shifted out on first bend & checked away from heels of rival runner & lost ground. Was 6.5L from lead entering last section, stayed along rail in straight but did nothing.
Shifted in at the start and made contact with the right side of its barrier, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced in 3rd, 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back turning in, rider's left foot slipped from stirrup early in straight, ran on same pace thereafter.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly and made contact, raced towards rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Jumped on terms, settled in a box seat position, closed off nicely near the rail, always doing enough.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, began to improve at 550M, switched out in the Straight, showed strong dash from 350M to 100M, only one pace to the line.
Aggressively ridden from the start, led and travelled smoothly throughout, kept on nicely until slightly weakened final 100M.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, stayed on fairly. (See Incident Report)
Jumped well, hard ridden early, sat just off the leader 2 wide, on terms with the leader at 250M, weakened afterwards.
Settled midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, under pressure from 500M, limited response in the Straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Sat at the rear on the rail, never really involved.
Settled last, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Jumped with the field, was hampered at 1500M, settled on pace 2 wide, lost ground at 600M and weakened.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, never in contention.
Began well settling within striking distance in 3rd or 4th on rail, came to challenge under pressure after straightening, gained upper hand about 50 metres out.
Travelled 3-wide in worse than midfield, saved ground for 4L 6th turning in for home, ran on to hold every chance but over-shadowed by eventual winner close to home.
Broke well to lead attempting to make all, joined by others upon straightening and swamped close to home.
Improved steadily from a wide draw reaching 3rd 3-wide 900 metres out and 2nd 700 metres out, disputed lead into straight but had no more to give 50 metres out.
Mainly in just worse than midfield to straight, ran on to be nearest finish.
Prominent early briefly despite moderate start, soon dropped to midfield into back straight and further back turning in for home, made steady progress to be nearest at finish.
Jumped awkwardly, well back to straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Well back to straight, hampered briefly inside the 200 metres, only ran past beaten horses.
Very slowly away from a poor draw, travelled wide in last few running widest into straight, failed to quicken to threaten.
Close up early briefly, gradually drifted back to 5th just better than midfield, lost further ground upon straightening.
Hard ridden for close-up 2nd, gave ground gradually from over 600 metres out.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield to straight, dropped out of contention to last place 200 metres out.
Jumped well enough, tracked leaders in a slowly run race, lengthened nicely to lead inside 200M, eased off closing stages when well in control.
Settled behind midfield 3-wide without cover, travelled well with little change to the turn, driven wide top of straight, came from a fair way back to finish joint 2nd.
Jumped on terms, restrained in midfield just over 3Ls off the pace, tracked path of eventual winner turning in, always held by winner in the run home but kept closing doggedly to finish joint 2nd.
Steadied after the start, maintained a midfield position along the fence, 4Ls away 400M, worked home hard under top weight for a 4th place finish. (Bled / Lame next day.)
Jumped cleanly from draw 1, set slow pace to straight, led them to 200M then wilted in the running late stages.
Pressed forward to be racing just off leader, fought hard early straight to maintain his position, couldn't sustain effort late, held ground near the line.
Jumped only fairly, ended up racing towards the rear, made moderate progress on straightening but had to shift lane near 100M to continue forward.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, in last place at 400M 7Ls off the pace, went for inside passage but had difficulty obtaining clear running over final 150M. Inconclusive effort.
Away with them, dropped back to a rearward spot 6Ls away, just battled to the line. Never threatened.
Taken back from wide draw, held up near last over 6Ls off the slow pace, hard pressed inside 500M but couldn't pick up well enough.
Tracked leaders in a slowly run race, always under pressure to maintain his position, weakened away 250M to finish last. (Jockey : would appreciate a firmer surface.)
Clean jump, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, took the lead 450M, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers.

Bumped on jumping, held up in rear, 10 lengths or so back, a bit closer in the middle stages, commenced move approaching 500M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 650M, commenced move 450M, very wide turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Bumped on jumping, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, closer on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on same pace to the line.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, not enough room early in straight, kept on same pace thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.

Shifted out on jumping and made contact, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 650M, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.

Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, moved closer after passing 600M, 2 wide from 450M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furling. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2-1/2 lengths, peaked and headed 450M, weakened early in straight.
