Fast into stride, took the lead easily, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight, won by 1-1/4L.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths back, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, made minor progress in straight.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide in the middle stages, 9 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, showed some response early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, weakened from 500M, eased final furlong.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the outside, still well back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled well behind and waited with after beginning from a poor draw, baulked for a run early in straight, responded well inside final 200 metres to snatch victory near the line.
Amongst leaders early before taken back to 3rd on rails just off the pace, ran on under pressure inside final 250 metres to hit the front 100 metres out but only to be caught close to home.

Prominent from a poor draw looking for cover, settled in 7th some 5L back without cover shortly after, further away from the pace into home straight, ran on inside final 250 metres to be nearest at finish despite laying in.

Held up in midfield on rails, gradually pulled his way forward to 5th about 4L off the pace, angled out for a run over 500 metres out and ran on under pressure to hold some chance briefly over 100 metres out.
Sluggish at start before picking up to 9th and then 8th over 1000 metres out, saved ground on rails turning in for home, made good progress under pressure in the run to the line.

Began well from the widest draw to soon take up running off the rails, obtained rails run over 1000 metres out kicking some 2L clear rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Never better than midfield, tightened between runners about 300 metres out, made no further impression.
Restrained in midfield in 6th, found nothing in straight.
Niggled along in 2nd, faded under pressure shortly after straightening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon detached from the main body of the field, never seen with a chance.
Ridden to first few about 2L off the pace, weakened noticeably after straightening.
Chased the leader, traveled comfortably, made good ground in the Straight, kept on well to win.
Ridden along to lead, saved ground on turn, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner (Must stalls test).
Sat in front of midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, responded okay under pressure.
Sat worse than midfield, made some progress over the concluding stages.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled okay, was bumped near the 250M, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, sat midfield 2 wide, one pace to the line.
Sat midfield on the rail, was steadied and crowded near the 250M, close off fairly.
Sat rear, raced keenly rounding the Turn, disappointing for clear run near 200M, blundered and held up, could not be ridden out (Rider dropped his whip).
Jumped only fairly, sat behind midfield 2 wide, angled out round the Turn, minor progress when asked.
Sat handy, traveled fairly, gave ground at the top of the Straight, faded gradually.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, raced greenly, was steadied and held up in the Straight, lay in inside the final 300M.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, was steadied when raced tight rounding the Turn, limited response in the Straight.
Sat handy, weakened inside 300M, shifted in abruptly and being corrected inside 250M, no impression.
Settled midfield, raced wide from 900M, traveled only fairly, no contention.
Raced along the rail just behind the leading pair. Switched over the heels of the leader near the 350m, surged to lead at 125m & drew clear to win very easily.
Raced in midfield between runners early. Was ridden along before straightening, was 3.5L from the lead entering last section, closed steadily to steal a well beaten second in the final few strides.

Pushed forward to lead when racing away from the rail. Crossed to the rail when leading approaching first corner, continued in the lead until being passed by the winner at the 125m mark, caught for second in final few strides.

Drifted back to race worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Was the widest runner on straightening, was 5.5L from lead entering last section, passed a number of runners when finishing off ok down the outside from a long way back.

Was slow to begin, improved along the rail to race worse than midfield in middle stages. Was over 4L from the lead on straightening, was held up passing the 350m, shifted outwards before closing steadily in late stages.

Got back to race second last along rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening, was 5.5L from the lead entering last section, drifted outwards in the straight, passed a few runners in the final stages without threatening.
Raced fourth away from the rail throughout. Was ridden along from the 550m, was only 2.25L from the lead entering last section, peaked near the 200m, weakened thereafter.

Raced in midfield between runners. Drifted slightly further back approaching the corner, was just over 5L from the lead on straightening, drifted out early in straight, finished only moderately to line & was beaten over 7L.
Was trapped racing three wide without cover just forward of midfield. Drifted slightly further back approaching corner, hung out slightly on straightening before weakening to be beaten over 7L.

Drifted back after the start, getting back to race third last away from the rail. Was second last and over 7L from the lead entering last section, passed a few to the line but was too far back to be a genuine threat.
Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Was ridden along before straightening when leader went a length clear, weakened out in final 300m & was well beaten.
Raced in midfield along the rail. Stayed along the rail on straightening when having clear ground but weakened poorly to be well beaten.
Drifted back after the start and raced at the tail. Moved wider on the track nearing the 600m, was a clear last on straightening when 8.5L from the lead, weakened badly to be a distant second last.
Raced three wide with cover in midfield for the majority. Was beaten before straightening, weakened out badly in the straight to finish a distant last.
Began well, raced better than midfield, 1 to 2 lengths back, easy run to turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Began smartly, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths back, moved closer on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 300M, finished off strongly to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, found rail near 600M, 4 lengths back turning in, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on outer, there to turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1000M, retook the lead near 800M, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, steadied near 900M, 5 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Jumped only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced prominently but 3 wide, took the lead 1000M, headed near 800M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped nicely, ridden along early to assume the lead, kept on strongly, battled to the line, always doing enough.
Began okay, showed good early speed to sit just behind the leaders, made good progress along the rail, always held. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, travelled smoothly, switched out final 150M and continued to run on, closest finish.
Broke alertly, settled in a prominent position 2 wide, held up early in the Straight, closed off fairly final 200M.
Jumped slowly, raced keenly in the early stages towards the rear, navigated through traffic in the Straight, stayed on once in the clear.
Sat just outside the leader, kept on until weakened final 75M. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, began to improve from the 650M, only one pace to the line.
Settled midfield on the rail, ran on only evenly.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, limited response until final 100M, made some late ground final 50M.
Sat midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Raced towards the rear 2 wide, made no ground in the Straight.
Sat last, raced ungenerously throughout, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, never in contention.
Raced at the rear, never a factor.
Pressed forward from the widest draw to soon lead, obtained rails run about 1100 metres under restraint, held 1L advantage into straight before forging clear under pressure.

Pressed forward from a wide gate, amongst leaders early before shifting just over 1L back to 4th 3-wide, improved to 2nd outside race leader onto home bend, failed to quicken under pressure to challenge in straight.
Began well with rails run amongst race leaders early stages but gradually shifting back for 3rd just behind the pace, came to challenge under pressure in straight but failed to quicken to threaten.

Jumped best, travelled keenly while taken back reaching 4th about 2L off the pace leaving the 1100 metres, remained quite keen rounding home bend, one-paced under pressure in straight before finding no extra close to home.
Held up just worse than midfield in 8th on rails, gained 7th before shifting out for a run approaching home bend, obtained clear passage over 300 metres out but unable to quicken to threaten.
Settled just off the pace in 5th on rails just over 2L off the pace, soon came under pressure after straightening but unable to quicken to threaten.
Settled well behind travelling keenly briefly rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening down the inside of straight.
Began awkwardly losing ground before settling in midfield or just worse, wide rounding home bend and into straight, found nothing under pressure.
Ridden early before setting in midfield in 6th, wide rounding home bend and into straight, wandered about under pressure after straightening and soon dropped out of contention.
Taken back to last few after beginning from a poor draw, wide into straight, never seen with a chance.
Knuckled over on jumping losing ground, always at the back and never seen with a chance.
Caught wide early stages before slotting into a midfield spot along the 2-path, swung wide home turn, kept closing doggedly to gain lead 150M, gamely held off the persistent runner up late stages.

Bounded on jumping and lost ground, raced as the back marker before commencing a rapid forward move 1200M, caught wide no cover home turn, finished off well enough but was always held by winner final 200M.
Jumped awkwardly, soon led setting a fast pace for the first half of the race, kicked nicely clear early straight, caught by first two inside 150M, held on well for 3rd.
Settled down in mid-division, driven along 500M, kept battling in the straight to take 4th near line.
Tracked leaders on inside, tried hard on straightening but lacked a turn of foot to launch a serious bid.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, at the back of the field from 1200M, 5Ls to make up 400M, stayed on moderately.
Settled behind midfield, struggled to pick up when the race got serious and was only fair to the line.
Obtained a position behind midfield, came under pressure middle stages, couldn't finish it off turning home. (Jockey : failed to handle the Yielding track conditions)
From wide draw moved up to press leader on outside in a race with genuine pace, under the pump 550M, soon beaten on straightening. (Jockey : changed tactics from wide draw but that didn't suit him.)
Held up behind midfield, checked 1400M, fell back to a rearward position after, failed to finish off on straightening. (Jockey : failed to travel at any stage after incident near 1400M.)
Chased leaders, shifted out to a 3-wide spot without cover from 1000M, struggled to keep up 500M, soon weakened and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on outer, moved closer on turn, finished off strongly to score, won by a narrow margin.

Away well, raced prominently on the inside early, allowed rival to cross 1100M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Taken back to race 3 wide with cover towards rear, moved a bit closer after passing 900M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to make frame.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few final 50M. (A laceration to the right hind pastern.)
Fast into stride, sent forward to race in 2nd, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well until approaching final 50M, weakened thereafter. (Bled.)
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter. (Lame both front legs next day morning.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Clean jump, tracked leaders, 3 wide, 2 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take 2nd.
Moderately away, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, hit the front 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home.

Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, same margin back turning in, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to make frame, nearest finish. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 550M, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began well from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened inside final furlong.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 700M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 3-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Away with them, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, found rail near 400M, 2 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 400M, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, 3/4L back turning in, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 4 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Out with rest, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 5-1/2L back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length back turning in, inconvenienced early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, failed to make any progress thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, unable to slot in, trapped very wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Soon led from wide draw and was allowed an uncontested lead, kicked strongly passing 400M under 10lb claimer, drew well clear mid-straight and was never challenged in the run home.
Tracked leader, bustled along 450M but couldn't get closer to the eventual winner, fought hard and held on for 2nd.
Tracked the pace on inside, lacked the dash to challenge leader passing 300M, kept battling to the line to hold 3rd.
Chased leaders early before settling down in a position ahead of midfield, worked home steadily final 300M but was always held by first few.
In midfield, held his position 7th entering home turn, fought on mildly passing 300M but found wanting closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards the rear further back than intended for cover, made limited progress on straightening, never in the hunt.
Held up behind midfield 6Ls back, came home fairly, never likely to feature. (Lame next day.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners and taken back to last 10Ls off the pace early stages, had some work to do 400M but got home only fairly. Never involved.
Commenced only fairly then dropped back to near last early stages, about 8Ls to make up 400M, lacked a kick in the straight. (Jockey lost whip 100M.)
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, given a waiting ride towards the rear, had the task ahead top of straight, failed to finish off.
Restrained in midfield 4Ls off the pace, similar position at the turn but couldn't go on with it, weakened rapidly final 200M.
Unable to slot in from draw 8, caught wide no cover chasing leaders for the majority of race, couldn't keep up 500M, weakened and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Ridden along to chase the leader 2 wide, traveled comfortably, made good ground over the final 50M, kept on well to win.
Settled in front of midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, responded okay when asked inside 100M, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear on the rail, was held up rounding the Turn, closed off okay.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled smoothly, kept on well until no extra to hold 4th.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled okay, made some progress inside 150M, one pace thereafter.
Sat towards rear, minor progress made in the early Straight, one pace to the finish.
Settled behind midfield, traveled fairly, limited response when asked.
Sat rear, commenced to improve approaching 600M, could not make up ground entering the Straight (See Incident Report).
Settled midfield, traveled fairly, no clear run until near 200M, no impression.
Jumped awkwardly, ridden hard to lead, weakened entering the Straight, never a threat.
Settled midfield, switched out and rolled forward to chase the leader passing 1000M, raced wide thereafter, gave ground over the concluding stages (See Incident Report).
Settled midfield, raced wide throughout, weakened and fade notably rounding the Turn (Unacceptable Performance, Must BT).
Jumped well from middle draw to share lead before taking leader's back on rail at 800. Came off fence on point of turn, took lead at 150m and fought on strongly to win.
Jumped on terms but soon drifted back to be ninth on the fence. Held up slightly when trying to improve approaching 800m. Closed quickly last 100m when in clear ground to take second.
Ridden along from rails draw to hold forward position, but had to ease first turn, settling fifth the rail. Came to centre of track on straightening and ran on strongly to take third.
Went forward to dispute lead taking over and crossing to rail at 800m. Headed at 150m, fought on but swamped last 20m to just miss placings.
Ridden hard from the gates to hold forward position. Inconvenienced on first turn. Chased along to be third the fence, stayed on well for fifth after laying in first half of straight.
Lacked early speed, settling near the rear. Ridden along before the turn and ran on fairly near the rail to be closest on the line.
Jumped quickly but soon three wide coming to first turn, ridden along to be one off the rails at 800m. Brought three wide to challenge on straightening but soon one paced to the line.
Even start, settling midfield one-off fence. Travelled well to turn, coming to centre of track, slight bump 200m. Stayed on last 150m.
Jumped evenly, settling slightly worst than midfield one-off fence. Eased slightly coming to 800m as pace slackened. Ran home fairly down middle of track.
Slow to move and held up before crossing to rail to be last. Ridden along near rails from top of straight, one paced last 200m.
Caught three wide early, before dropping into moving line, one-off fence worse than midfield. Went forward three wide again from 800m, shifted out on point of turn, no impression and well beaten.
Jumped fairly but soon in rear division, three wide with cover. Widest on corner and eased slightly at top of straight, failed to make ground.
Made contact shortly after start, raced prominently on the outside, shared lead from 450M, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to the line, won by 1/2L. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Made contact shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival from 450M, peaked and headed early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Began well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made no impression in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, taken back to race at rear on the outside, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, switched out to 3 wide at 800M to improve, closed off strongly, got up in the final stride.
Sat box-seat, travelled smoothly throughout, hit the front at 100M, just can't hold off the winner.
Tracked leader 2 wide, kept on nicely in the Straight.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made good ground near the rail.
Caught 3 wide no cover throughout the early and middle stages, challenged the leader at 550, kept on until weakened final 100M.
Jumped slowly, sat the rear, stayed on fairly. (Blood in trachea)
Settled midfield on the rail, ran on evenly.
Settled at the rear on the rail, made some late ground, not tested.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Broke well and showed good early speed to lead, under pressure at 400M, limited response.
Raced behind the leaders, never impress.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, under pressure from 700M, weakened quickly and faded.
Tracked leaders, commenced move approaching home turn, hit the front upon straightening and soon drew clear.
Settled behind midfield, obtained clear run shortly after straightening, finished off race strongly inside final 150 metres.
Well there 3-wide, drifted backward gradually in back straight reaching 4th leaving 700 metres, renewed effort entering home straight but failed to quickened to threaten.
Never far off on rail, came under pressure after straightening, kept on at the same pace without threatening.
Broke well holding slender lead most of the way until headed on straightening, soon weakened.
Travelled in midfield, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Prominent early, gradually drifted backward towards rear 3-wide, remained in similar position into straight, ran home one-paced.
Crowded after awkward start, soon recovered to midfield between 7th and 5th with rails run, ridden into straight but could find nothing.
Nearly unseated rider at start, trailed the field most of the way to straight, ran past well-beaten horses only.
Began fairly from a poor draw settling wide without cover in midfield, remained similar and widest into home straight, soon faded under pressure.
Soon taken back to last few from a poor draw, remained well behind to straight, never seen with a chance.
Soon led and dictated the race, skipped away early straight, was challenged by a rival late stages but had enough in reserves to hold on.
Chased leaders on inside, little change at the home turn, tried hard to close the gap on winner but came up short.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards the rear 7-8Ls behind leader, driven nearing 400M, came with a good run from well back to get 3rd without reaching first two.
Hampered on jumping then taken back to near the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, stayed on moderately to claim a distant 4th.
Unable to slot in, raced wide no cover in midfield, struggled to make an impression over final 300M, held ground to the line.
Chased leaders before falling back to a position ahead of midfield, worked home only fairly final 300M. No threat to leaders.
Caught wide early before crossing to race outside leader, couldn't go on passing 300M, faded towards the finish.
Began awkwardly, settled down midfield 5Ls off the pace, gave limited response on straightening and couldn't get into the finish.
Slow to begin, settled behind midfield further back than intended, hard driven 450M but made no impression in the run home.
Jumped fairly, adopted a midfield position 5Ls on settling, struggled to keep up from 500M, already beaten when eased down in the home straight. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Obtained an on-pace position, under the pump 500M, fell away sharply early straight and eased over final 200M. (Jockey : didn't handle the 'Good to Yielding' track conditions)
From wide draw dropped back to race in last, came under serious pressure home turn, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Began smartly, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line, lost second close home.

Moderately away from gate 11, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths back on turn, commenced move 350M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the outside, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 600M, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped only fairly, raced towards rear, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently on the stands' rail, shared lead in the middle stages, hard ridden approaching 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 75M.
Shifted right at start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.

Made contact at start, positioned 2Ls behind the leader on the middle track in the early stages, unable to maintain position midway, 3 to 4Ls back at 400M, closed off well to make frame without threatening. (Lost right hind plate.)
Bumped shortly after start, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden from 350M, kept on evenly until 75M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lost left front plate.)
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, made no progress final 400M.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival in the middle stages, peaked on run 300M, weakened final 250M.
Away well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, 2 away from the stands' rail, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 4 lengths or so back in the middle stages, hard ridden 400M but only showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 4 lengths or so back, hard ridden 350M, showed no response, weakened 200M, eased final 100M.
Jumped well ridden to front, in early three horse speed battle before clear lead 1400m. Steadied pace middle stages of race. Kicked clear early in straight, easy win.
Held rails and settled leader's back, asked for effort at 300m mark, no match for winner but safely held second position.
Settled midfield in clear running, soon three wide with cover as pace slowed, made good ground to 200m to be third and stayed on final stages.
Caught wide on first turn and pushed on to be in battle for lead, before settling one out, one back. Clear run from top of straight, tended to lay in slightly, stayed on.
Crossed to rail at tail of field, stayed near fence in straight taking inside runs, finishing on fairly, closest at finish.
Settled in rear group, one off fence. Three wide from 800m and moved up widest on home turn. Last at 400m, ran on fairly, peaked on run 100m out.
Eased at start to cross to rail, settling second last. Stayed near rail, one paced in straight. Slight bump from outside at 200m but made no impression.
Five wide first turn, ridden to contest lead before settling outside leader at 1400m. Ridden along from 400m, soon under pressure and faded last 200m.
Jumped well, behind lead group early. Shuffled back worse than midfield when pace slowed. Held up for run 350m-200m but one paced when clear.
Jumped on terms, three wide first turn, ridden along to stay in touch with leaders three wide throughout, in touch on turn but beaten at 300m mark.
Sat handy, traveled smoothly, crowded and no clear run until 200M, made good progress thereafter, closed off strongly.
Ridden along to lead, traveled nicely, kept on well but not a threat to the winner.
Settled in front of midfield, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, responded well when asked.
Shared the lead, traveled okay, slightly weakened passing 150M, ran on evenly.
Settled midfield on the rail, traveled fairly, minor progress made in the Straight.
Sat rear, showed some response when asked entering the Straight, closed off okay.
Sat towards rear, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, finished off fairly (See Incident Report).
Sat midfield, not much response when asked, ran on only fairly (Disappointing Performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, weakened passing 300M, never a threat.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, weakened notably near 200M, never a factor.
Sat towards rear, was eased down entering the Straight, no impression (Unacceptable Performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Sat midfield, raced wide throughout, weakened and faded entering the Straight, no contention (Blood in trachea, Unacceptable Performance, Must BT).
Jumped well, quickly in perfect position, one out, one back. Angled out top of straight, took lead passing 200m, safely held winning margin last 150m.
Ridden forward from gates to settle clear second. Challenged leader top of straight, took lead 200m out but soon headed by winner. Fought on well.
No early speed, at tail early then last at 600m one off fence and crowded for room. Came wide to make run, still last at 300m, closed strongly final stages for third.
Even jump from rails draw, came off fence at 1400m and then three wide with cover. Came widest top of straight, made ground peaked on run final 100m.
Slow to move but ridden forward on rail to find lead. Increased tempo before turn, challenged passing 400m, headed at 200m, stayed on for fifth.
Travelled keenly, third the fence. Held up slightly approaching 300m waiting for clear run, one paced when clear final 250m.
Went back from wide gate, last on rails half way point. Held up for run early part of straight, taken back to inside passing 200m and ran on fairly when in clear ground.
Settled midfield on rails, didn't have a lot of room early part of straight but failed to run on when in clear ground.
Hard ridden early to find forward position, before trapped three wide midfield most of trip. Pushed along before turn, had to ease passing 300m, one pace to finish.
Settle back half of field, one off fence. Travelled well, blocked for run approaching 300m, eased and then offered no more.
Bumped start, slightly inconvenienced near 950M, raced in midfield on the middle track, moved a bit closer midway, hit the front 250M, kept on very well to the line, won comfortably.
Crowded shortly after start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, commenced move after passing 300M, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Crowded start, raced at rear, 6 lengths back at 400M, finished off strongly to take a place without threatening the first two.
Crowded shortly after start, raced behind midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden approaching 300M, kept on well to the line to make frame without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, 3 lengths back at 400M, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, made some progress after passing 300M, no extra final 100M.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L at 400M, peaked and headed 250M, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped well from gate 14, raced towards rear, 6 lengths back at 400M, passed some tired runners final 300M.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the middle track, hard ridden from 400M, kept on evenly until approaching 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race prominently on the stands' rail, hard ridden 350M but only showed limited response, weakened quickly final furlong.
Bumped shortly after start, raced slightly better than midfield on the stands' side, peaked in the middle stages, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced behind midfield, nearer to the middle track, ridden 300M but showed no response, weakened final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted right at start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, 3 away from the stands' rail, unable to maintain position in the middle stages, weakened final 300M.
Moderately away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Bled.)
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, improved between horses from the 800M, tracked through nicely before switching out in the Straight, closed off nicely, just got there on the line.
Ridden along early to sit outside the lead, kept on nicely, just got caught final stride. (See Incident Report)
Settled towards the rear 3 wide with cover, stayed on well for 3rd.
Not the quickest out, ridden along to assume the lead, kept on okay final weakened final 75M. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield 2 wide between horses, took some time to respond before staying on nicely final 150M.
Jumped nicely and sat box seated, held up for the majority of the Straight, never seriously tested.
Raced in front of midfield 2 wide, only one pace to the line. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide no cover on pace, kept on only fairly.
Settled midfield on the rail, had trouble finding clear running in the Straight, ran on very late.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, made little impression. (See Incident Report)
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, limited response in the Straight.
Sat last, never in contention.
Settled midfield 3 wide, weakened and faded final 250M. (See Incident Report) (Performance disappointing, must trial)
Sat worse than midfield 3 wide, never a factor. (Bled, must trial)
Began well from a poor draw travelling wide without cover in prominent position, came to join race leader 1000 metres out and hit the front narrowly on straightening, hung on well to the line.

Began moderately and soon improved to close-up position, gradually shifted backward to joint 5th some 3L back on rail over 1000 metres out, angled out for a run into straight, ran on steadily under pressure.
Ridden positively 3-wide, obtained rails run in front over 1000 metres out, led until narrowly headed by eventual winner entering straight, kept on well for 3rd.
Travelled keenly just off the pace 2-wide in 3rd or 4th, awkward behind runner 850 metres out, remained within 2L of pace into straight, gradually faded under pressure.
Settled towards rear from a poor draw, went widest into straight, ran on steadily under pressure near the centre of the track.
Began well from the widest draw settling 3-wide better than midfield in joint 5th, lost position when wider into straight, recovered some late ground closing stages.
Began well but soon taken well back, went wide into straight, made up good ground under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Began well before taken back to last few on rail, saved ground turning in for home sneaking up to 8th, sustained progress early in straight but could find no extra closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly setting 3-wide in midfield, became 9th just worse than midfield leaving the 1000 metres, shifted wide into straight, only produced moderate impression close to home.
Prominent early before settling in rear of midfield, lost position rounding home bend, made no impression in the run to the line.
Soon took up running on the rail, ceded advantage for one back position about 1150 metres out, came under pressure after straightening and weakened noticeably inside final 200 metres.
Began moderately settling in midfield on rail, saved ground turning in for home, kept on before fading under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Always well back, came under pressure in last few early in home straight, never seen with a chance.
Lost considerable ground at start and detached from the main body of the field throughout, never seen with a chance.

Reserved in midfield, pressed along near 600M, still had some ground to make up top of straight, showed good stamina and dug deep to get home narrowly. (Trainer : advantaged by being stepped up in distance.)
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, travelled best of all home turn, let down well on straightening, led 180M, just couldn't hold off winner late stages.
Settled ahead of midfield in a fast run race, moved up to 3rd 1000M, loomed behind leader top of straight, briefly led 200M but was outstayed by first two late stages.
Sent forward to the lead, pressed by rival on outside setting fast pace early and middle stages, driven 500M and maintained lead until mid-straight, no extra closing stages.
Reserved near last over 10Ls off leader in a fast run race, swung widest for home and had plenty to do 400M, made limited progress only.
Settled in second half of the field 9-10Ls off the fast pace, failed to find much from 500M and got to the line only fairly. Never in the picture.
From wide draw taken back, given a waiting ride in last over 10Ls off the fast pace, had task in hand 400M and never looked likely, ran past beaten horses in the run home. (Lame RF leg.)
Tracked the pace setting duo, 5Ls away middle stages, under the pump 700M, couldn't keep up passing 250M, fell away sharply.
Jumped only fairly, reserved towards the rear in fast run race, plenty to do 400M but couldn't muster any sort of challenge in the straight.
Vied for lead on outside setting fast pace, came under pressure 800M, no extra top of straight and weakened. (Jockey : may have been better suited by obtaining cover in middle stages.)
Settled behind midfield, little change at the turn but came up empty on straightening, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight, won by 2 lengths.
Began fairly, positioned 1-3/4L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Jumped only fairly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1/2L back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.

Bumped start, taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly inconvenienced at start, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Shifted out at start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Fast into stride, tracked leaders, 3 wide with no cover, peaked on run approaching 400M, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect. (Mucus.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the outside, dropped towards rear on turn, emptied early in straight.
Began only fairly, showed no speed, raced at tail, 11 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield but trapped very wide, unable to maintain position on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took toll. (Mucus.)
Clean jump, raced prominently, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, hit the front 300M, kept on strongly, easily scored.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, stayed on well to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, closed off well to take a place.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, still last turning in, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, peaked on run 300M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same position on turn, kept on same pace in the run home.
Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 1-3/4L back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Away well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, travelled keenly and steadied near 700M, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Well there from a poor draw, came to join race leader rounding home bend, hit the front on straightening and just held on to the line.
Improved steadily from moderate start to reach 5th some 2L back rounding home bend, fought on under pressure in straight to just fail to get up on line.
Settled wide in midfield, ran on under pressure down the centre of home straight to snatch 3rd late.
Always thereabouts, held every chance early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
Settled towards rear, saved ground turning in for home, baulked for a run until the 300 metres, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled well behind from a poor draw dropping to last rounding home bend, shifted out for a run on straightening, made up good late ground.
Attempted to make all, unable to sustain effort and overhauled shortly after turning into straight.
Jumped awkwardly, travelled wide towards rear most of way, ran on past well-beaten horses in straight.
Prominent on rail to straight, weakened inside final 250 metres.
Not far off in 5th early stages, lost position rounding home bend and into straight, made no further impression.
Jumped awkwardly travelling in last few, made short-lived effort on rail turning in for home, found no extra over 250 metres out.
Never better than midfield, run ended over 200 metres out.
Always at the back and never seen with a chance.

Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Blundered on jumping, positioned 3 wide, a length or so back, no cover throughout, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, always held.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 3rd, nearest finish.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly, lost 3rd on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.

Knuckled over on jumping and lost ground, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, cleared 200M, one-paced thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide from 700M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the outside, moved closer after passing 800M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Chased leaders in 3rd, remained in touch 400M, quickened well to challenge for the lead nearing 100M, gained upper hand close home.
Began well from draw 1, soon led setting fast pace under 7lb claimer, kicked 2L clear early straight, joined by rival nearing 100M, grudgingly gave way close home.
From wide draw given a waiting ride, settled towards the rear 9Ls off the fast pace, closed off final 400M fastest coming from a long way back to get 3rd, nearest finish.
Tracked leader in a fast run race, held 2nd spot until 250M, ran home one paced final stages.
Settled midfield in a fast run race, stayed on final 300M without threatening.
Held up midfield in a fast run race, 7Ls to make up top of straight, worked home fairly without threatening.
Caught wide early then shifted in and chased leaders along the 2-path in a fast run race, driven along 500M but couldn't launch a challenge.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in midfield further back than intended 7Ls away , travelled only fairly during the race and failed to close off.
Awkwardly away and lost ground, lacked early pace, in detached last over 10Ls behind leader, plenty to do top of straight, ran past beaten horses only.
Jumped awkwardly, towards the rear over 10Ls off the fast pace, had big task in hand 400M but only made limited progress.
Jumped only fairly, chased leaders in a fast run race, came under serious pressure home turn, soon beaten.
From wide draw dropped back towards the rear, 10Ls to make up 400M, held up 200-150M but failed to finish off over the concluding stages. (Jockey questioned riding tactics.)
Jumped nicely, sat handy, traveled strongly, made good ground passing 200M, kept on well to win.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, traveled smoothly, responded well when asked, closed off nicely.
Jumped only fairly, sat handy on the rail, traveled nicely, ran on evenly to the finish (See Incident Report).
Ridden along to lead, traveled okay, weakened slightly passing 200M, one pace to the line.
Sat towards rear on the rail, switched out rounding the Turn, was briefly held up at 300M, made some progress over the final 75M.
Sat worse than midfield, gave ground slightly rounding the Turn, one pace thereafter.
Sat towards rear, traveled fairly, no impression made in the Straight.
Stood flat-footed on jumping, sat rear, switched in to obtain clear running, closed off only fairly (Barrier manners unacceptable, Must BT).
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide throughout, weakened entering the Straight (See Incident Report).
Settled behind midfield, traveled fairly, minor progress made.
Settled midfield on the rail, traveled okay, but failed to respond under pressure, could not be ridden out to the finish (See Incident Report).
Settled midfield, limited response when asked, weakened inside 150M, no contention.
Jumped evenly and crossed to rail to settle midfield on fence. Eased slightly at 550m, quickly off fence to challenge top of straight, closed late to just get up last bound.
Ridden forward to cross to fifth one off fence on settling. Three wide run at 500m mark and challenged down centre of track. Went to line in stride with winner to miss narrowly.
Jumped well and ridden up to race second outside leader. Found front just before turn, kicked clear at 200m, fought on strongly. Headed on the line by two runners out wide.
Eased to take up good position, fourth in clear running by half way mark. Made run three wide on turn and soon clear second at 200m. Fought on and run out of placings last 25m.
Only jumped fairly and in rear group early. Stayed near inside to make run in straight. Crowded for room 300m to 200m and ran on well when clear .
Jumped well from inside gate, settled behind leader. Held up slightly behind tiring leader before turn but soon in clear ground. Layed in slightly and straightened 150m, one paced final stages.
Reared as gates opened, losing considerable ground. Tailed field down back, chased hard to be in contact on home turn and ran on strongly. Big run.
Settled midfield early and eased slightly and shuffled pack a pair at 800m as horse in front crossed. Brought to middle of track in straight, ran on fairly.
Blinkers applied first time, bumped on jumping, ridden early to try and hold position, but settled rear group on fence. Around tiring leader at 250m mark , soon under pressure.
Three wide rear group at first turn, then three wide no cover down back. Made run down middle of track but beaten passing 200m mark. Dropped out.
Slow to move, ridden forward three wide to fifth half way mark. Under pressure and drifted wide home turn, dropped out last 200m.
Driven forward from outside gate to cross to lead just after first turn. Headed just before straightening and faded badly run home. Long last.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.

Began well, raced prominently but 3 wide, slightly taken back after passing 650M, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, showed good response early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 50M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear, bumped near 800M, 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on outer, 4 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, kept on same pace in the run home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 length or so back turning in, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear, bumped near 800M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Lame left front leg.)
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened 200M, eased final 100M. (Bled.)
Hard ridden early to be prominent, sat outside the lead at 1200M, kept on strongly in the Straight, always doing enough.
Jumped nicely and showed good early speed to lead, kept on and battled hard to the line, always held.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, under pressure at 750M, hard ridden from the 550M, found the line okay.
Sat box-seat, showed some dash early in the Straight, but soon one pace.
Settled midfield 2 wide, stayed on fairly.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, made minor progress near the rail.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, switched out to 3 wide to improve at 800M, limited response in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, made little impression.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, made no ground in the Straight.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never involved.
Sat towards the rear 2 wide, never in contention.
Sat last, swung wide into the Straight, made no progress.

Pressed forward from the widest draw going 5-wide onto first turn before gaining 1L 2nd 2-wide, commenced move rounding home bend hitting the front 450 metres out, just held off runner-up's strong late challenge.
Settled towards rear 3-wide, made headway past 850 metres to midfield 6th about 3L off the pace remaining wide, fought on well from a similar position into straight to just fail to get up on line.

Broke well settling about 2L off the pace on rail in 3rd or 4th, gained closer to lead when pace slackened around home bend, came to challenge upon straightening, ran on steadily down the inside without threatening.

Soon prominent after moderate start settling 3-wide without cover in 5th in midfield in back straight, made headway past 850 metres to be joint 3rd, held place chance from 4-wide into straight only to miss narrowly.

Jumped awkwardly and crowded, improved from worse than midfield on rail to reach 7th on first bend, angled off rail for a run into straight, ran on under pressure to hold place chance but no clear run inside final 70 metres.
Trailed the field to home bend, commenced move about 500 metres out going one of the widest into straight, ran on without making any serious impression on place-getters.

Prominent early stages shifting just over 2L back in 5th into back straight, came to challenge under pressure rounding home bend coming within 1L of pace into straight, unable to sustain effort 200 metres out.

One of the best to start, well there before taken back to midfield passing winning post first time, drifted further back to 8th early in back straight, came under pressure final bend but found nothing from widest into straight.
Broke well but soon settled in last few, came under pressure from over 700 metres out going 3-wide around home bend and wider into straight, found nothing. (Mucus in trachea)
Began from a poor draw, took up running passing winning post the first time and set pace to home bend, soon weakened under pressure.
Led early stages before sitting back in 2nd 1200M, moved up alongside leader 400M, gained the lead near 200M then kept on well to maintain his advantage in the run home.
Chased leaders in 3rd, driven nearing 400M, kept on steadily under top weight but was always held by winner in the run home.
Maintained a midfield position along the fence, travelled well going into straight, stayed on moderately to take 3rd.
Sent forward, crossed to the lead 1200M setting steady pace, soon challenged by rival top of straight, fought hard but was outstayed by first 3 final 200M.
Reserved in mid-pack 5Ls off the pace, little change to the turn, finished off steadily over final 300M but was always held by leaders.
Jumped cleanly from draw 1, chased leaders in 4th, had every chance top of straight, run ended 150M, no extra towards finish.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind mid-division 7Ls off the lead, hard driven 500M but got home only fairly.
From wide draw taken back to the last spot, 10Ls off the pace middle stages, had task in hand top of straight, ran past beaten horses only. (Jockey : instructed to ride in a conservative manner.)
Settled towards the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M but couldn't quite finish it off.
Jumped only fairly and from wide draw dropped back to near last, plenty to do 400M but failed to finish the job.
Jumped awkwardly, switched off to a rearward spot 9Ls away, had nothing to offer turning in, never came on.
In touch with leaders early before falling back to a midfield position, no extra 300 and went backwards. (Roarer.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 400M, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 900M, headed near 550M, 2nd on turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 900M, retook the lead near 550M, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced in 3rd, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
