Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside, easy run on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line, won by 3-1/2L.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed good response early in straight, no clear run 150M to 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, kept on same pace to the line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 150M.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in the run home. (Lame left front leg.)
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 500M, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start, raced prominently on the outside, there to turn, peaked near 450M, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths back, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
From draw 1 soon hit the front and dictated the lead, kept going well early straight, was strongly challenged by runner-up final 200M but found the necessary to hold on.
Moved up chasing leaders in a 3-wide position without cover, hard pressed to challenge for the lead 200M, tried hard and was just held at the line.
From wide draw switched off to race in last, 6Ls off the pace home turn, closed off strongly from the rear to take 3rd beaten only a neck, nearest finish.
Always in touch behind leaders, moved up to 3rd 180M but not able to challenge first two, lost 3rd late.
Held up behind midfield but never far off from leaders, maintained his spot to the bend then worked home fairly over final 400M.
Maintained an inside spot just off the leading division, hard driven 500M, soon no threat to leaders.
Moved up to track leader on outside, little change to the turn but offered little under top weight when asked 500M, faded final 200M.
Raced keenly early stages when steadied to obtain cover behind leaders, had a 3-wide trip and hung out making the home turn, couldn't finish it off on straightening.

Began awkwardly, dropped back to a rearward position, pushed along 600M but failed to respond, eased top of the straight. (Irregular Heart Rhythm / Jockey : made respiratory noise in the home straight.)
Sat midfield, traveled comfortably, switched in to the center of the track inside 300M, closed off strongly.
Ridden along to lead, traveled smoothly, ran on evenly to the finish.
Chased the leader, made up ground under pressure inside 250M, closed off nicely.
Sat midfield, responded okay when asked inside 200M, finished off okay.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards rear, slightly weakened passing 200M, one pace to the line.
Sat behind midfield, traveled fairly, minor progress made over the final stages.
Sat in front of midfield, weakened notably after 300M, gradually faded (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, settled worse than midfield, no impression made.
Slow to jump, sat rear, raced rear, no contention.
Settled in front of midfield, gave ground under pressure, weakened and could not finish the race off (See Incident Report).
Settled in last few on rail, saved ground turning in for home, fought on dourly between runners inside final 100 metres to just get up in the bob.

Ridden early before settling over 2L back in 4th on rail, became 3rd onto home bend and on heels of leader into straight, obtained clear run over 150 metres out and responded well only to be pipped at post.
Settled well behind from the widest draw, commenced move from last over 800 metres out, circled the field home bend and ran on under pressure from 9th near the centre of the track to miss narrowly.
Tracked leader to straight, hit the front narrowly under pressure over 200 metres out only to be overshadowed last few strides.
Soon took up running on the rail setting a sound pace, led until narrowly headed over 200 metres out, plugged on and swamped for a placing final strides.
Settled in last few from a poor draw, remained similar into home straight, shifted out for a run early on, finished off the race strongly inside final 150 metres.

Wide in prominent position early stages settling one-out-one-back in 3rd into back straight, became 4th in similar position rounding final bend, kept on before gradually faded inside final 150 metres.

Ridden amongst leaders early, tightened and drifted 3L back to 5th 3-wide, improved to within 2L of pace in 5th early in straight, unable to sustain effort close to home, wide without cover most of the way.
Settled well behind, saved ground on rail turning in for home, never nearer despite not finding much room inside final 200 metres in straight.
Broke well gradually settling over 3L back in 6th, came under pressure when 7th 3-wide rounding home bend, kept on same pace and did not find much room inside final 100 metres.

Soon recovered from moderate start and gradually settling in midfield on rail, gained slightly closer rounding final bend, baulked for a run past the 200 metres and unable to make any impression in the run to the line.
Settled 3-wide in worse than midfield in 8th, came under pressure rounding home bend from 650 metres out, dropped to last into straight, made no further impression.
Made contact at start, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 800M, challenged the leader approaching 500M, took the lead 400M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Made contact at start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.

Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some progress early in straight, not enough room near 250M, cleared 200M, closed off well to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced in 3rd, 2 wide, angled out 550M, 3 wide turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide in midfield, carried wider 550M, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 550M, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (Bled.)
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 800M, challenged by rival 500M, peaked and headed 400M, hampered and made contact with the rail 200M, weakened final 150M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, angled out approaching 550M, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide at rear, very wide into straight, showed no response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Broke well, showed very good early speed to lead, kept on strongly to score.
Broke a step slow, settled behind midfield on the rail, saved ground before switched out at 300M, closed off strongly, closest finish.
Settled on pace 2 wide, kept on nicely to the line, finish a non-threatening 3rd.
Settled midfield 2 wide, showed some dash early part of the Straight, just one pace to the line.
Ridden along early but showed no speed, sat towards the rear, stayed on fairly. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, one pace to the line.
Restrained at the start from the outside barrier, settled at the rear, held up early part of the Straight, made some ground final furlong.
Jumped nicely, restrained and taken back to last after the start, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 3 wide, raced keenly throughout, limited response in the Straight.
Sat on pace 3 wide, weakened in the Straight.
Broke well, sat outside the leaders 3 wide, weakened and faded final 300M.
Settled midfield 2 wide, never a factor. (See Incident Report)
Began well from a poor draw settling just behind midfield in 6th 2-wide, commenced move on straightening and quickened well to hit the front 200 metres out, won readily.
Pressed forward from a poor draw to track the leader, hit the front over 300 metres out only to be caught 100 metres later.
Always thereabouts chasing in 3rd on rail, baulked behind runners after straightening, switched back to the rail for a run 300 metres out but unable to quicken under pressure.
Travelled some 3L back in 5th on rail, fought on steadily in straight, without threatening.
Travelled mainly in 4th some 3L off the pace, in similar position turning in for home, one-paced under pressure without quickening.
Settled in rear on rail, baulked for a run after straightening, kept on well inside final 200 metres.
Gradually took up running obtaining rails run about 1200 metres out, led until headed about 300 metres out, folded up quickly inside final 150 metres.
Gradually settled just worse than midfield in 7th on rail, baulked for a run off the rail after straightening, found nothing inside final 300 metres. (Jockey reported horse lay in throughout.)
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Settled well behind from the widest draw, never a factor.
Settled ahead of midfield, travelled well into straight, shifted into clear 300M then sprinted quickly for an emphatic win.
From wide draw shifted across to race along the fence, maintained a position behind midfield, ran on steadily final 400M along the inside for 2nd.
Bustled along after the start, vied for early lead before dropping back to race behind leaders, battled away over final 400M to take 3rd.
Switched off to the rear on jumping from wide draw, 7-8Ls off leader early stages, still some work to do 400M, made solid gains and got up for 4th late.
Caught wide early stages, shifted in for cover passing 1100M, fought on well to take lead nearing 200M, couldn't sustain run late faded to 5th.
Pressed forward, emerged as leader from 1100M, headed nearing 200M, faded towards the line. (Jockey reminded to ride his mount out to the finish.)
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders, fought hard on straightening but only maintained his position in the run home.
Moved forward from draw 1, stalked the leader from 900M, right there on straightening but couldn't go with the leaders final 200M.
Jumped awkwardly, gradually improved to a midfield spot along inside, held up from 450M-150M but the final effort was just fair.
Dropped back to a 3-wide position towards the rear, wide into straight, responded well and moved up to 2nd 200M, run ended soon and no extra close home.
Shared lead on outside, was gone passing 300M and offered little. (Jockey : intended to hold a more forward position but didn't expect to lead.)
Jumped on terms, restrained to race behind midfield, lacked a kick passing 400M, couldn't get near them in straight.
Jumped only fairly and then from a wide draw was dropped back to the rear, under riding 500M but couldn't finish off.
Given a waiting ride at the back of the field, wide into straight but failed to pick up. (Jockey: travelled well in the event but failed to respond to his riding in the home straight.)
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, a length or so back turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after the start, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1100M, 2nd in the middle stages, challenged the leader 500M, took the lead 400M, headed 200M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place, nearest on line.
Began well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide after passing 600M, a length or so back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced towards rear on the outside early, found rail near 900M, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until 250M, finished off well without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back turning in, angled out early in straight, made some progress final 300M.
Crowded shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, wider turning in, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, no clear run early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, wider from 600M, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on outer, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 800M, sat right behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Bumped on jumping, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1100M, challenged by rival from 500M, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened 300M, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 1/2L back turning, challenged the leader from 400M, kept on very well, took the lead close home, won by a neck.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Out with rest, positioned 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, angled out 450M, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Commenced well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until approaching final 50M, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Began awkwardly, taken back to race at rear on the inside, a bit closer on turn, angled out 500M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside early, 2 wide from 800M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, made some progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped awkwardly, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, carried wider 600M, a length or so back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run approaching 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 600M, a length back turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight, ran on same pace to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Began well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced behind midfield on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Jumped well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 350M, finished off strongly to score.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest finish.
Average to begin, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well, tracked leaders, 2 wide, angled out 450M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/4L, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped with them, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide in midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Tracked leaders along the 2-path, worked nicely into the race passing 400M, stuck to task well hitting the front 150M out, was strongly challenged late but managed to hold on.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield slightly further back than anticipated, swung wide for home, did best work late under big weight, just missed out.
Went forward to be sharing lead on the inside passing 1400M, kept fighting hard on straightening, couldn't hold off first two over final 150M.
From draw 1 moved up to chase leaders on inside, close up 3rd turning for home, ran to the line one paced.
Jumped on terms, settled down midfield on the inside, briefly held up on the home turn before finishing off the race fairly.
Maintained a midfield position along the 2-path, couldn't muster in the straight and was never a threat. (Jockey : may appreciate a surface with more give.)
Reserved in a rearward position, little change to the turn, briefly held up 350M but worked home only fairly afterwards, always held by leaders.
Taken across on jumping from wide draw, settled at the rear 8Ls off leader, wide into straight and couldn't go on. Never involved. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, ended up racing at the rear 8Ls away, under serious pressure home turn, soon left behind by rivals.
Moved forward to race outside the lead, came under pressure from 600M, soon gave ground and was eased down in the home straight. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)
Ridden along to lead, traveled comfortably, responded nicely when place under pressure inside 100M.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, made good progress passing 150M, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Sat worse than midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, slightly held up entering the Straight, ran on evenly.
Settled behind midfield, traveled okay, one pace to the line.
Sat rear, commenced to improve inside 800M, closed off okay.
Sat midfield, responded only fairly under pressure, weakened entering the Straight, could not be ridden out (Substantial amount of blood in the horse's trachea, See Incident Report).
Chased the leader, traveled okay, gave ground rounding the Turn, weakened inside 200M (See Incident Report).
Slow to jump, sat towards rear, raced wide until 800M where elected to shifted back in, no impression in the Straight.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide and without cover, raced keenly thereafter, failed to respond over the concluding stages (See Incident Report).
Settled nicely behind midfield, waited with until top of straight, quickened up strongly to lead near 150M, drew away for a big win giving nothing else a chance.
Jumped only fairly, caught wide no cover early and was allowed to stride forward 800M, pressed leader entering home turn, took over early straight but no match for the fast finishing winner 150M.
Held up in midfield along the fence, had a ground saving trip, fought on steadily under top weight to claim 3rd, no threat to runaway winner.
Jumped on terms and held a prominent position behind leaders, tried hard on straightening but couldn't quicken enough.
Not far off from leaders early stages then sat back in midfield, switched 3-wide 600M, battled on over final 300M but lacked the dash to launch a serious bid.
Settled towards the rear, held 11th position at the turn, came wide into straight then stayed on for non-threatening 6th.
Reserved towards the rear 6Ls off leader, held up making the home turn, no clear running again from 200M-100M. Could do better.

Contested early lead before obtaining a trailing position behind leaders from 1200M, shuffled back to midfield making home turn, got to the line only fairly. (Jockey: may be better suited if it is able to race in the lead.)
Soon led setting fast pace in the first half of the race, joined by rival entering home turn, wilted in the running passing 300M.
Jumped awkwardly, soon ended up at the rear 9Ls off the pace, driven along home turn but failed to muster the speed to challenge.
Caught wide early stages, moved up to race outside leader 1200M, under pressure to keep up 600M, no extra top of straight.
Bumped at the start, maintained a position ahead of midfield, moved closer to leaders 600M, found disappointingly little on straightening, soon out of contention. (Bled.)
Quickly into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths behind the leader, easy run to turn, took the lead after passing 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Shifted in at start, raced in 3rd, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no impression on winner.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed after passing 200M, weakened final 100M.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear, 9 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 9 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced at rear on the inside, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with the field, settled at the rear on the rail, travelled smoothly throughout, saved ground rounding the Turn, switched out in the Straight and stayed on very well to score.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, made good ground along the rail, got bumped final 150M, could not hold off the winner.
Showed very good early speed to lead, kept on nicely until slightly weakened final 100M. (See Incident Report)
Tracked leader 2 wide, kept on okay for 4th.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Settled towards the rear 3 wide, stayed on and made some late ground.
Ridden along early but was caught wide no cover on pace, limited response in the Straight.
Settled midfield 3 wide, raced greenly throughout, made some progress in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, got hampered rounding the Home Turn, took some time to respond but did make ground final 100M.
Settled behind the leaders 2 wide, made little impression.
Got crowded at the start, settled towards the rear, never a factor. (See Incident Report)
Under pressure from the beginning, never involved. (Performance unacceptable, must trial) (See Incident Report)

Jumped well but soon taken back to last and waited with, came under pressure rounding home bend before going widest into straight, ran on well near the centre of the track to snatch victory final strides.

Pressed forward from wide draw to share early lead 2-wide, restrained half a length off the pace into back straight, renewed effort to join race leader making final turn, held every chance in straight only to be denied final strides.
Shared early lead before gaining some 1L advantage into back straight, led until joined again making final turn, held every chance on rail only to be denied final strides.
Always prominent travelling one-out-one-back most of the way, came under pressure from 600 metres out holding place chance into straight, unable to sustain effort.
Settled in midfield on rail, came under pressure from approaching final turn sneaking closer into straight, fought on steadily on rail without threatening.
Soon taken back to worse than midfield, commenced move under pressure rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure in straight without threatening.

Began well from the one draw before settling over 2L back in 4th on rail, closer in 3rd early in back straight before becoming 5th about 700 metres out, saved ground turning in for home but had no more to give in the run to the line.
Settled in last few after moderate start from a poor draw, came under pressure rounding home bend saving ground into straight, kept on same pace without threatening.

Settled in last few on rail, came under pressure from 600 metres out saving ground on rail turning in for home, baulked for a run over 200 metres out, hung in a difficult ride shortly after, made no impression closing stages.

Settled in forward of midfield in 5th some over 4L back rounding first bend, travelled keenly before rapid headway past the 800 metres to reach close-up 3rd 3-wide, drifted wider into straight and soon weakened.
Travelled 3-wide in midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend and one of the widest into straight, soon faded.
Ridden forward from wide draw, pressed leader from 800M, responded strongly to take lead nearing 200M, drew clear winning decisively.
Held up in midfield along the fence, took a while to muster on straightening, did best work final 150M to claim 2nd close home.
Jumped awkwardly, never far off from leaders, 3rd at 400M, lay in when under pressure, fought on evenly to the line but couldn't bridge the gap on winner.
Chased leaders early, fell back to a position ahead of midfield middle stages but remained in touch turning for home, kept on steadily over final 300M but not making ground on first few.
Not hurried on jumping from a wide barrier, towards the rear 6Ls off the pace middle stages, made some minor headway in the straight but never threatened.
Adopted a rearward position 8Ls on settling, wide into straight and had plenty to make up, failed to get into the finish despite closing off fastest.
Settled in the second half of the field, 8th at 400M 6Ls away, worked home only fairly and never a winning hope.
Dropped back to the rear 8Ls off the pace, saved ground on inside, gave limited response on straightening, No impression.
From wide draw obtained a 3-wide spot in midfield, failed to finish off in the straight. (Jockey: would derive benefit from tonight's race experience and potentially being stepped up in distance.)
Settled behind midfield, struggled to go with the pace entering home turn, never in the hunt.
Soon in front, pressed by rival from 950M, came under pressure on entering the home straight and drifted out of contention.
Bustled along, moved up to join leader from 950M, raced greenly after being crossed by rival near 600M, soon came under pressure then weakened in the straight.
Commenced well, raced better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly, took the lead close home.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, angled out 350M, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, 3 wide after passing 500M, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made some headway in the run home.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, made no impression thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the inside, 8 lengths back, 2 wide from 400M, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, made minor progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Made contact at start, positioned 3 wide, a length or so back, slightly taken back 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked on run 350M, weakened early in straight.

Made contact at start, raced at rear on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared approaching 150M, finished off well to take 2nd.

Jumped well from gate 12, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, hard ridden after passing 300M, hit the front 150M, peaked and headed 50M, kept on evenly, lost 2nd last stride.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, same position on turn, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 150M, made some progress thereafter.

Away well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 800M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, angled out 450M, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, unable to obtain clear run until final 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 600M, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (Roarer.)
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, no clear run 300M to 100M, made no progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 800M, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed approaching 200M, weakened quickly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced prominently on the outside, 1/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened quickly final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Bled.)
Ridden out of gates to settled fifth on the rail. Came off fence at 800m, then four wide on straightening to make run. Challenged at 200m by runner up but cosy win. winner.
Eased from wide gate to settle rear group. Made run from 400m, sprinted quickly to join leader at 150m, peaked on run, held second, well clear of others.
Jumped well but drifted back to fourth last. No clear run early part of straight, badly baulked for run 200m, ran home strongly when clear, good run.
Raced keenly early and middle stages, settling back half. Raced greenly under pressure early in straight. Ran home fairly, closest on the line.
Ridden for speed to challenge for lead, then eased before first turn to sit second, one off fence. Challenged for lead at 350m, laid in past 200m and one pace from then on for fifth.
Tightened on jumping from rails draw, tightened coming to first turn and had to ease. Last on home bend, ran home well last 200m, but well beaten.
Jumped fairly, sixth, handy to speed coming to first turn. Challenging at 300m mark but soon one paced and well held on line.
Ridden hard early three wide to cross and lead coming to first turn. Raced keenly in front, challenged at 400m, headed at 300m. Faded last 150m.

Caught wide in forward division early, tried to take a sit but over raced and then went forward three wide coming to home turn. Challenged for front at 400m but soon under pressure and faded last 250m.
Eased at start from wide gate, crossing to fence in last position. Under pressure to improve position from 800m, but always in tail group.
Ridden hard early to try and lead. Settled fourth on rail behind leader. Beaten passing 300m and allowed to run to line there after.
Settled midfield, traveled smoothly, responded well under pressure.
Sat rear, traveled nicely, switched out rounding the Turn, made good progress over the concluding stages.
Sat handy, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, kept on well to hold 3rd.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, raced tight over the concluding stages, could not be fully tested.
Ridden along to lead on the rail, weakened inside 300M, closed off okay (Substantial blood in trachea).
Sat in front of midfield, obtained cover passing 800M, weakened notably inside 250M (See Incident Report).
Jumped well, able to cross to rail and lead easily first 200m. Gave good kick in straight going clear at 300m, won easily.
Jumped fairly, then railed through to be third on rail, behind the leader. Came off leaders back at 400m to challenge but winner too strong. Clear second.
Ridden forward from wide gate to settle second one off fence. Challenged at top of straight but no match for first two. Held on well for third.
Ridden along to hold fourth early, one off fence. Brought to middle of track and stayed on well to just miss third.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards rear, one off fence. Brought widest in straight, made good ground last 150m, closing quickly.
Jumped well, eased into first turn to be one off fence midfield. Brought to middle of track, drifted out further in straight. Stayed of well.
Ridden along early, then slight ease before first turn. Settled midfield one off fence. Switched across heels at 350m, made some ground late.
Forward position three-wide early, before easing and dropping to rails midfield half way mark. Stayed on fairly in straight.
Settled back half, slight ease when on rails coming to first turn. Clear running in straight, stayed on fairly.
Three wide without cover early and middle stages, brought to outside in straight, failed to make any impression last 200m.
Slow to begin. Made ground on rails, eased slightly before first turn. Clear run from top straight, failed to run on.
Jumped awkwardly from wide gate and eased to back of field, one off fence. A little green in run home, but failed to run on.
Made contact at start, took the early lead, headed near 1350M, 2nd in the middle stages, hit the front 450M, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.

Moderately away, trapped wide in midfield early, sent forward 1500M, took the lead 1350M, led by a length in the middle stages, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from a wide draw, tracked leaders, 2 wide, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, 2 wide approaching 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back turning in, unable to obtain clear run until final 150M, made some progress thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Jumped only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 300M.
Jumped with them, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped on terms, settled midfield 2 wide, switched out in the Straight, closed off nicely, won going away.
Broke well, settled behind the leaders on the rail, improved nicely along the rail, hit the front at 300M, kept on but just can't hold off the winner.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, raced ungenerously in the early stages, made good ground on the rail for a non-threatening 3rd.
Settled midfield on the rail, took some time to respond, closed off fairly final furlong.
Not the quickest out, settled behind midfield 3 wide no cover, stayed on okay. (See Incident Report)
Settled towards the rear, improved along the rail at 1000M, stayed on only fairly.
Sat on pace 2 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Tracked leader 2 wide, weakened inside final 200M.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, made no ground.
Raced in front of midfield 2 wide, weakened and faded final 250M.
Jumped well and ridden along to assume lead, weakened in the Straight.( See Incident Report)
Sat last, never a threat.
Settled towards the rear 3 wide, never in contention. (See Incident Report)
Began well from the widest draw to soon take up running, gradually obtained rails run about 1100 metres out setting a steady pace, held clear advantage in straight.
Settled mainly 3-wide in 6th about 3L off the pace, in similar position turning in for home, fought on steadily near the centre of home straight without threatening.
Travelled mainly in midfield in 8th, baulked in similar position early in straight, finished off the race well inside final 200 metres.
Gradually settled towards rear from moderate start, tight between runners early in straight until the 300 metres, fought on steadily without threatening.
Not far off in 4th or 5th travelling keenly around home bend, switched in for a run over 300 metres out, kept on steadily without quickening.
Gradually recovered from moderate start to just worse than midfield in 10th over 4L off the pace, saved ground on rail turning in for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Ridden early while settling 3-wide in rear of midfield, went one of widest into straight, ran home one-paced.
Soon taken back to last few from a poor draw, came under pressure when one of the widest entering straight, fought on steadily near stands rail without threatening.
Improved steadily along the rail from the one draw to soon reach one back position in 3rd, came under pressure inside final 250 metres but gradually faded.
Jumped awkwardly from a poor draw niggling along in first few 4-wide without cover, some 2L back in 4th 3-wide rounding home bend, weakened under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Settled in forward of midfield on rail just over 3L off the pace, soon weakened out of contention after straightening.
Well there from a poor draw gradually obtaining 2-wide position coming onto home bend, kept on early in straight before weakening out of contention inside final 200 metres.
Soon dropped to last few from a poor draw, made no impression throughout.
Ridden along at the back after moderate start, never seen with a chance.
From draw 12 caught racing wide behind midfield 5-6Ls , let down in good style on straightening, hit the front 150M out putting a good gap on the field towards the finish.
Chased the pace 2-wide, battled on well early straight, led by a slim margin inside 200M but couldn't hold off winner late stages.
Settled towards the rear 5-6Ls away, ran on steadily from top of straight, steadied 150M, not pace of winner final stages.
Slow to begin, settled towards the rear of the field along the inside, had big task in hand 400M , unable to obtain clear running 300M-200M then finished off pleasingly to take 4th.
Failed to show sufficient pace to hold a more forward position, caught racing wide towards the rear, had some work to do 400M, made steady progress towards the line.
Caught racing 3-wide in midfield on settling, little change to the turn, responded well early straight when asked but run ended 150M and no extra towards the finish.
Sent forward on jumping from wide draw, tracked leader into straight, kept battling to stay in contention early straight, outpaced by rivals final 150M.
Soon led setting a good pace, driven inside 300M found less than expected under top weight, faded towards the line. (Jockey : raced too keenly in the lead and left without a finishing effort.)
Stayed close to leaders early stages before dropping back to a position ahead of midfield, couldn't quicken enough on straightening. Never threatened.
From wide draw chased leaders in a 3-wide spot without cover, couldn't rally under a big weight, faded to 10th closing. (Jockey : made abnormal breathing noise during race / Vet - no abnormality.)
Settled down in mid-division, driven along 550M but couldn't accelerate in the straight.
Jumped only fairly, maintained a position behind midfield, similar position turning home but offered little when it mattered. (Jockey : prefer a firmer surface.)
Switched off to race at the rear, came under serious pressure home turn, well beaten.
In midfield early stages, lay out making the home turn and soon pushed along, already beaten top of straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Fast into stride, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, always held.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off well to make frame, not quite able to challenge.
Clean jump, raced better than midfield, 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield, 3 wide, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Crowded start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 2 lengths back turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead approaching 200M, kept on well to hold off the challenger late.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, unable to obtain clear run until final 50M, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 200M, weakened gradually final 50M.

Began fairly, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 12 lengths or so back, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Made contact shortly after start, tracked leaders on the outside, similar position on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 150M.
Began well from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Away with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced behind midfield on outer, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 550M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.

Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight, won by 2 lengths.

Jumped awkwardly, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 wide from 400M, challenged the leader early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Out in line, raced in midfield on the inside, slightly improved along the rail on turn, angled out 350M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 800M, angled out 400M, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Crowded shortly after start, taken back to race towards rear on the inside, angled out 600M, commenced move 500M, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.

Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1650M, 2Ls or so back in the middle stages, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 7, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back in the middle stages, moved a bit closer on turn, very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, sent forward after entering the back straight, raced in midfield on outer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, dropped towards rear 550M, found rail 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, tracked leaders on the inside early, 3 wide from 1500M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced in midfield on the outside, sent forward after passing 1600M, 2nd in the middle stages, weakened gradually 600M, eased final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, dropped towards rear in the middle stages, last turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Fast into stride, set early pace before taking up a trailing position behind leaders, picked up well top of straight, led near 150M and was strong through the line.
Hard pressed early stages, led from 1000M, boxed on gamely on straightening and held the front until headed 150M, held on or 2nd just.
Never far off from leaders but raced wide no cover throughout, worked home well final 300M to be nearest at the finish, almost claimed 2nd.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, ended up near the rear, saved ground on inside then came with a good run final 300M, safely held by first three towards the finish.
Away well from draw 1, settled down midfield along the fence, in touch turning for home, kept on steadily under big weight and wasn't beaten far at the end.
Restrained to a position behind midfield, raced keenly along the 3-path, wide into straight then finished off moderately. Not reach leaders.
Jumped on terms, maintained a position in midfield, 3Ls off leader 400M but wasn't able to finish the race off .
Settled just off the lead division, held up making the home turn, couldn't quicken enough passing 300M.
Slow to begin, raced at the tail of the field 6Ls, ran past a few beaten rivals on straightening, Failed to threaten at any stage.
Dropped back to the rear 6Ls off the pace, wide into straight but found little. Never in the equation.
Caught wide early and was ridden forward to take up a position outside the lead, gave ground rapidly 250M.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards the rear, gave limited response on straightening, awkwardly placed nearing 100M and stopped riding.
Ridden along to lead on the rail, slightly weakened on straightening, kept on well to win.
Sat handy, traveled smoothly, made some progress over the final stages when under pressure.
Blundered on jumping, settled behind midfield, could not be fully tested when held up over the concluding stages.
Settled towards rear, traveled okay, commenced to improve inside 700M, ran on evenly.
Settled behind midfield, raced wide throughout, responded okay when asked inside 150M.
Sat towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, made some progress inside 100M.
Sat midfield on the rail, slightly weakened rounding the Turn, held up making the Turn, closed off fairly.
Sat midfield, raced keenly in the middle stages, one pace to the line.
Slow to jump, sat worse than midfield, was badly help up entering the Straight, failed to run on (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, traveled fairly, pressed on passing 650M, no impression in the Straight.
Sat handy, weakened notably near the 150M, never a danger.
Settled in front of midfield, gave ground quickly passing 550M, faded gradually (Heart Irregularity, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Jumped quickly from rails draw and able to lead without pressure. Kicked clear and fought on strongly when challenged and holding margin on the line.
Jumped well from good draw and quickly third behind the leader. Came off fence to challenge coming to home turn. Fought hard to the line but unable to chase down leader.
Began well and settled fifth, one off the fence. Chased hard in the straight but well held by first two.
Quickly away and settled outside leader. Pushed three wide on home turn stayed on strongly to hold fourth.
Only jumped fairly and then ridden hard to hold forward position settling midfield on the fence. Ridden hard near rail in the straight to challenge and stayed on final 100m.
Allowed to cross to rails at tail of field from outside draw. Stayed on rails in straight and tightened at 150m mark, then ran on last 100m.
Only fairly away and ridden hard from 800m to hold position. Laid in at 200m and continued to fight hard to the line when straightened.
Slowly away and ridden along early to stay in touch with field in second last position. Brought to middle of track in straight and made some ground late, closest on the line.
Jumped well and ridden to take up forward position, but caught three wide without cover most of the race. Under pressure from top of straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped before being caught three wide with cover from 800m mark. Came wide on the home turn and too far back to make impression.
Caught wide from wide gate early before settling midfield, one off the fence at 700m. Rider lost whip at 200m and faded last 100m.
Settled midfield, three wide with cover. Under pressure passing 700m mark and made no impression in straight, finishing last.
Fast into stride, tracked leaders, 3 wide, 2 wide from 600M, commenced move 400M, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well to hold off the challengers.
Out with rest, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, finished off strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, finished off strongly to take a place, just beaten by a head.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, slightly improved after passing 600M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, 3 wide from 400M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead in the middle stages, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Began awkwardly, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened 150M, eased final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, shared lead in the middle stages, weakened early in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, sent forward after entering the back straight, peaked on turn, weakened 400M, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled midfield on the rail, improved along the rail rounding the Home Turn, closed off nicely and held on.
Broke well, settled behind the leaders, switched out in the Straight, made good ground, just missed.
Got crowded at the start, settled towards the rear, closed off okay for a non-threatening 3rd.
Settled midfield 2 wide, stayed on fairly.
Not the quickest out, ridden along early and assumed the lead, travelled keenly, kept on until weakened final 100M. (See Incident report)
Sat on pace 2 wide, ran on only evenly.
Caught 4 wide no cover behind midfield, limited response in the Straight.
Settled 3 wide midfield, made little impression.
Settled towards the rear, made no ground (Bled)
Got crowded early, settled at the rear, never a threat.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never in contention. (Bled)
Caught very wide on the 1st turn, improved to sit outside the lead, weakened badly from 500M. (Bled and Heart Irregularity)
Well there from the one draw settling one back on rail just behind race leader in 4th, came to challenge under pressure on straightening, just got up final strides.
Ridden along wide in first few, obtained 2-wide position alongside race leader in 2nd coming onto home bend, hit the front narrowly on straightening only to be denied final strides.
Broke well to soon take up running setting a sound pace, led until narrowly headed into straight, kept on steadily for a place.
Jumped awkwardly from a low draw settling in midfield on rail, saved ground turning in for home, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.

Jumped well from a poor draw before settling very wide without cover in prominent 3rd, in similar position into straight, fought on under pressure down the centre of the track without threatening first trio. (Lost place in race)

Lacked early pace despite ridden along, gradually recovered to reach 9th on rail just worse than midfield 700 metres out, saved ground turning in for home, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Pressed forward from moderate start travelling 4-wide without cover about 3L off the pace in midfield, widest turning in for home, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Soon taken back from the widest draw, trailed the field on rail to home bend, saved ground turning in for home, fought on steadily and never nearer.
Travelled in prominent position in 5th about 2L 3-wide off the pace, went wider into straight, kept on before making no further impression inside final 100 metres.
Travelled wide in last few after beginning from a wide draw, in similar position into straight, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped to last few and never seen with a chance.
Settled in forward of midfield within 3L of pace, weakened out of contention about 150 metres out.
Adopted a midfield position 4Ls off leader, wide into straight, responded well passing 300M, got up near 50M.
Went forward from wide draw, reached the lead 1200M, kept going well on straightening, dug deep late stages only to go down narrowly.
Reserved towards the rear 6Ls off leader, held up for clear running on the home turn, didn't have a neat run until 200M, worked home well down inside, just missed 2nd.
Pressed on to be chasing leader, poised to strike turning home but never found that extra gear. No threat to first three final 100M.
Dropped back from wide draw, given a waiting ride 7-8Ls off the pace, had some work to do 400M, closed off nicely but not getting to first three.
From draw 2 enjoyed a ground saving trip, maintained a spot in midfield from 800M, fought hard in the straight but was never a real threat.
Jumped on terms from draw 1, never better than midfield the trip, switched away from fence 400M, closed off only fairly.
Dropped back to race at the rear 7Ls off the pace, improved position along the 3-path home turn, couldn't accelerate enough.
Tracked leaders early stages, sat ahead of midfield on settling, pushed along 500M but lacked a finishing effort.
Chased leaders, obliged to race wide without cover during the race, left without a finishing effort in the straight, weakened 200M.
Jumped only fairly, ended up racing towards the rear, last at 300M, never came into it.
Vied for early lead before settling down in a trailing spot behind leader, struggled to keep up home turn, dropped out top of straight.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 800M, led by 1/4L turning in, kept on very well in straight and scored. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 800M, 1/4L back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually final 100M, finished 3rd.

Began smartly from the widest draw, trapped very wide, 2 lengths or so back in the early stages, slightly taken back after passing 1000M, 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Away well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, 8 lengths back, saved ground on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Began well from a tricky gate, tracked leaders, 3 wide with no cover, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened 200M, eased final 100M.

Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 600M, wider 500M, 6 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly, led last stride.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside, saved ground throughout, hard ridden from 400M, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Shifted in at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.

Began awkwardly and crowded, positioned 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress early in straight, short of room final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well from a wide draw, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, angled out 450M, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Crowded start and unbalanced, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, found rail after passing 700M, angled out 500M, kept on same pace in straight.
Away with them, raced slightly behind midfield on outer, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 9 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced towards rear on the outside, 8 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Settled slightly worse than midield passing 1200m mark, sprinted quickly through gap off fence at 350m, found lead passing 200m and won comfortably.
Jumped fairly from inside gate, settling behind the leader. Held up early part of straight before securing rails run, finished well but no match for winner.
Broke well from middle draw, three wide early before eased to be fifth, one off fence. Clear running in straight and stayed on well.
Broke on terms, allowed to drift back to second last pair on the rails. Came off fence on turn, finished well, closest on the line.
Jumped evenly, caught wide, ridden forward to be outside leader by half way mark. Challenged for lead in straight, fought on well to line.
Jumped well and able to settle midfield one off the fence passing 1200m mark. Three wide to improve from 600m, prominent to 200m and then changed stride and peaked on run.
Started quickly, led. Challenged at top of straight, Fought on, then headed at 250m, faded last 100m.
Allowed to cross to rail at tail of field from wide gate. Middle of track in straight to make run, ran home fairly. Found to have Bled, subsequently retired from racing.
Jumped quickly to be outside leader before taking sit in third place. Three wide to make run home turn, soon under pressure and one paced last 150m.
Away well and ridden forward, but caught three wide, midfield without cover. Ridden along from 800m to stay in touch. Faded last 150m.
Jumped well but caught wide and eased back to gain cover, but remained three wide throughout. Stayed on in straight but never a threat and well beaten.
Allowed to drift back from widest gate and settled in last pair, one off fence. Still last on turn and then ran out under pressure in straight.
Drew wide and restrained to settle second last pair, one off fence. Held up for run prior to turn, but plenty of room in straight and failed to make any ground.
On back foot when gates opened and slow to move, ridden forward to settle three-back the fence. Raced with high head carriage. Under pressure at 300m, faded last 200m.
Sat towards rear, strode forward from 1300M, shared the lead thereafter, responded well when asked.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield 2 wide, made a forward move from 1300M and settled midfield, made good progress over the concluding stages (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, traveled smoothly, stayed on well to grab 3rd.
Settled in front of midfield, raced wide until 1400M, strode forward and shared the lead on the rail thereafter, ran on evenly.
Sat handy, traveled okay, one pace to the line.
Sat midfield until 1300M, raced wide from 1000M, slightly weakened entering the Straight, closed off fairly.
Slow to jump, sat rear, over-raced in the early stages, could not make up ground in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, limited response when asked no impression in the Straight (Lame left fore).
Sat handy, traveled fairly, weakened and could not be ridden out in the Straight (Disappointing Performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Settled midfield, weakened notably entering the Straight, held up for clear running until 300M never a threat (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, slightly weakened rounding the Turn, no contention.
Jumped well, shared lead and challenged on far side at 250m mark, found front and held on, all out on the line.
Settled sixth, three off fence with cover. Brought off heels at 300m to challenge, continued to make ground taking second last few strides.
Started quickly, crossed to nearside rail and soon shared lead. Raced keenly, headed inside 250m fought on well.
Laid out after jumping, soon fourth, one off fence. Ridden along to make challenge from 400m, stayed on well to be closest at finish.
Jumped fairly, settled worse than midfield. Rallied when asked for effort at half way mark. Continued to make good ground to finish. Good effort, will improve with racing.
Settled just off speed, racing between horses. Shifted out abruptly shortly after start, tight for room and shifted down to stand side to gain clear ground last 400m.
Jumped well and showed good speed to be in third place. Asked for effort from 400m, faded last 150m.
Hesitated at start and at back of field after first 200m. Still last passing 400m, ran home strongly last 200m but beaten 5-1/4L on line.
Crowded shortly after start and settled in rear division. Chased hard when asked for effort and stayed on, but well beaten.
Usual race pattern, no early speed and settled last. Had to come round heels near rail to make ground pass half way mark. Making good ground late between runners.
Showed good early speed to settle just behind leading group. Under pressure passing half way mark and faded last 100m.
Bumped shortly after start and carried outward, settled in last group. Last at the 400m mark and one paced from there on.
Jumped on terms, settled worse than midfield in clear ground. Under pressure from half way mark, one paced to the line and well beaten.
Drew near side rail and held rail throughout. Settled worse than midfield, many lengths off lead. One paced and finished last.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/4L turning in, kept on well in straight and scored.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began smartly, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 1/4L back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to make frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in 4th, 2 wide, carried wider turning in, ran on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, one-paced in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide entering straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped wide in midfield, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Broke nicely, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled comfortably throughout, under pressured at 500M, switched out in the Straight, closed off strongly and won going away.
Settled midfield 3 wide with cover, made good progress in the Straight but no threat to the winner.
Jumped slowly, settled at the rear, stayed on well for 3rd.
Jumped smartly, settled outside the leader, responded nicely early in the Straight but weakened final 100M.
Sat box-seat, slightly crowded early in the Straight, only one pace to the line.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield early, improved to be on pace from the 950M, kept on one pace to the line.
Hard ridden early but was settled worse than midfield 2 wide, ran on only fairly. (See Incident Report)
Settled towards the rear 3 wide, made little impression. (See Incident Report)
Jumped with the field and showed speed to assume the lead, weakened final furlong.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never impress.
Settled midfield on the rail, never a threat.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, made no ground.

Improved steadily from the widest draw of 8 to track the leader onto the first bend, came to tackle leader rounding home bend gaining narrow advantage upon straightening, drew clear inside final 200 metres.
Settled at the back of the small field and waited with, saved ground on rail turning in for home, quickened well under pressure in straight without threatening.

Settled some 3 to 4L off the pace in 3rd, commenced move halfway out to come within 2L of the lead, given reminders in quickened tempo rounding home bend, failed to make any serious impression in the run to the line.

Soon took up running setting a smart pace, steadied up the tempo in back straight but quickened up when challenged by eventual winner home bend, narrowly headed into straight before fading under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Broke well before taken well back, made some headway over 1000 metres out coming under pressure rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening from 4L 5th into straight.
Held up in 6th some 8L off the pace, lost position to 7th despite closer to pace 1000 metres out, commenced move approaching home turn 500 metres out and widest into straight, never nearer.

Broke well from the one draw before taken back to settled in 5th some 7L back early in back straight, became 6th despite closer to pace rounding home bend, found nothing under pressure in the run to the line.
Settled over 5L back in 4th early stages, gained closer halfway out to within 2L of pace approaching home bend, weakened out of contention upon straightening.
Settled towards the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, closed off strongly under top weight to hit the lead 100M out, won at big price $165. (Trainer: the horse was advantaged by being down in class.)
Taken back from wide draw, last turning for home 6Ls off the pace, came with a strong finish to go 2nd near line, nearest finish.
Dropped back to race towards the rear, moved close to midfield home turn, kept on well from 300M, outsprinted by winner final 150M before losing 2nd near line.
From draw 12 went forward and crossed to the lead 1000M, ran on well on straightening and led the charge until 100M, dropped to 4th place near line.
Tracked leaders on inside, battled on steadily turning home but couldn't quicken enough to challenge first few.
From draw 3 ended up chasing leaders in a 3-wide spot without cover, battled on one paced over final 400M.
Jumped awkwardly from draw 13, unable to slot in and raced wide no cover in midfield throughout, couldn't quicken enough on straightening, well held by leaders.
Always in touch behind leaders, held up from 400-250M losing momentum, didn't run on final stages.
Shifted in abruptly at the start, fell back to a rearward position on settling, wide into straight before making non-threatening progress from 400M.
Jumped only fairly, ended up racing in midfield along the inside, ran home fairly final 400M. (Jockey : did not appreciate racing inside other horses / Lame next day.)
Bumped at the start, settled near last, plenty to do 400M but found very little under pressure.
Vied for early lead before settling in a trailing spot behind leader, failed to pick up on straightening, gave ground passing 250M.

Crowded shortly after the jump, settled down in midfield, had difficulty obtaining clear running 400M-300M but failed to finish the race off thereafter. (Jockey - no excuse for disappointing performance / Mucus.)
Held up behind mid-division, 5Ls off the pace 400M but couldn't muster the speed to challenge.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on very well in straight, easily scored. (Lost left hind plate after the race.)
Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on outer, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest finish.
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on same pace to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide turning in, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in the run home.
Bumped start, taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Began only fairly and made contact, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 600M, 2 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly to score. (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 600M, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, wider turning in, closed off well to make frame, nearest on line.
Began well, raced prominently, took the lead approaching 1000M, led by 1/2L in the middle stages, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few final 50M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, tracked leaders, 3 wide, 3/4L back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 550M, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced prominently on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, wider turning in, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)

Horse Name: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Jockey: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
