Taken back to race at tail, 4 lengths back, hard ridden after passing 550M, 2-1/2L back turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, commenced move 600M, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, positioned 1-3/4L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, cleared after passing 200M, finished off evenly.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, hard ridden from 550M but only showed limited response, one-paced in the run home.
Chased leaders, raced keenly early stages, 3-wide no cover from 700M, travelled best of all turning home, quickened to lead inside 300M then drew well clear for his maiden victory.
From draw 11 slotted into a 3-wide spot in midfield, 5th at 400M, put in a mild effort to go 2nd near 100M but not able to challenge winner.

Slow to begin from draw 12 then switched off to race at the rear 6-7Ls away, had task ahead 400M, finished off best to claim a non-threatening 3rd close home. (Jockey dropped left rein for a number of strides near 100M.)
Jumped awkwardly, soon pushed along to take up a midfield position, 6th at 400M 3Ls off leader, couldn't quicken enough to challenge.
Strode to the front and shared lead on inside, couldn't hold off winner inside 300M, faded final stages.
Went forward to be vying for the lead on outside, fought hard to stay in contention early straight, ran home one paced final 250M.
Failed to muster early speed, unable to hold a forward position as instructed, 10th at 400M 6-7Ls back, ran to the line only fairly.
Positioned ahead of midfield 4Ls off leaders, responded fairly to pressure on straightening, never looked likely. (Jockey : would be benefit by stepping up in distance.)
Jumped fairly, pushed along to obtain a position behind midfield, gave limited response on straightening, No impression.
Slow to begin, held up near last 5-6Ls back, pushed along nearing 400M but lacked a finishing effort.

Hard driven out the gate to take up a trailing position behind leader, couldn't keep up passing 500M, soon weakened and fell back through the field. (Jockey - no explanation for disappointing performance.)
Away with them then dropped back to a position near last, under pressure home turn, had the job ahead top of the straight and couldn't make any headway.
Sat towards rear 3 wide, traveled smoothly, showed some dash inside 150M, closed off strongly.
Chased the leader, traveled nicely, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Sat towards rear, traveled okay, held up for clear running entering the Straight, closed off nicely.
Settled midfield 2 wide, switched out rounding the Turn, made up some ground inside 100M.
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, traveled comfortably, made good progress over the concluding stages.
Sat midfield, traveled okay, ran on evenly to the line.
Sat worse than midfield, limited response when asked in the Straight, closed off okay.
Sat in front of midfield, lay out in the middle stages, raced wide, little impression made.
Settled worse than midfield, lay out rounding the Turn, was checked near the 200M, closed off only fairly.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide throughout, weakened inside 150M (See Incident Report).
Ridden along to lead, traveled fairly, weakened approaching 250M, faded gradually (Disappointing Performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Sat handy, hung out in the early stages, weakened and gave ground notably entering the Straight (See Incident Report).
Jumped fairly, mustered speed to be sixth, one off fence first turn. Driven through gap, early in straight, fought strongly to hit front closing stages.
Broke well, ridden forward. Trapped three wide, no cover early stages. Brought to middle of track to challenge top of straight, just peaked on run closing stages, big effort.
Jumped well, crossed to lead easily at strong tempo. Kicked clear top of lane and fought on well after headed at inside last 100m.
Jumped fairly, slight ease passing 1200m before settling midfield. Brought to middle of track in straight and ran on well for fourth, closest on the line.
Quick back-up from Sunday. Settled fourth last, one off fence. Held up round turn, then finished well when in clear ground from 300m mark, closing strongly last 100m.
Jumped on terms but outpaced to first turn settling worse than midfield. Stayed on rails in straight and made some ground last 250m.
Caught wide first turn, settled second last. Ridden along from 700m to improve, came widest in straight, made good ground late.
Jumped quickly from inside draw, settled fourth the fence. Came off rail top of straight, slight ease at 300m, soon under pressure, faded last 150m.
Eased back from wide gate, settling clear last and ridden along at 800m to improve. Still last top of straight, made ground towards rails, stayed on.
Ridden forward to be clear second after first 300m, tendency to over race middle stages. Under pressure passing 300m and soon beaten off.
Settled third, one off fence. Travelled keenly, presented to challenge on home turn. Soon beaten and eased closing stages. Substantial blood in trachea post race.
Caught wide early and then obliged to raced three wide without cover from 1200m. Tried to make ground in straight but one paced after torrid run. Well beaten.
Travelled midfield off the fence. No challenge in straight. Beaten passing 250m and dropped out.
Eased back from wide gate, settling third last. Under pressure from 600m. Dropped out last 300m, respiratory noise in running (Continuous epiglottic entrapment)
Jumped well, took the early lead, headed near 950M, 2nd in the middle stages, hard ridden 300M, hit the front 250M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Began smartly from the widest draw, raced in 3rd, 3 lengths or so back turning in, kept on well in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, same margin back turning in, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on outer, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced in midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped only fairly, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 950M, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Mucus.)
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began awkwardly from gate 1, raced better than midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, hard ridden from 500M but only showed limited response, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Made contact at start, taken back to race at rear on the outside, still 10 lengths or so back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with the field, ridden along early to sit outside the lead, kept on nicely to the line, won comfortably.
Raced keenly early, sat box-seat, angled out in the Straight, made good ground, had every chance.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely late.
Sat towards the rear on the rail, under pressure from the 600M, took some time to respond, had some difficulty obtaining clear running early in the Straight, stayed on nicely once in the clear.
Showed good early speed to lead, kept on until weakened final 150M.
Settled just behind midfield on the rail, made some late ground along the inside, nothing impressive.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, only one pace to the line.
Slow to jump, sat last, began to improve from the 600M, loop around the field, showed some dash early in the Straight but only one pace final furlong.
Settled towards the rear, switched out rounding the Turn, limited response in the Straight.
Sat midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Sat at the rear, got checked top of the Straight, ran on okay afterwards.
Sat on pace, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, made no ground. (See Incident Report)
Raced midfield 2 wide, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Broke well before settling just off the pace in 4th over 2L back, commenced move entering home straight and quickened well to hit the front 200 metres out.
Ridden along after moderate beginning before settling in 8th on rail just worse than midfield, shifted 3-wide for a run rounding home bend and ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Vied for lead taking over at about 1000 metres out, gained rails run in front about 800 metres out and led until headed by winner about 200 metres out.
Ridden positively from the widest draw before settling 1L back 3-wide without cover in 3rd, gained 2nd onto home bend but could make no further progress under pressure after straightening.
Soon recovered to some 3L back in midfield on rail after moderate start, came under pressure after straightening but could only produce modest progress inside final 200 metres. (Bled)
Settled in midfield, travelled 4-wide without cover rounding home bend and into straight, fought on steadily to the line without threatening.
Settled wide in last few after beginning from a poor draw, dropped to last about 750 metres out trailing the field into straight, produced good late impression for best work late.
Travelled keenly and wide in last few, fought on steadily in home straight, never nearer.
Soon dropped to the last, ridden along at the back before making headway to about 5L 8th home bend, angled out for a run entering straight but ran home one-paced. (Bled)
Soon took up running on rail before ceding advantage for 2nd passing the 1000 metres, became 2L 3rd rounding home bend and 4th into straight, faded steadily under pressure.
Settled very wide without cover in midfield, drifted backward from approaching home bend reaching last into home straight, made no further impression.
Always in last few, given reminders upon straightening, found nothing. (Lame next day)
Settled 3-wide in a midfield spot 4-5Ls away, improved position 500M and within striking distance turning home, fought tenaciously under top weight, found extra late to get up near line.
Obtained a 3-wide spot ahead of midfield, crept forward along the 4-path home turn, took over top of straight then kicked nicely clear mid-straight, gave all only to be nailed on the line.
Jumped on terms, reserved behind midfield 5Ls back, switched away from fence 650M, responded well to go 3rd with 200M to go, kept battling hard late but not getting to first two.
Away cleanly, maintained a midfield position along the 2-path, came wide home turn, ran on mildly but couldn't quite crack the top three.
Jumped awkwardly, chased leaders and stayed within striking distance turning home, kept on mildly final 300M. Always held by leaders.
Not hurried early stages, settled down near last 6-7Ls away, saved ground on inside but was held up for clear running from 250-150M, had too much to make up final stages.
From wide draw rolled across behind runners, given a patient ride at the rear 8Ls away, worked home fairly final 300M and couldn't make any impact.
Jumped only fairly, settled in the second half of the field, held up making the home turn and fell back to the rear, ran home fairly over final 300M and was never a threat.
Away in line from draw 1, settled midfield 3Ls off leaders, held up behind weakening horses 350M-150M, had too much to make up when the race was nearly over.
Jumped fairly, ended up racing towards the rear 3-wide, swung widest on the home turn, couldn't go on passing 300M and failed to threaten at any stage.
Pressed forward from wide draw, vied lead along the 2-path from 1400M, struggled to keep up from 300M, soon dropped out of contention.
Chased leaders on inside, close enough turning home but was held up behind weakening rivals from 300M-100M and lost every chance.
Unable to slot in from wide draw, strode to the fore but remained 3-wide without cover throughout, had enough passing 250M, weakened rapidly.
Worked to the lead, pressed by rival throughout the race, soon headed on straightening, no extra 200M and fell back through the field. (Mucus.)

Began fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide approaching 1000M, commenced move 700M, took the lead 650M, led by a length turning in, kept on very well in straight, won by 2 lengths.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, headed approaching 650M, 2nd turning in, kept on well in straight without threatening the winner.
Began well, raced prominently on the outside, allowed rival to cross near 1100M, 3rd on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the leading pair.
Began well from a wide draw, tracked leaders on the outside, moved closer after entering the back straight, outpaced 550M, 4 lengths back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, wider turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, raced behind midfield on the outside, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, race at rear throughout, never a factor.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 650M, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped on terms and settled second, one off the fence. Challenged leader passing 300m and hit front in closing stages.
Jumped well and able to find lead easily. Controlled tempo and gave good kick at top of straight. Fought on strongly to the line, headed last 50m.
Settled fourth, one off the fence. Travelled well, presented to challenge at 300m mark and chased hard to the line.
Settled third the fence, raced keenly middle stages. Came off heels passing 300m and stayed on well for close fourth.
Jumped on terms, crowded shortly after and settled at tail of field. Stayed on but unable to make ground on leaders.
Jumped on terms, allowed to settle second last on the fence. Chased hard but outpaced in straight and well beaten.
Jumped nicely, chased the leader 2 wide, made good ground inside 200M, closed off strongly (See Incident Report).
Settled handy, traveled comfortably, responded well under pressure, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, switched out entering the Straight, made good progress over the concluding stages.
Settled handy, traveled okay, ran on evenly to the finish.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened passing 250M, one pace.
Jumped only fairly, sat midfield, traveled fairly, briefly held up entering the Straight, closed off okay.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, traveled fairly, made some progress when asked.
Sat rear, traveled fairly, limited response when asked, ran on fairly.
Settled midfield, raced wide throughout, could not make up ground in the Straight.
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, switched out rounding the Turn, held up entering the Straight, never a threat.
Sat in front of midfield, raced keenly and got its head up in the early stages, weakened passing 250M.
Sat towards rear, raced wide from 1200M, left without a finishing effort in the Straight.
Settled midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, minor progress made when asked (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, traveled only fairly, no contention (See Incident Report).
Jumped quickly and soon disputing lead. Travelled well and fought on strongly when leader kicked clear. Hit front last few strides.
Jumped well from rails draw and shared lead with winner. Asked for effort just before 300m mark and gave good kick, headed last few strides.
Slow to move and then settled worse than midfield. Held up passing 800m and raced keenly. Again held up coming to home turn. Finished strongly last 200m to get third on line.
Jumped well and settled fourth on fence, behind leader. Raced keenly during middle stages, held up for a run from 400m to 300m. Stayed on strongly.
Obliged to race wide from outside gate, without cover majority of race. Challenged at 300m and continued to chase hard to the line.
Raced keenly early stages, settling midfield one off fence. Not a lot of room early part of straight, in clear running 200m, ran on, closest at finish.
Jumped well, three wide with cover , pushed wide on home turn. Loomed up at 300m, peaked on run last 150m.
Went back at start , eased passing 1000m. Settle in rear group. Bumped and unbalanced 150m. Ran on well.
Slow to move and had a tendency to race greenly on inside of other runners. Under pressure passing 400m but continued to make ground, tried hard.
Slow to move from wide gate and allowed to cross to tail of field, settling second last. Last on turn, chased hard and made ground last 200m.
Jumped well from wide gate, but drifted back settling fourth last. Came widest in straight, continued to make ground all the way to line.
From outside barrier shifted across behind runners to settle last. Still last at 400m. Well beaten but stayed on and closest at finish.
Jumped well, but then outpaced. Ridden along from 900m to improve. Stayed on in straight but well beaten.
Jumped awkwardly, drove through to settle fifth, one off fence. Under pressure passing 300m and faded last 100m.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 500M, 2 lengths back turning in, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line.

Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, briefly headed approaching 900M, retook the lead 600M, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 200M, finished 2nd.
Crowded shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 12 lengths or so back, moved closer on turn but still 6 to 7 lengths behind, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.
Bumped start, taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.

Jumped awkwardly, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Blundered on jumping and crowded, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead approaching 900M, headed 600M, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 550M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Broke well and showed very good speed to lead, travelled comfortably throughout, responded nicely when asked at 300M, kept on strongly, won going away, impressive.
Settled midfield on the rail, held up early in the Straight, closed off nicely once in the clear, but no threat to winner. (See Incident Report)
Jumped nicely, tracked leader 2 wide, held together top of the Straight until final 300M, closed off okay when asked.
Sat on pace 2 wide, switched out in the Straight, made some progress.
Settled in front of midfield, travelled keenly, no clear run for the majority of the Straight, never seriously tested.
Bounded on jumping, settled behind midfield 2 wide, ran on only evenly. (See Incident Report)
Sat towards the rear on the rail, made some late ground near the rail until got hampered final 50M.
Settled at the rear, stayed on fairly.
Sat towards the rear 2 wide, made no impression.
Caught 3 wide no cover on pace, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Sat behind the leaders on the rail, gave ground in the Straight.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, quickened well to hit the front 300 metres out, won comfortably.

Recovered swiftly along the rail from slow start to reach 3.5L 7th 1000 metres out, shifted out for a run entering straight, ran on well under pressure to reach 2nd 100 metres out but never threatening.
Settled in midfield in 8th about 4L off the pace, obtained a run between runners 300 metres out, ran on steadily without threatening.
Soon took up running and led to the 800 metres when narrowly headed, remained in close-up 2nd to straight, kept on before finding no extra inside final 150 metres.
Towards rear in 10th, commenced move rounding home bend, produced good late impression inside final 150 metres.
Settled well back on rails in 11th towards rear after troubled start, did not find much room behind runners early in straight, made up good late ground inside final 100 metres.
Settled just over 2L off the pace in 5th or 4th on rail, in similar position turning in for home, kept on same pace until finding no extra inside final 100 metres.
Soon dropped to rear of midfield, saved ground on rail turning in for home, kept on steadily without quickening.
Quickly improved from moderate start to 6th within 3L of pace, found nothing under pressure after straightening.
Always in last few and only ran past well-beaten horses inside final 150 metres.
Began well from a poor draw travelling prominently and wide, took slender lead 800 metres out and led until dropping out quickly inside final 300 metres.
Always in last few after beginning from a poor draw, never seen with a chance.
Settled well behind after beginning from the widest draw, never seen with a chance.
Niggled along 3-wide in first few, went wider into straight and soon weakened.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in second half of the field but was never far off, ran on strongly final 300M, got up to beat the long time race leader just in time.
Led from 1300M, kicked on well early straight, shifted in under pressure between 200M-100M, caught by winner last stride. (Jockey's left foot dislodged from stirrup iron closing stages.)
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled at the rear until making a wide move 650M, battled on steadily to claim 3rd near line but no threat to first two.
Pressed forward, raced keenly outside the lead, fought on well to hold 2nd until nearing 150M, faded late and lost 3rd on the line.
Tracked leaders on inside, couldn't quicken enough turning home, always held by rivals final 200M.
Towards the rear in a 7 runner race, lacked a finishing response passing 400M. Never threatened.
Tracked leaders, taken to a 3-wide spot entering the turn, couldn't go on and dropped away top of straight. (To consecutive Barrier Trials, OVE including diagnostic assessments.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, a length or so back turning in, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 250M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, positioned 2-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, closed off well to make frame, no threat to the first few. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Quickly into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Bumped start, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced in 3rd, 3 wide with no cover, there to turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rivals turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, stayed on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start and unbalanced, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, angled out 450M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide on turn, made some progress in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, wider from 600M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out approaching 500M, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped only fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.) (Sustained a left front fetlock injury on the day after racing.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Settled just worse than midfield, quickened well inside final 350 metres to hit the front over 150 metres out, won readily.
Not far off in 5th or 6th, became further off the lead by 3L when pace increased onto home bend, 1L back when baulked behind leaders early in straight, quickened well inside final 250 metres.
Settled just over 2L back in 7th, further off the pace 3-wide when tempo increased onto home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.

Soon recovered to 3-wide in first few from moderate start, became 4th just over 2L back 3-wide without cover onto home bend, came to challenge entering straight, held every chance until finding no extra inside final 150 metres.
Broke well from the one draw settling not far off the pace, some 3L back when tempo increased early in home bend, fought on steadily under pressure despite inconvenienced about 150 metres out.
Gradually taken back to worse than midfield from a poor draw remaining 3-wide in last few to straight, fought on steadily under pressure inside final 200 metres, did best work late.
Ridden forward to be up with the pace, came to share lead into straight gaining narrow advantage shortly afterwards, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 200 metres.

Gradually picked up to midfield just over 3L off the pace on rail after moderate start, slightly further back when tempo increased onto home bend, hampered 700 metres out, produced good late impression closing stages.
Soon taken well behind from a poor draw, detached from the main body of the field until the 600 metres, making good progress when baulked for a run inside final 150 metres.
Niggled along in last few from moderate start, inconvenienced 600 metres out but saved ground on rail turning in for home, made some late progress closing stages.

Soon taken back to last few from the widest draw remaining 3-wide most of the way, commenced move entering home straight, kept on steadily without quickening under strong pressure in the run to the line.

Not far off and wide after beginning well from a poor draw, pulled forward to take up running over 900 metres out, narrowly headed after straightening, weakened under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Always in last few, made no impression in the run to the line.
Soon took up running and led until headed over 900 metres out, chased leaders around home bend and into straight, soon weakened.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly, led close home.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed very good response in straight, took the lead near 75M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began smartly, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in midfield, 2 wide, angled out 350M, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1-1/2L back turning in, kept on well early in straight, took the lead 100M, peaked and headed shortly thereafter, weakened final 50M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths or so back turning in, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover from 700M, 6 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back turning in, show some response in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced at tail, 9 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Stayed in touch with leaders throughout, in 3rd place from 1000M, bustled along 500M, quickened up nicely to lead near 200M, kept battling under pressure for 2nd win over course and distance.
Taken back from wide draw, given a waiting ride at the rear, swung widest for home before running on strongly to claim 2nd inside 100M. Couldn't quite get to the winner.
Bumped at the start, maintained a position in midfield, finished off moderately final 400M but posed little threat to first two.
Jumped only fairly, recovered to race behind midfield 5-6Ls off leader, pushed along 500M, stayed on to claim 4th without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly, settled down midfield but no closer than 3-wide during the race, ran on mildly turning for home, lay in and difficult to ride out final stages. Never a winning hope.
Dropped back to the rear, 8-9Ls off leader middle stages, saved ground on the inside throughout, stayed on fairly final 300M. Never threaten.
Strode forward nearing 2000M to take the lead, set steady pace, under pressure to maintain the lead 550M, headed near 200M, no extra late stages.
Settled towards the rear, held up for clear running making the home turn, had some work to do top of straight but managed to run past beaten rivals only.
Settled down midfield along the inside, little change middle stages, in touch turning for home but couldn't quicken enough, no extra 150M. (Jockey : no explanation for disappointing performance.)
Jumped only fairly, held up towards the rear 6-7Ls behind leader, couldn't go on 250M. (Jockey : disappointing in its failure to respond to his riding in home straight.)
Obtained a position outside the lead early stages, driven passing 500M but was gone mid-straight. (Jockey: failed to change its lead leg in home straight and gave ground.)
Never far off leaders but raced wide without cover throughout, under pressure from 600M and gave ground before weakening badly in the straight. Finished tailed out.
Sat handy, traveled comfortably, commenced to improve approaching 750M and chased the leader, showed some dash passing 200M.
Sat handy, raced keenly in the early stages, made good progress passing 200M, closed off nicely.
Settled midfield, raced wide throughout, kept on well to hold 3rd.
Ridden along to lead, traveled okay, slightly weakened near 200M, ran on evenly.
Settled behind midfield, steadied near 750M, raced keenly and got its head up thereafter, closed off okay.
Sat in front of midfield, minor progress made when asked, one pace to the finish.
Sat rear, traveled fairly, minor progress made under pressure.
Sat rear, slightly held up rounding the Home Turn, could not be ridden out over the concluding stages (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, traveled fairly, no clear run entering the Straight, one pace to the line (See Incident Report).
Settled behind midfield, gave ground quickly in the Straight, never a danger.
Jumped awkwardly, sat midfield, gave ground in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, improved rounding the Turn, weakened and faded quickly passing 250M (See Incident Report).
Settled slightly worse than midfield, one off fence. Brought to centre of track in straight to challenge, finished to strongly, comfortable on the line.
Prominent from gates before taking sit, sixth one off fence. Travelled well in the run and then urged along passing 400m, finished well in straight, but no match for winner.
Jumped well then eased out of speed battle coming to first turn. Settled fourth one off fence. Three wide to make run on turn, hit front at 200m headed 50m out, beaten for second just before line.
Fairly way and crossed behind field to settle in last pair. Held up momentarily top of straight and ran home strongly last 200m when clear. Eye catching.
Ridden along early to hold position, settled seventh on fence. Held up and raced keenly on fence leaving back straight. Kept on rail in run home, stayed on to take fifth.
Fairly away, settled fourth last. Difficulty obtaining clear running 300m to 200m, made ground late without threatening to be placed.
Slow to move from wide gate, settling third last. Brought widest on turn to make challenge. Ran home fairly in straight, closest on line but well beaten.
Began quickly, vied for lead but caught three wide no cover. Challenged at top straight, beaten by 150m, faded last 100m.
First to leave gates, eased to take sit behind first three and then three back the fence. Held up early part of straight, failed to make ground when placed under pressure.

Saddle slipped back on jumping place rider at disadvantage during running. Found fence and in three way battle for front down the back, before third the fence. Came off rail in straight but beaten passing 200m. Faded closing stages.
Jumped only fairly. Ridden to stay in touch but settled in last pair. Clear last and ridden along passing 400m, passed tiring leader in straight but detached from main group at finish.
Ridden out of gates to contest lead, caught wide on to first turn , worked hard to finally cross to rail second turn. Found nothing in straight, eased down last 200m.
Out with rest, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader from 400M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 400M, closed off well to take 2nd, always held.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider 400M, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening the front pair.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, challenged by rival from 400M, headed early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, made little progress in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, kept on same pace in the run home.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide after entering the back straight, no cover from 700M, 6 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, unable to maintain position after passing 750M, last turning in, showed nothing in straight.
Out in line, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped on terms, settled just behind the leaders on the rail, angled out for clear running rounding the Home Turn, closed off well, always doing enough.
Settled midfield on the rail, closed off well, closest finish.
Sat behind the leaders early, raced keenly and switched out to lead 2 wide, kept on nicely until weakened slightly final 100M. (Roarer)
Not the quickest out, settled behind midfield on the rail, caught behind horses in the Straight, no clear run, ran on late once in the clear.
Showed good early speed to lead, kept on okay until weakened final 150M.
Hard ridden early but showed no speed, settled towards the rear 2 wide, began to improve near the 700M, ran on only evenly. (See Incident Report)
Initially sat outside lead, sat on pace with cover in the middle stages, one pace to the line.
Settled at the rear 2 wide, switched out in the Straight, made minor progress.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Sat midfield 2 wide, under pressure at 500M, limited response.
Raced towards the rear on the rail, never a threat.
Caught wide early, restrained towards the rear 2 wide, never in contention. (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Settled one back in 3rd on rail, came to tackle leader over 400 metres out, hit the front approaching home turn and soon drew clear.

Crowded at start before settling behind midfield in 8th, commenced move over 500 metres out, 3-wide rounding home bend and briefly baulked on straightening, ran on under pressure inside final 200 metres.

Crowded after moderate start settling at the back, made steady headway on rail in back straight to reach 9th 700 metres out, angled out wide for a run into straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Pressed forward from the widest draw settling some 3L back in 4th, came under pressure to challenge rounding home bend, kept on steadily in straight without quickening.
Soon taken back to just worse than midfield on rail in 7th, saved ground rounding home bend, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening in straight.

Jumped awkwardly from a poor draw settling in last few, travelled keenly passing the 800 metres, commenced move 400 metres out and the widest into straight, made modest progress past beaten horses near the centre of the track.
Led the field on rail after beginning from the one draw setting a sound pace, headed when found no extra about 400 metres out.
Settled some 4L off the pace in 5th on rail, commenced move rounding home bend for 2.5L 4th into straight, unable to sustain effort after straightening.

Began awkwardly from a poor draw, travelled 3-wide in midfield early stages before taken well back approaching first bend, given reminders in last from 650 metres out, saved ground on rail turning in, ran home one-paced.
Gradually settled in midfield in 6th, came under pressure rounding home bend and soon faded.
Pressed forward from a wide draw before settling 2-wide in 1L 2nd, lost position over 500 metres out and weakened soon after straightening. (Jockey said not suited by the going.)
Chased runaway leader, clear 2nd at 400M, quickened up nicely to lead 80M out, held on gamely at the finish.
Jumped only fairly, held up towards the rear 9-10Ls off runaway leader, had task ahead top of straight, came home strongly to claim 2nd, nearest finish.
Jumped awkwardly then taken back from wide draw, given a waiting ride at the rear 10Ls off leader, closed off strongly down the inside to take 3rd at the line, nearest finish.

Soon led and opened up a 3Ls lead, kept on well early straight and led the charge until 100M, edged out to 4th close home. (Jockey : attempted to restrain and set a more sustainable pace but horse did not respond to his efforts.)
Held up in behind midfield 6-7Ls from the runaway leader, closed off mildly final 300M to be nearest at the finish.

Went forward chasing runaway leader, hard driven 450M, battled on one paced in the straight, lacked finishing effort final 200M. (Jockey : not comfortable racing around HV circuit first time / Lame next day.)
Away with them, settled down midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, driven along 400M but couldn't quicken enough to challenge leaders.
Settled towards the rear, plenty to do 400M, made limited progress in the home straight, not reach leaders.
Caught wide no cover until 750M then raced along the 2-path in midfield, ran on same pace passing 300M, well held by leaders.
Jumped fairly, obtained a position behind midfield, 8Ls to make up 400M, failed to run on in the straight.
Dropped back to the rear on jumping from a wide barrier, 10Ls off the pace middle stages, couldn't pick up on straightening, never in the hunt.
Jumped fast, soon restrained to a position behind midfield, struggled to go with them passing 400M, soon out of contention. (Blood in trachea.)
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 3/4L back turning in, hit the front approaching 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Away well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.

Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 400M, very wide into straight, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 150M, weakened final 100M.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.
Jumped only fairly, raced at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 350M, made no impression in the run home.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out approaching 350M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)

Jumped only fairly, raced 3 wide towards rear, angled out approaching 500M, 3-1/2L back turning in, finished off strongly to score by a neck.

Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out 500M, hard ridden approaching 300M, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M, beaten by a neck.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, short of room early in straight, kept on well thereafter to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 600M, 2-1/2L back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to make frame.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until approaching final 100M, finished off well without threatening.
Quickly into stride, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Missed break and lost a considerable amount of ground, detached in the early stages, latched on to rear of field 800M, 5-1/2L back turning in, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide towards rear, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 150M.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled in perfect position three off the fence in clear ground, 5 lengths from lead. Came off heels passing 300m mark found front passing 200m. Won handily.
Taken across towards rails to settle second last with cover. Switched to centre of track to get clear ground and ran home strongly.
Allowed to settled third last and then improved pass 600m between horses. Brought to centre of track to challenge, continued to run on and fought hard for third.
Jumped quickly and taken to front before sitting second under a hold. Hit front at 350m headed passing 100m. Just missed third last few strides.
Jumped well, allowed to settle midfield on rails, travelled nicely making good ground from 300m. Came across heels at 150m to challenge but soon one paced to finish line.
Hesitated when gates open, settled at rear of field. Dipped at 500m mark. Still last at 350m, made good ground late between horses, held up last 50m between runners.
Jumped on terms, followed field across to stand side, sat in second group. Asked for effort passing 400m, under pressure passing 150m and faded last 50m.
Ridden hard to lead, but not able to cross to rail. Joined passing half way mark and soon headed. Stayed on but faded last 100m.
Quickly away and then eased to take sit behind leading group. Ridden along to stay in touch from half way. Stayed on but baulked for run passing 150m.
Held up behind runners and tight for room passing half way. Switched back to rails to make ground, but soon one-paced passing 200m and failed to run on.
Slow to move and pushed along early. Settled midfield between horses. Disappointed for run passing half way and gave ground. Ran home fairly again last 100m.
Bounded in air as gates opened but mustered speed to settle worse than midfield. Hard ridden passing half way and failed to make ground, well beaten.
Jumped well, tracked across to settle in second group chasing leaders. Under pressure at 400m and faded in final stages to only beat one home.
Showed good speed to settle in forward division, under pressure from half way and then lost action when tight on heels of another runner and dropped out.
Chased the leader, traveled comfortably, responded well when asked.
Ridden hard to lead on the stand's rail, raced keenly in the early stages, ran on evenly.
Sat towards rear, traveled nicely, made good progress under pressure near 150M.
Settled rear, switched in to obtain clear running passing 400M, closed off okay.
Settled in front of midfield at the center of the track, traveled okay, lay out over the final 200M, one pace to the line.
Settled midfield, raced tight over the concluding stages, ran on evenly.
Sat handy, weakened from 250M, never a threat.
Jumped awkwardly, sat worse than midfield, traveled fairly, weakened notably after 200M, never a factor.
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, could not be ridden out, no contention.
Sat midfield, weakened and faded passing 200M, never a danger.
Hesitated at start but quickened to settle sixth, three back the fence. Came off rail at 400m and in clear ground passing 300m. Reeled in leader last 50m and soft win.
Jumped quickly from outside gate to lead easily early. Crossed to rail passing 800m. Good kick from 300m and fought on strongly. Winner too good.
Jumped well, settling third the fence behind leader. Held up for a run on inside first half of straight and then ran home fairly when in clear ground last 150m.
Jumped well and went forward when caught three wide to sit outside leader coming to first turn. Asked for effort coming to 300m, stayed on fairly to hold fourth.
Last to leave the gates. Settled between horses slightly worse than midfield. Held up for run early in straight, switched direction to get clear running, closest on line.
Slow to move at start, drifted back to last. Stayed on rail in straight, still last at 400m, continued to make ground last 300m, closest at finish.
Jumped on terms, ridden to hold midfield position, forced to race three wide no cover. Asked for effort passing 400m. Stayed on last 100m.
Quickly away and prominent early settling behind leading pair. Tended to lay in around last bend. Challenged in straight but beaten off by 150m and faded closing stages.
Fairly away and then drifted back to settle second last on fence. Came off rail passing 400m, brought to middle of track, finished fairly but beaten long way.
Jumped well and went forward before steadied after going 200m. Settled fifth, one off fence. Made ground when asked for effort, soon one paced and tired last 100m.
On toes as gates opened and slow away. Railed through to settle midfield but eased and raced keenly middle stages. Under pressure passing 300m and faded in last 150m.
Settled third last, one off fence. Ridden along approaching straight and brought to centre of track to make run. Failed to make any ground.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run approaching 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 550M, finished off evenly.

Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, dropped towards rear on turn, 5 lengths or so back turning in, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress, no threat to the first few.
Shifted in shortly after start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 1100M, 2 wide on turn, angled out 500M, finished off well without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight, nearest finish.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, angled out 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, 2 wide in the middle stages, made no impression in straight.

Moderately away from a wide draw, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 950M, angled out 600M, 2-1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 850M, carried wider 600M, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear of midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, eased final 100M.
Jumped with the field, showed good early speed to lead, travelled smoothly throughout, kicked clear at 250M, kept on, won comfortably.
Not the quickest out, settled behind midfield on the rail, made some ground along the inside, no threat to winner.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, closed off okay.
Sat on pace 2 wide, kept on okay, only one pace to the line.
Settled just behind the leaders, raced keenly in the early stages, nothing extra in the Straight.
Sat towards the rear on the rail, made some late headway.
Raced behind midfield 2 wide between horses, stayed on fairly.
Settled midfield 2 wide, limited response in the Straight. (Mucus in Trachea)
Steadied from the start from the outside barrier, sat towards the rear, made no impression.
Hard ridden early, sat outside the lead, weakened in the Straight.
Sat last, never a threat. (Bled)
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, gave ground in the Straight.

Jumped well from a poor draw settling over 2L back in 3rd, became 4th in a similar position 600 metres out, commenced move inside the 300 metres and hit the front under pressure over 200 metres out, hung in away from whip 100 metres out.

Improved steadily on rail after moderate start, just over 3L back in 4th coming onto home bend, hit the front briefly just inside the 300 metres, bumped by the winner 100 metres out, fought on gamely to the line.
Ridden early stages before settling some 4L back in 5th, came under pressure to challenge upon straightening holding every chance 150 metres out, unable to sustain effort shortly afterwards.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon ridden forward along the rail to over 5L back in 7th, gained one closer rounding home bend, angled out for a run on straightening, ran on under pressure and did best work late.
Settled behind midfield for cover after beginning from a poor draw, remained one from last into straight, ran on under pressure near the centre of the track inside final 300 metres.
Ridden positively before settling just off the pace in 2nd on rail, gained slightly closer hugging inside rail on final turn, faded under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly from a wide draw, settled 2-wide behind midfield approaching home bend, came under pressure entering straight but find no extra.

Pressed forward from the widest draw to soon take up running after first 100 metres, obtained run closer to rail in front coming onto home bend, faded under pressure inside final 300 metres. (Lame next day)
Always well behind after slow start, never seen with a chance.
Bumped on jumping, obtained a 2-wide spot in mid-division, wide into straight, finished off strongly under top weight to lead 150M before keeping on well final stages to score.
Urged along early stages to take up a spot in midfield along the fence, into clear 300M, closed off the race well to claim 2nd near line, nearest finish.
Bumped on jumping, from draw 1 moved up to track leaders, gave good response on straightening, went 2nd 150M out before dropping to 3rd close home.
Bumped at the start, dropped back and given a waiting ride at the rear, had task ahead turning home, finished off final 400M best to take 4th near line.
Caught wide and raced keenly early stages , allowed to stride forward and lead nearing 800M, kept on well early straight, headed 150M and faded to 5th late.
Crowded on jumping, settled down behind midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, finished off nicely gaining ground on leaders late.
Vied for early lead before settling down in 3rd, fought hard to stay in contention early straight, faded final 150M.
Close up behind leaders early, fell back to a midfield position entering home turn, checked 350M but lacked a finishing response after.
Went forward, pressed by rivals in the lead, sat in 2nd spot from 1000M, kept on same pace when driven out 350M, no extra 200M. (Jockey : unsuited by being pressured in early stages.)
Up with early pace before obtaining a trailing spot behind leaders, lacked a finishing response passing 400M, soon beaten.
Bumped at the start, settled towards the rear, switched widest passing 600M but couldn't quicken on straightening. Failed to threaten at any stage.

Held up towards the rear, pushed along 500M before easing down 300M. (Jockey : travelled reasonably well but didn't respond to riding 300M, concerned something amiss with his horse / No Vet findings.)
Dropped back to the rear over 10Ls behind leaders middle stages, didn't travel well throughout, eased 300M. (Jockey concerned something amiss with his horse / No Vet findings.)
Fast into stride, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead approaching 800M, led by 3 lengths turning in, kept on well to hold off the challenger late.
Out with rest, taken back to race 3 wide towards rear, 5 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, made very good progress final 300M to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, positioned 3 wide better than midfield, angled out 500M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.

Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 500M, 6 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, made good progress final 200M to make frame without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, dropped towards rear on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, angled out 550M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently, 3 wide, peaked on turn, hampered near 300M, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Commenced well, raced prominently, 2 wide, peaked 550M, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped 4 wide, dropped to midfield after passing 800M, peaked 500M, weakened early in straight, eased inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, peaked 500M, weakened early in straight.
Jumped only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/4L turning in, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, saved ground on turn, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, bumped near 1000M, 2 wide in the middle stages, angled out 450M, finished off strongly to take a place.
Shifted in at start, tracked leaders, a length or so back turning in, kept on well in straight to make frame, always held.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, crowded near 1000M, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, difficult to settle in the early stages, 2 wide on turn, taken wide in straight and made some headway.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, found rail approaching 950M, 2 wide from 550M, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, checked near 1000M, found rail near 850M, angled out early in straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began well from a wide draw, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away and crowded, raced 2 wide towards rear early, crowded 1000M, 3 wide behind midfield in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, found rail near 800M, dropped to 3rd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, led by 2 lengths turning in, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, found rail near 1050M, 2 lengths back in the middle stages, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away well, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside early, 2 wide from 1000M, angled out 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually close home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, commenced move approaching 400M, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, saved ground on turn, still 8 lengths or so back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from 1000M, peaked on run 400M, weakened thereafter, eased final 150M.

Jostled at start, settled in 7th on rail about 4L off the pace, gained steadily around home bend and into straight, hit the front strongly 200 metres out kicking 2L clear 100 metres out, just held off runner-up's strong late challenge.
Settled in last few and waited with, came under pressure to challenge rounding home bend kicking widest into straight, ran on well while shifting in under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
Settled towards rear in 9th on rail, commenced move rounding home bend and saved ground on the inside turning in, switched off rail for a run over 200 metres out, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Taken well behind from the widest draw and waited with, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.

Ridden forward to better than midfield, some 4L 6th rounding first bend, given reminders on home bend while shifting 3-wide for a run into straight, fought on steadily to the line despite tightened 150 metres out.

Broke well from the one draw, settled one back before joining leader onto first bend, disputed lead most of back straight, came under pressure home bend but unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Settled not far off the pace in 5th on rail, gained 3rd just over 2L back 550 meres out, angled out for a run entering straight, faded gradually under pressure.
Ridden positively from a poor draw to take up running on the rail, joined in front soon after turning into back straight, folded up quickly inside final 250 metres.
Never better than midfield, saved ground turning in for home, kept on one pace.

Settled not far off the pace in 4th, gained 3rd in similar one-out-one-back position turning into back straight, came under pressure when drifted backward to 3L 4th home bend, dropped sharply out of contention into straight.

Pressed forward after moderate start from a wide draw, one back 3-wide without cover rounding first bend and into back straight, shifted back to 5th passing the 900 metres, dropped out of contention over 500 metres out.

Placing: PU
Comment: In last few throughout before pulling up approaching home straight.
Sat rear, made good progress in the Straight, stayed on well to win (See Incident Report).
Settled worse than midfield, traveled okay, lay in near the 150M, responded nicely when asked
Settled behind midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, showed some dash over the final 100M.
Sat handy, steadied near the 1200M after being crossed, raced keenly thereafter, slightly weakened entering the Straight.
Settled in front of midfield, steadied when raced tight near the 1000M, ran on evenly.
Sat worse than midfield, made a forward move passing the 1000M and raced wide thereafter, ran on okay.
Sat towards rear, traveled fairly, switched out rounding the Turn, one pace to the line.
Ridden along to lead on the rail, weakened passing 200M, closed off only fairly.
Sat midfield, crowded near the 1600M, raced keenly in the early stages, not much impression made.
Sat towards rear, traveled fairly, limited response when asked (See Incident Report).
Settled midfield, held up near the 150M, could not be ridden out, never a threat.
Chased the leader, weakened after 150M, faded gradually (See Incident Report).
First to leave the gates, held lead into first turn, challenged at top of straight, kicked strongly, drifted in under pressure and fought on gamely to win.
Jumped on terms, allowed to settle sixth on the rails. Raced keenly approaching 500m, stayed on fence in straight, closed strongly for second.
Prominent early, settling third the fence. Poised on turn and stayed on inside of leader who drifted in under pressure. Ran out of room passing 50m, not fully ridden out. Placing not impacted.
Quickly away, then eased to take sit, , settling midfield one off fence. Travelled well to turn, middle of track to make run, closed strongly late, closest at finish.
Slow to jump, ridden along to settle worse than midfield. angled out in straight, made good ground last 200m to get fifth right on the line.
Ridden forward from wide gate to challenge for lead. Sat outside leader down the back, challenged leader on home turn and prominent until last 150m when peaked on run and tired.
Ridden out of gates from wide gate and caught three wide throughout the run. Ridden to stay in touch to final bend. Continued to stay on after hard run and tired last 75m.
Jumped on only fairly, allowed to drift back to tail of field. Crowded near 550m, came wide on final turn, continued to make ground but well beaten.
Jumped well and prominent early. Had to ease coming to first turn and settled fifth, between horses. In clear ground early in straight but failed to run on and well beaten.
Rider had to take hold and slowly away. Settled fourth last on fence. Off rail at 500m to make run but one paced last 200m and failed to make any ground.

Lunged forward before gates opened, lost considerable ground. Caught field approaching 900m. Made some ground early in straight and then beaten and faded last 200m. [Substantial blood in trachea post-race]
Caught wide down back straight and eased back to third last, wide no cover. Gave ground approaching final turn and eased down last 200m.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back in the early stages, 3 lengths or so back in the middle stages, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.

Average to begin, raced towards rear on the outside early, sent forward approaching 1050M, took the lead near 900M, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, stayed on evenly to take 3rd.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 1050M, 2nd in the middle stages, 1-1/2L back turning in, kept on well in straight to make frame, always held.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Made contact at start, took the early lead, headed near 900M, 3rd on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped on terms, settled midfield 2 wide between horses, switched out into the clear final 300M, ran on very strongly, won easily.
Settled behind the leader, hit the front at 150M, kept on but no match to winner.
Settled midfield on the rail, raced greenly, stayed on okay.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made good ground along the rail.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, only one pace to the line.
Jumped nicely, hard ridden early to lead, weakened final 150M.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, stayed on fairly.
Sat one pace, under pressure at 350M, limited response and soon weakened.
Not the quickest out, sat last, made no impression.
Settled midfield 3 wide with cover, never ran on. (See Incident Report) (Continuous epiglottic entrapment)
Caught 3 wide no cover in front of midfield, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Sat towards the rear, never in contention.
Vied for lead early, gained slender advantage 2-wide 950 metres out obtaining rails run passing the 700 metres, just held off runner-up's strong late challenge.

Began well, amongst leaders early before settling just over 1L back in 5th, dropped further away inside the 800 metres becoming 3L 6th rounding home bend, renewed effort inside final 150 metres and did best work late.

Settled on rail mainly in rear of midfield, baulked behind runners in 7th on rail rounding home bend, snuck up under pressure early in straight reaching 3rd 200 metres out, did not find much room near finish.
Soon taken back to last from a poor draw and waited with, baulked for a run rounding home bend and early in straight, ran on well inside final 250 metres.

Began well from the widest draw, persevered 5-wide into back straight to match pace with the leaders gaining 2-wide 2nd position over 700 metres out, shifted one back onto home bend, one-paced in straight.

Broke well from a poor draw, soon taken back to midfield for cover briefly, lost cover 3-wide 700 metres out, some 3L back in 5th rounding home bend, one of the widest into straight, ran home one-paced.
Settled 3-wide with cover in last few, shifted widest entering home straight, ran on upon straightening past well-beaten runners down the centre of the track.
Jumped fairly, in midfield early stages before taken back to last few on rail, saved ground on inside turning in for home, kept on past well-beaten runners.

Began moderately, 9th in rear of midfield until hampered and lost position 750 metres out, tightened between runners and lost position passing the 560 metres and baulked early in straight, kept on well to the line.

Travelling keenly in 1.5L 6th when steadied 1050 metres out, continued to race keenly in back straight and lost position approaching home bend, one of the widest entering straight, made no further impression.

Ridden along to be up with the pace 4-wide early stages, taken back for cover in 4th 2-wide passing the 900 metres, gained closer to 3rd 600 metres out switching 3-wide rounding home bend, folded up quickly upon straightening.
Ridden along from the one draw to hold slender advantage early stages until the 950 metres, given reminders to hold prominent position rounding home bend, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Shaken up after the start, emerged as leader 550M, drew clear top of straight and kept on powerfully to the line giving rivals no chance.
From widest gate switched off to race in last, over 6Ls to make up 400M, closed off fastest to claim 2nd close home but not reach runaway winner.
Stayed in touch with leaders throughout, moved up to 2nd place top of the straight, tried hard but couldn't get closer to the leader, lost 2nd final stages but held 3rd comfortably.
Dropped back to a rearward position 5-6Ls back, commenced his challenge down the inside on straightening, ran past beaten horses but couldn't quicken enough to pose any threat to first three.
Restrained to a 3-wide position 5-6Ls towards the rear, still last at 200M, made some ground late to claim a non-threatening 5th.
Went forward, caught racing wide no cover outside leaders, ran on one paced in the straight.
Jumped on terms, settled down in mid-division, hung out making first turn losing one or two length, ran on final over 300M without threatening leaders.
Jumped only fairly, near the rear early stages before improving to a midfield spot home turn, battled on one paced early straight, faded final 200M.

Jumped only fairly from draw 10, failed to show sufficient pace to hold a more forward position, caught 3-wide in midfield, lacked finishing effort final 300M. (Jockey : raced "flat" / No Vet findings.)
Up with early pace before obtaining a trailing spot behind leaders, fell back to midfield 400M, unable to finish the race off. (No Vet findings.)
Obtained a position outside the lead early stages, came under pressure 500M before weakening in the home straight to finish last. (Trainer : may race better when able to obtain cover.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 400M, showed good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to make frame.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually close home.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Out with rest, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, kept on evenly in straight.

Taken back to race 2w towards rear, 5Ls or so back, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run 150M to 50M, ran on evenly thereafter. (Lame right front leg and had sustained lacerations to both hind legs.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, raced tight early in straight, no clear run final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out 350M, very wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
