Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, ridden after passing 300M, not enough room approaching 200M, cleared 150M, hit the front 100M, kept on strongly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on the middle track, commenced move approaching 350M, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently on the middle track, hard ridden from 350M, every chance entering final furlong, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently, 3 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M but only showed limited response, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the middle track, 5 lengths back at 400M, finished off well without threatening the first few.
Jumped well from gate 14, raced prominently on the stands' rail, hard ridden approaching 350M, kept on well until 150M, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped heavily shortly after start, raced at rear, 9 lengths or so back in the middle stages, passed some tired runners final 400M.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear, 8 lengths back in the middle stages, one-paced final 400M.
Out with rest, tracked leaders, 1-1/2L back at 400M, peaked 250M, weakened thereafter.
Away well, tracked leaders on the stands' side, ridden approaching 300M but only showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the middle track, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Reared as stalls opened and started very slowly, recovered to race 4 lengths behind the leader on the middle track, ridden approaching 300M but showed no response, weakened final 250M.
Began only fairly, sent forward to race prominently on the stands' side, took the lead 600M, peaked and headed 300M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, settled third behind leader. Held up for run and in clear ground passing 250m. Finished strongly to hit front last 50m.
Showed customary early speed to lead clearly. Held up until 350m and then gave strong kick. Fought on gamely, only headed inside last 50m.
Jumped only fairly. Unbalanced near 850m when tight for room. Settled midfield on the rail. Waited for run early in straight, closed well last 150m.
Jumped well, prominent early settling outside leader. Shifted out under pressure passing 400m, fought on strongly, missed third last 50m.
Raced wide, without cover throughout in leading group. Loomed up at 300m and then under pressure and once-paced last 100m. Good effort.
Ridden patiently from wide gate, drifted back to last, one off. Held up between runners on turn, made good ground last 150m when in clear room.
Bumped heavily at start. Settled midfield between horses, over raced passing 800m. Three wide to make run on turn. Laid out under pressure, one pace last 100m.
Jumped well but caught wide and drifted back to fourth last, four off fence with cover. Widest in straight, made ground early and stayed on but well beaten.
Jumped well then obliged to race wide without cover from 850m mark. Centre of track in run home, ran on but then one paced last 200m.
Bumped heavily at start and as a consequence settled further back than intended, near last on fence. Not a lot of room in straight but one paced when in clear ground last 250m.
Jumped only fairly and ridden to hold position, settled third last between horses. Under pressure passing 300m, last at 200m and faded.
Jumped well, settled fifth, one off fence. Held up coming to turn, under pressure passing 250m and dropped out last 200m, long last.
Stood flat-footed and missed the Start, sat rear, commenced to improve approaching 800M, switched out rounding the Turn, made good ground and won.
Settled midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, obtained clear running from 300M, showed some dash inside 100M.
Settled towards rear, raced keenly in the early stages, lay in over the concluding stages, stayed on well to grab 3rd.
Began well, chased the leader throughout, slightly weakened inside 300M, ran on evenly.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled okay, slightly held up entering the Straight, one pace to the line.
Sat handy on the rail, traveled comfortably, made some progress in the Straight, ran on okay.
Jumped fairly, sat towards rear, made minor progress over the concluding stages.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened and gave ground inside 400M, ran on fairly.
Sat handy, traveled fairly, weakened passing 300M, no impression thereafter (See Incident Report).
Settled rear, raced rear throughout the event, could not be ridden out.
Settled in front of midfield, raced wide from 900M, gave ground from 500M.
Sat midfield, steadied near 350M, became unbalanced and faded gradually.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, gave ground rounding the Turn, never a threat.
Settled behind midfield, weakened notably rounding the Turn, no contention.
Only jumped fairly but mustered speed to drive to lead. Travelled strongly in front, kicked three lengths clear passing 200m mark and won easily.
Flew gates and then ridden along to hold position outside leader. Asked for effort passing 350m and stayed on well, no match for winner.
Slow to move and then crowded after jumping. Crossed to rail settling fourth last, 10 lengths from front. Ran on well last 250m, closest at finish.
Jumped quickly, settled third, leader's back. Raced keenly passing 600m. Held up early in straight, but in clear room passing 300m. Beaten out of third last few strides.
Bumped after jumping, rider becoming unbalanced, losing iron briefly. Travelled three wide middle stages. Ran home well down centre, closest on the line.
Settled midfield on the rail. Travelled well to final turn, Stayed on rail, one paced when asked for effort, well beaten.
Drew widest and allowed to shift across to tail of field, one off fence. Came to centre of track in straight, ran on fairly, beaten long way from placings.
Jumped well, settling fourth, one off. Travelled well to turn. Came off heels to challenge but beaten at 250m and faded last 200m.
Allowed to go back from wide gate, settling third last, one off fence. Stayed towards rail in straight, under heavy pressure passing 300m and made no impression.
Jumped well, ridden forward. Trapped three wide midfield without cover throughout. No turn of foot in straight, faded last 200m.
Hard ridden out of gates but failed to muster speed, travelled last. Brought to middle of track in straight, failed to run on, passed one last 50m.
Jumped on terms, midfield between horses. Slight ease passing 800m. Ridden along from top of straight, Soon under pressure and faded last 200m.

Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, commenced move after passing 600M, 3 lengths back turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 750M, led by 1-3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to take a place.
Crowded on jumping, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 550M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on outer, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back turning in, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after start, positioned a length behind the leader, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, took the early lead, headed approaching 1000M, 1 out 1 back from 800M, peaked near 500M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 1000M, headed 750M, peaked on run 500M, weakened early in straight, eased inside final furlong.
Jumped well, showed good early speed to lead, kicked clear in the Straight, kept on strongly without being asked, very impressive
Tracked leader, kept on nicely, winner just too good.
Sat behind the leaders, made some progress in the Straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide, made some late ground.
Settled behind midfield, ran on evenly.
Settled near midfield 2 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Broke slowly, at rear, made little impression.
Settled midfield on the rail, made no ground.
Caught 3 wide midfield, never a threat.
3 wide behind midfield, never in contention.

Badly crowded and blundered at start dropping to last, trailed the field on rail to the 750 metres, improving in 10th when running into heels and steadied 550 metres out, renewed effort in straight to assert authority late.

Ridden positively after fair start to take up running passing the 900 metres, obtained rails run approaching first turn, kicked over 3L clear from 1L advantage into straight only to be caught final strides.
Close up early stages before gradually shifting to some 2L back in 6th, renewed effort 4-wide rounding home bend to share 2nd into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Travelled prominently in 4th after moderate start, steadied and lost position passing 600 metres, switched to obtain clear run 300 metres out, fought on steadily without threatening.

Niggled along just worse than midfield after beginning from a poor draw, held rails run in a similar position rounding home bend, did not find much room between runners early in centre of straight, fought on steadily to the line.
Drifted gradually back to last few from the widest draw despite ridden along, shifted wide into straight, made up good ground down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Soon dropped well behind despite ridden along, dropped to last onto home bend, produced good late impression running past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Close up early, gradually drifted back to 5th onto home bend, renewed effort to briefly share 2nd into straight but soon faded.
Soon picked up to close-up 3rd on rail after moderate start, chased leader into straight and soon came under pressure, dropped out of contention inside final 200 metres.
Prominent from a poor draw gradually drifting back to some 3L back in midfield while 5-wide, shifted wider when 10th into straight, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped to some 3L off the pace 6-wide in 7th or 6th, remained very wide in similar position rounding home bend before losing position into straight, never recovered.
Ridden to lead out wide from a poor draw, headed 900 metres out before obtaining 2-wide position in 2nd coming onto home bend, given reminders entering home straight and soon weakened.
From draw 1 jumped only fairly, moved up to track leaders home turn, held up 350M-250M then closed off strongly to score.
Vied for the lead on inside, kicked home strongly passing 300M, only caught by fast finishing winner late.
Tracked leaders along the 2-path, loomed a serious threat 400M, chased hard but couldn't get near to winner, lost 2nd 150M out but held 3rd comfortably.
Settled down midfield, ran home one paced and never posed any threat to first three.
Slow to begin, towards the rear early stages before moving closer to midfield home turn, couldn't quicken enough on straightening, never a threat to leaders.
Dropped back to race at the rear, plenty to make up 400M, failed to run on.
In mid-division, came under pressure home turn and was already beaten top of the straight.
Vied for lead on outside, failed to respond to riding early straight, weakened rapidly nearing 200M. (Jockey : not able to obtain a position on the rail and performed disappointingly.)
Caught wide chasing leaders and had no cover for the majority of the event, had enough nearing 400M, weakened away. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Unable to slot in from wide draw, raced very wide and no cover for the majority of the event, dropped to last 500M, eased top of straight. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 500M, finished off very strongly to score.

Made contact shortly after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, showed good response in straight, took the lead 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Began well, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced better than midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made contact 450M, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3 lengths in the middle stages, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, made contact 450M, peaked 300M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield, 2 wide, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Slowly away, raced at tail, pulled up approaching 1000M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight, won by 2-1/2L.

Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside early, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 wide from 600M, 2 lengths or so back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, there to turn, peaked on run 300M, kept on evenly to the line, just held third.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 3-1/2L back, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back to race 2 to 3 wide towards rear, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear, found rail near 800M, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, raced towards rear on the outside, last turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, raced in midfield on outer, very wide turning in, outpaced early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, wider turning in, weakened early in straight.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide better than midfield, hard ridden from 650M but only showed limited response, wider turning in, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
From wide draw dropped back to near the rear, had 6Ls to make up 400M, closed off powerfully to lead close home, won going away.
Went forward and crossed to the lead before home turn, kept on well passing 400M, still had 1.5L lead over nearest rival at 150M but winner proved too strong closing stages.
Slow to begin, held up at the rear, headway on inside passing 550M, ran on well to go 3rd near 100M
Crowded at the start, driven forward to chase leader, battled on well to hold 2nd until 150M, faded closing stages.
Settled down in midfield along the 2-path, kept on mildly on straightening, never going the pace to challenge leaders.
Jumped awkwardly, towards the rear early stages before improving to a midfield position from 800M, moved up to 3rd mid-straight but run ended soon. No extra late stages.
Held up behind midfield 3-wide, swung widest into straight, stayed on without threatening leaders.
Bumped on jumping, settled down ahead of midfield, held up behind a weakening rival 500M, wide into straight and ran past beaten horses only.
Bustled along to maintain a midfield position, came under serious pressure home turn, failed to run on in the home straight. (Jockey : hung in throughout the race.)
Raced keenly in a position ahead of midfield, didn't respond to riding in the home straight. (Jockey : not comfortable on the "Soft" track.)
Taken back from wide draw, settled towards the rear, fell back to last turning for home and failed to run on. (Jockey : not comfortable on the "Soft" track.)
From draw 1 moved up to chase leaders on inside, no extra 300M, weakened rapidly.
Bumped on jumping, went forward from wide draw and chased leaders without cover, weakened from 500M and was gone top of the straight. (Unacceptable performance.)

Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to snatch win on line.
Made contact shortly after start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, hit the front 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 3-1/2L back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back turning in, showed good response early in straight, blocked near 150M, cleared 50M, ran on evenly to the line.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, slightly improved after passing 700M, 2-1/2L back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Crowded start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Taken across from outside gate to last on fence, came off rail passing 1100m. Sent forward at 600m to loop field on turn, found front inside 200m. Easily, impressive.
Settled close to speed on rail, leader's back. Travelled strongly before final turn, held up for run early in straight. Finished well when clear but no match for winner.
Settled fourth last on rail. Held up when improving leaving back straight. Off fence early in straight but held up for run at 300m. Made late ground when in clear, closest at finish.
Blundered at start then ridden early along to find lead into first turn. Quickened tempo when challenged passing 800m. Headed at 200m mark, tired late, run out of third last few strides.
Caught wide first turn and allowed to settled second last 10 lengths off leader. Came off fence passing 600m and held up for run. Ran home well down middle of track, closest at finish.
Jumped well, torrid run three wide on speed throughout. Under pressure on home turn. Stayed on well in straight but never threatened.
Settled in good position, one off fence behind leading trio. Lost ground when pace quickened mid-race. In touch on turn, but one paced last 200m.
First to leave gates and settled second outside leader. Had to work mid-race when speed went on between horses. Asked for effort early in straight and faded last 150m.
Slow from gates settling third last, one off fence. Raced keenly with high head carriage early. Ridden along from 600m mark to stay in touch. Widest in straight and well beaten behind main group.
Sat midfield, raced wide until making a forward move near the 800M, made good progress inside 200M, kept on well to win.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled strongly, had every chance (See Incident Report).
Ridden along to lead, traveled okay, ran on evenly to the line.
Settled midfield, traveled comfortably, closed off okay.
Sat in front of midfield, held up rounding the Turn, slightly weakened inside 250M, closed off okay.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, minor progress made, one pace to the line.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, switched out in the Straight, ran on fairly.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield, weakened over the final 100M.
Sat behind midfield, traveled fairly, limited response when asked.
Settled behind midfield, traveled only fairly, no impression.
Slow to jump, sat rear, raced rear, made some ground and angled out rounding the Turn, never a threat.
Sat handy, weakened entering the Straight, gave ground quickly.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear, could not be ridden out, never a danger.
Sat towards rear, weakened and faded inside 200M, no contention.
Jumped well from wide gate, three wide early, then slotted in fourth, one off fence. Three wide on home turn, ran home strongly last 300m. Took lead passing 100m. Impressive.
Ridden along early stages to dispute lead, challenged passing 1200m and handed up lead. Took front at 200m but then headed by winner. Fought on gamely.
Jumped on terms from inside gate, settling fourth behind leader. Held up momentarily early in straight. Angled out at 350m and finished well, closing strongly last 100m.
Taken across from wide gate to settle in tail group one off fence. Held up in rear until straightening and made good ground last 150m, closest at finish.
Jumped well, ridden forward to contest lead, taking lead and going clear passing 1000m. Kicked clear on home turn, headed at 150m out and lost third place last 50m.
Fairly away then mustered speed to settle third one off fence. Travelled well to home turn, tendency to lay in early part of straight, stayed on well to finish just behind placings.
Jumped on terms settling worse than midfield, one off fence. Pushed along at 800m to make ground, and held up for run early part of straight. Made good ground last 150m.
Travelled well early stages, settling midfield one off fence in clear ground. Three wide from 550m and made ground without threating to run into the placings.
Jumped well but allowed to drift back to rearward position, three wide with cover. Came widest on home turn, made ground last 250m and closest at finish but well beaten.
Bounded in air on jumping and slow away, crossing to rails and settling in rear group. Chased hard in straight before peaking on run last 100m.
Jumped well but obliged to race midfield, wide without cover for majority of race. Brought wide on turn to challenge and stayed on until last 50m when well beaten.
Went forward from wide gate, then caught wide and taken back to second last. Brought to middle of track but no impression and well beaten. Blood in trachea post-race.
Slow to move at start, before settling midfield on rail. Came off rail passing 600m, not a lot of room passing 400m but soon under pressure and well beaten.
Caught wide early from gate and taken back to last. Stayed on rail in straight but one paced and faded last 200m to be long last.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled well on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead in the middle stages, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Commenced well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take a place, nearest on line.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, kept on well in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Average to begin, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, angled out 600M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back in the middle stages, kept on evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear, inconvenienced near 1100M, 9 lengths or so back in the middle stages, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, still well back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 10 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, difficult to settle in the early stages, raced better than midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, inconvenienced near 1100M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped nicely, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled smoothly throughout, switched out in the Straight and ran on strongly, won comfortably.
Took hold after the start from a wide barrier, settled at the rear 2 wide, stayed on strongly, no threat to the winner.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Settled midfield on the rail, angled out at 250M, made good ground until run peaked at final 75M.
Tracked leader, kept on nicely until weakened final 100M.
Sat last on the rail, made some late ground near the rail.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, ran on evenly. (Lost Right Front plate)
Raced at the rear, under pressure from the 550M, no clear run in the Straight, stayed on fairly.
Sat on pace, limited response in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly, settled behind midfield, made no impression.
Caught 3 wide midfield, made no ground.
Showed good early speed to lead, weakened final 300M. (See Incident Report)
Sat behind the leaders, weakened and faded in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Performance disappointing, must trial)
3 wide no cover in front of midfield, gave ground in the Straight.

Travelled wide in midfield early stages, lost cover early in back straight, made swift progress passing 1300 metres to dispute lead from the 1200 metres, gained outright advantage upon straightening, hung on well under pressure.
Settled just worse than midfield, carried slightly further back to 10th about 1200 metres out, commenced move under pressure 3-wide 600 metres out, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled just better than midfield, pulled forward swiftly to 1.5L 4th 1200 metres out and 3rd onto home bend while 3-wide, unable to quicken to threaten the length of straight.

Well there early, gradually shifting back to forward of midfield in 6th far side, some 4L back in 8th on rails rounding home bend, angled out for a run on straightening, ran on between runners to be nearest at finish.
Settled well behind and waited with, baulked behind runners early in straight until the 300 metres, finished off the race strongly for best work late.

Sluggish at start settling in rear of midfield, commenced move half-way out gaining to within 3L of pace rounding home bend, fought on steadily from 6th into straight but did not find much room on heels near the finish.
Soon taken well behind, gained slightly closer 3-wide early in back straight, commenced move wide in 11th entering home straight, ran on near the centre of the track without threatening.

Settled towards rear on rail from moderate start, dropped further back when pace quickened around home bend, saved ground turning in for home, baulked for a run in straight until the 200 metres, finished off the race nicely.

Pressed forward from a poor draw, prominent 3-wide without cover first bend, pulled forward to close-up 3rd inside the 1300 metres, 4th onto home bend, tight between runners early in straight, one-paced final 250 metres.
Broke well before settling better than midfield, carried slightly further back over 1250 metres out and even further back under pressure about 750 metres out, found no extra inside final 200 metres

Pressed forward from a poor draw, chased leader in 2nd rounding first bend, became 4th after pace slackened over 1250 metres out, came under pressure in similar position in 5th home bend, no extra inside final 200 metres.
Soon dropped well behind, given reminders passing the 600 metres, found nothing.
Broke well from the one draw to take up running on rail, led until joined by the eventual winner over 1000 metres out, unable to sustain effort and gradually weakened out of contention.
Jumped awkwardly, travelled keenly wide in last few before pulling forward in back straight to reach 3L 6th 4-wide without cover, lost position into straight and never recovered.
Dropped back to last in a 7 runner race, closed off strongly final 250M to claim the lead near line.
Soon led, kept on well under top weight on straightening, caught by winner late.
Slow to begin, settled towards the rear in a 7 runner race, held up 400M-350M along the inside, closed off well when brought to outside. Nearest finish.
Chased leader on inside, fought hard on straightening but was always held by higher rated rivals.
Towards the rear in a 7 runner race, lacked a strong finishing response passing 400M. Always held by leaders.
In touch with leaders, not quickened when driven along early straight, faded final 200M.
Chased leader on outside, no extra 250M weakened to last.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear, 9 lengths back in the middle stages, closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 550M, showed good response in straight, took the lead 50M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the outside, a length or so back turning in, took the lead 150M, peaked and headed 50M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, not enough room early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 600M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until 100M, finished off evenly.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1/2L back turning in, hit the front 300M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 100M.
Began well, taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, commenced move approaching 500M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final 150M.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 300M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Away with them, raced in midfield on outer, 2 lengths or so back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, one-paced thereafter. (Lost right hind plate after the race.)
Shifted out at start and made contact, taken back to race at rear, 5 lengths or so back, showed limited response early in straight, no clear run final 75M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L behind, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Settled well behind on rail after crowded at start from a poor draw, saved ground on rail turning in for home, ran on gamely under pressure to snatch victory final strides.
Settled in midfield mainly in 7th, switched out to challenge approaching home turn, inconvenienced twice between 400 and 300 metres out, finished off the race well inside final 200 metres.
Crowded shortly after start settling 3-wide with cover just worse than midfield in 9th, in similar position turning into straight, ran on well inside final 250 metres to be nearest at finish.
Soon took up running setting a quick early pace, kicked over 2L clear upon straightening but soon unable to sustain effort and overhauled 100 metres out.

Soon dropped to last few after beginning from the one draw, commenced move entering home straight but did not find much room until the 250 metres, produced good late impression until out of room late.
Gradually settled in last few, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, quickened well inside final 300 metres, lost 5th late.
Broke well in front briefly before settling 2L back in 4th racing wide without cover from the 900 metres, came under pressure upon straightening, heavily bumped 350 metres out, ran home one-paced.

Soon recovered from bumping at start to reach 5th within 3L of pace, barged out for a run shortly after straightening and inconvenienced shortly after, reached 2nd momentarily just inside 300 metres before weakened. (Blood in trachea)
Settled in last few, wide into straight, ran past only well-beaten horses.

Soon picked up to first few settling just off the pace in 3rd on rail, travelled keenly behind race leader rounding home bend, baulked for a run early in straight until the 350 metres, found nothing under pressure.
Gradually settled wide in last few after beginning from a poor draw, never seen with a chance.
Recovered steadily from moderate start to midfield in 8th on rail over 1000 metres out, did not find much room early in straight, ran home one-paced closing stages.
Soon dropped to wide in forward of midfield despite ridden along, weakened under pressure from over 500 metres out.
Prominent from the widest draw travelling outside race leader and keenly at times, soon weakened under pressure after straightening.

Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move 450M, 3 wide turning in, closed off well to take 2nd.
Away well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, found rail 600M, saved ground on turn, finished off well to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Bumped shortly after start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 700M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide after passing 800M, peaked on run approaching 500M, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Soon led and enjoyed uncontested lead, continued on strongly passing 300M and always maintaining a good margin to rivals, eased late when well in control.
From draw 1 moved up to track leader, tried hard on straightening but couldn't get closer to the winner, beaten margin reduced when winner eased late.
In midfield early stages, moved up to track leaders home turn, responded moderately under top weight, comfortably held by top two.
Jumped only fairly, recovered to race in midfield, fought on one paced to the line. Never a serious threat.
From wide draw taken across to race behind midfield, kept on fairly over final 300M, not reach leaders.
Tracked the pace, couldn't keep up with leaders top of straight, faded to finish 6th.
Jumped awkwardly, given a waiting ride near last, 6Ls to make up 400M, made some progress without troubling leaders.
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders, held ground early straight before weakening final 200M.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled towards the rear, gave limited response on straightening and posed no threat to leaders.
Jumped on terms, settled down midfield, failed to respond when asked 400M, never a threat.
Obliged to race very wide without cover on the first turn, restrained to find cover behind leaders middle stages, couldn't quicken on straightening, no extra final stages.
Bounded on jumping and lost ground, ended up at the rear, raced keenly early stages, 7Ls to make up 400M, couldn't pick up pace top of straight , held up behind beaten horses 150M-50M.
Sat towards rear, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, responded well when asked (Substantial blood in trachea).
Settled midfield, slightly held up making the Turn, closed off strongly.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled comfortably, finished off nicely.
Settled midfield, no clear running until 150M, ran on evenly (Whip was knocked off).
Sat rear, raced rear, made some progress over the concluding stages.
Settled worse than midfield, switched out rounding the Turn, one pace to the line.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled fairly, limited response when asked.
Jumped only fairly, slightly weakened near 450M, not much impression in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Chased the leader throughout, weakened near the 300M, left without a finishing effort.
Reared as the start was effected and lost ground, settled worse than midfield, never a threat (Must Stalls Test, See Incident Report).
Ridden along to lead, weakened notably entering the Straight, faded (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, traveled fairly, never responded when placed under pressure, never a factor.
Jumped quickly to cross to the rail and lead. Travelled strongly, came off rail in straight and fought hard to win well.
Jumped well and settled on rail behind leader. Raced keenly in running, stayed on rail and challenged leader early in straight but safely held in second.
Settled midfield, one off fence. Brought to centre of track to challenge and finished strongly last 200m to just miss second place.
Jumped on terms, mustered speed to settle second, one off fence. Pushed along passing 400m, chased hard in straight and stayed on well for fourth.
Shifted across behind runners from wide gate settling third last. Travelled well to home turn, came widest in straight making good ground late.
Ridden out of gates from wide draw, settling eighth one off fence, under pressure from half way mark to improve and stayed on well making ground last 150m.
Jumped well from inside gate, but headed for lead and settled three back the fence. Ridden along from 500m mark, once paced last 200m.
Jumped well, settling fourth, one off fence. Brought to middle of track to challenge in straight, faded last 100m.
Only jumped fairly, taken down to rail settled midfield. Brushed running rail at 600m becoming unbalanced. Under pressure early in straight, well beaten.
Taken back to tail of field on rail from wide gate after being three wide early stages. Came of fence in straight but failed to make up ground in last 200m.
Wide early and taken back to last pair, one off fence. Last on home turn, failed to make any ground in straight.
Jumped on terms, allowed to go back, settling on rail fourth last. Unable to make ground early part of straight and well beaten in last.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, angled out 700M, 3 wide on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Crowded shorty after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, no cover after entering the back straight, sent forward 800M, 2nd on turn, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 75M.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, carried wider 750M, 3 wide on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to take a place.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, found a 2 wide spot after entering the back straight, 3 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 750M, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began only fairly and made contact, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.

Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, inconvenienced 400M, showed limited response early in straight, no clear run final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)(Lame left front leg next day.)
Taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Crowded shorty after start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Rider dropped whip near 350M.)
Not the quickest out, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on strongly, won comfortably.
Jumped well, settled just behind the leaders, kept on nicely, no threat to winner.
Broke nicely, showed good speed lead, kept on nicely, just slightly weakened final 50M.
Sat on pace 2 wide, closed off okay.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, made good progress in the Straight, no clear run final 100M.
Settled midfield on the rail, stayed on fairly. (See Incident Report)
Sat towards the rear, ran on evenly.
Slow to jump, sat worse than midfield on the rail, made some late ground.
Settled midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Sat last on the rail, limited response in the Straight.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, weakened in the Straight.
Sat outside leader, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Broke well from the two draw settling just off the pace on rail, commenced move rounding home bend gaining slender advantage shortly after straightening, won readily.

Pressed forward to vie for lead 3-wide, obtained rails run in front inside the 800 metres, led until joined by eventual winner on home bend and narrowly headed into straight, unable to draw level throughout.

Jumped awkwardly, blundered and jockey badly unbalanced before picking up quickly to 3L 4th on rail some 3L back, gained closer under pressure home bend before angling out for a run into straight, ran on inside final 100 metres.
Taken back from a poor draw for rails run in 6th over 5L back, came under pressure rounding home bend, switched out from heels for a run 200 metres out and ran on without threatening.
Jumped fairly from the widest draw before settling well behind, trailed the field to home bend, saved ground hugging the rail turning in for home, one-paced under pressure.
Jumped moderately settling in 5th in midfield dropping further back in 6th approaching home bend, found nothing in straight.
Settled in last few after moderate start, switched wide into home straight, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Niggled along in first few early stages, taken back to 3rd turning into back straight, further away in 2L 4th approaching home bend, faded under pressure in straight.
Blundered shortly after start, gradually settled towards the rear 3-wide without cover, never seen with a chance. (Found to be a roarer)
Settled towards the rear, travelled well to home turn, swung wide for home before quickening strongly to lead 50M out, won going away.
Restrained from draw 11, raced wide no cover at the rear before making an early move 850M, outside leaders home turn, continued on well to the line only caught by stable companion final 50M.
Jumped on terms, settled down in mid-division before moving closer to leaders 600M, swung wide for home, ran on steadily to take 3rd.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, pushed along 500M, closed off nicely to claim 4th near line.
Tracked leaders, raced keenly early and middle stages, loomed a threat early straight, had every chance but was outsprinted final stages.
From wide draw moved up to press leader on outside, took over 500M, led the charge until headed 150M, faded late stages.
Jumped only fairly, moved up to 4th racing along the 2-path, under pressure to maintain his position home turn before keeping on same pace to the line.
Crowded on jumping, dropped back to a position near the rear on settling, 5Ls to make up 400M but only responded fairly on straightening.

From draw 1 maintained a midfield position along the inside, pushed along 500M but didn't respond to riding. (Jockey : came under pressure home turn and finished off in a disappointing manner. / Lame next day.)
From wide draw taken across behind rivals, raced at the rear of the field 6-7Ls off the pace, failed to run on final 300M.
Soon led, joined by rival 1200M, lost lead 550M, came under serious pressure, weakened to last.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 500M, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 800M, led by a length on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 400M, 6 lengths back turning in, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 800M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began well, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Moderately away, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, dropped towards rear on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Average to begin, raced behind midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, 3-1/2L back at 400M, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 600M, hard ridden after passing 300M, ran on well but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Began well, raced slightly better than midfield on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 400M, closed off well to make frame, not quite able to challenge.
Slightly slow out, raced slightly behind midfield on the middle track, 3 lengths back at 400M, closed off well without threatening.
Away well, raced in 3rd, 2 lengths or so back, same margin back at 400M, hard ridden 300M, kept on well to the line without threatening.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, 4 lengths or so back, no clear run final 400M, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the stands' side, 6 lengths or so back, made good progress final 400M to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield, 4-1/2L back, made some progress after passing 400M, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced slightly better than midfield on the middle track, hard ridden 350M, kept on well until approaching 100M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced better than midfield, hard ridden 400M but only showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on the stands' rail, outpaced 400M, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Jumped well from gate 14, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 600M, 1/2L back at 400M, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.) (Lame right hind leg next day morning.)
Began only fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Settled midfield three wide with cover. Worked into race coming to home turn and sustained run from 400m mark to win, safely held second who ate into margin late.
Jumped only fairly, settling fourth last and raced keenly. Switched across heels at 400m to make run and finished strongly last 200m.
Jumped on terms but beaten for early speed by leading group, settling fourth the rail. Not a lot of room in straight and hit line strongly when clear last 100m.
Restrained at start from outside gate diving down to rail and making ground along the rail to settle midfield. Held up for run 400m to 250m and made good ground when clear.
Jumped well and settled second crossing to rail passing 800m. Came off rail at 300m and momentarily hit front at 200m before headed by winner, losing third last 25m.
From a wide barrier was shifted across behind runners in the early stages. Lay in in the home straight but made good ground to be closest at the finish.
Raced wide and without cover from the 900m and pushed on towards lead group. Continued to make ground passing 150m mark. Peaked on effort late after tough run.
Jumped on terms and then drove through to lead clearly. Good lead on home turn but headed at 150m mark and tired last 50m losing many places.
Allowed to settle third last on rail. Held up for clear running between the 400m and the 300m. In clear ground passing 250m and made good ground to be closest at finish.
Jumped well but eased out of speed battle after first 200m to settle fifth, between runners. Held up for clear run early part of straight but did not finish the race off when clear.
Jumped well but unable to find a position and obliged to race three wide. Pushed on passing 1000m but still wide on speed. Stayed on in straight but gave ground last 100m.

Jumped only fairly. Raced keenly middle stages, shuffled back to worse than midfield. Off heels in clear ground passing 300m mark but one paced and gave ground last 150m. Irregular heart rhythm post race.
Raced wide without cover for the majority of race. Under pressure early in straight and failed to make any ground after torrid run.
From the outside barrier was shifted across behind runners in the early stages settling at tail of field, three wide. Came widest in straight but unable to make ground and well beaten.
Sat midfield on the rail, traveled strongly, made good ground inside 200M, kept on well to win.
Sat on-pace, traveled comfortably, closed off nicely.
Sat in front of midfield, switched out entering the Straight, made some progress inside 150M.
Sat in front of midfield, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, ran on evenly to the line.
Chased the leader, traveled okay, slightly weakened passing 300M, closed off okay.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, limited response when asked, ran on fairly.
Ridden along to lead, traveled okay, passed in the Straight.
Sat towards rear, traveled fairly, one pace to the line.
Sat towards rear, ran on fairly (Lame left front on the day after racing, See Incident Report).
Bumped at the Start, settled worse than midfield, could not be ridden out in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, improved rounding the Turn, switched out, did not make up ground (Roarer previously reported, See Incident Report).
Sat rear, raced rear, no impression made (Epiglottic entrapment).
Sat midfield, lay out rounding the Turn, raced wide thereafter, never a threat.
Settled worse than midfield, raced wide and without cover, weakened inside 300M, never a danger.
Jumped well from his gate and able to hold prominent position on rail behind leader. Held up for run passing 400m but sprinted quickly when in clear ground. Easy win.
Quickly away and in good position one off rail close to lead. Travelled well passing 400m and then good kick when asked for effort but no match for winner.
Allowed to work in to race early and passing 400m challenging for lead and travelling well. Stayed on well last 200m and clearly held third place.
Showed brilliant gate speed to cross from far side gate to rail and lead after 200m. Challenged passing 400m and gave good kick, headed 150m out, stayed on final stages.
Jumped on terms but drifted back to last after going 300m. Still last at 400m mark and then switched to centre of track and closed strongly last 100m.
Jumped only fairly. Recovered and within length of lead at 400m. Tended to lay in under pressure last 300m and unable to make ground last 150m .
Jumped on terms and in behind runners first 300m. Held up for clear run passing 400m and then stayed on fairly last 200m when in clear ground.
Unbalanced after jumping when bumped twice. Raced in second on outside of leader through half way. Challenged for lead at 300m, faded last 150m.
Fairly away. Prominent amongst pack chasing leader through half way. Under pressure passing 300m and gave ground last 100m.
Bumped just after start becoming unbalanced. Prominent in chasing pack at half way. Under pressure at 300m mark and tended to get head on side last 200m and faded.
Awkward start becoming unbalanced, but handy to lead on far side half way mark. One paced last 200m and failed to make any ground.
Travelled keenly through first half of race. Presented to challenge at 400m mark but soon under pressure and faded last 200m to be well beaten last.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight and scored.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, always held.
Bumped start, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run until approaching 100M, kept on well to take a place without threatening.
Began awkwardly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well to make frame, nearest finish.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, finished off well without threatening.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Out with rest, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, angled out approaching 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 600M, 8 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, peaked on turn, one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with the field, taken back to last on the rail, saved ground, stayed on nicely along the rail, just got there on the line.
Broke nicely and led, travelled comfortably, kept on strongly, just missed.
Settled midfield 2 wide, showed some dash from the 400M to 200M, one pace afterwards.
Settled at the rear 2 wide, switched out to 3 wide to improve at 750M, stayed on fairly.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, one pace to the line.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, ran on evenly. (See Incident Report)
Sat behind the leader, limited response in the Straight.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Performance disappointing, must trial)
Jumped awkwardly, pressed forward from a poor draw travelling 3-wide with leaders around home bend, gained upper hand under pressure over 70 metres out.
Taken well back from the widest draw, trailed the main body of the field into straight, ran on well along the rail to just fail to get up on line.
Bumped heavily at start, travelling keenly in 2L 5th when steadied 900 metres out, in similar position turning into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well and ridden to lead holding some 1L advantage most of the way to home straight, unable to sustain effort and headed inside final 100 metres.
Recovered quickly from moderate start settling one back in 4th on rail onto home bend, baulked briefly after straightening, improving well when running out of room inside final 70 metres.

Towards rear early stages, keen behind runners in midfield leaving back straight, re-gained midfield position rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure in straight despite not finding much room throughout.
Ridden positively from a poor draw settling just off the pace 2-wide in 3rd, held some chance early in straight but could make no impression under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly, soon taken well back, gained slightly closer rounding home bend, ran on under pressure in straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled towards rear, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend going wider into straight, could only keep on steadily at the same pace without threatening.
Began moderately, improved steadily 3-wide in back straight to reach 6th over 3L back around the bend, lost position entering home straight and tight between runners most of the way.

Settled in forward of midfield on rails, saved ground rounding home bend, did not find much room early in straight, made no further impression inside final 200 metres. (Jockey said saddle shifted at start.)
Reared at start losing considerable ground, detached from the main body of the field most of the way, produced good late impression closing stages.
Soon dropped to last few travelling 3-wide most of the way, ran past only well-beaten horses.

Held up in rear on rail, made swift headway on rail passing 1100 metres, travelling keenly when steadied, lost position 1000 and 800 metres out remaining towards rear to straight, dropped out after baulked for a run 300 metres out.
Crowded at the start, restrained in mid-division, raced keenly 1000M, wide into straight then quickened up strongly to lead near 200M, fought hard late to hold off runner-up by nose.
Crowded for room at start, held up in midfield, shifted to outside for clear running 250M and charged at leader late, just denied by a nose. Clear from remainders.
Restrained to race in a position ahead of midfield, close enough turning in, responded well 300M and challenged for the lead mid-straight, not pace of first 2 late.
Unable to slot in, raced wide no cover behind mid-division, swung very wide into straight, battled on to take 4th without troubling the runaway front pair.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards the rear on inside, had difficulty obtaining clear running until 300M, ran on well to take 5th although no match for first two.
Slow out, held up towards the rear, was commencing to finish off the race when checked 200M and lost momentum, ran on again late. Could do better.
Jumped on terms, settled down in midfield but never far off leaders, kept battling to the line but couldn't quicken enough to challenge first two. Finished 7th but only a neck behind the 3rd.
From wide draw given a quiet ride and settled further back than its most recent starts, had task in hand turning for home, stayed on mildly and was never a winning hope.
Chased leaders 2-wide, moved up to challenge early straight and had every chance, outsprinted by rivals final 150M.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced ungenerously near the rear and refused to settle, lacked finishing response final 400M. Never dangerous.
From wide draw moved forward to be vying the pace on outside, emerged as clear leader 500M, continued well early straight, but run ended 250M, no extra late stages.
Bumped at the start, up with early pace before taking a trailing spot behind leaders, couldn't go on passing 300M, faded away.
Outpaced early stages, raced in detached last, failed to finish off the race. Never in the picture. (Jockey : failed to travel at any stage.)
Went forward, emerged as co-leader passing 1000M, couldn't keep up on straightening, weakened to last.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, made contact 350M, finished off very strongly, led close home.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, beaten by a narrow margin.
Jumped well, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed good response in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Out with rest, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame, always held.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, hampered approaching 350M, no clear run until approaching 150M, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5-1/2L back turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 125M. (Roarer.)
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.

Jumped well from the widest draw, raced better than midfield on outer early, moved closer after passing 1200M, 2nd in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 12, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, hampered 350M, weakened thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Average to begin, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away well, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, nearest finish.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, wider turning in, one-paced in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced 3 wide with no cover, 1-1/2L back, weakened 500M, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Caught wide early stages and was allowed to stride forward tracking leader, challenged strongly early straight and gained lead near 200M, gave all to hold off the persistent runner up final stages.
Jumped well, chased the pace and always handy enough, responded well and vied for lead mid-straight, fought hard to the line and was just held.
Obtained a 2-wide spot behind midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, came with a good run and was closest at the line. Just missed 2nd spot. (Jockey drop whip 250M.)
Jumped only fairly, held up towards the rear, had difficulty obtaining clear running 250M before closing off the race nicely, nearest finish.
Jumped on terms, settled ahead of midfield, fought hard passing 400M, had difficulty obtaining clear running 100M, held by leaders late.
Strolled to the lead from draw 13, had uncontested lead until top of straight, couldn't fend off rivals 200M, faded late to finish 6th.
Chased leaders, in 4th spot over the bend but lacked the dash to launch a serious challenge on straightening, got home fairly final 200M.
Restrained to a rearward position 6-7ls behind leader, picked his way through the field passing 400M, shifted ground 150M to continue forward, not beaten far.
From draw 1 obtained a midfield spot along the inside, kept on one paced final 400M, always held by leaders.
From wide draw taken back to the rear, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, wide into straight, stayed on without troubling leaders.
Jumped only fairly and failed to show sufficient pace to hold a more forward position, towards the rear throughout, ran on fairly final 350M and was well held by leaders. No clear running late.
Settled down in mid-division, unable to obtain clear running early straight before closing off final 200M in a one-paced manner.
Slow to begin, towards the rear early, moved up to midfield middle stages but raced wide no cover, lacked finishing response top of straight, steadied 250M and outsprinted by rivals.
Dropped back from wide draw, settled 3-wide towards the rear, soon behind on straightening, not able to finish the race off.
