Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead approaching 100M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.

Began awkwardly and made contact, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 100M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M. (A small cut to the left hind fetlock.)
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.

Crowded shortly after start, trapped very wide early, slightly better than midfield, moved closer after passing 1200M, 2nd in the middle stages, 2 wide, peaked on run 350M, weakened final furlong. (Lost left front plate.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, angled out 350M, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (Lost right front plate.)
Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, angled out 400M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped wide, 1-1/2L back, peaked on run 500M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Gradually settled in 6th or one from last from a poor draw, saved good ground on rail turning in for home, ran on from over 2L back to gain upper hand inside final 50 metres.
Began moderately from the one draw settling one back on rail, angled out to challenge entering straight holding every chance only to be denied by a narrow margin.
Jumped awkwardly settling one-out-one-back in 3rd, hung out wider into straight, ran on dourly to be nearest at finish.
Soon ridden to lead after moderate start setting a standard pace, obtained rails run about 700 metres out, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres and swamped close to home.
Settled in 5th within 3L of pace after fair start, did not find much room early in straight until the 200 metres, ran home one-paced. (Reported with tendon injury next day)
Broke well before taking 2L back 3-wide in 4th, drifted back to 6th while hanging rounding home bend and further backward approaching home straight, never recovered.
Soon dropped well behind after beginning from the widest draw of the small field, tailed-off rounding home bend but saved ground on rail into straight, never a danger.
Jumped only fairly, sat midfield, traveled nicely, made good progress over the final 150M.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled comfortably, kept on well to hold 2nd.
Chased the leader, slightly weakened inside 75M, closed off well.
Sat worse than midfield, switched out at the top of the Straight and bumped, ran on evenly.
Sat behind midfield, traveled okay, made some ground inside 100M.
Slow to jump, settled midfield, ran on fairly (See Incident Report).
Ridden hard to lead, weakened notably entering the Straight, left without a finishing effort (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, steadied near the 600M, minor progress made in the Straight.
Sat towards rear, traveled only fairly, no impression made.
Sat handy, weakened inside 200M, could not be ridden out.
Sat rear, raced rear, no contention.
Settled midfield, bumped at the top of the Straight, unbalanced and lost momentum.
Jumped well but caught wide and taken back to fifth last, still three wide. Ridden forward passing 700m mark. Sustained long run, taking lead at 150m mark. Big effort to win.
Settled midfield, one off fence. Travelled well to home turn and ran on well when clear in straight making ground on winner without threatening to win.
Hesitated at start and then ridden forward to settle fourth, one off fence. Layed in slightly early in straight but continued to chase hard.
Slow to move and settled third last on rail. Ridden along from 500m and came off fence in straight and made good ground, closest at finish.
Jumped on terms from inside draw and midfield on rail. Steadied near 900m mark and raced keenly. Came off fence on turn and ran home well last 250m.
Jumped only fairly. Ridden hard to settle fourth last, one off fence. Came widest in straight, Continued to run on last 200m, closest at finish.
Ridden hard early to settle fifth on rail. Held up on turn, steadied near 300m. Near 200m had difficulty obtaining clear running but one paced when clear.
Jumped on terms but no early speed settling at tail. Approaching the 1000m became unbalanced when bumped and then long last. Still last at 100m, made good ground late.
From wide gate shifted across behind runners at the start, settling second last. Made some ground late from long way back when coming off rail.
Jumped quickly and led into first turn. Strode clear at 600m, headed at 150m and faded last 100m.
Ridden forward and three wide early, working hard, before settling outside leader. Under pressure on turn, rolled down to rails and faded, well beaten.
Ridden hard early to sit outside leader between horses to first turn, then eased to sit third. Under pressure at 500m mark and beaten early in straight.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off strongly to score by a nose.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 650M, no cover throughout, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move 450M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths in the middle stages, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 3/4L back turning in, raced tight early in straight, peaked approaching 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced at rear, 6-1/2L back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, raced tight and no clear run early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, commenced move approaching 400M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off evenly.
Out with rest, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Made contact at start, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Mucus.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped smoothly, settled in front of midfield on the rail, angled out into the clear at 250M, ran on strongly to score.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, stayed on well for 2nd.
Sat behind the leader, under pressure near the 500M, kept on, lost second final stride.
Sat midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely, just one pace final 75M.
Raced in midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Sat towards the rear 2 wide, stayed on fairly.
Sat on pace on the rail, switched out to 2 wide at 750M to improve, weakened final furlong. (See Incident Report)
Showed good early speed to lead, travelled keenly throughout, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat last, made no impression.
Settled at the rear on the rail, hard ridden from the 600M, limited response.
Sat behind midfield on the rail, made no ground. (See Incident Report)
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, hard ridden rounding the Home Turn, weakened and faded in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Pressed forward from a poor draw settling in 2nd just outside race leader, hit the front on straightening and hung on well under pressure to the line.
Settled wide in midfield, in similar position into straight, ran on under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
Settled wide in rear of midfield after beginning from a poor draw, commenced move approaching home turn, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening, baulked late.
Jumped well just off the pace settling some 3L back in 5th on rail, saved ground in similar position into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.

Settled behind midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, produced good impression on rail after straightening to reach within 2L of pace of leaders early, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.
Slow out and crowded, soon recovered to last few, saved ground on rail turning in for home, did not find much room until the 200 metres, kept on steadily without quickening.
Soon dropped towards rear, commenced move very wide into straight, fought on steadily under pressure.
Soon dropped well behind, baulked for a run early in straight, kept on well closing stages. (Bled)
Broke well to lead briefly before taking 2L back to 3rd on rail, switched out for a run entering straight, found nothing under pressure.
Pressed forward from the widest draw to take up running into back straight, obtained rails run shortly afterwards and led to home straight when found no extra.
Ridden forward before drifting over 2L back to 4th while niggling along, did not find much room upon straightening and folded up quickly inside final 150 metres.
Slow out and soon tailed-off, never seen with a chance.
Moved up to chase leaders along the inside, travelled strongly into straight, quickened well when asked to lead inside 200M, well in command late stages.
Began fairly, always close up to leaders, fought on well final 300M to claim 2nd in a photo finish. Safely held by winner towards the line.
Crossed to the fence 1300M, tracked leader on settling, vied for lead 400M, stuck on well under top weight, lost out for 2nd place in a photo.
Dropped back from wide draw, towards the rear early before making a forward move passing 800M, kept on steadily to the line, held by first 3 late stages.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, 3Ls off leaders 400M, stayed on well closing stages on his Hong Kong debut.
Held up in midfield along the inside, kept on chasing leaders on straightening but was always held.
In mid-division early stages, dropped back towards the rear halfway, kept to inside turning into straight, ran on one paced.
From wide draw ridden forward to obtain the lead from 1300M, pressed by rivals 400M, lost lead nearing 200M, faded away.
Towards the rear early stages, made mid-race move near 800M, caught wide no cover chasing leaders, couldn't quicken enough on straightening. (Roarer.)
Dropped back to race at the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, failed to run on.
Held up behind midfield in early stages, fell back to near the rear passing halfway, not able to finish the race off.
Bumped at the start, raced wide no cover in midfield, couldn't hold his position 500M, soon left behind on straightening.
Away well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back in the early stages, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight, just beaten by a narrow margin.

Crowded start, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two late. (Lost left hind plate.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off well to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to make frame.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Crowded on jumping, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, not clear run final 50M.

Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, headed 650M, allowed rival to cross 550M, 2nd on turn, retook the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 50M. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 350M, unable to obtain clear run in straight. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Began smartly, raced prominently but trapped 4 wide early, 3 wide from 700M, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.

Shifted out at start, trapped wide, a length or so back, sent forward 750M, took the lead 650M, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced prominently, 3 wide, crowded near 1000M, 2 wide from 750M, peaked on run approaching 400M, weakened early in straight.

Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, hard ridden approaching 300M, showed good response, took the lead 50M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Bumped on the hindquarters at the start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until passing 150M, finished off well to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back turning in, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped with them, raced better than midfield but trapped wide early, raced in 2nd approaching 900M, 2 wide on turn, a length back turning in, kept on evenly in straight, hampered final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some headway. (Lost right front plate.)
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 600M, same margin back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Out with rest, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, inconvenienced near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, trapped very wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, no clear run until final 75M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on outer, 6 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Raced wide throughout. Ridden along from half way mark to improve, posted four wide on last turn. Finished strongly last 200m and impressive win.
Settled midfield one off fence. Held up for run early part of straight. Flashed late to take second on line.
Jumped quickly then eased to sit fourth on rails. Held up in straight. Finished strongly on rails, just denied second last stride.
Raced wide from 600m. Went forward on home turn, Took lead at 150m, kept on, lost third on the line.
Jumped on terms before going forward to sit wide early, dropped in to third one off fence. Continued to chase hard in straight and not beaten far from placings.
Slowly away from inside draw. Settled fourth last on the fence. Came off rail before turn and made ground down centre of track. Closest at finish.
Slowly away, at tail before going forward to settle midfield on fence. Unable to get clear running most of straight. Made ground late, had more to offer.
Jumped well and crossed to rail and led. Fought hard in straight but headed at 100m and tired late.
Settled second last pair and pushed wide on home turn to improve. Kept making ground from long way back but well beaten.
Began well, caught wide before settling second outside leader. Challenged early in straight , under pressure and faded last 150m.
Hard ridden middle stages to hold position drifting back to second last. Under pressure from top of straight and failed to make any ground.
No early pace and settled back. Under pressure throughout race. Back to last at half way mark and failed to respond to hard riding. Long last.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled nicely, slightly held up at the top of the Straight, responded well when asked.
Settled towards rear, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, showed some dash inside 150M, battled to the line.
Shared the lead on the rail, made good progress under pressure, closed off strongly (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, traveled okay, held up until 250M, made good ground after obtaining clear running.
Slow to jump, settled midfield, ran on evenly.
Sat handy, traveled okay, hampered near the 300M, ran on okay.
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, switched out rounding the Turn, finished off fairly.
Settled midfield, traveled fairly, minor progress made in the Straight.
Sat worse than midfield, no clear running in the Straight, could not be ridden out (Lost right hind plate).
Shared the lead, weakened after entering the Straight, no impression made.
Sat in front of midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, limited response under pressure (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, traveled only fairly, weakened notably entering the Straight, no contention.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide throughout, hampered near the 300M (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, weakened and faded after 200M (Unacceptable performance, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Jumped on terms from inside gate but quickly railed through to lead. Held up to 300m before extending lead to four lengths and kept going to win easily.
Began well before eased to sit midfield, three wide. Brought to centre of track and ran home strongly to take second.
Raced wide without cover most of race, midfield. Improved to be fifth on home turn, second at 50m but back to third last 25m.
Jumped quickly, settling third then fourth one off fence after surrendering front. Second at 150m, kept on but one paced last 100m fading to fourth.
Allowed to settle at tail of field early crossing to rail. Taken wide at 600m to improve. Widest in straight, ran on fairly closest at finish.
Hesitated at start but mustered speed to settle fourth on rail behind leader. Ridden along from top straight and one paced.
Jumped well, settling fifth early, one off fence. Ran on in straight to 150m mark before one paced closing stages.
Over raced early stages and eased at 1000m and dropped back to be long last passing 500m. Ran on last 200m.
Taken back from wide gate, but trapped wide early. Ran on in straight in middle of track but tired last 100m.
Ridden hard out of gates but no early speed and settled on rail third last. Came off rails on turn, one paced in straight.
Jumped on terms, settled fifth last between horses. Ridden along from 500m, rolled down to rails. Beaten at the 200m and dropped out.
Ridden forward to be wide early before sitting outside leader. Under pressure on home turn and dropped out from 300m. Bled both nostrils.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail approaching 700M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, angled out 450M, finished off strongly to score.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.

Began well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 650M, sat right behind the leader turning in, hit the front 250M, peaked and headed 50M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 to 8 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line. (Lost left hind plate.)
Began smartly from the widest draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, found rail approaching 700M, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide from 700M, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening. (Lost right hind plate.)
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, found rail near 650M, led by a length turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, made no impression in straight.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, hampered near 700M, still well back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear throughout, never in contention.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, 6 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.

Placing: PU
Comment: Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, went wrong and quickly pulled up near 800M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Hard ridden early to assume lead, travelled smoothly throughout, kept on well, just held on.
Settled midfield 2 wide, held up early in the Straight, switched in, closed off well, closest finish.
Settled behind the leaders, angled out to challenge at 300M, made some ground early but soon just one pace.
Jumped slow, settled at the rear, had some trouble finding clear run in the early part of the Straight, ran on nicely late.
Settled in front of midfield 3 wide no cover, ran on evenly.
Sat midfield 3 wide, only one pace when asked.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, limited response when asked.
Ridden along in the early stages to be prominent, sat behind the leaders 2 wide, shifted out 3 wide from the 800M, showed some response early in the Straight, but soon weakened. (See Incident Report)
Sat at the rear 2 wide, made minor progress.
Settled 3 wide behind midfield, made no impression.
Settled midfield on the rail, no clear run in the Straight, never tested.
Sat outside leader, weakened in the Straight.
Raced at the rear, never a threat.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, travelled keenly, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Niggled along in 4th just some 2 to 3L off the pace, saved ground on rail turning in for home, quickened well late inside final 200 metres to snatch victory final strides.
Soon took up running from a poor draw, led 2-wide before obtaining rails run onto home bend, held 1L advantage most of the way in straight before collared close to home.
Travelled keenly towards rear, commenced move very wide without cover on top of home bend, quickened well from over 5L back in 10th to narrowly miss 2nd.
Settled in midfield on rail early, travelled keenly around home bend, switched out for a run entering straight, obtained clear run over 250 metres out, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Soon picked up to 2nd travelling keenly leaving the 1200 metres, came to dispute lead briefly turning into straight, faded under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Settled in last few on rail, switched wide into straight, ran on steadily under pressure near the centre of the track.
Began well from a poor draw settling over 2L back in 3rd 2-wide, commenced move 3-wide entering home straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 150 metres.
In midfield throughout, kept on same pace under pressure in straight.
Soon recovered from moderate start to 8th on rail just worse than midfield, became 9th coming onto home bend, saved ground turning in for home, found nothing under pressure.
Gradually drifted backward from a poor draw to reach last near rail passing the 1100 metres, trailed to field into straight, made no further impression.
Taken backward to last few from a poor draw, made headway 3-wide rounding home bend, forced wider approaching home turn, weakened under pressure inside final 250 metres.
Soon dropped to last few and never seen with a chance. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled wide just better than midfield in 5th after beginning from a poor draw, 4-wide into home straight and soon dropped out of contention.
Switched off after the jump to be racing towards the rear, swung to outside of straight for his challenge, quickened up impressively to claim the lead nearing 50M. Too strong late.
Ridden forward and crossed to the lead 1000M, kept on well on straightening and led the charge until headed by fast finishing winner nearing 50M. Held 2nd comfortably.
Jumped on terms, restrained in a midfield position along the inside, got out 350M to challenge, ran on mildly under top weight to take 3rd.
Settled behind mid-division along the fence, stayed on moderately final 400M to finish modest 4th.
Not hurried early stages, settled towards the rear, came wide home turn before closing off mildly. (Jockey: rode a little more conservatively in early stages with the expected fast early pace.)
Chased the pace, tried had passing 400M but couldn't take ground off leader, lost 2nd inside 200M, no extra late stages.
From draw 1 began with them, tracked leaders on inside, fought on same pace final 400M and was no threat from mid-straight.
Dropped back from wide draw, 6Ls to make up 400M, ran home fairly and failed to trouble leaders.
Caught racing wide no cover chasing leaders, kept battling to mid-straight then no extra final stages.
Went back and settled near last, had task in hand top of straight, couldn't quicken enough, failed to get involved.
Settled down in midfield along the 2-path, soon outpaced by leaders top of straight. Never dangerous.
Began fairly, failed to show sufficient pace to hold a more forward position and ended up behind midfield, failed to run on final 400M, never a factor. (Roarer.)
Caught 3-wide in mid-division, struggled to keep up 500M and was gone 300M.
Up with early pace before sitting just behind leaders, under pressure 500M, came up empty 300M and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, showed good response in straight, hit the front 250M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced towards rear on the inside early, angled out after passing 700M and moved a little bit closer, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Away well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, no clear run and hampered near 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.

Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, hard ridden after passing 400M but only showed limited response, peaked 300M, headed 250M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved a little bit closer on turn, angled out 550M, made some progress in straight.
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail after passing 650M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back to race 3 wide at rear, 2 wide from 650M, 4-1/2L back turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 9, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, angled out 450M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 700M, same margin back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider after passing 700M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight. (Roarer.)
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight and scored.
Crowded start, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, always held.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, closed off well to take a place.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until 75M, ran on well without threatening.
Shifted in at start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 550M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 500M, made no impression in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Crowded start, raced in midfield on the outside, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Crowded start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Average to begin, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place , no threat to the first two.

Began well from a wide draw, showed good speed to take the lead, led by 3-1/2Ls on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, headed 50M, weakened thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced at rear on the outside, 9 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight, nearest finish.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, 8 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.) (Mucus.)
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped start, trapped wide in midfield, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect. (Roarer.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide in midfield, dropped towards rear after passing 600M, 8 lengths back turning in, showed nothing in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Led early stages before sitting back behind leaders passing 1400M, little change to the turn, quickened past weakening leader inside 200M, kept on well to register first win in Hong Kong.
Settled down ahead of midfield, not far off from leaders home turn, wide into straight, fought well to the line but was always held by winner final stages.
Reserved in midfield along the inside, switched away from fence nearing 400M, chased hard to go 3rd near 100M, held by first two towards the line.
Chased leaders, taken wide after 1000M and was left racing wide without cover, challenged for the lead early straight but run ended 150M and faded late stages.
Soon crossed to the fence and assumed a position in midfield, in touch with leaders turning home but couldn't quicken to challenge.
Held up behind mid-division 2-wide, 5-6Ls off leader on settling, wide into straight, kept on only fairly final 300M.
Settled towards the rear, driven along passing 500M, ran home fairly to the line. Never a winning hope. (Jockey : raced "flat" / small wound to RH pastern.)
From draw 12 dropped back to race at the rear 9Ls off the pace, crowded 450M when improving into a doubtful run, couldn't quicken enough in the home straight.
Jumped fairly, taken back from wide draw and was given a patient ride at the rear, pushed along 500M, gave limited response on straightening.
Strolled to the lead, pressed by rival middle stages, headed nearing 200M, no extra and weakened rapidly final stages.
Settled towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, had nothing to offer turning home. Never involved.
Moved up to press leader on outside, under pressure 500M out, gave ground rapidly top of straight. (No Vet findings.)
Sat handy, traveled nicely, kept on well to win (Substantial blood in trachea).
Settled midfield, traveled comfortably, bumped near the 350M, switched out entering the Straight, closed off nicely.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled okay, responded well when placed under pressure inside 250M.
Bumped on jumping, sat handy, made some ground inside 200M, ran on evenly.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened rounding the Turn, one-paced thereafter.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled smoothly, closed off okay.
Sat behind midfield, minor progress made in the Straight, ran on fairly.
Jumped only fairly, sat midfield, lay in in the Straight, could not be ridden out.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, gave ground rounding the Turn (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, raced rear until 500M, limited response when asked.
Slow to jump, sat towards rear, raced wide and without cover when commenced a forward move near 600M, nothing in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, weakened notably passing 600M, faded (Heart irregularity, Must BT).
Broke quickly from inside gate and led into first turn. Extended margin leaving back straight and four lengths clear in straight. Kept going to win easily.
Jumped on terms then switched down to rail to settle midfield. Made progress on the rail and moved to clear second at 200m mark, winner too good.
Driven forward to be in leading group then eased to settle fourth, one off fence. Ran on well down middle of track to be clear third, well behind first two.
Drifted back from wide gate to be last early before making ground on rail. Ridden along from 600m to improve, stayed on inside and kept on for distant fourth.
Jumped well to settle second outside leader. Travelled keenly down back, urged along from 500m to stay in touch. One paced last 200m.
Good early pace to settled third behind leader. Hard ridden coming to home turn. Failed to make ground last 200m and beaten long way from placings.
Jumped on terms but taken back to settle second last, three wide with cover. Crossed to fence at 600m mark and stayed on rails and closest at finish but beaten many lengths.
Bumped at start and settled in last group. Improved position passing 600m and ran on fairly last 200m down centre of track when in clear ground. Well beaten.
On back foot at start and then mustered speed to settle between runners slightly worse than midfield. Tendency to race greenly in straight, no impression.
Jumped well but eased out of speed battle after 100m to sit midfield, three wide without cover. Failed to run on and eased last 100m.
Ridden out of gates to be handy but caught four wide and taken back to midfield where still raced wide. Came to centre of track in straight but always near the tail.
Jumped well from widest gate but caught wide into first turn and taken back to last. Ridden along coming to 600m, failed to make any ground in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 900M, led by 1/2L on turn, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Made contact shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the inside, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out 350M, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place.
Bumped start, tracked leaders, 3 wide with no cover, pressed leaders from 450M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out 350M, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 900M, 2nd in the middle stages, kept on well until approaching 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide approaching 700M, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on outer, dropped towards rear on turn, 5-1/2L back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside early, a bit closer in the middle stages, showed some response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, dropped towards rear from 500M, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well, sat box-seated, travelled comfortably throughout, ran on nicely to win.
Tracked leader, kept on nicely until slightly weakened final 100M.
Settled midfield 2 wide, under pressure from 650M, took some time to respond, closed off okay final furlong.
Settled behind the leaders 2 wide, angled out in the Straight, showed some dash early but one pace final furlong.
Sat behind midfield on the rail, ran on evenly.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Sat last on the rail, limited response in the Straight.
Sat towards the rear 2 wide, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Settled at the rear on the rail, never a threat.
Showed good early speed to lead, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)

With leaders early gradually settling 2L back on rail in 5th, gained 4th over 700 metres out and further closer onto home bend, obtained clear run about 250 metes out and quickened well to hit the front over 100 metres out.
Prominent early despite moderate start, soon taken back to midfield in 7th gaining 6th onto home bend, ran on under pressure in straight to hold every chance only to be denied narrowly.
Soon taken back to last few, remained well behind into straight, made significant progress inside final 150 to grab 3rd late.
Ridden along in prominent position 4-wide without cover, joined race leader in 2-wide position 600 metres out, drew level briefly on straightening, swamped inside the 100 metres. (Enquiry held)
Niggled along 3-wide in first few, gained one-out-one-back position over 700 metres out, shifted 3-wide for a run entering home straight, held every chance until finding no extra 150 metres out.
Badly bumped at start losing ground, quickly recovered to 6th in forward of midfield into back straight, widest turning in for home, kept on one pace without threatening.

Jockey badly unbalanced and lost use of iron at start, held up in 8th just worse than midfield, saved ground on inside turning in for home, made short-lived effort early in straight, found no extra 100 metres out.
Settled towards rear after forced to check at the start, came under pressure rounding home bend, hung in and straightened over 200 metres out, fought on well to finish.
Crowded shortly after start settling in last few on rail, saved ground turning in for home, improving when steadied for a run between the 150 and 100 metres, found no extra closing stage.
Settled well behind from a poor draw, trailed the field most of the way and only went past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Soon took up running from a poor draw, obtained rails run in front passing the 900 metres, held narrow advantage to home straight, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres
Travelled keenly just off the pace, gradually shifted over 2L back to 5th over 600 metres out, shifted wide into straight and soon weakened.
Settled in midfield, driven wide into straight, did best work late hitting the front close home.
Stayed in touch with leaders, in 4th spot making the home turn, ran on well to claim 2nd near line but couldn't quite match winner's finish.
Began well from draw 1, soon led setting a good pace, kept on well in the lead on straightening, caught by first two concluding stages.
Chased leaders in 3rd, moved up to 2nd mid-straight, kept on steadily to the line, not pace of first two closing stages.
Soon taken across to race along the fence, settled towards the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, ran on moderately to line and not beaten far at the finish.
Moved forward to be tracking leader, couldn't hold his spot mid-straight, faded towards the finish.
Bumped at the start, obtained a midfield spot on inside, raced keenly middle stages, got home only fairly. Never a threat to leaders.
Restrained after the start, raced keenly towards the rear middle stages, steadied away from rival 600M and raced wide into straight, plenty to make up but never near to challenge.
Slow to begin, raced at the rear, lacked a finishing response 400M. Never in the picture.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 800M, shared the lead on turn, kept on well to the line, won by a nose.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide from 700M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly, just beaten by a nose.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take a place.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, sent forward after passing 900M, took the lead 800M, shared lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Checked shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move approaching 400M, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, commenced move after passing 450M, wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.

Away with them, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 1300M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, angled out 350M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, carried wider 450M, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on outer, awkwardly placed 550M, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced in midfield on the outside, unable to maintain position from 700M, eased final 400M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)

Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed very good response, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually close home, finished 3rd.
Bumped shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the outside, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide after passing 700M, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped on jumping, raced towards rear on the inside, a bit closer in the middle stages, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Made contact shortly after start, tracked leaders, 2 wide, 3 wide from 700M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Quickly into stride, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on the inside, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Slow to move at start, settled second last on rail. Held up for run between 350m and 300m. Finished strongly when in clear running. Impressive.
Caught three wide early, before settling third, one off fence. Ran on well, took lead at 150m but quickly claimed by winner. Clear second.
Taken back to last from widest gate, three lengths away at 800m mark. Came off fence on turn and continued to make ground, closest at finish.
Jumped quickly from inside gate before settling fourth on fence. Not a lot of room early in straight and ran on well closing stages to be fourth.
Ridden early to vie for lead, eased at 700m to sit second behind leader. Came off fence in straight. Hit front at 300m, quickly headed. Lost two places last 50m.
Began quickly and able to hold early lead going clear passing 600m. Headed at 300m mark and tired last 100m.
Slow to leave the gates and ridden along to settle fifth, one off fence. Asked for effort at 300m mark but quickly under pressure and faded last 100m.
Sat midfield on the rail, traveled comfortably, switched out rounding the Turn, made good ground over the final 200M.
Crowded at the Start, sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, battled to the line.
Sat handy, traveled nicely, got every chance.
Settled towards rear, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, raced wide from 800M, made some progress in the Straight.
Sat handy on the rail, shifted out to obtain clear running near 300M, ran on evenly.
Chased the leader, slightly weakened passing 200M, kept on okay.
Sat midfield, dropped back rounding the Turn, minor progress made in the Straight (Lost right front plate).
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, raced rear, responded only fairly when asked.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled fairly, one pace to the finish (See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, limited response when placed under pressure, nothing in the Straight.
Ridden along to lead, responded only fairly when asked, weakened inside 150M (See Incident Report).
Bumped at the Start, sat in front of midfield, lay in making the Turn, no impression.
Bumped at the Start, settled behind midfield, could not be ridden out, no contention.
Sat towards rear, one pace throughout, never a factor.
Settled worse than midfield, one off fence from wide gate. Brought to centre of track and finished strongly to get up in last stride.
Slow to move from inside draw and ridden to settle three back on fence. Off rail at 550m and finished strongly to make run with winner. Just beaten on line.
Jumped well and able to lead at moderate pace. Fought on strongly in straight and only headed inside last 75m.
Jumped well, went forward to sit outside leader, then third, one off fence. Three wide at turn to challenge, lay in under pressure in straight but stayed on.
Settled in good spot, fifth, one off fence. Made run inside 400m and within length of lead at 200m before one paced last 150m.
Jumped on terms, settling midfield one off fence. Held up for run on straightening, stayed on well when in clear room, without threatening placegetters.
Crossed to rails to be just worse than midfield on fence at half way mark. Under pressure at 200m and made some ground under hard riding last 200m.
Taken back from wide gate to be in second last pair one off fence. Brought wide on turn to make run, Under pressure at 300m, stayed on but well beaten.
Jumped well, wide early before working hard to go forward and sit second. Under pressure passing 400m and gave ground last 200m.
Raced wide without cover middle stages. Made run inside 400m but failed to make ground and one paced last 200m.
Stood at start and left six lengths. Ridden hard to tack on passing 1400m mark and settled in last pair on rail. No impression in straight.
Taken across behind runners from wide gate to be in last pair, one off fence. Hard ridden on turn and last at 400m, passed a couple of tired horses.
Over raced early stages, when racing on fence behind leader. Ridden along from 600m, beaten passing 300m and no further effort.
Jumped on terms but taken back at start from wide gate to be in second last pair on fence. Came to middle of track but no impression and long last.
Average to begin, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.

Bumped start, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 wide from 700M, 1-1/2L back turning in, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.

Out with rest, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, found rail near 700M, a length or so back on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, kept on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from the widest draw, positioned 3 wide, 3 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 700M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 8 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail near 700M, a bit closer on turn, made some progress in the run home.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield on the outside, dropped towards rear on turn, 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide towards rear in the early stages, 2 wide on turn, found rail 450M, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, steadied off heels 100M, one-paced thereafter.
Shifted in at start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed 400M, weakened final 300M.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, closed off strongly, just got there on the line.
Settled behind the leaders on the rail, angled out at 300M to improve, made good progress, battled gamely, just missed.
Settled towards the rear 3 wide, stayed on well for 3rd.
Showed good early speed to lead, kept on until weakened final 100M.
Settled midfield on the rail, took some time to respond, made good ground final 100M.
Caught 3 wide near midfield, one pace to the finish.
Settled at the rear 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Sat outside leader, weakened final 250M.
Sat midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, showed some dash early in the Straight, one pace final 250M.
Sat worse than midfield 3 wide, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, blundered at 250M and weakened. (Blood in Trachea)
Sat last, never in contention.
Caught 3 wide no cover, weakened and faded in the Straight. (Unacceptable Performance, must trial)
Never far off settling just over 2L back in 4th, shifted out for a run entering straight hitting the front about 250 metres out, hung on well to the line.
Pressed forward from a wide draw travelling 3-wide without cover, gained 1L 2nd 2-wide 1000 metres out, held every chance early in straight until overhauled over 250 metres out.
Broke well from a poor draw gradually settling in forward of midfield in 6th 3-wide without cover, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly settling well behind from a poor draw, tight between runners early in straight, ran on under pressure inside final 250 metres to be nearest at finish.

Gradually picked up along rail to 5th about 3L off the pace, became 6th in a similar position rounding home bend, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, fought on steadily closing stages without threatening .
Soon recovered to midfield after moderate start, some 4L back in 7th rounding home bend, came under pressure entering straight, produced good late impression closing stages, baulked late.
Broke well settling one back in 3rd on rail, some 2L off the pace rounding home bend, baulked for a run early in straight, ran home one-paced inside final 200 metres.
Settled in last few on rail, switched out for a run upon straightening, produced good late impression inside final 100 metres.
Jumped fairly settling towards the rear, in similar position into straight, fought on steadily without quickening. (Diagnosed a roarer)
Settled 3-wide towards the rear, went wider into straight, ran on under pressure near the centre of the track land but without threatening.
Settled 3-wide in rear of midfield, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.

Began well and soon took up running, obtained rails run in front over 1000 metres out setting a steady pace with 1L to spare, came under pressure when joined early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 250 metres.
Taken well back from the widest draw, trailed the field most of the way, never a factor.
Settled just worse than midfield on rail, came under pressure upon straightening, found nothing.
Reserved behind midfield, 7th of 10 turning home, quickened up impressively to lead nearing 200M, pulled clear for a commanding win.
Chased leaders early stages, fell back to a midfield spot halfway, picked up well early straight to challenge for the lead but not pace of winner final 200M.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, did best work final 250M, just failed to get past 2nd at the finish. Not reach winner.
Slow out, waited with at the rear of the field, 6Ls to make up 400M, stayed on mildly towards the finish. No threat to first few.
Chased leaders, fought on early straight to hold his position, not pace of leaders final 200M.
Held up at the rear, 6Ls off leader 400M, ran past beaten horses only. (Jockey : would appreciate a firmer track.)
In touch chasing leaders, ran on one paced on straightening, held up 250-200M, no extra late. (Jockey : could offer no excuse for the disappointing performance.)
Pressed leader on outside, kept vying for the lead on straightening, outsprinted by rivals from 200M, weakened towards the line.
Soon led, joined by rival middle stages, vied for lead to 250M then weakened away.
Caught wide no cover on settling, chased leading group entering home turn, came up empty on straightening.
Jumped only fairly and bumped, raced in 2nd, 1-1/2L back, challenged the leader approaching 500M, took the lead early in straight, kept on very strongly to the line, easily scored.
Began only fairly, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off strongly to take 2nd on line, no threat to the winner.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in 3rd, 3 wide, there to turn, kept on well in straight, no chance with clear winner, lost second on line.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, no cover throughout, kept on evenly in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, closer on turn, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Began fairly and crowded, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, made no progress thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (Bled.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival from 500M, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (Roarer.)
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, angled out approaching 500M, hard ridden from 350M, showed very good response, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced slightly behind on the inside, 2 wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider turning in, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take a place, nearest finish.

Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, sent forward after passing 1200M, 2nd in the middle stages, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, very wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, bumped near 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back in the middle stages, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home without threatening.

Began well, raced slightly better than midfield, 2 wide, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, angled out 500M, very wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 100M.
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, moved closer along the rail on turn, blocked 300M, cleared 200M, made no impression thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rival after passing 450M, peaked and headed 300M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded at the start, obtained a position ahead of midfield, travelled strongly into final 400M, cruised to the lead mid-straight before kicking away to score a huge win under top weight.
Not hurried, settled down behind midfield, into clear 400M, closed off nicely to get 2nd near line but not able to trouble the runaway winner.
Restrained to race 3-wide in midfield, left with no cover home turn, quickened up well to challenge for lead early straight but not pace of winner final 200M, lost 2nd near line.
Jumped only fairly, switched off to race at the rear, plenty to make up top of straight, closed off well final 350M but left with too much to do.
From a wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled near last, swung wide for home, ran on steadily to the line but no serious threat to first few.
Settled down midfield, held up for clear running 450M-400M, kept on fairly towards the line. Never a winning hope.
Tracked leaders, in 3rd spot 400M, gave a short-lived finishing response early straight, out-finished final 200M.
Bumped at start, moved up to be vying for lead, led them to near 300M, no extra final stages.
Jumped awkwardly, settled towards the rear, had no clear running early straight then responded only fairly final 300M.
Settled down midfield along the inside, shifted out to challenge 350m but couldn't quicken enough. (Jockey : may not have appreciated the 7 day back up from last start.)
Dropped back towards the rear, had big task in hand 400M, ran past beaten horses only. Never dangerous.
Vied for early lead before taking a trailing position behind leaders halfway, came up emptied 300M, dropped away.
Pressed forward, caught wide no cover outside the lead, no extra 300M, weakened rapidly.
Jumped well, caught wide and was restrained to a position ahead midfield, under pressure home turn and didn't finish the race off. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)

Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, angled out 500M, hit the front 250M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.

Slightly slow out from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside early, 2 wide after passing 1200M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, showed good response in straight, no clear run final 25M, missed 3rd on line.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move 550M, 6-1/2L back turning in, finished off well without threatening the first few.
Began awkwardly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced better than midfield but trapped 3 wide, no cover throughout, challenged the leader early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened final 150M. (Bled.)
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the outside, there to turn, 8 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.

Began well from a tricky gate, raced better than midfield but trapped wide, taken back after passing 1300M, raced slightly behind midfield on outer in the middle stages, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, challenged the leader early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened inside final furlong.
Slightly slow out, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, challenged by rivals from 500M, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Jumped well, moved up passing 900M to chase leader, quickened up impressively early straight to lead 200M , held off fast finishing 2nd late. (Jockey : raced in a more forward position where his horse was comfortable.)
From wide draw dropped back early stages, held up 450M-300M before closing off eye-catchingly to be beaten 0.5L at the line.
From draw 4 ended up racing 3-wide no cover in midfield, fought on steadily under pressure but was always held by winner. (Jockey : jumped a marking on the track 170M and became unbalanced.)
Driven forward, stalked the leader into the straight, kept battling from 400M but lacked the extra gear to challenge winner, just missed out on 3rd.
Reserved behind midfield, over-raced middle stages, into clear 350M then worked home well to finish in the money.
Soon in front and enjoyed uncontested lead, unable to hold off winner mid-straight, no extra 150M losing several places close home. (Jockey: instructed to go forward and endeavour to lead.)
Caught racing 3-wide behind mid-division, kept on fairly passing 400M, couldn't launch a serious challenge.
From draw 1 maintained a midfield position along the fence, in touch with leaders home turn but then only worked home fairly final 400M.
Jumped only fairly, raced towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, took time to muster in the straight, steadied 250M, ran past beaten rivals late and was too far back to trouble the leaders.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, settled in the back half of the field, had plenty to do as they headed for home, failed to pick up speed and never looked likely.
Bustled along after the start, settled ahead of midfield, battled on one paced early straight, was tired after 200M and eased down. (Jockey : raced in a disappointing manner.)
Settled in the second half of the field, failed to make much impression on straightening. Never a threat. (Jockey : unable to hold a more forward position / better suited racing at Happy Valley.)
Blundered after the start then dropped back to race at the rear, caught wide throughout, had the job ahead 400M but gave no response when asked, failed to threaten at any stage.
Sat handy, traveled strongly, responded nicely when asked after 200M, kept on well to win.
Settled in front of midfield, raced 2 wide, switched out rounding the Turn, finished off nicely.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, made some progress over the final 150M.
Ridden hard to lead, slightly weakened entering the Straight, ran on evenly.
Settled worse than midfield, responded fairly when asked, closed off okay.
Sat midfield, traveled fairly, one pace to the line.
Sat rear, raced rear throughout, switched out rounding the Turn, minor progress made (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear on the rail, limited response when asked, closed off fairly.
Slow to jump, settled behind midfield, weakened passing 300M, never a threat.
Sat midfield, lay out in the middle, race wide throughout, no contention (See Incident Report).
Tracked leader until ridden ahead at the 150m line. Soon on top and won comfortably.
Showed good speed to lead until headed by winner 150m out. No extra closing stages and just held second.
Settled in rear of mid-field after very briefly hampered early. Stayed on for pressure from 200m out and gaining quickly on runner-up closing stages.
Out sharply from rail draw and tracked leader. Under pressure to maintain position from over 200m out and stayed on at the one pace.
Mid-field after sluggish start. Headway onto heels of principals at halfway but one paced under pressure and unable to challenge when tight for room against rail from 100m out.
Raced mid-field throughout and lacked the speed to get involved having come under pressure at the 200m line, though some late gains.
Tracked principals from middle draw and a bit keen. No extra from the 150m line after becoming unbalanced briefly and faded.
Took a hold as he tracked leaders from outside draw with no cover. Under pressure from 200m out and weakened final 100m.
Needed to be ridden from the stalls and in rear. Some limited headway when short of room 200m out and never a danger.
Held up in last pair after slow start. Limited headway under pressure from 200m out and never involved.
Dropped in from wide draw. Under pressure over 200m out and soon left behind.
Pecked when checked briefly after slow start. Soon under pressure and left behind from halfway.
Crowded shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, travelled well in the middle stages, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 1-3/4L back, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take a place without threatening the first two. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 9, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run 100M, cleared 50M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out 500M, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, hampered and snatched up final 75M.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide better than midfield, slightly taken back 800M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, switched out when turning for home, ran on strongly, just got there on the line.
Settled midfield 2 wide, navigated through traffic in the early part of the Straight, found clear running at 250M, closed off strongly.
Not the quickest out, ridden hard to obtain the lead, kept on okay to the line, held 3rd.
Caught 4 wide no cover throughout, ran on nicely in the Straight.
Tracked leader, switched out in the Straight, made decent progress in the early part of the Straight but one pace final 200M.
Settled at the rear on the rail, no clear run in the Straight, never seriously tested.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, limited response in the Straight.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Settled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, held up early in the Straight, made some late ground.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, weakened in the Straight.
Caught 3 wide no cover throughout, made little impression.
Settled on pace, never a threat.
Settled near the rear, never in contention. (See Incident Report) (Performance disappointing, must trial)
Settled over 4L off the pace in 4th, quickened well from 300 metres out to swoop on the leader 150 metres out.

Crowded at start, ridden up to join the leaders early before gradually settling 1L back in 2nd, came to hit the front shortly after straightening only to be overhauled when found no extra 150 metres out.
Gradually settled worse than midfield in 5L 6th and 3-wide without cover, in similar position into straight, ran on under pressure inside final 300 metres to reach 3rd late.
Shared early pace on rail before shifting back to 3rd passing the 1100 metres, kept on at the one pace under from a similar position into straight.
Settled well back after crowded at start and waited with, ran on under pressure without threatening.
Settled worse than midfield in 5L 5th on rail, saved ground turning in for home, switched out for a run over 300 metres out, made moderate late impression.
Soon dropped to 7th, made no impression in straight. (Jockey said pace did not suit.)
Broke well to share early pace 3-wide down the back straight, steadied up slightly on rail approaching home bend, folded up quickly inside final 300 metres.
From wide draw taken back to a rearward position, 5Ls to make up top of straight, finished off strongly when asked 300M, got up 50M from home.
Blundered shortly after the start, maintained a position behind midfield, shoved along 550M, got going passing 250M, ran on nicely to take 2nd near line.
Jumped fairly, tracked leaders on the inside, held up behind one-paced rivals early straight, shifted lane 200M to obtain clear running, fought on nicely under top weight to take 3rd close home.

Prominent outside leaders, caught wide no cover throughout the trip, fought well on straightening and vied for lead to 50M, claimed by first 3 late. (Trainer confirmed the instructions were not to lead.)
From draw 1 moved up to be sharing the lead on inside, hard pressed from 300M to hold its lead, no extra 50M and swamped by rivals close home.
Given a waiting ride at the rear, held up for clear running 300M-200M, did best work late, nearest finish. (Jockey questioned regarding his riding in the straight.)
From wide draw taken across behind runners, waited with at the rear of the field, made good progress final 300M.
Settled down midfield, raced keenly middle stages, disappointed for clear running from 300M and badly held up to 100M, left with too much to do.
In touch with leaders, ran home one paced passing 400M, wasn't beaten far but never looked like getting involved.
Away well, shared lead on outside, tried hard early straight to stay in contention, faded final 100M.
Jumped on terms, settled in midfield along the inside, fought on one paced turning home, checked 150M but was posing little threat to leaders at the time.
Not hurried after the jump, dropped back to a position behind midfield, lacked a finish passing 400M and was never involved. (Lame next day.)
Jumped only fairly, ended up racing in mid-division 3-wide, couldn't go on from 300M, eased towards the finish. (Jockey could offer no explanation for the disappointing performance.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well in the middle stages, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Jumped well from gate 12, raced in 2nd, 1-1/2L back turning in, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, always held.
Moderately away, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back turning in, closed off well to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide, 2-1/2L back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, positioned 7 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 150M, finished 2nd.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, finished off well to take a place, nearest on line
Away well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, wider turning in, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Began only fairly and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, peaked on run 200M, weakened final 100M.
Out with rest, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, a bit closer in the middle stages, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Shifted in at start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on outer, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run final 300M, not able to test properly. (See Racing Incidents.)
