Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear early in straight, ran on strongly to the line, won by 3 lengths.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the outside early, dropped to 3rd approaching 700M, 2 to 3 lengths back in the middle stages, kept on well in straight without threatening the winner.
Out with rest, raced towards rear of midfield on the outside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening.

Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside early, sent forward after passing 1050M, raced in 2nd approaching 700M, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began only fairly and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, made no impression in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Mucus.)
Taken back from gate 7, raced at rear on the outside, 9 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened final 400M, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Mucus.)
Ridden early to soon take up running, kicked some 3L clear into straight, won cosily.

Slightly slow out and hampered, soon recovered to 6th on rail over 3L back, became slightly closer in 5th about 800 metres out, obtained a clear run 200 metre out, quickened well to snatch inside the 50 metres.
Settled alongside race leader, failed to quicken to challenge in straight.
One back in 3rd on rail travelling keenly early stages, ran home one paced.
Settled in last early travelling keenly in 7th in back straight, commenced move out wide rounding home bend and widest into straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Began well from a poor draw, bumped and taken back for cover in 4th over 2L back shortly after turning into back straight, switched 3-wide rounding home bend and wider into home straight, one-paced.
Inconvenienced early dropping to last, saved ground turning in for home, ran home one-paced.
Never better than midfield, in last few turning into straight, made no further impression.
Sat handy, traveled comfortably, showed some dash passing 150M, closed off strongly.
Settled midfield on the rail, traveled nicely, responded well when asked (Blood in its mouth after race).
Sat in front of midfield, slightly gave ground inside 500M, kept on okay.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, traveled fairly, one pace to the line.
Sat behind midfield, weakened inside 200M, minor progress made in the Straight.
Ridden hard to lead, weakened entering the Straight, no impression (Rider dropped whip).
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, finished off only fairly (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, commenced to improve from 550M, limited response when placed under pressure.
Tracked leaders. Pushed along turning into straight but responded and stayed on to get to the front late in bunched finish.
Settled in mid-division from wide draw. Travelled smoothly to home turn before staying on for pressure to snatch second on the line.
Allowed to stride on and took overall lead after 300m. Responded to pressure from last turn and stuck to task well when challenged on both sides in the final 100m.
Dropped in from widest draw and raced in last. Still plenty to do turning into home straight and finished off strongly despite a troubled passage (see incident report).
Stuck to the inside rail throughout from stall 1. Under pressure at end of back straight in rear of mid-field but responded to make headway on final bend and not beaten far in bunched finish.

Tracked leader until challenging and in a share of the lead from top of home straight. No extra and lost a few places final 50m. Had to be steadied when short of room final strides (see incident report).

Waited with after sluggish from the stalls. Involved in bumping match with rival from 200m line but good headway nonetheless until running out of room final 50m in packing field (see incident report).
Tracked leader but failed to pick up for pressure in home straight and no extra as passed by rivals from the 200m line.
Held up from wide draw. One paced for pressure in home straight and unable to make much impression despite not beaten far in bunched finish.
Towards rear of mid-field. Some headway out wide at end of back straight but lost ground on final bend and no impression.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.

Began awkwardly and made contact, raced better than midfield on the outside, sent forward approaching 700M, took the lead 500M, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few final 50M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced behind midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off well without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened final 50M.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 500M, challenged the leader turning in, peaked on run 150M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out 500M, very wide turning in, made little progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Jumped okay, settled worse than midfield 3 wide no cover, ran on nicely to score despite the tough run.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, made good progress but can't hold off winner.
Jumped nicely and led, travelled smoothly throughout, kept on until weakened slightly final 100M.
Settled midfield 2 wide, under pressured from the 500M, stayed on. (See Incident Report)
Raced in front of midfield 2 wide, one pace to the line.
Sat at the rear, stayed on fairly.
Settled last, made some late ground.
Sat midfield on the rail, made little impression.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, made no ground.
Tracked leader 2 wide, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Blood in Trachea)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Sat behind the leader, gave ground in the Straight.
Made all setting a fast pace early in back straight holding a 2L break, came back to within 1L of 2nd rounding home bend, hung on well under pressure in the run to the line.

Broke well but soon taken back to 3L 3rd and over 4L off the fast pace early in back straight, chased along in 3rd rounding home bend, baulked behind eventual winner after straightening, unable to draw level throughout.
Restrained from a poor draw to last few in 9th on rail, ran on well between runners in straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled well behind, commenced move from over 450 metres out and widest into straight, ran on well under pressure inside final 200 metres down the centre of the track.
Held up wide in last few from the widest draw travelling keenly at times in back straight, commenced move rounding home bend but behind runners early in straight, fought on to be nearest at finish.

Unbalanced at start settling just worse than midfield 3-wide without cover, commenced move 3-wide 500 metres out to reach 3L 5th briefly shortly after, kept on at the one pace under pressure in the run to the line.
Settled just worse than midfield on rail, inconvenienced passing the 200 metres, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly and soon taken back well behind, saved ground on rail turning in for home, produced good late impression inside final 100 metres.

Jumped moderately gradually improving to 2nd on rail, chased 2L back in the fast pace early in back straight, unable to draw level under pressure in the final stretch, found no extra under pressure inside final 200 metres.

Improved steadily from a poor draw before settling in 4th and over 6L back in back straight half-way out, gained closer to about 2L 4th when pace slackened rounding home bend, weakened under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well before gradually settling over 7L back in 5th in the fast pace in mid-way down back straight, folded up under pressure quickly shortly after straightening.
Jumped on terms, travelled well in a position ahead of midfield, quickened up strongly to lead nearing 200M, held off fast finishing 2nd late on.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, settled 8Ls off the pace in last, responded strongly when asked, had to shift lane 200M to continue forward, chased hard to come up just short.
Maintained a position behind midfield but raced wide no cover throughout, swung to outside of straight and worked home well to fill a minor placing.
Bumped at the start, settled towards the rear, kept on mildly passing 300 to claim 4th without troubling first two.
Held up behind mid-division, wide into straight, closed off only fairly never a threat to leaders.
Dropped back to a rearward position, had plenty to do 400M but couldn't quite finish off.
Settled down midfield on the inside, lacked a kick on straightening and was safely held in the end.
Bumped at the start, held up towards the rear along the fence, checked 200M when commencing a run on the inside, couldn't quicken enough final stages to get involved.
Chased leaders, raced keenly middle stages, ran home one paced under pressure. (Trainer : disadvantaged by the pace of the event easing during the middle stages.)
Bumped on jumping, tracked leaders on inside, couldn't quicken passing 300M, soon out of contention.
From wide draw ridden forward to be pressing leader on outside, took over top of the straight, caught nearing 200M, no extra. (Noted to be making abnormal respiratory noise.)
Jumped awkwardly, sent forward to lead, found nothing on straightening, weakened rapidly towards the line.

Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 500M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M, finished 2nd.
Made contact at start, raced in 2nd early, positioned 3rd from 1100M, 2 to 3 lengths back in the middle stages, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began only fairly from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced better than midfield on the outside early, raced in 2nd from 1100M, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Tracked leaders. Responded to pressure to take up the lead at the 150m line and ran on well to open account.
Mid-field and raced a bit keenly after briefly checked early. Chased the winner home from the 200m line but never quite getting to that rival.
Away well and bustled up to race handy behind leader. Lacked speed to challenge winner from the 200m line but kept on for third.
Tracked leaders from rail draw. Responded to pressure in home straight but no extra final 50m and run out of a place.
Waited with from wide draw. Stayed on as he followed runner-up home from the 300m line but lacked pace to challenge.
Keen in front after getting across to lead from wide draw. Headed at the 150m line and no extra.
Slowly into stride from low draw and raced in mid-field. One paced under pressure and unable to challenge.
Got across to race mid-field from widest draw. Unable to quicken for pressure in home straight and weakened final 100m.
Raced in last after slowly into stride. Under pressure from 400m line but only moderate late headway and never a danger.
Bustled up from stalls to take handy position behind leader but weakened quite tamely from 300m line.
Waited with and became detached from main body of runners in home straight.
Always in rear after held up and no impression.
Settled handy, 2 wide, traveled strongly, responded well when asked, peak at 100M (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, switched out rounding the Turn, made good progress in the Straight.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, responded nicely when placed under pressure.
Shared the lead, slightly weakened inside 300M, ran on fairly well.
Settled midfield, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Sat in front of midfield, steadied to avoid heels near 100M, kept on okay (See Incident Report).
Sat midfield, not much improvement in the Straight, finished off fairly.
Sat midfield, responded only fairly when hardly ridden, one pace to the line (Lost right hind plate).
Settled towards rear, minor progress made in the Straight, never a threat.
Sat rear, raced rear, limited response when asked, nothing in the Straight.
Shared the lead, raced wide throughout, weakened notably entering the Straight.
Raced wide into home straight after waited with from high draw. Came with sustained run down the outside to challenge and edged out runner-up near line.
Out smartly but settled back in mid-division. Quickened to challenge from the 200m line and every chance. Edged out by winner near line.
Drawn high but across to race prominently from an early stage. Unable to match speed of front two from the 200m line but stuck to task under pressure.
Did plenty to get across and force pace from high draw having raced freely and 3L+ clear turning in. No extra final 150m and edged out for third on line.
Held up. Stayed on well having come under pressure on home turn but lacked pace to challenge.
Awkward start and lost a few lengths. Good headway on inside turning into straight but no further impression final 150m.
Tracked leaders and well positioned but one paced under pressure from the 300m line.
A bit keen in mid-field. Every chance from 300m line but unable to pick up for pressure and lost ground.
Raced in last after having to be nudged along early and ended up widest into home straight. Moderate late headway under pressure.
Raced wide in mid-field. No impression under pressure from 300m line and well held.
Recovered from slow start to race mid-field on rail but keen. Weakened home straight.
Always towards rear and never going pace to get competitive.
Tracked pace early but under pressure from halfway and dropped out home straight.
Began well from the widest draw, raced in midfield but trapped wide, moved closer approaching 800M, 2nd on turn, took the lead 200M, kept on very well to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 2 lengths or so back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Average to begin, raced towards rear, 2 wide, wider turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.

Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, checked off heels near 1200M, 2-1/2L back on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 600M, 4 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Out with rest, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Out in line, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled midfield 2 wide, closed off strongly, won going away, impressive.
Settled behind the pace on the rail, switched out rounding the Home Turn, made good ground, hit the front final 150M but can't hold off the winner.
Sat behind the leaders, kept on nicely for 3rd.
Settled midfield on the rail, stayed on late.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, made some late ground.
Shared lead 2 wide, weakened final furlong. (See Incident Report)
Jumped well and led, weakened and faded final 150M.
Not the quickest out, sat in front of midfield on the rail, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield, never impress.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Sat last, never in contention.
Settled at the rear, never involved. (See Incident Report)
Gradually picked up to one back 3-wide position after moderate start, one-out-one-back rounding home bend and disputed lead into straight, hit the front 200M out and hung on dourly under pressure.

Travelled keenly wide without cover in midfield after beginning from a poor draw, remained in similar position when 4-wide in 6th rounding home bend, ran on under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled keenly in 8th on rail just worse than midfield, soon came 2-wide to challenge after straightening, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.

Broke well from the one draw before taken one back on rail, forced to steady losing ground about 1050M out, some 2L back in 5th rounding home bend, baulked for a run early in straight and produced good late impression final 100M.

Ridden positively from a poor draw to lead or dispute lead out wide, gained outright advantage on rail coming onto home bend, re-joined in front by eventual winner into straight and soon found no extra under pressure.
Chased leaders early, lost ground drifting back to over 2L back in 5th onto home bend becoming 4th 3-wide shortly after, faded steadily in straight.
Soon taken well back from a poor draw for rails run, trailed the field into straight, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Broke well from a poor draw and soon taken well behind, shifted widest when 5-wide rounding home bend, ran past well-beaten horses down the centre of the straight.
Never better than midfield, 3-wide rounding home bend and wider into straight, made no further impression. (Jockey said horse did not travel at any stage.) (Blood in trachea)
Well there sharing early pace in back straight while travelling keenly, held back for 2nd on heels of race leader rounding home bend, soon weakened under pressure in straight. (Blood in trachea)
Shoved along after the start to obtain a handy spot behind leaders, picked up well passing 300M, led nearing 100M and gamely held off the challenge from the persistent runner up.
Travelled well in a 3-wide spot midfield, quickened nicely 300M and loomed up outside eventual winner, fought hard but just came up short.
From wide draw taken back to the rear, swung wide 500M into straight, came with a big run from well back to get pretty close in the end.
Went forward vying for the lead on outside, fought on one paced in the straight, no match for first 3 final over final 200M.
Showed good early speed to lead, joined by a rival from 800M, kept going well leaving the home turn, caught by rivals nearing 100M, faded to 5th.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, driven out 350M but gave limited response, never a winning hope.
Away well but soon restrained to race towards the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M but wasn't able to finish the race off.
Jumped on terms, settled behind midfield along the 3-path, lacked a turn of foot from 400M. Never involved.
From draw 1 stayed close to leaders early stages, had to be pushed along home turn, couldn't pick up passing 400M, no extra mid-straight.
Began only fairly, moved up to chase leaders 3-wide no cover, lay in home straight, found little and drifted out of contention.
Dropped back from wide draw to race at the tail of the field, had plenty to make up 400M, made no impression in the run home.
Settled in the second half of the field, over 6Ls to make up 400M, didn't respond to riding, weakened to last.
Away well, raced prominently on the stands' side, took the lead near 700M, led by 1/2L in the middle stages, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Shifted in at start, took the early lead on the stands' rail, headed near 700M, 1/2L back in the middle stages, kept on well to the line to take 2nd, no impression on winner.
Bumped start, raced in 3rd, 1-1/2L back, same margin in the middle stages, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the stands' rail, made good progress final 300M to make frame, no threat to the first few. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, positioned 3 away from the stands' rail, 2 lengths back, similar position in the middle stages, hard ridden from 400M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped shorty after start, raced in midfield on the stands' side, kept on same pace final 400M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, raced towards rear of midfield on the stand's side, a bit closer in the middle stages, no clear run final 400M, not able to test properly.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2-1/2L behind the leader, 2 away from the stands' rail, similar position in the middle stages, kept on evenly until approaching final 100M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced towards rear, 4 to 5 lengths back, same margin back in the middle stages, made no progress final 400M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the stand's side, made no impression final 400M.
Began well, raced in midfield on the stands' side, peaked 500M, weakened gradually final 300M.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield, nearer to the middle track, peaked 300M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced at rear on the middle track, lost touch from 300M.
Began well, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 150M, ran on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, found rail 700M, a bit closer on turn, finished off well to take 3rd without threatening.

Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 1/2L back, same position in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line. (Blood in its mouth after the race.)
Jumped with them, tracked leaders, 2 wide, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened close home.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, no clear run early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight.
Began fairly, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 500M, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, one-paced in the run home.
Bumped on the hindquarters at the start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened and eased final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, checked near 1250M, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, slightly inconvenienced 200M weakened thereafter.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move 500M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, blundered 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rival turning in, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Began well from gate 1, raced in 2nd, a length or so back, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well in straight but always held.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from gate 8, raced towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Shifted out shortly after start and made contact, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2-1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Reared as stalls opened and missed break, raced towards rear on the inside early, 2 wide after passing 900M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Chased leaders early stages, moved up home turn and took over from leader nearing 400M, kept going strongly over final 300M and kept rivals at bay.
Jumped well from draw 1, always in touch behind leaders, picked up well on straightening, fought hard to the line and claimed 2nd close home. Held by winner.
Broke alertly to be tracking the pace, checked 800M by leader, poised to strike top of straight, dug deep but was always held by winner. Lost 2nd close home.
Jumped awkwardly, raced keenly early stages, held a midfield position to the turn, came with a good run and wasn't beaten far in 4th.
Settled ahead of midfield, pushed along 550M, kept battling in the straight for a modest 5th but was always held by leaders.
From wide draw bustled along after the start, guided to a 2-wide position behind midfield, worked home fairly over final 300M and never troubled leaders.
From draw 8 dropped back to race near the rear, had some work to do 400M but failed to finish off under top weight.
Caught wide early stages before moving up passing 1000M to take the lead, came under serious pressure 400M, soon weakened out of contention. (Jockey : not his intention to lead.)
Dropped back from wide draw to race the tail of the field, pushed along 500M but couldn't muster the pace to challenge. Never involved.

Jumped on terms, soon drifted back to race towards the rear, struggled to keep up home turn, before dropping right out of contention early straight. (Jockey : failed to travel at any stage. / Unacceptable Performance.)
Settled midfield, traveled strongly, responded well when asked.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled comfortably, made good progress in the Straight.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled okay, stayed on well to grab 3rd.
Settled midfield, made gradual progress in the Straight, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, improved from 750M, closed off fairly.
Sat in front of midfield, weakened on straightening, limited response when asked.
Ridden hard to lead, gave ground quickly entering the Straight (Must BT, See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, raced rear, not much impression.
Sat handy, weakened entering the Straight, faded.
Handy from the outset tracking pacesetter. Driven from 200m out and headed runner-up on line.
Tracked leader and raced on inside rail throughout. Quickened to lead from 150m out until headed on line.
Wide early as he tracked leaders from high draw. Responded to pressure and kept going to line as he chased home front two.
Raced in mid-field and driven from an early stage. Kept on but never a danger to front three.
Tracked leaders until one paced from 200m line.
Driven early from inside stall and raced in rear of mid-field. Kept on in straight but never a danger to leaders.
Not the best away and soon pushed along in rear after briefly crowded out. Switched wide entering straight and modest headway final 100m.
Set strong pace. Challenged from 200m line and weakened, losing several places final 50m.
Raced in mid-field. Under pressure from top of home straight and no impression.
Held up last from widest draw and never on terms.
Always in rear after soon pushed along and unable to hold position.
Held up from high draw. No headway under pressure and always in rear.
Away well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, commenced move 400M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 200M, ran on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Away with them, taken back to race towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, commenced move 400M, made some progress in straight.
Began only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, awkwardly placed 350M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, commenced move 450M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in the run home.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, unable to maintain position from 400M, weakened final furlong. (Roarer.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, weakened from 550M, finished tailed out. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped nicely, ridden along to assume the lead, kept on nicely, battled hard and just held on.
Tracked leader, under pressured from the 500M, kept on, just missed.
Sat just behind the leaders, angled out rounding the Home Turn, closed off nicely, had every chance.
Sat box seat, made good ground on the inside, closest finish. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, ran on evenly.
Sat midfield 2 wide, one pace to the line.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, switched to 3 wide to improve after 600M, stayed on fairly.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, made some headway late.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, under pressure at 600M and weakened.
Sat last, made no impression.
Sat midfield on the rail, hard ridden from the 650M, no response.
Settled near the rear on the rail, never a threat.
With leaders early, taken one-out-one-back to 3rd early in back straight, switched in near the rail for a run upon straightening, asserted authority over 100M out.

Travelled wide without cover in worse than midfield, made steady headway from 900M to reach 1L 3rd 3-wide approaching home bend, held every chance over 200M out but had no more to give inside the 50M.
Settled one from last and waited with, baulked behind runners rounding home bend, ran on strongly inside final 200 metres.
Pressed forward after moderate start to soon join the leader, hit the front passing the 600M holding 1L advantage into straight, unable to sustain effort and caught over 100M out.
Settled just worse than midfield over 3L back in 7th, angled off the rail for a run entering straight and ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled well behind on rail from the widest stall and waited with, saved ground turning in for home, made good late impression.
Ridden along with leaders briefly, gradually dropped back towards rear in 8th 800M out, wide rounding home bend and the widest into straight, ran on past well-beaten runners.
Ridden to hold early advantage, led until inside the 600M, dropped out from 2nd shortly after straightening.
Settled just 2L off the pace in 4th or 5th on rail, forced to steady and lost position about 550M out, faded steadily from 3L 5th into straight.
Gradually settled in 6th some 3L off the pace, gradually faded under pressure home bend.
Settled ahead of midfield 3-4Ls off leader, had some ground to make up 300M but dug deep to get home narrowly.
Held a forward position 3rd 2.5L on settling, loomed top of straight, drove hard to the line only to just miss out in a close finish.
Held up in mid-division on the inside, drifted away from fence 450M, found the line well but just held by first two.
Settled down midfield along the 2-path, swung wide for home then came with a big run from off the pace, nearest line.
Not hurried after the start, dropped back to race towards the rear 8-9Ls off the pace, closed off nicely when asked, coming from well back to be nearest at the finish.

Caught racing 3-wide after the start before moving up to race outside leader, travelled well going into home turn, fought hard under top weight after taking the lead but unable to hold off rivals late stages.
Reserved in the second half of the field, gave limited response turning home, never a winning hope.
From wide draw restrained to a rearward position, was commencing to finish off the race but became held up from 150M to 50M. Could do better.
Chased leaders, loomed up top of straight but didn't go on with it, tired passing 200M.
Jumped only fairly and then was crowded shortly after the start, settled towards the rear further back than usual, could not muster any sort of challenge in the straight.
Pressed on to lead 1L on settling, soon came under pressure when a rival moved up alongside nearing 500M, went backwards 250M. (Performance considered disappointing.)
Dropped back from wide draw, soon detached from the field, never in contention. (Jockey concerned there may be something amiss and didn't fully test his mount. / Unacceptable Performance.)

Began smartly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, commenced move approaching 400M, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1300M, 3/4L back on turn, showed good response in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, still 6 lengths back turning in, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to be nearest on line.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position in the middle stages, kept on well in straight to make frame, always held.

Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead after passing 1300M, led by 3/4L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened close home.

Jumped only fairly, raced slightly better than midfield but trapped wide, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, a length or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out 400M, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground throughout, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.

Began well from the widest draw, gradually shifted back towards rear remaining 3-wide without cover, commenced move home bend and sustained effort from 1L 4TH 4-wide into straight to assert authority 200M out.
Broke well settling just over 2L off the pace in 4th on rail, commenced move 2-wide home bend to share the lead into straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 150M.
Settled in midfield in 5th some 3L back, commenced move 4-wide home bend sharing the lead into straight, weakened under pressure inside final 250M.
Niggled along worse than midfield, given reminders from approaching home turn and kept on same pace from 2L 6th into straight, found no extra closing stages.
Well there early settling one back in 3rd on rail, found nothing after straightening.
Settled well behind, gained closer to 4L back in 6th on rail passing the 900M, baulked for a run turning for home, made no further impression.
Settled towards the rear 3-wide in back straight, came under pressure home bend and faded upon straightening.
Set fast pace, obtained rails run into back straight, led until finding no extra shortly after home turn.
Soon dropped well behind and never seen with a chance.
Soon recovered to first few after moderate start settling alongside race leader in back straight, weakening when tightened inside the 400M.
Settled midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, made good progress when asked.
Sat worse than midfield, switched out to obtain clear run entering the Straight, responded nicely when placed under pressure.
Sat handy, traveled okay, slightly weakened over the final 150M, kept on okay to hold 3rd.
Ridden hard to lead, traveled keenly, ran on evenly to the line.
Settled in front of midfield, raced wide and without cover throughout, minor progress made (See Incident Report).
Sat handy, traveled fairly, limited response when asked.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, improved rounding the Turn, closed off fairly.
Settled towards rear, traveled only fairly, not much impression made.
Settled behind midfield, traveled okay, switched out rounding the Turn, failed to respond in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, gave ground notably entering the Straight (See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, blundered when placed under pressure in the Straight, no contention (Must BT, Unacceptable Performance).
Reared and started slowly from high draw. Still in rear turning into home straight but came with sustained run out wide to edge ahead close home. Did well.
Dropped across from high draw and ended up on rail. Finished off well after briefly having to wait for a run at the 300m line and just edged out.
Led after 200m and got across to rail. Stayed in front until passed by first 2 at the 50m line.
Raced in mid-field after briefly crowded at start. Had to wait for a run at the 300m line and kept on once in the clear.
Slowly away from stall 1 and bustled up to recover and take handy position behind leaders. No extra final 100m.
Waited with in rear of mid-field. Kept on after angled out in straight but lacked pace to challenge.
Keen as he tracked leaders from wide position. Challenged and every chance from 300m line but no extra final 150m.
A touch keen in mid-division. Lacked pace to challenge in straight but did keep on.
Out sharply and tracked pacesetters. Every chance at 200m line after ridden along into straight but soon no extra.
Across to dispute lead from high draw. Still handy at 300m line but weakened.
Raced in mid-division. Struggling to quicken when short of room and snatched up at 200m line. No impression after.
Struggled to go the pace and raced wide. Never competitive.
Dropped in from widest draw. Soon pushed along and never out of last place.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3 lengths at 400M, kept on well to the line, won by a neck.
Taken back to race towards rear, 5 lengths or so back at 400M, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, 5 lengths back at 400M, unable to obtain clear run until 150M, made some progress thereafter to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Clean jump, raced better than midfield on the stands' side, 3 lengths back at 400M, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the middle track, 4 lengths or so back at 400M, hard ridden from 350M but only showed some response, one-paced final 150M.
Blundered shortly after start, tracked leaders, 3 lengths back at 400M, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually final 150M.
Moderately away from gate 13, raced at rear on the stands' side, 5-1/2L back in the middle stages, no clear run final 400M, not able to be properly tested.
Out with rest, raced slightly behind midfield on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 350M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, raced at rear on the stands' side, 6-1/2L back at 400M, no clear run until approaching 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped only fairly, raced in midfield, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden from 350M but only showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Began well from gate 14, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, made minor progress after passing 300M, crowded near 125M, eased final 100M.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the stands' rail, ridden after passing 400M but only showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced better than midfield on the stands' side, peaked 300M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Began awkwardly from gate 1, raced alone on the far side, peaked on run 500M, weakened thereafter, eased final furlong. (Mucus.) (Roarer.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped nicely, settled behind the leaders, travelled strongly throughout, angled out at 350M into clear running, hit the front at 200M and ran on.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, slightly help up at 200M, shifted out and closed off nicely.
Jumped well, tracked leader, kept on nicely until final 100M.
Caught 3 wide no cover behind midfield early, improved up near the pace at the 900M, showed some dash from the 400M, nothing extra final furlong. (See Incident Report)
Settled at the rear on the rail, last turning for Home, made some late ground.
Raced towards the rear 2 wide, stayed on fairly.
Settled midfield on the rail, only one pace when asked.
Ridden along early to lead, weakened final 150M. (See Incident Report)
Not the quickest out, settled at the rear, never impress.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield in the middle stages, never a threat.
Sat midfield 2 wide between horses, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Last early, improved to 5th some 3L back over 1000M out, saved ground on rail turning in for home, obtained a run inside the 200M and quickened well to assert authority final strides.
Moderate beginning, made steady headway to one back in 3rd on rail 1100M out, obtained run 2-wide shortly after straightening, hit the front under pressure 200M out only to be caught close to home.
Began well from a poor draw, soon took up running passing the 1200M obtaining rails run shortly afterward, led until joined into straight, narrowly headed 200M out and ran home one-paced.
Niggled along amongst leaders, ceded advantage after first 200M becoming, 2-wide rounding home bend and disputed leader into straight, faded steadily under pressure.
Settled wide at the back of the small field, made swift progress 3-wide around home bend reaching 1L back in joint 3rd into straight, found no extra inside final 150M. (Reported a roarer)
Broke well with leaders, restrained 2L back to 4th after first 100M becoming 5th rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening in the run to the line.
Travelled some 3L back in 6th dropping to last onto home bend, 3-wide into straight, found nothing under pressure.

Began well enough from draw 1, maintained a midfield position along the inside, had difficulty obtaining clear running 300M before quickening up nicely to hit the front 100M. Held on well late stages.
Reserved in midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, still a fair way off leader top of straight, finished off strongly down the outside to just go under.
Went forward as expected, vied for lead on the inside, kept on well passing 400M and led them until 100M. No match for first 2 late stages.

Never far off in the group chasing leaders, driven 450M and closed off steadily. Comfortably held by first three final stages. (Jockey : instructed to ride positively to capitalize the horse' s light weight.)
Not hurried early stages, settled down behind midfield, had some work to do passing 400M, did best work late got up for 5th near line.
Chased leaders in 3rd, loomed top of the straight, had his chance but couldn't sustain run passing 200M, faded towards the finish.
Settled ahead of midfield, swung wide for home but lacked a strong finish, held by rivals final 200M.
Never far off from the pace, moved closer to leaders home turn, held up for clear running from 400M to 250M but the finishing effort was only fair closing stages.
Away with them, held up behind mid-division along the inside, failed to pick up when asked on straightening. Never a threat to leaders.
Vied for lead on the outside, couldn't keep up passing 350M, soon went backwards.

Slow to begin, ended up in last further back than intended, had big task in hand 400M, ran past beaten horses only. Never in the picture. (Trainer confirmed the instructions were to take up a forward position.)
Drifted back to a rearward position, plenty to make up top of straight but failed to respond to riding. (Jockey reported his mount was coughing subsequent to the race / Bled.)

Jumped on terms from a middle draw, caught racing wide no cover in midfield from 900M, couldn't sprint enough entering home straight. Never a factor. (Jockey : didn't appreciate Yielding track conditions.)
From wide draw taken back to near last, struggled to keep up 600M, soon out of contention and finished tailed out (Unacceptable Performance.)
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after the start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L in the middle stages, kept on well in straight and scored.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, always held.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 4-1/2L back, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Slightly slow out from gate 1, positioned 2-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, unable to obtain clear run until final 100M, made minor progress thereafter.
Fast into stride, taken back to race behind midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, crowded near 800M, angled out after passing 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Bumped on jumping, sat right behind the leader, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out at start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 3/4L back turning in, ridden after passing 300M, hit the front approaching 100M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Jumped smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, ridden after passing 300M, peaked and headed approaching 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced in 3rd, a length or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, carried wider and bumped 500M, made some progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out and bumped 500M, 5 lengths or so back turning in, kept on same pace in the run home.

Began only fairly, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, only showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on outer, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the outside, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened 200M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced slightly behind midfield, angled out 500M, 3-1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.

Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/4L behind the leader, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out approaching 400M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, peaked on turn, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 7, raced towards rear, 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Tracked leaders. Challenged between horses from 200m line and driven ahead final 50m.
Crowded on rail on first bend as he tried to take up handy position from inside draw. Angled off rail in home straight to challenge and ran on strongly.
Started quickly and got across to lead on rail from middle draw. Hassled in front but passed by front two only inside final 50m.
Pressed leader. Every chance until no extra and run out of places final 100m.
Dropped across to rail after slightly squeezed at start and raced in mid-division. One paced in home straight and unable to challenge.
Last on final turn after held up from high draw. Made headway from the 200m line and never nearer.
Dropped in from outside stall. Made some headway in home straight under pressure but never a danger.
Keen as he tracked leaders after briefly crowded at start. Unable to quicken for pressure from 200m line and lost ground.
Raced wide throughout in mid-division and made little impression under pressure in home straight.
Raced wide throughout towards the rear and never on terms.
Needed to be niggled along from an early stage and soon towards the rear. Never involved.
Settled in mid-field. Under pressure turning into home straight and soon weakened.
Ridden along to lead, traveled comfortably, responded nicely when asked, kept on well to win (See Incident Report).
Sat rear on the rail, witched out on Straightening, made good progress over the final 100M.
Sat worse than midfield, made some ground inside 200M, closed off nicely.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled okay, ran on evenly to the finish.
Sat handy, traveled strongly in the early stages, slightly weakened inside 150M.
Jumped only fairly, sat behind midfield, held up rounding the Turn, closed off okay.
Settled midfield, lay in in the Straight, raced in restricted room passing 200M (See Incident Report).
Settled in front of midfield, weakened inside 250M, closed off only fairly.
Sat midfield, raced wide and keenly, raced tight from 150M, could not be fully ridden out.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, raced in restricted room over the concluding stages, could not be ridden out.
Lowered its head ash the start was effected, lost ground, sat midfield, no impression (Must stalls test, See Incident Report).
Settled towards rear, raced ungenerously, hung out rounding the Turn, limited response when asked (See Incident Report).
Held up. Under pressure and still well back on final bend before coming with strong run from 200m out to lead on line.
Held up initially before big move in back straight to lead at halfway. Responded to pressure in home straight and headed only the line.
Tracked leaders from inside stall. Challenged and every chance from 150m line.
Made running until headed at halfway. Stayed handy and every chance from 200m line.
Raced in mid-field. Under pressure from final turn and kept on at the one pace.
Raced towards rear after briefly crowded at start. Caught between horses when trying to improve off final bend and kept on once clear from 150m line.
Raced in mid-field. Under pressure from end of back straight and never going pace to get competitive, tending to hang left. Short of room between rivals closing stages.
Briefly crowded at start but still able to track leaders. Unable to respond to pressure from end of back straight and weakened.
Rear of mid-division after crowded at start. Struggling in last pair final band and never involved.
Prominent until gradually losing position from 600m mark and well held.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, sent forward approaching 800M, 3/4L back on turn, hard ridden from 250M, showed good response, hit the front 75M, kept on very well to the line.

Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, sent forward after entering the back straight, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 75M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 800M and moved a bit closer, 2 lengths or so back on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, 3 lengths back turning in, made some progress in the run home.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the outside, commenced move approaching 600M, 3 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Away with them, positioned 3 wide, a length or so back, 2 wide from 1000M, same margin back on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1250M, led by 3/4L, shared lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, dropped towards rear 700M, 3 wide at rear on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Began smartly from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, dropped to rear 600M, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, positioned 2-1/2L behind the leader on rail, dropped towards rear 600M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 12, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 800M, 4 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Average to begin, took the early lead, headed near 1250M, allowed rival to cross 1000M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, travelled smoothly throughout, split horses in the Straight, ran on strongly to score.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, angled out in the clear at 400M, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Settled midfield on the rail, stayed on okay.
Showed good early speed, tracked leader, kept on okay.
Settled midfield 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Raced just behind the leaders, only one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Sat last, made some late ground.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression.
Jumped nicely and ridden along early to lead, weakened final furlong. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide no cover on pace, weakened in the Straight. (Performance disappointing)
Sat midfield 3 wide, under pressure at 600M, never in contention.
Settled in 6th just better than midfield, slightly worse onto home bend, obtained a run over 200M out and quickened well to assert authority close to home.
Settled worse than midfield, shifted wide into straight, finished well like a train down the centre of the track inside final 200M.
Travelled wide in rear of midfield, improved to 2L 4th 2-wide 800M out, fought on steadily from a similar position into straight but found first two too good.
Pressed forward from a poor draw to soon take up running, led until narrowly headed turning into straight, regained lead momentarily inside the 200M but soon swamped.
Jumped best settling just off the pace in 4th or 5th, became 3rd in similar position rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening in straight.
Close up, improved to join race leader 700M out hitting the front briefly early in straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 100M.
Settled in rear, switched off heels for a run over 150M out, made some late impression.
Settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in for home, kept on steadily until finding no extra inside final 200M.
Slowly away, niggled along in last few, saved ground on rail turning in for home, found nothing.
Settled in rear of midfield, dropped slightly worse in back straight, bumped and widest runner into home straight, one paced.
Pressed forward from a poor gate to close-up 3rd 3-wide with cover, taken 1L back to 5th remaining without cover around home bend, soon weakened after straightening.
Soon dropped to last and trailed the field throughout. (Lame)
From draw 10 unable to slot in, caught 3-wide in mid-division throughout the race, quickened up strongly 250M and flew home down the outside to snatch victory near line.
Crowded at the start, gradually improved to a midfield position, closed off well final 300M to go 2nd nearing 50M but couldn't hold off the fast finishing winner.
Jumped well, tracked leaders on inside, stuck to task well from 300M, not pace of first two late but managed to hold on for 3rd.

Crowded at the start, soon taken back to the rear, over 5Ls off the pace at 400M, closed off fastest to almost claim 3rd at the line. (Jockey : instructed to ride his mount in a conservative manner in the early stages.)
Went forward to be vying for lead on outside, kept battling top of straight, held slender lead 200M but couldn't hold off pursuing rivals late stages, faded to finish 5th.
Away in line, drifted back to race behind midfield, caught wide no cover from 700M, ran home steadily down outside of straight to be nearest at the finish.
From outside gate dropped back to race at the rear, had plenty to do 400M but made limited progress only. Never a threat to leaders.
Jumped on terms, chased leaders 2-wide, close enough top of the straight but couldn't quite finish off. (No Vet findings.)

Pressed forward to be vying for the lead on the inside, fought hard under big weight early straight to hold his lead, faded inside 200M .(Trainer : disadvantaged by being pressured in the lead / Roarer.)
Jumped awkwardly, ended up racing towards the rear further back than usual, failed to finish off the race on straightening. (Jockey : may not have appreciated being stepped up in Class 3 company.)

Began only fairly, settled further back than intended, raced in midfield early stages before drifting further back home turn, couldn't go on in the straight. (Jockey: instructed to hold a forward position.)

Began well, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, 3 wide turning in, showed good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began fairly, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out 550M, 4-1/2L back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place on line.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently on the outside, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 400M, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped on jumping, settled midfield always close enough to leaders, loomed 300M, quickened past leader 150M and continued on well closing stages.
Tracked leader 2-wide, responded well to lead 250M but was outstayed by winner final stages.
Had uncontested lead, headed 250M by first two, fought on to hold 3rd.
Slow to begin, given a waiting ride at the rear, swung wide into straight then closed off the race moderately for a non-threating 4th.
Held up in second half of the field, ran home only fairly over final 400M, never a winning hope.
From draw 1 moved up to track leaders on inside, failed to respond to riding passing 400M, soon drifted out of contention.
Bounded on jumping losing ground at the start, settled towards the rear further back than intended, couldn't finish it off on straightening. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced keenly in midfield, caught wide no cover from 1000M, had nothing to offer turning home, weakened away.
Jumped nicely, ridden along to lead, traveled strongly, responded well when asked.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear, switched out and improved rounding the Turn, closed off nicely.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Sat rear, angled out entering the Straight, made some progress over inside 200M.
Tracked leader, traveled okay, limited response when placed under pressure (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, one pace to the line.
Settled midfield, switched out rounding the Turn, minor progress made (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, no impression made.
Sat behind midfield, traveled fairly, no clear run from 200M, not fully tested.
Settled midfield, raced wide throughout, weakened notably in the Straight.
Disputed lead until taking clear advantage 200m out. Ran on well for pressure to record first win.
Raced wide in rear of mid-field from outside stall. Stayed on strongly for pressure in home straight but unable to reel in winner.
Tracked pacesetters but caught wide. Stuck to task in straight but lacked speed to challenge winner.
Tracked leaders on rail from inside draw. Every chance from top of straight but unable to quicken.
Dropped in from wide draw and soon pushed along. Finished off well after having only one behind turning into home straight but couldn't reach leaders.
Bumped shortly after sluggish start and in rear. Made some headway with a clear run up rail in home straight but lacked pace to get on terms.
Tracked pace and well placed into home straight but no extra from 200m line.
A bit keen in early stages as he raced in mid-division. Failed to respond to pressure from final bend and no impression.
Pressed in front by eventual winner. Driven along from top of home straight and weakened.
Wide early and dropped back into mid-field after soon pushed along. Never a factor.
Raced out wide in mid-field. No response to pressure from final bend and weakened.
Niggled along from an early stage and gradually lost position. Struggling from over 400m out, lost touch and eased.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, short of room early in straight, cleared 350M, finished off strongly to score.
Began well from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 850M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home, finished 2nd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take a place.
Began well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 900M, sat right behind the leader on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 700M, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, no daylight early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off well without threatening.
Bounded on jumping and lost ground, raced at tail, 4 lengths or so back turning in, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (Roarer.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Crowded shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 700M, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Jumped well from gate 12, unable to slot in, raced in midfield on outer, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Not the quickest out, soon ridden to lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kicked clear at the top of the Straight, just held on. (See Incident Report)
Taken back towards the rear from a wide barrier, stayed on well, just missed.
Settled near the rear 2 wide, no clear run until 250M, closed off nicely.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide with cover, showed good dash from the 250M to 100M, kept on.
Settled towards the rear 3 wide, stayed on nicely.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, kept on.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, ran on until weakened final 75M. (See Incident Report)
Sat behind midfield on the rail, made some ground along the rail, nothing impressive.
Settled midfield 2 wide, hampered at 150M, one pace to the line.
Tracked leader, challenged the leader at 600M, weakened final furlong.
Settled midfield on the rail, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Sat the rear, never a threat.
Began well, gradually settled some 5L back in 6th, responded well inside final 200M to just get up on line.
Settled 1L back 2-wide from a poor draw, soon came to join the leader early in straight hitting the front 200M out only to be caught final strides.
Began awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to 5th on rail some 4L off the pace, angled out for clear run upon straightening, produced moderate impression inside final 150M.
Pressed forward from the widest draw to take up running on the rail 1000M out, attempted to make all but unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 200M.
Travelled 3-wide without cover in last few, tended to hang out rounding home bend, switched out for a run when inconvenienced over 300M out, finished off the race nicely.
Settled well behind, trailed the field into straight, ran on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Travelled 3-wide without cover in 4th, hung in a difficult ride early in straight and faded under pressure inside final 150M.
Travelled one back in 3rd on rail to straight, faded under pressure gradually.
Taken back for rails run one from last, travelled keenly rounding home bend, found nothing under pressure in straight.

Chased the pace, quickened up nicely 350M vying for the lead, gained upper hand late stages and just held on from the fast finishing 2nd on the far side. (Jockey fined for using the whip forward of the saddle in the home straight.)
Dropped back to race at the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, closed off strongly down outside of track, line came too soon just beaten a short head.
Sent forward, led to nearing 700M, fought alongside eventual winner on straightening, vied for lead from 250M to 50M, grudgingly gave way late.
Settled behind midfield, had a few lengths to make up on leaders 400M, not clear 200M then hit the line well late stages.
Away well, close enough to the pace early stages, drifted back to midfield home turn before keeping on steadily final 400M. Comfortably held by leaders.
Settled towards the rear, swung wide into straight before running on fairly to the line. (No Vet findings.)
Drifted back to a rearward position early stages, had some work to do 400M, stayed on without posing serious threat to leaders. (Jockey : would appreciate being stepped up in distance. / Bled.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced keenly early stages before striding forward to lead nearing 700M, caught inside 300M, weakened towards the line.
Up with early pace before easing back to a midfield spot halfway, couldn't go on passing 400M.
In mid-division early stages, already under pressure before turning home, couldn't keep up with rivals top of straight. (Bled 2nd time. Compulsory retirement.)
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross 1100M, 3rd on turn, 4 lengths or so back, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 900M, 2nd on turn, retook the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Made contact at start, raced slightly better than midfield, 5 lengths or so back, similar position in the middle stages, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Slightly slow out, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 800M, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, closed off well to make frame, no threat to the first few.

Away well, raced in 3rd, travelled keenly from 1300M, took the lead near 900M, led by 1-3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, 12 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, still 9 lengths behind the leader at 400M, made good progress in straight, nearest finish.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 500M, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made some headway early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 500M, 8 lengths or so back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced behind midfield on the outside early, moved closer after passing 1350M, positioned 2 wide in midfield on turn, wider turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 10 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, dropped towards rear on turn, made no impression in the run home.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 11 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, shared lead on turn, hard ridden from 250M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Slightly slow out and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide after passing 500M, 3-1/2L back turning in, no daylight early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until passing 100M, closed off well to take a place.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead with rival on turn, headed approaching 250M, kept on well but lost two places near the finish. (See Racing Incidents.)

Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, dropped to midfield after passing 900M, 3 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Out in line, took the early lead, taken back approaching 1200M, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back in the middle stages, kept on well in straight but always held.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on outer, very wide into straight, made good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, slightly taken back 950M, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on turn, 2 wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced in midfield in the early stages, difficult to settle approaching 1200M, 2 wide behind midfield on turn, angled out 500M, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield early, difficult to settle 1150M, raced slightly better than midfield on outer in the middle stages, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, angled out 450M, made no impression in straight.

Average to begin, tracked leaders, 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back on turn, hard ridden from 350M, took the lead approaching 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 5 lengths back, 2 wide from 550M, same margin back turning in, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.
Jumped well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress, not quite able to challenge.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear, found rail 1000M, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, kept on same pace in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly. (Roarer.)
