Began awkwardly and bumped, raced in midfield, 2 wide, wider from 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped shortly after start, raced better than midfield but trapped wide, moved closer after passing 1050M, 2nd in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled just over 2L back in 4th, quickened well inside final 200M to take charge 100M out, won convincingly.
Attempted to make all, unable to sustain effort and swamped 100M out.
Slowly away, remained in last few despite ridden early, saved ground turning in for home, ran on to be nearest at finish despite inconvenienced 100M out.
Moderate start, settled in midfield on rail, baulked early in straight, produced late impression close to home.
Settled 2-wide in midfield after moderate start, ducked in away from whip just inside the 200M, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began smartly, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, travelled well to turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Chased leader in 3rd on rail, baulked for a run early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 200M.
Taken back gradually from a poor draw, remained well behind into straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track without quickening.
Settled behind midfield, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Very slowly away and trailed the field throughout despite ridden early.
Settled midfield, traveled okay, slightly held up entering the Straight, made some ground over the concluding stages.
Sat midfield 2 wide, lay in in the Home Straight, responded nicely when asked (Dropped right rein).
Sat in front of midfield, held up approaching 300M, showed some dash inside 100M.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, switching out rounding the Turn, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, raced greenly, steadied to avoid a runner near 100M, closed off okay.
Sat rear, raced rear, crowded near 100M, one pace to the finish.
Sat behind midfield, traveled fairly, weakened entering the Straight (Substantial blood in trachea).
Sat handy, traveled only fairly, no impression.
Ridden along to lead, weakened rounding the Turn, gave ground notable after 200M.
Sat handy on the rail, very limited response when asked, never a threat.
A bit keen in rear after dropped in from wide draw. Made good headway from 300m line to edge ahead final 50m and win cosily.
Tracked pacesetters. Smooth headway into contention and went to the front 150m out but unable to repel winner closing stages.
Mid-field until moving into contention from 300m line. Unable to quite match front 2 final 150m but stayed on for pressure.
Tracked leaders on rail from inside stall. Caught in a pocket from top of home straight and not clear until switched out at 200m line. Ran on.
Disputed lead until no extra final 150m.
Showed speed to lead narrowly from other pacesetter. Stayed in contention under pressure from 300m out until no extra final 150m.
Started well from widest stall but moved across behind runners after 150m and held up. Only moderate headway in home straight and never on terms.
Raced in mid-division and no impression under pressure from 400m line.
Raced wide without cover and never out of rear.
Minimal response to pressure after waited with and never involved.
A bit keen towards rear after slow start and dropped away in home straight.

Began well from a wide draw, taken back to race slightly behind midfield on outer, very wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, closed off well to take 2nd.

Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, made contact 250M, cleared 200M, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, travelled well to turn, hard ridden from 300M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 300M but only showed limited response, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 3 wide with cover towards rear, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Away well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 450M, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, one-paced thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on same pace to the line. (Epiglottic entrapment and a dorsal displacement of the soft palate.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, angled out 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Settled in front of midfield, switched out at 500M, quickened nicely once in the clear, ran on, won comfortably.
Raced in front of midfield 2 wide, under pressure from the 650M, took some time to respond, closed off nicely, no threat to winner.
Settled midfield 2 wide, stayed on nicely.
Tracked leader 2 wide, kept on nicely.
Ridden along early to lead, kicked clear top of the Straight, kept on until weakened final 100M. (Substantial blood)
Settled towards the rear, stayed on okay.
Sat behind the leader, lay in in the Straight, just one pace. (See Incident Report)
Sat last, limited response early in the Straight, stayed on late
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, blundered at 1300M, made no impression.
Caught 3 wide no cover on pace, weakened in the Straight.
Settled midfield on the rail, made no ground.
Raced towards the rear, never a threat.
Sat 3 wide midfield, weakened final furlong.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never in contention.
Settled within 2L of the pace off the stands rails, came to challenge inside the 300M and gained upper hand about 100M out.
Always thereabouts, hit the front from tiring leader 400M out, led until headed about 100M out.
Began well from a high draw near stands rail, gradually settled one back in joint 3rd, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening closing stages.
Broke well settling within 2L of the pace, came under pressure inside the 400M but unable to sustain effort after coming onto the course proper.
Slowly away, improved steadily to within 2L of pace in 6th about 600M out, came under pressure about 400M out, kept on at the one pace.
Gradually settled near last of the small field, kept on same pace without quickening.
Began well to lead, fading when headed inside 400M out. (Lame next day)
Just over 2L off the pace sharing 4th near stands rails, weakened under pressure out of contention inside final 400M.
Went forward and crossed to the lead 900M, kept on well turning home, was strongly challenged by rival from 200M and pulled out all the stops to hold on.
Settled down midfield, quickened up well to challenge for the lead mid-straight, fought hard to the line and was just denied in a driving finish.
Jumped only fairly, moved up to race in mid-division, chased leaders from 250M, had no room late and was not ridden out final 50M.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up towards the rear, closed off final 300M steadily to finish a pleasing 4th after a break of over 6 months.
Jumped on terms, tucked in to race behind leaders, steadied 500M, held up for clear running early straight but the finishing response was only modest.
Settled towards the rear, little change in position to the straight, stayed on final 400M without threat to the leaders.
Vied for lead early before taking a sit from 900M, found disappointingly little in the straight. (Jockey : raced too keenly early and middle stages when positioned outside the leader.)
Jumped only fairly, soon ended up at the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, still a fair way form leaders at 400M, couldn't quicken enough. Never in the picture.
Caught wide no cover in mid-division early before moving closer to leaders from 900M, had no extra 300M, weakened to last.

Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, challenged the leader early in straight, hit the front approaching 200M, kept on well to the line and scored. (Blood in trachea.)

Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, travelled comfortably on turn, challenged by rival early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 200M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.

Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, bumped and not enough room early in straight, cleared 300M, closed off strongly to take a place, nearest finish.

Began only fairly, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader, found rail after passing 700M, saved ground on turn, no clear run until final 150M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.

Made contact at start, taken back to race at rear on the inside, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, hung in and peaked near 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Average to begin, in touch, 2 wide, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, peaked on run 300M, weakened final furlong.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (Roarer.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced behind midfield on outer, no cover throughout, bumped early in straight, peaked 300M, weakened final 200M.
Bumped start, taken back to race at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 to 3 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, showed good response in straight, took the lead near 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Jumped with them, raced prominently but trapped very wide in the early stages, 2 wide from 800M, 3/4L back turning in, hit the front 300M, peaked and headed 100M, stayed on evenly to take a place.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out 500M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, no daylight early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, wider turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, took the early lead, headed approaching 1100M, positioned 3 wide, 1-1/2L back in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter.

Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 800M, angled out after passing 500M, not enough room early in straight, cleared 200M, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Made contact at start, raced prominently on the outside early, took the lead approaching 1100M, found rail 850M, led by 3/4L in the middle stages, peaked and headed 300M, weakened inside final furlong. (Bled.)
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross 850M, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Made contact with the right side of its barrier on jumping, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Slow into stride, settled towards rear, traveled smoothly, switched out on straightening, show some dash over the final 150M.

Settled in front of midfield, traveled okay, ran on evenly.

Sat in front of midfield, weakened notably approaching 800M, faded (Unacceptable Performance, Must BT).

Good headway from mid-field mid-race but no further impression on leaders final 100m.
Made running. Challenged by winner from 400m out and no extra final 200m.
Some headway into mid-field after held up but no further impression final 150m and never a danger.
In rear after awkward start. One paced under pressure from 400m out and never a danger.
A bit keen as he tracked leaders. Faded under pressure from 300m line.
Towards rear of mid-division. Never going pace to get involved from 300m out and little impression.
Held up and lost touch with main body of runners final 300m.
Recovered from sluggish start to race in mid-field but dropped away under pressure from 400m line.

Clean jump, raced better than midfield, 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed very good response, took the lead 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Began well from gate 9, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 150M, finished 2nd.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (Lost left front plate.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly thereafter.

Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail near 700M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Jumped well, sent to the front, travelled smoothly throughout, kept on well to the line, just held on.
Taken back towards the rear, had trouble obtaining clear run for the majority of the Straight, closed off strongly once in the clear, just missed.
Sat outside the leader, kept on nicely for 3rd.
Hard ridden to sit behind the leaders, one pace to the line.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide with cover, stayed on late.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Caught 3 wide no cover, limited response in the Straight.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, made little impression.
Jumped slow, settled midfield on the rail, lay in in the Straight, never seriously tested.
Settled at the rear, never a threat.
Settled 3 wide midfield, weakened in the Straight.
Caught 4 wide no cover, weakened and faded in the Straight.
Began only fairly from a low draw, soon took up running narrowly obtaining stands rails run over 600M out, just held off runner-up's strong late challenge.
Settled just off the pace on stands rails after beginning from a high draw near stands side, fought on well inside final 300M to just fail to get up on line.
Tightened at start settling in midfield near stands rails, tight between runners over 150M out, quickened well to snatch 3rd final strides.
Jumped awkwardly and had to be straightened, came to join the leaders over 700M out, looked tiring at about 200M out but kept on well to the line.
Broke well gradually settled just off the pace near stands rails, came under pressure coming onto course proper, fought on to take 5th, finished just behind 3rd and 4th .
Restrained in last few, switched in towards the centre of the track for a clear run over 200M out, responded well inside the 150M but unable to sustain effort final strides.
Settled near midfield just over 2L off the pace near stands rails, produced good late impression inside final 100M.
Inconvenienced at start from a low draw, gradually recovered to within 2L of the pace near the centre of the track, faded under pressure inside final 150M.
Settled in last few, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Always in last few, ran on well past well-beaten horses inside final 100M.
Gradually settled just worse than midfield, came under pressure coming onto course proper, found nothing.
Crowded early stages before travelling keenly in worse than midfield, faded steadily inside final 200M after travelling without cover near the centre of track from 600M out.
Travelled in forward of midfield, raced keenly coming onto course proper, weakened inside final 100M.
Settled in last few, found nothing under pressure inside final 400M.
Sat prominently behind leaders, travelled strongly into straight and quickly took over the lead 300M, continued on well final stages for a comfortable victory.
Jumped on terms, settled ahead of midfield, 3-wide no cover from 650M, chased hard final 300M but couldn't get closer to the winner.
Held up in mid-division, had difficulty obtaining clear running early straight then ran home steadily under top weight to take 3rd. No threat to runaway winner.
From wide draw ended up racing 3-wide towards the rear, shifted out abruptly 400M to avoid the heels of a rival before closing off the race mildly. Got up for non-threatening 4th near line.
From draw 1 maintained a midfield position along the fence, not far off from leaders over the turn but then only worked home fairly final 400M.
Caught racing wide no cover in midfield, couldn't go on with leaders passing 400M and never posed serious threat
Crowded on jumping, settled towards the rear further back than intended, couldn't quicken enough final 400M, never threatened.
Emerged as leader passing 1100M, caught near 300M, no extra towards the line.
From draw 12 moved up to track leader, fought hard to keep up with rivals early straight but couldn't sustain run 250M, drifted out of contention.
Away with them, settled in 4th never far off leaders, lacked a finishing response when asked early straight, weakened final 200M.
Drifted back to race towards the rear along the inside, found nothing when asked 400M, never involved.
Restrained on jumping from draw 10, gradually dropped back to near last, had plenty to do 400M but couldn't make any progress.
Taken back to last from wide draw, settled 7-8Ls off the pace middle stages, couldn't keep up on straightening, never in the picture.
Made contact at start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, challenged the leader early in straight, took the lead 300M, kept on well to the line, just able to hold off the challenger late.
Began only fairly and made contact, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, no clear run 250M to 75M, finished off well to be nearest on line.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked on turn, weakened final 300M.
Away well, tracked leaders on the inside, 2 wide turning in, hit the front near 250M, kept on strongly to the line, won comfortably.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear in early stages, found a 2 wide spot shortly after entering the back straight, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Moderately away from gate 9, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, took the lead 600M, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final 100M.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, ran on evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide in the middle stages, not enough room until final 100M, showed some response thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in the run home.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 600M, 1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, something amiss and eased near 600M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, finished off well to score by a head.

Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, commenced move 800M, took the lead near 700M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.

Taken back to race at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 3 to 4 lengths back in the middle stages, commenced move 550M, very wide turning in, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 700M, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail early, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Reared as stalls opened and started slowly, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 4 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at rear on the outside, 5 lengths back, found rail near 550M, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away on terms, settled in second half of the field, quickened up well on straightening, swept to the lead final stages to win going away.
Shifted in abruptly on jumping, raced handily behind the runaway leader, worked into the race well inside 300M but unable to hold off the fast finishing winner final stages.
Unable to slot in from draw 9, maintained a midfield spot but raced wide and without cover to the straight, kept on steadily under top weight but not going the pace of first two final stages.
Prominent as always, chased runaway leader, stuck to task fairly well early straight before out-finished by first two late stages, just missed out 3rd spot.
Maintained a midfield position along the inside, ran home one paced and never able to challenge leaders.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards the rear, swung wide for home before staying on fairly over final 300M. Never dangerous.
Away with them, restrained to a midfield position, 4-5Ls to make up on leader 400M but found disappointingly little. (Jockey reported his horse lay out throughout the race / Mucus.)
Settled towards the rear, pushed along nearing 400M but lacked a finishing response.
Rushed forward from wide draw, opened up a sizable lead middle stages, couldn't last passing 200M, weakened rapidly final stages.
Jumped only fairly, ended up racing in last, failed to respond on straightening. Never in the picture.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled smoothly, responded very well when asked, impressive.
Sat rear, improved passing 450M, no clear run until 100M, stayed on well.
Settled behind midfield, traveled nicely, made some ground in the Straight, closed off okay.
Jumped awkwardly, settled midfield, ran on evenly.
Sat midfield, made the turn wide, lost ground, closed off fairly.
Ridden hard to lead, traveled okay, weakened inside 200M (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear, stayed on steadily.
Settled worse than midfield, traveled only fairly no impression made.
Sat handy, traveled okay, limited response when asked (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, had difficulty obtaining clear running until 100M, never a factor.
Sat handy, gave ground notably passing 200M, never a danger.
Bounded and made contact with the barrier as the start was effected, lost ground, settled rear, never a threat.
Tracked clear leader. Quickened past that rival to lead 150m out and soon clear, winning readily.
Tracked pace. Lacked speed to challenge winner final 150m but stuck to task to take second late on.
Dropped in after slowly into stride from outside stall. Finished off strongly through field and almost got up for second.
Hurried along from stalls to lead and set good pace. Headed and no extra from 150m line, losing two places late.
Held up. Pushed along into home straight and kept on steadily after angled wide.
Kept on steadily from mid-field but never going pace to challenge.
One paced under pressure after racing in mid-division and never a danger home straight.
Raced in rear of mid-field. Just moderate headway under pressure home straight and never threatened.
Held up. Failed to get clearest of runs final 150m when trying to make ground and never on terms.
Raced in last after taken back from wide draw and never a factor.
Recovered from sluggish start to race in mid-field but weakened under pressure from over 200m out.
Well placed into home straight after tracking pace but weakened final 200m.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move 450M, wide into straight, finished off strongly to score.
Away well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, commenced move 400M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just beaten by a narrow margin. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced prominently on the outside, challenged the leader turning in, kept on very well in straight, just beaten by a neck.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rivals turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few final 50M.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 400M, kept on well early in straight, no clear run final 150M.
Jumped awkwardly, taken back to race at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, nearest finish.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced a tail, 6 lengths back on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared near 200M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, angled out 400M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, no clear run final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped nicely, settled worse than midfield 2 wide, switched to 3 wide from 600M, angled out round the Home Turn, ran on strongly despite laying in, easily.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, kept on nicely for 2nd.
Sat on pace 2 wide, ran on okay.
Raced behind midfield on the rail, stayed on okay.
Sat midfield 2 wide, ran on only evenly.
Settled towards the rear, made some late ground, closest finish.
Sat last, stayed on fairly.
Tracked leader 2 wide, weakened in the Straight.
Settled in front of midfield, one pace to the line. (See Incident Report)
Sat towards the rear, made no impression
Sat behind the leaders, limited response in the Straight.
Ridden along to lead, weakened and faded in the Straight. (Performance disappointing, must trial)
Settled over 2L off the pace in 4th, became 5th in a similar position about 900M out, commenced move between runners turning into straight, fought on dourly to gain upper hand close to home.
Pressed forward from a poor draw for 2-wide prominent position, gained 2nd turning into back straight, hit the front over 200M out only to be caught final strides.
Settled just worse than midfield, came to challenge under pressure into straight, ran on dourly to reach 3rd late.
Missed the break settling well behind, commenced move and very wide into home straight, produced good late impression inside final 200M.
Well there early stages before settling wide in midfield, one of the widest turning in for home, held place chance under pressure the length of the straight only to be denied 50M out.
Settled in forward of midfield, in similar position into straight, baulked for a run early in straight and unable to sustain effort inside final 100M.
Settled in last few, came under pressure rounding home bend, produced good late impression final stages.
Settled in last few, commenced move rounding home bend and the widest into straight, hung in a difficult ride early in straight and made no impression thereafter.

Gradually settled from a poor draw in better than midfield in 5th, gained slightly closer to 4th 3-wide without cover about 900M out reaching 3rd briefly home bend, inconvenienced on straightening and soon weakened.
Lost considerable ground at start, remained well behind throughout, weakened into home straight.
Shared early pace before restrained for cover on rail about 1100M out, remained close up until finding no extra shortly after straightening.
Pressed forward from the widest draw to take up running passing the winning post the first time, obtained rails run about 1100M out, led until weakened shortly after straightening.
Smoothly away from draw 1, had a perfect run tracking leader on inside, quickened up nicely to take lead nearing 200M, continued on strongly final stages for a comfortable win.
On jumping was bumped heavily by rival, soon improved to the lead taking them along at a steady pace, caught by winner nearing 200M, held on for 2nd despite weakening late.
Given a patient ride, restrained behind midfield along the 3-path, wide on straightening, worked home well to take 3rd close home.
Dropped back on jumping from wide draw, settled near last 5-6Ls off leader, swung widest into straight before staying on well to take 4th in a photo finish.
Away well, maintained a position behind midfield, kept on steadily final 300M but couldn't quicken enough to challenge leaders. Lost 4th in a photo finish.
From draw 12 obtained a 3-wide spot in midfield, raced keenly middle stages, lay in in the home straight and finished off only fairly.
Began well but soon restrained to a position ahead of midfield, fought on one paced in the straight and posed little threat to leaders.
Not hurried after the jump, restrained in a rearward position along the inside, ran to the line only fairly under top weight. (Jockey - did not travel as strongly as it did last start.)
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, recovered to race in midfield along the fence, lacked a finishing response turning home, never a danger.
Jumped very awkwardly and lost ground, raced as the back marker throughout, couldn't go on final 300M. Never in the picture.
Jumped on terms, moved up to track leader, under pressure home turn, couldn't sustain run passing 250M, faded towards the line.
From draw 9 unable to slot in, chased leaders in a 3-wide spot without cover, gave ground from 250M, weakened to last.

Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, unable to obtain clear run until approaching final 100M, finished off very strongly, led close home.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 3 wide with cover, 2-1/2L back, there to turn, finished off strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, hard ridden 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Began fairly, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, finished off strongly, nearest finish.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 10, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover throughout, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out after passing 500M, 4 lengths back turning in, made some progress in the run home.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, there to turn, hard ridden approaching 300M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, found rail 600M, same margin back turning in, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, tracked leaders, 3 wide, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Slowly away, gradually recovered to some 6L back in 6th on the rail, gained closer rounding home bend into straight, quickened well to assert authority over 100M out.
Settled in last few, came to challenge under pressure upon straightening, ran on well under pressure to snatch 2nd close to home.
Gradually settled in 5th or 4th in the middle of the small field, commenced move passing the 500M, fought on steadily under pressure to reach 3rd late.
Settled at the back and waited with, switched off rail for a run upon straightening, ran on between runners to be nearest at finish.
Began well from a poor draw gradually settling just off the pace in 2nd on rail, shared lead early in straight hitting the front briefly at about the 200M, soon found no extra.
Began fairly and ridden early settling some 4L back in joint 4th on rail, commenced move switching out for a run 500M out, one-paced without quickening under pressure in straight.
Prominent in 3rd, switched off the rail to challenge passing the 700M, held some chance briefly 300M out and soon weakened.
Soon took up running, led by over 1L to home straight, weakened out of contention inside final 300M.
Sat handy on the rail, traveled comfortably, made good ground inside 200M.
Jumped only fairly, settled midfield, switched out rounding the Turn, made steady progress in the Straight.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened approaching 300M, closed off okay (See Incident Report).
Sat handy, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, tracked leader, weakened passing 200M.
Settled rear, raced rear, improved rounding the turn, minor progress made.
Sat behind midfield, traveled fairly, limited response when asked.
Sat worse than midfield, switched out rounding the Turn, no impression.
Settled midfield, raced wide from 1100M, left without a finishing effort (See Incident Report).
Waited with in mid-field. Steady headway from 400m out and led on line.
Prominent but wide from high draw. Every chance from top of home straight but pipped by winner final strides.
Raced in mid-field. Improved to challenge from 200m line and every chance in tight finish.
Never far away and kept going under pressure from 400m out.
In rear after slow into stride. Still in last pair turning into home straight before sustained headway down the outside and not beaten far.
Tracked leading bunch. Maintained position under pressure but unable to quicken sufficiently to challenge.
Raced in mid-field from high draw. Keeping on when short of room and jockey forced to ease final 50m.
Raced in mid-division against rail. Angled out to make headway in home straight but carried head awkwardly and one paced when short of room 200m out. Limited impression after.
Raced prominently after fast start but faded in home straight.
Held up and still last turning into home straight. Made some headway but never on terms.
Waited with from high draw. Minimal headway when short of room 200m out and again closing stages.
Held up after rousted along early and never involved.
Led until headed and weakened from 200m out.
Never out of rear after sluggish start.
Quickly into stride, showed good speed to take the early lead, headed 900M, 2nd on turn, retook the lead 450M, kept on very well in straight, won by 2-1/4L.
Began smartly, positioned 1-3/4L behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 600M, bumped 500M, 2 lengths back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned slightly better than midfield on the outside, carried wider 600M, 2-1/2L back turning in, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out approaching 500M, very wide into straight, kept on evenly in the run home.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Taken back to race 3 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, very wide turning in, made minor progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back, same margin back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 450M, made minor progress early in straight, no clear run near 250M, cleared 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, positioned 3 wide with cover, 3-1/2L back, carried wider 500M, very wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, showed no early speed, taken back to race at rear, 6 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, 2 wide from 850M, bumped 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped only fairly from a wide draw, raced slightly better than midfield but trapped very wide early, sent forward 1000M, took the lead 900M, headed 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened 300M.
Settled few lengths behind the leading group, improved into the race smoothly from 800M, slightly held up top of the Straight, closed off nicely once in the clear, comfortably.
Caught 3 wide with cover midfield, checked at 800M, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Caught 4 wide early on pace, kept on okay for 3rd.
Settled towards the rear, stayed on.
Settled midfield 2 wide, showed some dash from 350M to 200M, one pace after. (See Incident Report)
Hard ridden early, caught 3 wide no cover on pace, limited response in the Straight.
Sat midfield on the rail, took some time to respond, made some late ground.
Ridden along early to lead, weakened final furlong. (See Incident Report)
Sat towards the rear, made no impression.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, raced keenly in the middle stages, nothing in the Straight.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, never a factor.
Sat outside the lead, weakened and faded in the Straight. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Sat box seat, under pressure from 600M, gave ground quickly. (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Slow to jump, always at rear, never in contention. (See Incident Report) (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Settled in last few after moderate start dropping to last briefly over 1200M out, commenced move 3-wide home bend, responded well inside final 200M to hit the front over 100M out.

Restrained off the pace and travelled wide without cover most of the way about 3L off the pace in 4th or 5th, commenced move home bend reaching close-up 3rd into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Soon gained narrow lead from the widest draw, gradually taken back 2-wide to travel alongside race leader, re-gained advantage inside the 500M only to be headed over 200M out.
Well back early, made headway from the 1200M to reach 5th briefly just over 3L back on rail, angled out for a run upon straightening but baulked until over 150M out, made up some last ground.
Began fairly, made steady headway along the rail to reach 2L 3rd on rail 1000M out, chased leaders into straight and baulked behind runners most of the way until the 100M.
Improved steadily from moderate start to take up running at about 1300M out, led keenly in front until narrowly headed into straight, hung on under pressure until finding no extra inside final 150M.
Broke well but taken back to 3rd 2-wide just off the pace, became 2L 4th at about 1000M out and 5th on top of home bend, hampered and lost position over 300M out before recovered some ground late.
Began fairly gradually settling over 3L back in 6th, slightly further back in 7th rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped well behind and never seen with a chance.
Bumped shortly after the start, given a waiting ride behind midfield, loomed behind leaders mid-straight before unleashing a good turn of foot to wrestle the lead close home.
Bumped shortly after the start, restrained in mid-division, worked into the race nicely 400M, quickened past leader mid-straight, just couldn't hold off winner late stages.
Caught wide early stages then strode forward to take up running, set steady pace to straight then responded well when placed under pressure, all out but couldn't hold off first two late stages.
Jumped only fairly from draw 1, settled down in midfield along the fence, held up 400M-300M, was making progress when denied clear running 100M-50M. Could have done better.
Unable to slot in after the start, pushed along 1000M to be chasing leaders 3-wide without cover, fought on one-paced in the straight, no match for leaders final 200M.
Taken back after the start, reserved near last 6Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly final 400M but never looked likely.
Chased leader 2-wide, kept up with leaders early straight but couldn't sustain run passing 200M, faded to 7th.
From inside draw took up a more forward position than usual, tracked leaders into straight, lacked a finishing response inside 400M, eased when crowded for room late stages.
Failed to show sufficient pace to hold a more forward position, settled in midfield and caught racing wide no cover from 1000M, worked home fairly final 400M. No threat to leaders.
Jumped only fairly, ended up racing towards the rear along the fence, couldn't quicken enough on straightening, no impression on leaders.
From wide draw drifted back to race towards the rear, caught wide making the home turn, failed to make much impression on straightening. Never a threat
Jumped awkwardly, settled 3-wide behind midfield, kept on fairly final 400M, couldn't launch a serious challenge.
Began well, chased leader on settling, couldn't go on passing 300M, weakened towards the line.
Dropped back to race at the rear, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, found nothing on straightening. Never in the picture.
Away well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1200M, positioned 3rd in the middle stages, 3 wide turning in, hit the front 250M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide with no cover better than midfield, carried wider after passing 600M, 1-1/2L back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, finished off strongly to take a place.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Jumped only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, kept on well in straight, not enough room final 75M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, wider turning in, kept on well in straight, short of room final 50M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, closer in the middle stages, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Slowly away, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Shifted in at start, taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home without threatening.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced better than midfield but trapped wide, sent forward 1000M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, made no progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 1200M, led by a length turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened final 100M.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 3/4L back turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, found rail approaching 700M, led by 3/4L turning in, challenged by rival early in straight, headed 200M, stayed on well to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Took keen hold, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Began well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Taken back from gate 13, raced towards rear on outer, 4 lengths or so back turning in, closed off well to be nearest on line.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out after passing 550M, made some headway in straight.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, made no progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 wide in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, travelled keenly 600M, 3 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, detached 700M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, wider 400M, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Out fast to lead and in control after quickening two lengths clear at 200m line. Eased closing stages.
Tight for room briefly at halfway after settled in mid-field. Ran on well from 200m out to get close but never a danger to eased-down winner.
Raced on the inside from stall 1. Chased winner from top of straight but no extra and lost second final 100m.
Raced wide in mid-division from stall 10. Under pressure turning in but responded to keep on for never-dangerous fourth.
Held up from high draw. Stayed on for pressure but never a threat.
Tracked pace. Unable to quicken and one paced from 300m line.
Crowded briefly at start and raced in rear. Some headway but never on terms.
Raced in rear after slow start and never dangerous despite a clear run up rail in home straight.
Tracked leader but unable to hold position from over 200m out and weakened.
Raced wide without cover and no impression under pressure home straight.
Tracked pace in wide position. Weakened from 300m line and well held.
Sat handy, traveled comfortably, kept on well to win.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, made some progress over the concluding stages.
Crowded shortly after the start, settled towards rear, held up rounding the Turn until near 350M, ran on evenly.
Chased the leader, made minor progress in the Straight, one pace to the finish.
Jumped only fairly, ridden along to lead, weakened entering the Straight, closed off okay.
Settled towards rear, traveled okay, made steady progress over the concluding stages.
Sat midfield, traveled fairly, not much impression.
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, raced keenly in the early and middle stages, closed off only fairly (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, raced ungenerously, bumped on a number of occasions in the Straight, never a threat.
Sat midfield, weakened notably entering the Straight, never a danger.
Jumped awkwardly, sat midfield, raced wide when improved from 600M, gave ground quickly in the Straight.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide and without cover, weakened rounding the Turn, faded.
Set good pace and made all. Lead reduced closing stages but held on.
Towards rear of mid-field after sluggish start. Angled out in home straight and finished off strongly to get close to winner late on.
Tracked leader from low draw. Stuck to task under pressure from 200m out but never quite able to get to winner.
Recovered from slow start to race in mid-field. One paced under pressure from top of home straight and unable to challenge.
Broke well and tracked leader. Kept on under pressure from over 200m out but lacked speed to challenge.
Tracked pace. Unable to quicken and one paced home straight.
Held up. Some headway into mid-field final 200m but never on terms.
Widest into home straight from high draw and only moderate headway from rear. Never dangerous.
Raced wide from high draw. Forward move in back straight but lost place under pressure on bend and held from there.
Restrained in rear early and keen. No impression under pressure from 200m line.
Raced in last and niggled along back straight. No impression under firmer pressure from over 200m out.
Started to lose mid-field position from just after halfway and dropped away.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail 450M, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, found rail approaching 800M, angled out 350M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, closed off well to take a place.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 900M, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away well, raced slightly better than midfield on outer, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Took keen hold, tracked leaders, 2 wide, angled out 400M, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked early in straight, headed approaching 150M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced towards rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths back turning in, made no impression in the run home.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 1/2L back turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened quickly and eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened final furlong.
Raced 3 wide no cover on pace, kept on nicely to score
Settled towards the rear 3 wide after blundering at the start, stayed on well.
Settled midfield 3 wide, ran on okay.
Raced in midfield 2 wide, stayed on fairly.
Settled just behind the leaders, kept on only fairly.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Not the quickest out, sat last, went inside, no clear run until 200M, made some late ground.
Settled midfield on the rail, held up for the majority of the Straight, never seriously tested.
Slow to begin, settled towards the rear, held up early in the Straight, made some ground late.
Sat outside the leader, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Showed good early speed to lead, weakened in the Straight.
Settled near the rear, never a threat.
Jumped awkwardly settling well behind and waited with, came under pressure from home bend swinging one of the widest into straight, responded well inside final 150M to snatch victory final strides.
Settled in rear of midfield in 7th, came to challenge under pressure over 400M out, quickened well to hit the front 100M out only to be caught final strides.
Settled behind midfield in 9th after moderate start, came to challenge under pressure inside final 400M on top of home bend, ran on well to be nearest at finish.

Taken back from 3-wide onto first bend to settle some 4L back 2-wide in 5th, came to challenge under pressure but tight between runners early in straight, fought on steadily to narrowly miss a placing.
Settled some 3L back in 4th on rail, commenced move under pressure 450M out, held place chance about 1L off the leaders early in straight but unable to quicken to threaten.

Pressed forward to first few before settling one back on rail, switched 2-wide 700M out, commenced move rounding home bend hitting the front into straight but unable to sustain effort and overhauled 100M out.
Settled towards rear on rail, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, fought on steadily without threatening, baulked late.
Settled 2L back in 3rd, came under pressure rounding home bend swinging wide into straight, held place chance early on but swamped inside final 50M.
Settled in midfield in 6th from a poor draw, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, did not find much room in straight and steadied behind runners inside final 150M.
Took up running 1300M out turning onto stables bend, set fast pace and led until headed into straight, faded under pressure inside the 150M.
Always in last few, never nearer.
Always in last few, never seen with a chance.
Settled behind midfield along the fence, loomed behind leaders top of straight but was held up 200M before shifting out 150M to secure clear running, flew home to get up just in time.
Sent forward, tracked leader into straight, responded strongly to wrestle the lead 150M, just couldn't hold off winner late.
Bumped on jumping, raced wide no cover in midfield, moved closer to leaders home turn, responded well early straight, bumped 150M by rival before staying on strongly to take 3rd.
Bumped at the start, waited with at the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, switched to wide outside on straightening, closed off fastest to be beaten 0.5L in a busy finish.

Given a waiting ride at the rear, improved position passing 550M, swung widest into straight before running on well under top weight, nearest finish. (Jockey had difficulty in fully testing his mount over final 100M when it shifted in.)
Away quickly from draw 1, stayed close to leaders, shifted away from fence 400M to challenge, ran home mildly to get 6th in a busy finish.
Maintained a midfield position 3-4Ls off the pace, closed off steadily final 300M to be not beaten far at the line, placed 7th in a busy finish.
Caught wide from draw 11, quickly moved up and crossed to the lead, led them to 150M then emptied and weakened towards the line.
Always prominent behind leaders, couldn't quicken top of straight, soon out of contention.
Bumped at the start, settled down behind midfield, came under serious pressure to hold position 450M, failed to run on in the straight.

Jumped on terms, moved up to race just off the pace, couldn't sustain run inside 250M, faded towards the line. (Jockey : raced keenly with blinkers first time and as a result settled outside the lead.)

From wide draw dropped back to race towards the rear, didn't respond to riding passing 400M. Never in the picture. (Jockey could offer no excuse for his mount's failure to run on in the Home Straight / Mucus.)

Shifted out at start, raced better than midfield on the inside, easy run to turn, angled out 450M, took the lead approaching 200M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out 650M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home to take 2nd, no threat to the winner. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover towards rear, moved a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 500M, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Moderately away from gate 11, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, challenged the leader turning in, peaked on run 250M, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Slightly inconvenienced at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 500M, showed limited response early in straight, not enough room near 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (Roarer.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced at rear on the outside, 9 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Taken back from gate 12, raced in midfield on outer, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked and crowded early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped shortly after the start, moved up to race handily behind leaders, poised to strike top of straight then lengthened nicely to lead 250M, soon in control winning it handsomely.
Urged along to be 4th chasing leaders, 4th on settling, driven 400M to chase eventual winner but couldn't get closer final 200M.
From draw 1 maintained a midfield spot along the inside, little change in position to the straight then ran on mildly to fill a minor placing. No threat to first two.
Switched off to the rear on jumping from draw 11, plenty to do top of straight, closed off fastest final 400M, got up for non-threatening 4th close home.
From draw 14 strode to the lead as expected, kept going top of straight, caught by winner near 250M, faded towards the line.
Slow to begin, taken across to the fence and settled in a rearward position, made non-threatening progress passing 400M, raced in restricted room late stages and not able to be fully tested.
Away with them, raced towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, held up 400M to 200M before making some late progress. Could do better.
Jumped only fairly, gradually improved to a position behind midfield, ran home fairly final 400M.
Dropped back to near the rear, wide into straight, gave short-lived effort early straight then failed to run on final 200M. (Trainer could offer no explanation for the disappointing performance.)
Settled down in midfield, hard pressed 500M to maintain his position, couldn't go on final 300M.
Jumped on terms, reserved behind mid-division 5-6Ls away, failed to finish off the race under top weight. Never troubled leaders.
Reserved behind midfield but caught 3-wide without cover for the majority of the race, gave limited response on straightening. Never in the picture.
Bumped shortly after the start, went forward from draw 13 to press the pace, run ended 250M then dropped out rapidly.
Restrained after the start, raced keenly in middle stages, in the rear 9Ls off leader making home turn, couldn't quicken.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled smoothly, switched out rounding the Turn, stayed on well to the line.
Settled midfield, raced on the rail, obtained clear running near 250M, made good progress thereafter.
Sat midfield, angled out at the Turn, responded nicely when asked.
Sat handy, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled fairly, awkwardly placed on heels at 150M, one pace to the finish.
Ridden along to lead, lay in inside 200M, closed off fairly.
Sat towards rear, made minor ground in the Straight, ran on fairly.
Jumped only fairly, sat in front of midfield, slightly weakened on straightening.
Tracked leader, gave ground quickly inside 150M (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, raced rear, failed to respond (See Incident Report, Must BT).
Sat worse than midfield, limited response when asked, no impression.
Sat midfield, switched out rounding the Turn, weakened and faded thereafter (See Incident Report, Heart irregularity, Must BT).
Sat towards rear, weakened notably rounding the Turn, eased down at the Straight (Bled).
Dropped in from high draw. Still had ground to make up on leaders at 200m line but quickened to get up on line. Did well.
Tracked clear leader. Responded to pressure to reel in that rival late on but pipped by winner on line.
Out fast to make running and set good pace in a clear lead. Still in front 100m out but reeled back closing stages.
Wide early from high draw but worked across to track clear leader. Stuck to task for long way and never far away but no extra closing stages.
Raced in mid-field. Stayed on for pressure home straight but lacked the speed to challenge.
Recovered from slow start to race in mid-field. Stayed on but one paced and unable to challenge.
Mid-field after briefly crowded at start. One paced under pressure from top of home straight and never involved.
Towards rear after hampered at start. Some late headway under pressure but never a danger.
Tracked pace on rail until weakening final 200m.
In touch but failed to respond to pressure from 300m line and weakened.
Dropped in from high draw and outpaced until passing some tiring rivals final 200m.
Raced wide towards rear of mid-field and lost ground home straight.
Held up. Hampered briefly 350m out and never involved.
Towards rear after slow start. No response to pressure from 400m out and eased after dropping away.
Taken back from gate 9, raced towards rear, 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Jumped well from gate 12, unable to slot in, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, carried wider 450M, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, last turning in, 5 lengths back at 400M, unable to obtain clear run until approaching final 100M, finished off well to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 1/4L back on turn, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run until 150M, made no impression thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made no progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/4L turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, closed off nicely to score.
Settled midfield on the rail, stayed on well, closest finish.
Raced in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Tracked leader, hit the front near 300M, kept on until weakened final 75M.
Settled at the rear 2 wide, stayed on.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, closed off fairly.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made ground in the Straight.
Sat on pace, one pace to the line.
Sat midfield 2 wide, stayed on fairly.
Ridden along early to lead, weakened final furlong.
Sat last, made no impression. (Roarer) (See Incident Report)
Raced towards the rear on the rail, never a threat.
Settled behind the leaders, weakened in the Straight.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, never in contention.
Crowded at start, ridden to share early pace, gradually taken one out one back to 3rd 1000M out, cantered to lead over 200M out, won comfortably.
Taken back to last from the widest gate and waited with, snuck up on rail early in straight, angled out to continue run inside the 300M, sustained significant progress to reach 2nd 50M out.
Ridden positively to eventually take up narrow running on the rail 950M out, led until finding no extra 200M out.
Jumped well from a poor draw, taken back for cover in 5th over 1000M out some 3L off the pace, in similar position home bend, kept on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Began well from a poor draw and gradually taken back to last few in 10th, ran on under pressure near the centre of the straight without threatening.
Slightly slow out settling just worse than midfield on rail in 9th, soon came to challenge after straightening, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Began fairly settling in last few, briefly baulked early in straight, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Vied for lead early before settling in 2nd alongside race leader, weakened steadily inside final 300M.
Ridden early but soon dropped to midfield in 6th on rail, found nothing under pressure after straightening.
Began well before taken over 2L back in 4th on rail, gained closer when on heels of race leader early in straight, found no extra inside final 200M.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground settling just worse than midfield in 8th 2-wide, switched out to challenge after straightening but soon weakened out of contention 200M out.
Soon dropped to last few, trailed the field from over 500M out, made no impression in straight.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield, lost position turning into straight and weakened further under pressure shortly afterwards.
From draw 12 moved up to track leader 2-wide, travelled strongly leaving the bend, quickened to lead 250M then kicked away for a comfortable victory.
Away well from draw 1, stayed close to leaders throughout, raced tight 300M when trying to get through between rivals, finished off nicely but no match for the unbeaten winner.
Jumped awkwardly, restrained in mid-division along the fence, raced keenly 900M, held up clear running early straight before running on steadily towards the finish, got up for 3rd late.
Quickly away taking up the lead, kept battling under top weight early straight, headed 250M, faded towards the finish, lost 3rd late.
From widest barrier managed to obtain a midfield position along the 2-path, kept on evenly over final 300M for a modest 5th.
Taken back to a rearward spot on jumping from wide draw, had some work to do top of straight, stayed on final 400M but not posing serious threat.
Hard pressed leaving the stalls to be tracking leader along the fence, fought on one paced in the straight, always held by leaders.
Began well, strode forward to avoid racing wide, settled in 4th more forward than anticipated, only held his ground early straight, got outpaced final 200M.
Ended up racing 3-wide behind midfield, no cover from 800M, not going the pace to challenge on straightening. Made no impression on his seasonal return.
Jumped only fairly, reserved behind midfield, gave limited response on straightening. Never threatened.
Settled down in the 2nd half of the field, hard driven 500M, couldn't keep up with leaders from 300M.
From wide draw switched off to race at the rear, had over 6Ls to make up 400M, couldn't go on.
Lacked early pace, ended up racing near last, weakened and detached from the field 400M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out approaching 500M, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (Dead-heat 2nd)
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, finished off strongly, nearest finish. (Dead-heat 2nd)
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, 1/2L back turning in, led narrowly approaching 100M, peaked and headed 50M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away well, tracked leaders, 3 wide turning in, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Blundered on jumping, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, wider on turn, no clear run until final 100M, kept on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly, eased final 75M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover from 900M, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 550M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Shifted in at start, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well without threatening the winner.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped only fairly, raced 3 wide in midfield, moved closer on turn, 4 wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.

Awkward leaving stalls and started very slowly, raced at rear, 8 lengths back in the middle stages, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead after passing 1200M, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened inside final furlong.
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on outer, very wide turning in, one-paced in the run home.

Jumped well, took the early lead, headed after passing 1200M, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, tracked leaders, 3 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Placing: UR
Comment: Began only fairly and bumped, stumbled and unseated rider near 800M. (See Racing Incidents.)
