Out with rest, raced better than midfield on the outside, commenced move 500M, took the lead 400M, kept on very well in straight, won by 1-1/2L.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide approaching 800M, moved closer on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, 3-1/2L back turning in, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 400M, no daylight run early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off evenly.
Began smartly, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, angled out 450M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left hind leg next day morning.)
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, shared lead with rival from 650M, peaked and headed 400M, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed no response in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, shared lead 600M, peaked and headed 450M, weakened early in straight, eased thereafter. (Bled.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well before taken about 1L back to 4th or 3rd, slightly further away from the pace onto home bend travelling 3-wide, ran on under pressure to gain upper hand about 50M out.
Gradually drifted backward towards the rear in 9th despite niggling along, commenced move under pressure from over 800M out, ran on well from well back in 10th into straight to be nearest at finish.
Began well from the widest stall and soon taken back behind midfield in 8th 3-wide without cover, switched out for a run after straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.

Ridden to lead after moderate start, narrowly headed 850M out drifting over 2L back around the bend, kept on in straight hitting the front briefly from tiring race leader 100M out, swamped close to home.

Soon ridden to just over 2L back in 5th, gradually drifted backward to over 4L behind in 7th 700M out, saved ground turning in for home on the inside, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.

Began moderately, improved steadily to take up running 3-wide 850M out, kicked some 3L clear rounding home bend, remained similar early in straight but unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 180M.
Amongst leaders early stages holding handy position until drifting some 3L back around the bend, made no impression in the straight.

Jumped awkwardly losing considerable ground, soon recovered to join the rear of field, gained slightly closer to 10th rounding home bend, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Travelled wide without cover in forward of midfield, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Began moderately, gradually recovered to mid-division of compact field in early stages, saved ground on rail turning in for home, found nothing under pressure.
Broke well from a poor draw, keen when taken back early stages, remained in last few and wide throughout dropping to last rounding home bend.
Jumped awkwardly losing consideration ground, always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, raced wide rounding the Turn, showed some dash over the concluding stages.
Ridden along to lead, traveled strongly, worked home nicely.
Settled midfield, traveled nicely, switched out rounding the Turn, made good ground in the Straight.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, one pace to the finish.
Tracked leader, weakened passing 300M, kept on fairly.
Sat rear, switched out rounding the Turn, minor progress made when asked.
Sat towards rear, weakened entering the Straight (See Incident Report, Substantial blood in trachea, Disappointing Performance, Must BT).
Sat worse than midfield, raced wide from 1100M to chase the lead, failed to finish off (See incident Report).
Sat rear, traveled fairly, limited response when asked (See Incident Report, Substantial blood in trachea).
Settled in front of midfield, gave ground before the Turn, no contention (Unacceptable Performance, Must BT).
Tracked leader. Pushed along and lost place going into final bend but picked up strongly once switched off rail. Led 150m out and well on top at line.
Raced in mid-field. Good headway to lead briefly 200m out but soon found winner too strong. Held on for second.
Had to be ridden from stalls but responded to take up mid-field position. Only sixth 200m out but stayed on well for pressure to make up a few places and closing on second at line.
Made running until headed and no extra from 200m out.
Tracked leaders in wide position. In second place off final turn but unable to find extra and lost a few places from there.
Travelled ok in mid-field but responded only briefly to pressure from final turn and lost ground final 200m.
Towards rear of mid-field. Minimal response to pressure from 400m out and no impression.
Taken wide on final turn after waited with in rear and never on terms.
Dropped in after sluggish start from outside stall. Taken wide into final bend but made headway only briefly and well held home straight.
Under pressure from just after halfway after held up. Struggling final bend and well beaten.
In good position tracking leader but in trouble from 500m out. Dropped right away and eased.
Bumped start, trapped very wide, a length or so back early, 2nd in the middle stages, 2 wide, hard ridden approaching 300M, took the lead 200M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Out with rest, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take a place without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the outside, still well back on turn, made good progress in straight but set an impossible task.
Jumped well, tracked leaders, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from the widest draw, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped nicely, settled just off the leaders, kept on well to score.
Not the quickest out, settled midfield 3 wide, raced keenly early, closed off nicely, no threat to winner.
Settled midfield 2 wide, ran on nicely on the inside, closest finish.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, showed some dash early in the Straight, one pace final furlong.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, one pace to the line.
Showed very good early speed to lead, travelled keenly, weakened final 200M. (See Incident Report)
Settled towards the rear, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Sat on pace on the rail, limited response in the Straight.
Raced behind midfield, took time to respond, made some late ground. (See Incident Report)
Sat in front of midfield 3 wide, weakened in the Straight.
Raced towards the rear, never a threat.
Sat last, never in contention.
Settled in rear of midfield in 7th, travelled the home bend 3-wide, tight between runners until 200M out, quickened well to assert authority close to home.

Began from a poor draw, towards the rear turning into back straight, switched wide for a run 750M out circling the field on home bend and the widest into straight, ran on steadily to reach 2nd final strides.
Soon taken back towards the rear on rail and waited with, ran on under pressure inside final 300M, switched for a run 150M out and did best work late.
Soon took up running and attempted to make all, narrowly headed inside the 200M, found no extra and when lost 3rd late.

Jumped awkwardly settling in midfield in 6th over 4L back, commenced move 3-wide around final bend going wider into straight, ran on to hit the front momentarily 200M out, tight between runnres 100M out and faded.
Began fairly settling in last few, kept on steadily without quickening inside final 200M.
Wide with leaders early settling within 3L of pace in 4th in back straight, held place chance under pressure early in home straight but had no more to give inside the 200M.
Soon taken back from the widest draw, made steady headway wide around home bend and one of the widest into straight, kept on steadily past well-beaten horses down the centre of the straight.
Settled some 4L back in 5th on rails, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, soon faded.
Vied for lead from a poor draw wide around first bend, settled in 1L 2nd 2-wide passing the 1200M, weakened badly out of contention upon turning into home straight.
Settled well behind from a poor draw, never seen with a chance.

Ridden along from the one draw early stages, settled some 2L back in 3rd on rails in back straight, came under strong pressure to hold position rounding final bend, soon weakened out of contention in straight.
Towards the rear early stages, improved his position along the fence from 800M, loomed behind leaders top of straight then kicked on well under top weight to lead 150M from home. Too strong.
Settled nicely in mid-division, worked into the race well passing 400M, chased on strongly to go 2nd near line.
Drifted back to race at the tail of the field, saved ground on inside, finished off well final 300M, briefly went 2nd late stages but was caught by the runner-up near line.
Maintained position just off the lead 1.5L on settling, little change at the turn, closed off steadily for modest 4th, not far from 2nd and 3rd.
Strode forward to be sharing the lead on inside, held lead to near 150M, weakened and lost several places close home.
Moved up to be sharing the lead on outside, fought on one paced early straight before fading over final 200M.
Jumped fairly, settled in second half of the field, 5Ls to make up 400M but couldn't go on. Never troubled leaders.
Jumped awkwardly, pressed along to obtain a position chasing leaders, badly crowded for room 700M, came under pressure and failed to finish the race off on straightening.
Not far off from leaders early stages, crowded for room 700M and shuffled back, failed to improve position in the straight.
Dropped back from wide draw, in detached last home turn, plenty to do on straightening, couldn't go on.
Unable to slot in from wide draw, caught wide towards the rear, brought wider home turn, failed to finish off in the straight. (Roarer.)
Jumped awkwardly, caught wide no cover chasing leaders, weakened rapidly on straightening and finished tailed out. (Lame RH leg / Unacceptable Performance.)

Shifted out abruptly on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well to the line and scored.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Badly crowded shortly after start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.

Severely checked shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact shortly after start, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Made contact shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped heavily and unbalanced at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, raced tight near 600M, checked 400M, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 6-1/2L back, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Tracked leader. Niggled from 600m out to hold position but responded generously and edged out runner-up on the nod after good tussle.
Tracked leader. Short of room briefly turning into home straight but soon every chance and denied on the nod after good battle with winner.
Raced in mid-field. Headway into contention from 200m line but tended to hang right and unable to reach first two.
Positioned in mid-field against inside rail. Kept on once getting a clear run off final bend but lacked speed to challenge leaders.
Towards rear after sluggish start. Headway out wide on final bend and kept on without reaching leaders.
Not the best away and waited with. Stayed on and made some late ground but never a danger.
Raced in touch around three lengths off leader. Headway to challenge on final bend but no extra and faded from 200m line.
Unable to get on terms from final turn after held up last and no impression.
Wide early from highest draw until across to lead outright after 500m. Folded quickly after headed at 200m line and eased.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled strongly, kept on well to win.
Chased the leader, traveled nicely, made steady progress to the finish (See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, sat midfield, slightly held up rounding the Turn, ran on evenly.
Sat midfield, traveled okay, made some ground inside 200M.
Sat handy, traveled smoothly, one pace to the line.
Sat worse than midfield, contested for a position near the 900M then shifted back in, ran on fairly thereafter.
Led on the rail, slightly weakened passing 200M, closed off fairly.
Sat handy, traveled okay, no clear running after 200M, could not be ridden out.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, angled out rounding the Home Turn, ran on only fairly.
Settled behind midfield, gave ground slightly rounding the Turn, not much impression made (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, raced rear until 700M, no contention.
Lunged forward as the start was effected, sat rear, made a mid-race move and raced wide and without cover thereafter, weakened notably (Must BT).
Tracked pace on rail. Quickened to front 200m out and soon in control for comfortable success, for all closed down by runner-up late.
Improved from mid-field to chase winner from top of home straight. Got closer final 50m and clear of rest but winner always in command.
Bumped at start after slowly away and raced in rear. No danger to front two but stayed on from 200m out to grab third. Promising.
Raced towards rear of mid-field. Lacked speed to get near leading pair final 150m but stayed on for pressure.
Waited with and kept on after taken widest off final turn.
Not the quickest away but improved to lead after 300m. Headed by winner 200m out and faded and lost a few places final 50m.
Held up from wide stall. Some headway under pressure home straight but never a danger.
Never better than mid-field and no impression.
Prominent from low draw until weakening final 250m.
Very wide to halfway from highest stall. Under pressure into home straight and weakened.
Ridden from the stalls to take up a prominent position but caught wide. Started to lose position from halfway and dropped away final 300m.
Crowded early up with pace but still able to track leaders. Weakened from final turn.
Began well, raced in 2nd, challenged the leader approaching 400M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well to the line, won by a head.
Jumped well, raced in midfield, 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, commenced move 400M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just beaten by a head.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place, nearest finish.
Away well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield early, checked off heels 1000M, found rail near 800M, angled out 400M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back turning in, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.

Began only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Made contact shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Moderately away from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 900M, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped okay, settled midfield 2 wide, closed off strongly, won comfortably.
Jumped nicely and showed good speed to lead, kept on well, just no match for winner.
Sat on pace 2 wide, kept on nicely for 3rd.
Not the quickest out, settled midfield on the rail, ran on nicely.
Sat last on the rail, switched out in the Straight, clear run final furlong, stayed on.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, saved ground, made good process along the rail.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, under pressure from 700M, only one pace when asked.
Tracked leader 2 wide, weakened final furlong.
Jumped sideway, settled at the rear, never impress.
Settled behind the leaders, hard ridden from the 650M, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat towards the rear 2 wide, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Jumped well with others, ridden along 4-wide before shifting one-out-one-back for cover 800M out, ran on under pressure inside final 100M to just get up on line.
Niggled along amongst leaders before taken back to forward of midfield on rail, tight inside runners 550M out, saved ground on inside turning in for home, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Amongst leaders early stages before taken back to forward of midfield over 850M out, over 3L back 2-wide in 6th rounding home bend, ran on dourly to be nearest at finish.
Settled towards rear in 8th, switched 3-wide home bend and the widest into straight, finished off the race well to narrowly miss a placing.
Jumped awkwardly from the widest draw, wide without cover towards rear making steady headway from 750M out, sustained progress from 3L 5th into straight, did best work late.
Niggled at after moderate start, settled one back on rail in 3rd, saved ground on inside turning in for home holding every chance only to be swamped final strides.

Jumped best from a poor draw before quickly taken back to last few, hung out and remained 3-wide without cover to home bend, produced good late impression from last few into straight despite tightened late.
With leaders with rails run, gained slender advantage coming onto home bend and led until narrowly headed on straightening, swamped for a placing inside final 50M.
Soon took up running 2-wide, narrowly headed coming onto home bend, renewed effort to hit the front narrowly upon straightening but unable to sustain effort close to home and forced to steady late.
Held up towards rear on rail after beginning from the one draw, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Settled well behind and never seen with a chance.
Soon taken back from a poor draw and never a danger.

Not hurried, settled towards the rear 4-5Ls back, swung wide into straight before running on strongly to hit the lead closing stages. (Jockey warned for using his whip forward of the saddle in a forehand manner.)
Jumped well from draw 1, always in touch behind leaders, worked into the race nicely on straightening, kept on well final 200M just couldn't hold off winner closing stages.
Settled down mid-division, raced wide no cover for the majority of race, kept up the chase final 300M, just missed 2nd in a photo.
Shifted in on jumping and was bumped, went forward tracking leaders along the 2-path, had every hope from 300M, kept on steadily to the line but was comfortably held by leaders.
Crowded on jumping, ended up racing behind midfield, raced keenly after 500M, 4Ls off leader on straightening, stayed on without serious threat.
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders first half of the race, pressed the pace from 600M, wrestled the lead early straight but couldn't sustain run final 150M.
Away fast then restrained to race behind leaders in 5th spot, 3Ls to make up 400M but not going the pace to challenge leaders.
Jumped only fairly, maintained a midfield position along the fence, kept on same pace final 300M. No threat to leaders.
Dropped back to near the rear, saved ground on inside but was held up for clear running on home turn, ran on fairly final 300M. Never likely.
Given a waiting ride at the rear, wide into straight but couldn't quicken enough to launch a serious challenge.
From wide draw pressed forward to take the lead, came under pressure to hold his position home turn, weakened top of straight and swamped by rivals.

Taken back to last from wide draw, hard pressed passing 400M but failed to improve position, eased final 150M. (Jockey : made a respiratory noise during the race and coughed post-race. / Blood in trachea.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly, led close home, impressive debut.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Out with rest, sent forward to race prominently early, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always just held. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, very wide turning in, closed off well to make frame, not quite able to challenge.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well, always held.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Out in line, raced 3 wide towards rear, very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Away well, tracked leaders in the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened final 100M. (Roarer.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear, 4 wide, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced better than midfield but trapped wide, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, detached from 700M, 9 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, took the early lead, headed near 850M, retook the lead 450M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on very well in straight, won by a nose.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, angled out 350M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a nose.
Crowded start, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Jumped well from the widest draw, tracked leaders on the outside, no cover throughout, kept on well in straight, always held.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, there to turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Bumped shortly after start, sat a length behind the leader, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Made contact shortly after start, trapped wide in midfield, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced towards rear, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 850M, headed 450M, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Knuckled over on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, showed no response early in straight, weakened 200M, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the outside, moved closer 1100M, positioned slightly behind midfield in the middle stages, challenged the leader turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Away with them, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, kept on very well in straight, always just held.
Out in line, took the early lead, headed approaching 1200M, allowed rival to cross 1000M, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader in the middle stages, kept on well in straight, always just held.
Made contact at start, taken back to race at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, kept on same pace in straight.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.

Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 1200M, led by 3/4L in the middle stages, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on rail, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2-1/2L back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Switched off to the rear on jumping from a wide draw, waited with at the back until making his move 500M, finished off strongly to lead near 100M and edged clear to score.

Shifted across behind runners early stages, settled towards the rear before moving closer passing halfway, held up for clear running in the home turn then stayed on to go 2nd late stages but not troubled the winner.
From draw 1 maintained a position ahead of midfield, switched away from fence 450M to challenge, ran home mildly to finish a modest 3rd.
Settled midfield, hard driven 450M, took narrow lead early straight but peaked on its run final 150M.
Always prominent, chased leaders into straight, had every chance, one paced final stages.
Jumped only fairly and from a wide barrier was taken across behind runners, settled near last and had plenty to do 400M, stayed on down the outside to claim 6th, not beaten far by the placegetters.
Jumped only fairly, reserved behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, driven wide into straight before finishing off moderately for a non-threatening 7th.
In midfield early stages, drifted back towards the rear halfway, under pressure home turn, kept on only fairly behind rivals. Never likely.
Maintain a position in mid-division, checked on home turn losing momentum before running on fairly under top weight.
Raced keenly, moved up to race just outside the lead, briefly led early straight but soon swamped by rivals, weakened from 250M. (Roarer).
Sped to the lead, set good pace first half of the race, caught up by rivals top of straight, soon no extra and dropped out rapidly.
Chased leaders, caught wide no cover early stages, struggled to hold his position 600M, soon drifted out of contention. (No Vet findings / Unacceptable Performance.)
Ridden along to lead, traveled strongly, made good progress over the concluding stages.
Sat towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, stayed on well.
Sat handy, traveled smoothly, responded nicely when asked.
Settled in front of midfield, raced wide, ran on okay.
Sat midfield, 2 wide, made steady progress in the Straight.
Sat behind midfield, raced greenly, no clear run near the 200M, closed off okay (See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, one pace to the line.
Sat worse than midfield, raced wide, lay in in the Home Straight, finished off fairly.
Tracked the lead, traveled okay, crowded near the 100M, minor progress made when asked (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, weakened after 200M, faded.
Sat rear, raced rear, never a danger.
Settled behind midfield, weakened notably inside 150M (Substantial blood in trachea).
Competition for lead early and set strong pace. Asserted over 200m out and always looked like holding on despite reduced lead final 50m.
Raced in mid-field behind leading bunch. Kept on well after checked briefly 200m out but never quite getting to winner.
Tracked pace. Hung left when giving chase to leader from 150m out and ran on well once straightened out final 75m.
On the back foot after hampered at start. Still in rear at top of home straight before making good headway to pass several final 150m.
Tracked pace. Hung right in behind leader off the bend and no extra final 100m.
Chased pace early but pushed along to hold position from 400m out and one paced.
Checked after sluggish start and raced in last place. Never a danger but some headway into mid-field final 150m.
Showed speed to press leader from wide stall until weakening final 200m.
Pushed along in rear to go the early pace. Had only one behind turning into home straight and little impression.
Never better than mid-field and lost ground under pressure final 200m.
Raced wide towards rear. Minimal response to pressure from 300m out and well held.
Mid-field after crowded early. Pushed along 400m out and dropped away.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the outside, found rail near 600M, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Away well, positioned 1-2Ls behind the leader on rail, crowded near 550M, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the outside early, moved closer after entering the back straight, 2nd in the middle stages, kept on well in straight but always held.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, commenced move approaching 400M, very wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths back, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, angled out 350M, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, 2 wide turning in, one-paced in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider on turn, made no impression in straight.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, unable to maintain position on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced behind midfield on the outside, dropped towards rear 800M, 7 lengths back turning in, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Jumped with the field, sat outside the leader, kept on well to score
Sat box-seated, ran on nicely, just missed. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield, travelled keenly, closed off okay.
Began well and led, weakened slightly final 100M.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, no clear run in the Straight, never seriously tested.
Caught 3 wide midfield, made its run from 450M, one pace final 150M.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, stayed on.
Settled at the rear on the rail, made little impression
Settled midfield on the rail, never impress.
Sat behind the leader 2 wide, held up in the Straight, limited response when asked.
Sat last, never a threat.
Sat midfield 2 wide, under pressure from 450M, weakened and faded. (See Incident Report)
Began from a poor draw gradually settling over 3L back in midfield in back straight, commenced move 3-wide 500M out swinging wide into straight, gained upper hand over 100M out.
Held up in 3rd some 2L back on rail, tightened on rail 550M out, renewed effort turning into straight holding every chance inside final 150M only to be denied narrowly.
Held up in forward of midfield on rail over 3L back in 6th and becoming 5th on the 1000M bend, back to be 6th over 450M out before commenced move on straightening, unable to sustain effort 100M out
Soon took up running attempting to make all while travelling keenly in back straight, folded up quickly inside final 200M.

Travelled keenly without cover early stages before taken back to last making first bend, angled out very wide for clear run into straight but met with interferences, recovered well inside final 280M to be nearest at finish.

Jumped well before taken back to just worse than midfield 2-wide in 8th or 7th some 5L off the pace, commenced move coming onto home bend but hampered and carried wide into straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled just worse than midfield in 8th or 7th on rail, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, hung in a difficult ride in straight but fought on steadily to the line.
Soon taken back from a poor draw for rails run well behind, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, kept on steadily without making any serious impression.
Soon taken back to last few with cover, commenced move home bend but badly hampered entering straight, made no impression thereafter.
Pressed forward for prominent position 2-wide settling some 2L back in 4th in back straight, severely checked and shifted wide turning in for home, never recovered.

Began awkwardly from a poor draw, pressed forward in wide run travelling 3-wide round first bend before obtaining 2-wide position in 2nd into back straight, struck into and badly unbalanced making final turn, never recovered.
Jumped on terms, maintained a midfield position 4-5Ls back, saved ground on inside before running on strongly passing 300M, hit lead inside 100M and just held on from fast finishing 2nd late.
Away swiftly, positioned just ahead of midfield, travelled well into straight before closing off nicely. Just missed.
Bustled along after the start to be vying the lead on outside, wrestled the lead nearing 200M, fought hard late but couldn't hold off first two.
Jumped only fairly, failed to show sufficient pace and ended up racing near the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, ran on well in the straight to claim 4th.
Jumped only fairly, settled towards the rear, 5Ls off leader on straightening, closed off nicely for 5th.

From draw 12 switched off to race at the back, had big task in hand 400M, finished off best but not able to trouble leaders. (Jockey : Instructed to ride conservatively from wide draw and the anticipated fast pace.)
Chased leaders 2-wide, in a good spot top of straight but couldn't quicken enough to challenge leaders.
Settled down in mid-division, switched wide 450M, ran home one paced under pressure.

From draw 1 soon took up running, pressed by rival middle stages, lost lead nearing 200M, faded towards the line. (Jockey: disadvantaged by being pressured in the lead and as a consequence gave ground in the Home Straight.)
Given a patient ride, restrained near last, brought wide into straight but made limited progress only.
Away well, chased leaders along the fence, kept on early straight but run ended 200M, no extra late stages.
Maintained a position ahead of midfield, didn't respond to riding in the straight, never involved.

Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Began well from gate 9, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide from 500M, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 750M, very wide into straight, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening the first two.
Moderately away from gate 12, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.

Made contact with the left side of its barrier on jumping, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually final 150M.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 600M, 3 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, angled out 600M, wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide at rear, angled out after passing 550M, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, peaked 450M, weakened early in straight.
Settled towards rear, commenced move over 300M out and quickened well to take command inside the 50M.
Ridden to first few in 4th, drifted some 3L back when pace quickened home bend, ran on under pressure to hit the front about 170M out only to be swamped close to home.

Jumped quickly from the one draw before gradually settling in 5th, drifted over 4L off the pace home bend, came to challenge shortly after straightening, held some chance inside final 200M but could find no extra 50M out.
Settled just off the pace in 3rd on rail, tight between runners in straight until the 100M, unable to make any impression closing stages.
Soon taken back for rails run in last few, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, produced good late impression closing stages.
Settled in midfield in 6th, some 6L back turning into home straight, found nothing under pressure.
Blundered badly at start, settled well back from the widest draw, trailed the field until approaching home turn, ran on past well-beaten horses in straight.
Ridden to take up running inside the 1100M, travelled keenly in front rounding home bend, went about 2L clear early in straight and flattered, weakened badly closing stages.
Settled in last few, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening in straight.
Ridden along in rear of midfield 3-wide without cover, drifted further back to 9th coming onto home bend, widest turning into straight, made no further impression.
Settled just worse than midfield on rail, slightly further back when pace quickened home bend, ran home one-paced.
Broke well from a poor draw, travelled in 2nd alongside race leader before drifting some 1L back on home bend, gradually weakened under pressure inside final 300M.
Sat handy, traveled comfortably, made good progress inside 150M, closed off well.
Settled behind midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, responded nicely when asked.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, disappointed for clear running near 100M, not fully tested.
Jumped only fairly, settled in front of midfield, raced keenly rounding the Turn, closed off fairly well.
Ridden along to lead, traveled smoothly, weakened approaching 300M (See Incident Report).
Sat handy, traveled okay, raced tight and hung in in the Straight, closed off okay (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, raced keenly, raced wide and without cover from 1100M, ran on evenly.
Sat midfield, slightly hung out rounding the Turn, weakened entering the Straight (Substantial blood in trachea).
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, was hampered rounding the Turn, one pace to the line.
Sat rear, traveled fairly, switched out rounding the Turn, closed off only fairly.
Sat towards rear, caught wide when attempting to make a forward move, nothing in the Straight.
Sat rear, traveled keenly when steadied rounding the Turn, never a threat.
Settled midfield on the rail, raced keenly and checked near the 700M, never a danger.
Stood flat-footed as the start was effected, slow out, raced rear, no contention (Barrier manners unacceptable, Must BT).
Raced in rear of mid-field. Steady and sustained headway from 400m out and responded to pressure to lead late on.
Waited with in rear. Made good headway to edge ahead final 50m but pipped by winner close home.
Improved from mid-field to lead 150m out but found first two too strong final 50m.
Raced in mid-field on rail. Quickened between horses once gaps appeared to challenge from 150m out but jinked left and unable to sustain effort late.
Towards rear from high draw and stayed on from 200m out. Never a threat to leaders but passed several rivals inside the final 100m.
Keen in dispute of lead until no extra final 150m.
Tracked leading pair. Challenged at 200m line but soon no extra and weakened final 100m.
In touch but wide from highest stall. Under pressure from top of home straight and faded.
Drawn high but got across to dispute lead until weakening final 200m.
Tracked pace against rail until weakening from over 200m out.
Under pressure in rear of mid-field on bend and dropped away home straight.
No response to pressure from over 300m out and never out of last place.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight, just able to hold off the challengers.
Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, very wide turning in, closed off well to take a place, always just held.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared after passing 150M, finished off evenly.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began well from gate 9, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly in the middle stages, 3 wide on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 1/2L back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear, 2 wide, angled out 450M, taken wide in straight and made some progress.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run until approaching 100M, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Settled just behind the leaders on the rail, no clear run early in the Straight, responded well once in the clear, won going away, cozily.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, angled out rounding the Home Turn, hit the front at 150M, kept on well, just no match for winner.
Sat behind midfield on the rail, stayed on well.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, showed good dash from 400 to 100M, only one pace to the line.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, stayed on nicely.
Settled midfield 2 wide, run peaked at 200M.
Slow to begin, settled towards the rear, ran on fairly. (See Incident Report)
Showed good speed to lead, weakened final furlong. (See Incident Report)
Sat towards the rear, made some late ground. (See Incident Report)
Sat last, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Sat on pace 3 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Tracked leader 2 wide, weakened and faded final 250M.
Raced towards the rear, never a threat.
Caught 4 wide no cover, weakened in the Straight.

Broke well from a poor draw, gradually taken over 2L back in 5th for cover, further back when pace quickened on home bend, 4-wide into straight and hampered just over 300M out, quickened well to assert authority at the 200M.
Chased leader in 3rd, became 4th over 3L back when pace quickened home bend, commenced move into straight, switched inside for a run inside the 300M and ran on to be nearest at finish.

Broke well from a poor draw looking for chance to shift closer to rail, over 4L back in 6th when clipped heels and lost momentum 1250M out, commenced move home bend but carried wide into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Held up in 2nd 2-wide becoming 3rd about 1000M out, hit the front momentarily 300M out but soon swamped under pressure inside final 200M.

Improved steadily along the rail to reach forward of midfield in 6th momentarily 1300M out, further off the pace in 8th when pace quickened home bend, commenced move entering straight but unable to quicken to threaten.
Gradually settled towards the rear, shifted wide to challenge entering straight, ran on inside final 250M without threatening.
Began fairly, settled wide in worse than midfield, obtained 2-wide position rounding home bend, angled out for a run down the centre of the straight, never nearer.
Settled in last few from a poor draw, saved ground on rail turning in for home, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Soon taken well back from a poor draw, 3-wide rounding home bend and wider in last into straight, ran on past well-beaten horses down the centre of the track inside final 300M.
Settled well back from the widest draw, chased the field into straight, produced good late impression inside final 100M.
Slowly away, gradually recovered to 10th on rail in worse than midfield, kept on steadily without quickening in the run to the line.
Travelled in midfield from a wide draw, made rapid progress out wide from the 1200M to take up running 2-wide 950M out, had to be straightened 400M out and soon faded.
Settled better than midfield some 4L off the pace, came under pressure to hold place when pace quickened home bend, saved ground turning in for home, faded under pressure inside final 200M.
Soon obtained rails run in front and led until narrowly headed 1000M out, folded up quickly inside final 200M.
Broke alertly, soon took up running, travelled well in middle stages and still on the bridle leaving home turn, kicked on strongly under a big weight to score a dominant win.
From wide draw pressed forward to track leader, driven 400M, fought hard but couldn't close the gap on the winner.
Jumped on terms, from draw 1 moved up to chase leaders in 3rd, not going the pace to challenge winner in the straight but stuck to task well for 3rd. (lay out under pressure in straight.)
Restrained to race in mid-division along the fence, had some difficulty obtaining clear running early straight before finishing off the race mildly. Held by leaders in the run to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, switched off to race at the rear 7Ls off the pace, had big task in hand 400M, ran on well when asked, awkwardly placed behind rival late and not ridden out to the finish.

Made contact with the barrier on jumping, lost ground and settled towards the rear further back than intended, stayed on final 400M without troubling leaders. (Jockey: better suited by being stepped up in distance.)
Jumped awkwardly and was crowded shortly after the start, maintained a position behind midfield, made some progress in the straight but was never a serious threat.
Lost ground shortly after the start, settled near rear 6-7Ls off the pace, ran on fairly passing 400M. Posed no danger to leaders.
Quickly into stride under 10lb claimer, restrained to race in 4th on settling, not quickened leaving the turn when placed under pressure, ran home one paced.
Jumped only fairly, raced keenly in a rearward position early stages, moved closer to midfield home turn but couldn't quicken enough on straightening, soon behind major rivals.
Urged along to be racing in midfield, gave limited response on straightening, soon outpaced by rivals.
Maintained a position ahead of midfield, raced 3-wide without cover, weakened inside 300M, finished last.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, shared lead from 500M, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Out with rest, tracked leaders, 2 wide, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Began well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, carried wider 450M, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 600M, 5-1/2L back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 3 wide behind midfield, carried wider approaching 500M, finished off well without threatening.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, a bit closer on turn, angled out 500M, made some progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide towards rear early, a bit closer after passing 800M, found rail 700M, angled out 450M, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (Roarer.)
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 1100M, shared lead with rival turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on outer, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Bumped start, in touch, 2 wide, there to turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 250M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4-1/2L back turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Average to begin, raced better than midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 500M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after the start, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, angled out 450M, kept on well in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.

Began well from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, taken back near 1200M, raced 3 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back in the middle stages, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted in at start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, slightly taken back 900M, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear, 11 lengths back, moved closer on turn, 6-1/2L back at 400M, passed some tired runners in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, cleared 250M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, shared lead with rival on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.

Began only fairly, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, commenced move 350M, finished off very strongly, led close home.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Jumped well, raced in 3rd, 2 wide, same position on turn, showed good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Made contact with the left side of its barrier on jumping and lost ground, raced at tail, 8 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run near 150M, cleared 75M, ran on evenly, short of run close home.
Away well, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide towards rear, similar position on turn, no clear run until final 100M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.

Crowded start, raced in midfield on the outside early, moved closer from 1100M, positioned 2nd in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, took the lead 150M, headed 100M, weakened quickly thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, 8 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed approaching 150M, weakened final 100M.
Still in rear at top of home straight after held up but came with a strong run out wide to surge to front final 25m. Well on top at line.
Took up forward position from low draw. Led 100m out and every chance but winner swept by late.
One of first pushed along in mid-field but stayed on well final 150m.
Made headway widest on bend after settled in mid-field and stayed on up the home straight.
Stayed on from mid-field despite not getting the clearest of runs, including final 25m when unable to be ridden out fully.
Made running and clear briefly with runner-up 200m out. Weakened and lost several places final 50m.
Wide early but settled behind leaders by halfway. No extra and losing ground when short of room final 50m.
Broke well but settled in touch with leaders. Keeping on at the one pace when running out of room final 50m.
Waited with in rear. Briefly short of room 100m out and never on terms.
Dropped in from high draw. Stuck to rail and some headway early in home straight but limited impression when briefly tight for room 100m out.
Tracked leading pair. Under firm pressure from 400m out and weakened final 200m.
Started to lose mid-field position on bend and dropped away.
Chased the leader, traveled strongly, kept on well to win.
Sat handy, traveled okay, responded nicely, had every chance.
Sat towards rear, traveled nicely, no clear run inside 300M, showed some dash over the concluding stages, closed off nicely.
Settled midfield, traveled okay, was steadied to avoid heels over the concluding stages, could not be fully tested.
Sat handy, briefly crowded near 100M, ran on evenly (Rider dropped whip).
Sat rear, switched out rounding the Turn, one pace to the finish.
Slow to begin, sat towards rear, made steady progress in the Straight.
Jumped only fairly, settled worse than midfield, no clear run in the Straight, could not be fully tested (See Incident Report).
Sat midfield, traveled fairly, not much impression.
Settled in front of midfield, raced wide throughout, weakened entering the Straight, never a threat.
Ridden along to lead, weakened notably passing 150M (Substantial mucus, See Incident Report).
Settled behind midfield, traveled fairly, never a danger.
Good headway into contention from mid-field on final bend. Led 150m out and driven out to hold off runner-up.
Raced in touch with leaders. Chased winner home from 150m out and ran on well.
Raced in mid-field against rail. Unable to challenge front 2 but kept on for third.
Made running. Challenged and headed 200m out and no extra final 75m.
Rear of mid-field. Headway off final bend but run flattened out final 100m.
Stayed on at the one pace from mid-field and unable to challenge leaders.
Wide into home straight after racing in mid-field and one paced under pressure, making no real impression.
A bit keen as he chased leader. Challenged and every chance 200m out but soon no extra.
Held up. Some headway out wide on final bend but soon flattened out and little impression.
Held up and a bit keen early. Under pressure from 500m out and no impression.
Tracked leaders until weakening from 150m out. Dropped away final 50m.
Dropped in from wide draw. Struggling final bend and lost touch.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, moved a bit closer on turn, angled out approaching 350M, finished off very strongly to score.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 350M, finished off very strongly, took the lead 25M, headed close home.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 25M.
Slightly slow out, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, not enough room early in straight, cleared 100M, closed off well to make frame without threatening.

Bumped on the hindquarters on jumping, raced towards rear on the outside, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide turning in, made good progress in the run home, nearest finish. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Began well from the widest draw, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, angled out 350M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 1-1/2L back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, no clear run and unbalanced near 75M, made no impression thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Jumped well, sat outside the lead, kept on well to score, won going away.
Sat just behind the leaders on the rail, no clear run from 450M to 350M, ran on afterwards, no threat to winner.
Sat on pace 2 wide, kept on nicely.
Sat towards the rear on the rail, saved ground, ran on okay, never threaten the top 3.
Settled midfield 2 wide, under pressure from 500M, stayed on fairly.
Settled midfield 3 wide with cover, ran on ordinarily. (See Incident Report)
Sat towards the rear, passed some weakened rivals.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, switched out at 400M, limited response in the Straight.
Raced midfield on the rail, never impress.
Showed good speed to lead, weakened final furlong.
Caught 3 wide no cover in front of midfield, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat last, never in contention. (See Incident Report)
Settled towards rear and waited with, came under pressure 600M out swinging very wide into straight, quickened well to assert authority close to home.

Settled in midfield on rail just over 4L off the speed, commenced move rounding home bend shifting 4-wide for a clear run into straight, hit the front under pressure 150M out only to be caught close to home
Settled at the back, trailed the field to the 400M, saved ground turning in for home, baulked until over 100M out, fought on dourly to the line.
Settled towards rear on rail, came under pressure to challenge upon straightening, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in midfield in 6th some 4L off the pace, shifted 3-wide rounding home bend and wider into straight, kept on steadily without quickening.

Pressed forward from the widest draw settling just over 2L back 2-wide in 4th from stables bend, commenced move entering home straight sharing the lead upon straightening, unable to sustain effort inside final 150M.
Settled just worse than midfield, held up behind runners over 400M out, dropped to last into straight, produced some late impression closing stages.
Amongst leaders early, settled 2-wide in 2nd from approaching back straight, kept on from similar position into home straight but unable to sustain effort inside final 100M.
Well there 3-wide early, took up running onto stables bend and rails run 1200M out, led until joined early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 150M.
Close up early, settled just better than midfield in 5th some 3L off the pace, came under pressure over 500M out, faded into straight,
Well there to straight, dropped away quickly.
Jumped on terms before moving up to track leaders along the 2-path, quickened up strongly inside 300M, got up nearing 50M for three consecutive wins.
Jumped only fairly and shortly after the start was crowded by a rival, ended up racing behind midfield, closed off well final 300M down the inside, just denied.
Vied for early lead before emerging as clear leader halfway, kept on well under top weight on straightening only to be overpowered by first two close home.
Taken back to near the rear on jumping from wide draw, swung widest home before finishing off fastest to take 4th. Nearest finish.

Shifted out at the start and was bumped, obtained a midfield position but raced keenly and refused to settle in early and middle stages, found less than expected in the finish but nevertheless a good effort.
Taken back from wide draw, settled in second half of the field 5Ls back, finished off well enough final 300M and not beaten far at the finish.
From wide draw switched off to race at the rear, raced keenly middle stages, brought wide to the straight before finishing off mildly. Not reach leaders.
Moved up to race outside leader, couldn't keep up home turn, soon drifted out of contention early straight.

Jumped only fairly and then was crowded for room after the start, settled at the rear of the field 6-7Ls away, kept to inside on straightening but failed to finish off. (Jockey : hung in and proved difficult to ride out.)
Jumped well, restrained in mid-division and raced wide no cover for the majority of the race, had little left on straightening and was never a serious threat.
Away fast but soon restrained to race in midfield, brought wide on straightening but lacked a finishing effort final 300M.
Close up chasing leaders, under the pump home turn, soon no extra and dropped out of the race.
Out with rest, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, angled out 350M, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Away well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on very well in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 750M, saved ground on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move 400M, showed good response early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Out in line, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2-1/2L back, angled out 400M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Bumped shortly after start, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight. (Rider lost whip at 300M.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, slightly improved after passing 650M, 6 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, raced at rear on the inside, 9 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
