Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead near 800M, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on strongly in straight and scored.
Out with rest, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, headed near 800M, 1/2L back turning in, kept on well in straight, always held.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Bumped on the hindquarters at start, raced behind midfield on outer, a bit closer in the middle stages, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside early, 2 wide from 1000M, commenced move 500M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 13, tracked leaders on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 600M, wider turning in, made no impression in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened final furlong.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Reared as stalls opened and lost many lengths, detached from the main group, finished tailed out. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well to be tracking leaders on settling, switched to 3-wide 650M, took some time to pick up on straightening but did best work final 150M to get up just in time.
Jumped on terms, chased leader on inside, worked into the race well 300M, quickened past leader inside 150M, tried hard late stages but was claimed by winner last stride.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in second half of the field, held up for clear running making the home turn before closing off nicely over final 300M to claim 3rd, nearest finish.

Soon led, travelled nicely into straight, kept on well until 170M when jumping a mark on the track, lost momentum and headed by first 3. (Jockey : might be better suited with the addition of blinkers and racing at Happy Valley.)
Jumped on terms, ended up racing 3-wide behind mid-division, gave good response early straight and got up for 4th mid-straight, peaked on its run final 150M.
Jumped only fairly, soon guided to the inside before improving to race in midfield, held up 450M-300M then closed off moderately for a non-threatening 6th.
Not hurried early stages, switched off to race towards the rear, held up on inside making home turn before closing off mildly in the straight. No serious threat to leaders.
Jumped fairly and then was crowded by a rival, raced keenly amongst horses, close enough turning in but ran home one paced.
Jumped awkwardly, taken back to last from draw 14, over-raced middle stages, last turning in, ran past beaten horses only.
Away well enough, settled ahead of midfield along the 3-path, ran on fairly when placed under pressure. Never likely.
From draw 1 stayed close to leaders early stages, shuffled back to midfield home turn, couldn't finish off on straightening.
Jumped only fairly, over-raced early stages, in 2nd half of the field making the turn for home, couldn't quicken enough on straightening.
Chased leader 2-wide, couldn't keep up with rivals passing 300M, weakened away.
Restrained to near last on jumping from draw 12, over-raced early stages, couldn't go on passing 400M, soon left behind by rivals.
Sat handy, raced wide, responded nicely when asked, kept on well to win.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, traveled smoothly, made good ground inside 100M.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled okay, closed off nicely.
Sat in front of midfield, raced on the rail, held up until 50M, could not be fully tested (See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, settled towards rear, lay out when placed under pressure.
Chased the leader, traveled okay, slightly weakened passing 200M.
Ridden along to lead, traveled fairly, minor progress made in the Straight.
Sat midfield, traveled only fairly, one pace to the finish.
Sat midfield, traveled greenly, held up for clear run over the concluding stages.
Sat towards rear, raced greenly, was steadied to avoid heels inside 100M, closed off only fairly.
Jumped awkwardly, sat in front of midfield, gave ground quickly in the Straight.
Jumped awkwardly, sat rear, raced rear, no impression.
Sat midfield, limited response when asked, never a threat.
Sat handy, raced wide throughout, failed to respond in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Raced in mid-field. Angled off rail at 200m line to give chase to leader and led close home.
Tracked leaders. Quickened to lead 200m out and edged out by winner only close home.
No danger to front two but kept on well from out of pack final 200m to take third.
Dropped out from high draw. Headway out wide on final bend and kept on for strong pressure.
Held up after slow start and in last place off final bend. Briefly short of room at 200m line and made good ground late once angled wide.
Made running until headed and weakened from 200m out.
Waited with. Headway out wide on final bend to get in touch with leaders but no extra and lost ground final 150m.
In touch but wide from high draw. Improved to challenge early in home straight but weakened final 200m.
No impression from mid-field and tended to hang right under pressure final 150m.
Tracked leaders. Made challenge at top of home straight but soon weakened.
Raced towards rear of mid-field. No clear run in home straight until 150m out but no impression from there.
Tracked pace and keen. Weakened after tight for room 350m out.
Waited with in rear. Pushed along on final bend and made no impression.
Raced keenly in dispute of lead. Weakened quickly off final turn and eased off after dropping back through field.
Began well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, challenged the leaders from 500M, shared lead 400M, kept on very well in straight, won by 2 lengths.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, 3 wide turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, improved from 650M, very wide turning in, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide turning in, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.

Moderately away, raced better than midfield but trapped very wide early, moved closer after entering the back straight, shared lead from 700M, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Taken back from gate 8, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader, 3 wide, improved on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 1200M, allowed rival to cross 700M, sat right behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1000M, allowed rival to cross 700M, 1-3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, showed no response early in straight, weakened final 300M.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead near 1000M, shared lead with rivals on turn, headed and weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, tracked leaders on the inside, dropped to midfield 800M, unable to maintain position on turn, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped on terms, sat on pace 2 off the stands' rail, challenged the lead at 600M, kept on well to score.
Dispute lead, raced middle of the track early, moved towards the near side at 550M, under pressure from 350M, closed off nicely, always held.
Led on the near side rail, lay in throughout, kept on.
Sat behind the leaders 2 from the stands' rail, made some progress but one pace final 100M.
Raced on the near side rail, hard ridden from the 450M, ran on evenly.
Sat behind the pace, made no impression
Sat close to the pace 3 wide from the stands' rail, limited response when asked.
Outpace early, never a threat.
Sat near the pace center field, weakened final furlong.
Settled prominently early drifting to some 5L back in 7th on rail when pace quickened rounding home bend, commenced move entering straight, responded well to assert authority close to home.
Wide with leaders early stages before taken over 2L back to 4th approaching first bend, came under pressure to challenge entering straight, ran on stoutly to snatch 2nd late.
Soon took up running on rail setting a quick pace, narrowly headed approaching home turn but renewed effort to hit the front again over 150M out, had no more to give when swamped close to home.
Began well from a poor draw and soon taken back towards the rear for cover, gained closer 3-wide approaching first turn, ran on well under pressure in straight to be nearest at finish.
Taken well back from the widest draw travelling keenly, obtained a clear run near the centre of the track upon straightening, ran on well without threatening.

Travelled wide without cover with leaders, obtained 2-wide position in 2nd coming onto home bend, hit the front narrowly over 500M out but unable to sustain effort and headed inside the 200M. (Blood in trachea)
Settled in midfield in 6th some 4L off the pace, kept on steadily without quickening in the run to the line.
Travelled 3-wide without cover in midfield, gained slightly closer to pace in 5th rounding home bend, kept on steadily from a similar position into straight.
Travelled wide in last few, kept on steadily without making any serious impression until late.
Began well before settling not far off the pace in 4th or 3rd; found nothing in home straight.
Began fairly travelling in last few, kept on steadily without quickening.
Modest beginning, gradually recovered to rear of midfield, tight between runners at around first turn, unable to quicken after straightening, ran out of room close stages.
Soon taken well back from a poor draw, remained wide in last few and never seen with a chance thereafter.
Gradually recovered to midfield from moderate start, steadied and lost position about 1150M out, in last few on rail into straight, dropped out inside final 300M.
Stayed close to leaders in 4th, responded well when asked early straight, vied for lead with rival final 200M and just prevailed at the finish.
Jumped only fairly, moved up to chase leader, quickened up well 300M to be vying for lead, fought neck to neck with rival all the way to the finish. Just denied.
Settled ahead of midfield, close enough behind leaders top of straight, went 3rd 150M, tried hard but couldn't get closer to first two.
Jumped on terms, restrained to race in mid-division along the fence, worked home steadily final 400M to take 4th but not reached first two.
Soon led and set a good tempo to straight, headed inside 300M and drifted out of contention.
From draw 12 taken across to a 2-wide position behind midfield, kept on fairly passing 400M, couldn't launch a serious challenge.
Switched off to race towards the rear of the field, into clear 400M, made some progress without threatening leaders.
Obtained a midfield position 3-4Ls away, had no clear running from 400M to 200M but lacked a finishing response late stages.
Chased leader 2-wide, couldn't quicken enough passing 400M, faded final 200M. (Jockey : his mount over-raced when positioned outside the leader.)
From wide draw restrained to race towards the rear, 6Ls to make up on leaders 400M but couldn't muster any sort of challenge in the straight.

From draw 6 ended up racing 3-wide without cover ahead of midfield, pushed along nearing 500M but failed to improve position, soon no threat to leaders. (Jockey : disadvantaged by racing wide without cover.)
Failed to show sufficient pace to hold a more forward position, caught wide no cover in midfield until 1000M, outpaced by rivals passing 300M. Soundly beaten.
Slow to begin, settled near last, couldn't keep up with rivals 600M, soon beaten.

Dropped back from wide draw, 7Ls off the pace 400M, gave no response, eased when no chance. Finished tailed out on the third consecutive occasion. (Jockey : not satisfied with the horse's action over final 200M.)
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide from 600M, 7 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Made contact with the left side of its barrier on jumping, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, not clear run near 125M, made good progress thereafter to make frame.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3 lengths turning in, kicked clear early in straight, peaked and headed 75M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, made some progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, 3 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 500M, 6 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well from a tricky draw, raced better than midfield but trapped 4 wide early, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 9 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Shifted out on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L turning in, hit the front 250M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 450M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared near 150M, finished off well to take a place.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared near 300M, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began well, raced behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, no daylight early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, commenced move 500M, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Slightly slow out, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off evenly.

Made contact with the left side of its barrier on jumping, then bumped shortly after start, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, still 7Ls back turning in, taken very wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out after passing 500M, made little progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened final 100M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, 3 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Made contact shortly after start, in touch, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted in at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, went clear halfway, led by 1-1/4L turning in, kept on well to hold off the challengers.

Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 11 lengths back in the middle stages, commenced move 650M, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a head. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, 4 lengths back in the middle stages, closer on turn, 1-1/4L back at 400M, kept on well in straight, inconvenienced near 50M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began fairly, raced in 4th, 2 wide, 7 lengths back in the middle stages, closer on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced in 3rd, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Stood flat-footed as the start was effected and lost ground, raced at rear, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 3 lengths back on turn but 4 wide, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Settled just off the pace despite blundered shortly after start, remained within 2L of pace between 3rd and 5th in back straight, hugged the rail turning in and quickened well to hit the front inside the 150M.
Broke well from the two draw before taken some 1L back 2-wide, remained similar before switching 3-wide for a run rounding home bend, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.

Broke well from the one draw gradually settling in forward of midfield on rail into back straight, commenced move approaching home turn, improving when baulked over 200M out, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Settled mainly in midfield, came under pressure from approaching home bend, went the widest into straight, ran on steadily under strong pressure down the centre of the track but without threatening.

Pressed forward from a poor draw, obtained rails run in front passing the 1300M, steadied up the pace into back straight and joined by one other 700M out, re-gained lead straightening for home but swamped inside final 200M.
Began well before taken back towards rear and waited with, did not find much room early in straight, produced good late impression inside final 100M.
Soon obtained rails run from a poor draw travelling in worse than midfield, came under pressure home bend, had to be straightened 150M out, kept on to the line. (Mucus in trachea)

Settled in forward of midfield on rail, made headway 2-wide 1200M out to about 2L off the pace in 4th, slightly further back in 6th down back straight, wide making final turn, kept on same pace and forced to steady late.
Broke well settling 3-wide in midfield, gained steadily closer to 4th in back straight, came under pressure to challenge home bend swinging wide into straight, made no further impression.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in last few, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, kept on same pace under pressure.
Settled in last few from a poor draw, made swift progress from the 1100M to join race leader 700M out, remained same into straight but tired noticeably shortly after.
Travelled wide without cover near midfield early stages before taken back to last for cover over 1100M out, came under pressure from over 650M out but had nothing to give.
Settled midfield 2 wide, began to improve from 500M, travelled strongly, ran on nicely to score.
Jumped nicely and led, kept on well.
Sat on pace 2 wide, kept on nicely.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, stayed on late.
Settled midfield on the rail, close off fairly.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, checked rounding the Home Turn, one pace when asked. (See Incident report)
Raced in midfield 3 wide no cover, ran on evenly.
Settled midfield 2 wide, limited response in the Straight.
Sat at the rear, passed some weakened rivals.
Sat last, took time to respond, made some late ground.
Tracked leader on the rail, weakened in the Straight.
Settled towards the rear, never in contention.
Rear of mid-field. Had to angle four wide off rail for clear run from 150m out and ran on strongly to lead close home.
Raced on rail throughout from lowest draw. Improved to hold every chance from 200m out and pipped by winner only close home.
Travelled well behind pace. Challenged and every chance from 200m out but run out of it close home.
Held up. Came widest off the bend and ran on late, making up several places in the final 100m.
Raced in touch and caught on heels briefly at halfway. Kept on in home straight but one paced and unable to challenge.
Held up after briefly crowded at start. Hung right under pressure final 300m and never nearer.
Did plenty to get across and dispute lead from wide stall and in front from halfway. Headed and weakened final 100m.
Ridden to race close up. Under stronger pressure from 300m out and unable to hold position.
Raced in rear. Stayed on and not beaten far in bunched finish but never a danger.
Led or disputed lead until weakening final 150m.
Mid-field. Looked awkward under pressure from bend and making no impression when short of room 50m out.
Held up. Keeping on but still in rear when running out of room and forced to snatch up final 50m.
Began well from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, a bit closer on turn, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 125M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Began only fairly, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead near 450M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 125M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 350M, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail 350M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Clean jump, raced prominently, allowed rival to cross approaching 650M, 1-3/4L back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, similar position on turn, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 850M, headed 450M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Not the quickest out, recovered and sat just behind the leaders, ran on well to score.
Sat towards the rear, stayed on well, just missed.
Restrained on jumping, moved towards the rail and sat midfield, closed off nicely.
Sat worse than midfield, stayed on okay.
Ridden along early to lead, kept on nicely until weakened final furlong.
Settled midfield 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Sat behind midfield 3 wide, hung out rounding the Home Turn, made little progress.
Sat on pace, only one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Caught 3 wide no cover on pace, made no impression.
Jumped slowly, sat at the rear, passed only weakened rivals. (See Incident Report)
Hard ridden to sit outside lead, weakened in the Straight.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, never a threat.

Quickly into stride, showed good speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead in the middle stages, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths or so back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began only fairly from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 to 8 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Raced tight shortly after start, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made little progress.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Made contact with the right side of its barrier on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, angled out after passing 500M, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced slightly better than midfield on outer, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly and crowded, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 14, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back turning in, made no progress in the run home.
Began well from a wide draw, taken back to race at rear on the outside, still well back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
A bit keen in mid-field. Had to wait for clear run in early part of home straight and picked up well from 300m line to reel in leader and get up close home.
Soon handy. Quickened into a two-length lead 200m out but run down in the final 100m.
Waited with in rear. Sustained headway out wide from over 300m out and ran on strongly.
Caught wide throughout from high draw. Good headway after pushed along on bend and kept on until flattening out final 50m.
Tracked pace. Gave chase to leader from 300m out but unable to quite get on terms and no extra final 50m.
Held up from high draw. Kept on steadily and never nearer.
Held up and came widest off the bend. Never on terms but kept on until flattening out late.
One paced after racing in mid-field and unable to get on terms.
Made running until headed 250m out. Weakened final 150m.
Prominent but caught three wide and soon weakened from 300m line.
Rough passage in mid-field. No impression after bumped 300m out and held when eased final 100m.
Wide early from high draw before dropped in. Pushed along and no impression home straight.
Recovered from slow start to track pace against rail. Soon weakened from 400m line.
Caught wide in touch and dropped away from 300m line to finish well beaten.
Sat handy on the rail, traveled okay, made good progress from 200M, kept on well to win (Dropped rein).
Ridden along to lead, traveled smoothly, closed off nicely.
Jumped okay, settled midfield, traveled okay, made steady progress when asked.
Sat worse than midfield, raced 2 wide, responded okay under pressure.
Settled midfield, raced wide, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, chased leader, slightly weakened inside 200M.
Sat rear, held up for clear running entering the Straight, again held up inside 250M (Dropped rein).
Chased the leader, raced wide, weakened passing 300M.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear, crowded rounding the Turn, not much impression.
Settled towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, closed off fairly (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, limited response when asked (See Incident Report).
Sat behind midfield, traveled only fairly, never a threat.
Sat in front of midfield, crowded near 150M and weakened notably thereafter.
Sat towards rear, raced rear, no contention.
Improved from mid-field to challenge leaders over 200m out and soon asserted, winning readily.
Made running. No match for winner final 150m but stuck to task to hold second.
Tracked pace and held every chance final 300m.
Raced in mid-field and had to wait for clear run early in home straight. Kept on from 200m out but lacked pace to challenge.
One paced under pressure after racing in mid-division and unable to get on terms with leaders.
Across from high draw to race prominently until no extra final 250m.
Ridden in mid-field from 300m line and no impression.
Waited with towards rear. Unable to quicken for pressure and never on terms.
Keen under restraint in rear. Minimal headway final 200m and never a danger.
Under pressure off the bend after held up and no impression, receiving a slight bump 350m out.
In rear after sluggish start from high draw. Briefly short of room when looking to improve over 300m out and never dangerous.
Dropped in from high draw and never a factor.
Well placed tracking leading pair but soon weakened after coming under pressure 300m out.
Struggling in rear off bend and soon lost touch.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' rail, a bit closer in the middle stages, took the lead 300M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Began well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden from 300M, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Away well, raced better than midfield on the middle track, made good progress after passing 300M, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly from gate 14, raced towards rear on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the stands' side, no clear run until approaching 200M, made some progress thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the middle track, hard ridden and made some progress after passing 350M, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, hard ridden after passing 400M, made some progress thereafter.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on the middle track, hard ridden from 350M but only showed limited response, kept on same pace to the line.
Began well, raced in midfield on the middle track, hard ridden from 400M, peaked on run 300M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Made contact at start, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' side, commenced move approaching 300M but failed to make any progress. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced prominently on the stands' side, hard ridden from 300M but only showed limited response, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, peaked 300M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final 200M.
Away with them, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands' rail, peaked 500M, weakened final 350M.
Not the quickest out, settled behind midfield 2 wide, travelled smoothly throughout, closed off strongly to score.
Sat at the rear 2 wide, held up early part of the Straight, stayed on well. (See Incident Report)
Settled just behind the leaders, angled out to 3 wide rounding the Home Turn, hit the front at 300M, kept on until weakened slightly final 50M.
Sat last on the rail, no clear run early in the Straight, stayed on fairly.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, took some time to respond, made late ground final furlong until ran out of room final 50M.
Tracked leader, kept on until weakened final 100M.
Caught 3 wide no cover near midfield, one pace when asked. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, made little impression.
Sat midfield on the rail, limited response when asked.
Settled midfield 2 wide, made no ground.
Sat towards the rear, under pressure from 650M, made no impression.
Jumped well and led, weakened in the Straight.
Sat on pace, weakened and faded. (See Incident Report)
Began well from a poor draw, taken over 1L back to 3rd behind race leaders onto home bend, responded well inside final 300M for commanding victory.
Settled in last few and waited with, commenced move on the inside passing the 300M, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Soon picked up to 9th over 6L back on rail after moderate start, remained similar to home straight, obtained clear run near the centre of the track and ran on to reach 2nd over 100M out.
Close up early settling nearly 4L back in 7th on rail, remained similar rounding home bend and into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Soon taken some 4L back to 6th 2-wide after beginning from a poor draw, slightly further back in 7th rounding home bend and one wider into straight, fought on to hold place chance until over 80M out.
Settled just worse than midfield in 8th some 6L off the pace, became 9th around home bend, behind heels early in straight, produced some late impression closing stages.
Improved steadily along the rail after moderate start to take up running over 950M out, held narrow lead until finding no extra and overhauled 250M out.
Began fairly, ridden forward to 4th on rail just over 2L off the pace onto home bend, soon came to challenge upon straightening but had nothing to give.
Soon taken well behind, trailed the field into home straight, ran on past well-beaten horses under pressure inside final 100M.
Prominent from a poor draw, some 3L back in 5th around home bend, kept on early in straight before fading under pressure inside final 200M.
Broke well from the widest draw, travelled with the leaders 3-wide without cover before settling alongside race leader coming onto home bend, folded up quickly under pressure inside final 300M.
Always in last few, never seen with a chance.
Prompted the pace on outside travelling well throughout, took over top of straight, kept going strongly in the lead final 300M, was challenged late but had more than enough to hold on.
Chased leaders on inside, took a while to get going on straightening, did best work late to challenge leader but was always held.

Jumped only fairly settling further back than anticipated, raced keenly early stages, pushed to a 4-wide spot without cover 900M, quickened to go 2nd mid-straight but lacked the extra final 150M, couldn't get near to the winner.

Restrained to race in midfield early stages, caught wide no cover from 1000M then crept closer to leaders home turn, kept on steadily early straight but couldn't quicken enough to challenge leaders final 200M.
Reserved behind midfield, raced keenly middle stages, driven along 550M but took a long time to respond, stayed on final 200M to take 5th.
From wide draw taken back to last, switched wide passing 500M before finishing off fairly, never a winning chance.
Chased leaders in a small field contest, in similar position home turn, outpaced by rivals on straightening, had some difficulty obtaining clear running 150M but was already beaten.
Soon led, raced keenly and would not settle, found disappointingly little top of straight, weakened away. (Jockey : had some concerns with the action near 300M.)
Held up behind mid-division, waited with until 400M but gave limited response only. Never involved.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, commenced move 600M, hit the front 350M, kept on very well to the line and scored, impressive.
Began well, raced in 3rd, 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, hard ridden after passing 600M, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away well, positioned slightly behind midfield on rail, 6 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield early, found a 2 wide spot near 1300M, 3 wide from 700M, carried wider 600M, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Moderately away, raced towards rear, 8 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, 3 lengths back at 400M, made some progress early in straight, blocked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, wider 600M, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back, angled out 500M, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the outside, no cover from 1100M, improved on turn, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, peaked on run 500M, weakened final 250M.
Moderately away from gate 1, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground throughout, showed good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, travelled keenly after passing 900M, moved closer on turn, 3 wide, took the lead 150M, headed 100M, stayed on well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 150M.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 1000M, moved closer on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening the first few.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, no clear run until final 50M, kept on evenly to the line.

Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, shared the lead with rivals turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped awkwardly, raced towards rear on the outside, improved on turn, very wide into straight, kept on well in straight without threatening. (Bled.)
Crowded start, raced 3 wide at rear, angled out 550M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in the run home.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 550M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 9, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 650M, wider 500M, one-paced in the run home.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Away well, raced better than midfield but trapped 3 wide, no cover from 1000M, improved on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Broke smartly and made running. Asserted when quickening around two lengths clear 300m out and always holding on even though closed down final 100m.
Tracked pace before chasing winner home from 200m out. Closed gap final 50m but never quite getting there.
Dropped out last after hampered at start. Still well back off bend and made up plenty of ground to get close at line. Promising run.
Towards rear after slow start. Unable to reach leader but stayed on final 300m.
Tight for room in mid-field when looking to improve from 300m out and stayed on once in the clear final 150m.
Held up. No impression until angled out at 150m line and ran on late.
Clear run up rail in home straight after racing in mid-field but never looked like getting on terms with leaders.
Tracked pace until fading final 200m.
Caught three wide early before getting across to press leader. Starting to lose ground when tight for room from 200m out and eased.
Raced in mid-field. Under pressure from 300m out and never a factor.
Never out of rear after held up. Briefly short of room 100m out.
Travelled ok in mid-field to 400m out but no response to pressure and weakened.
In touch with leaders when unable to obtain a clear run 200m out and eased off.
Wide without cover and keen early. Lost touch from 300m out.

Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, took the lead 200M, kept on well to the line and scored. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 850M, angled out 350M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.

Began well, raced better than midfield on the inside early, dropped to midfield after passing 1000M, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually close home. (Blood in trachea.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, commenced move 450M, made little progress early in straight, no extra final 200M.
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 3 wide, took the lead 1150M, led by a length in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually final 150M.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 400M, slightly hampered 350M, very wide into straight, made no impression in straight.

Began well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead 1250M, headed 1150M, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, showed limited response early in straight, hampered 150M, eased thereafter.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, unable to maintain position from 500M, eased early in straight.
From draw 1 restrained to race in midfield, worked into the race well 350M, quickened up to lead mid-straight, joined by rival final 150M, gamely prevailed by nose after a duel.
Reserved in mid-division, travelled well into straight, made good headway and vied for the lead over final 100M, just denied by nose.
Not hurried after the start, raced as the back-marker 8-9Ls off leader, brought widest home and finished off nicely for 3rd.
Settled behind midfield in first half of the race, drifted back to near the rear entering home turn, brought wide into straight and came with a moderate finish.
Crowded on jumping, dropped back to race near the tail of the field, plenty of work to do 400M, closed off well without threatening first few.
Given a waiting ride towards the rear, saved ground on inside but was held up for clear running home turn, steadied 250M when trying to get through a narrow gap, kept on fairly final 200M.
Stayed close enough to leaders throughout, quickened to challenge for lead early straight but run ended 200M, no extra close home. (Bled.)
Led early stages before settling back in 5th, couldn't quicken enough on straightening, no threat from 200M.
Jumped awkwardly, went forward pressing the pace, in 3rd place making the home turn but couldn't sustain run early straight, drifted out of contention 250M.
Jumped awkwardly then dropped back to race at the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M but failed to make much progress.
Jumped awkwardly, took up running 1200M, pressed by rival middle stages and under pressure home turn, soon dropped away. (Jockey: Not intended to lead, disadvantaged by being pressured in the lead.)
Caught racing wide no cover early stages then ridden forward to take up a position outside the lead, came up empty on straightening, weakened rapidly to finish last.
Sat handy, traveled strongly, kept on well to win.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled smoothly, made some ground over the concluding stages.
Jumped smart, ridden along to lead, slightly weakened inside 150M, closed off nicely.
Sat midfield, raced keenly in the middle stages, ran on evenly.
Tracked the leader, dropped quickly after 100M, closed off fairly.
Settled behind midfield, switched out entering the Straight, one pace to the finish.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, crowded near 50M, could not be ridden out (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, raced wide until 700M, finish off fairly.
Sat rear, raced rear, made contact with the running rail rounding the Turn, held up inside 150M, no clear run.
Sat towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, limited response when asked (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, traveled fairly, steadied and checked near the 50M (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, not much impression, never a danger.
Made running. Kicked over two lengths clear on final bend and always doing enough to hold on despite reduced lead final 50m and eased late.
Mid-division after sluggish start. Driven on final turn but kept on well with a clear passage up rail and went close.
Tracked pace and chased winner home from top of home straight. Got closer final 50m but never getting there.
Settled towards rear after wide early from high draw. Headway from 300m line and kept on.
Taken wide off final bend after held up and never nearer.
One paced and unable to quicken final 200m after racing in touch with leaders.
Raced in mid-field after awkward start and unable to make any progress under pressure final 300m.
Held up. Taken wide final bend and never dangerous, passing a few inside final 150m.
Had to wait for a run final bend after waited with and never a factor.
Held up after slow start. Made no impression after coming under pressure 400m out, carrying head awkwardly.
Well placed tracking leader but weakened and dropped back through field off final turn, eased.
Raced wide in mid-field. Under pressure 400m out and soon dropped back, finishing well beaten.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 450M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished of very strongly to score.
Began well, raced in 2nd, 3/4L back turning in, showed good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 100M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced behind midfield on the outside, travelled keenly for some distance after passing 900M, 6 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Bounded on jumping, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 400M, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, commenced move 400M, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced in 3rd, 2 wide, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 10, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Shifted in on jumping and bumped, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled midfield 2 wide, responded well in the Straight, won going away, comfortably.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely.
Jumped well and led, kept on okay.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, made some progress early in the Straight, one pace final 150M.
Caught 3 wide on pace, made some late ground.
Sat last, stay on fairly.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, ran on evenly.
Hard ridden early, sat outside the lead, weakened final furlong.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, made no impression.
Settled midfield on the rail, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Raced 3 wide outside the leaders, weakened in the Straight.
Settled on pace 2 wide, no response in the Straight.
Shared early pace on rail before taken back for cover in 3rd behind race leader, fought on dourly under pressure to hold every chance but carried in closing stages. (Finished 2nd, placed 1st.)

Prominent early, forced to steady 1200M out, soon recovered to 2L 5th in back straight, well poised to challenge turning in 4-wide, quickened well to lead over 200M out, shifted in inside the 100M. (Finished 1st, placed 2nd.)
Settled in rear of midfield in 8th, soon came to challenge upon straightening, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled in around midfield on rail, obtained clear run 200M out, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Settled well behind from the widest draw and waited with, trailed the field to home straight, ran on well down the inside only to be swamped for a placing late.
Gradually settled towards rear 3-wide in 10th, gained closer to 9th in slackened pace approaching home bend, swung widest into straight, ran on under pressure without threatening.
Pressed forward from a poor draw settling 2-wide in 2nd alongside race leader, came to dispute lead rounding home bend but unable to sustain effort and weakened inside final 250M.

Hampered at start settling in worse than midfield on rail, drifted steadily further back in back straight reaching 11th despite coming under pressure, short-lived effort after saving ground home turn, folded up inside the 100M.
Soon taken back, remained in last few near the rail, commenced move rounding home bend and saved ground turning in for home, run ended about 150M out.
Settled 3-wide in midfield from a wide draw about 3L off the pace, came under pressure rounding home bend swinging wider into straight, found nothing under pressure.

Broke well from a poor draw, pressed forward out wide before settling some 2L back in 4th 3-wide without cover, closer to lead when pace slackened approaching home bend, weakened noticeably into straight.
Pressed forward from a poor draw to obtain lead on rail passing the 1200M, under pressure when joined passing the 400M, folded up quickly on straightening.
Knuckled on jumping, settled towards the rear, brought very wide on straightening, kept responding to pressure and arrived late to edge out leader in a close finish.

Began well from draw 1, restrained to race behind leaders, soon quickened to lead early straight, kept going well late only to be caught close home. (Jockey dropped left rein for a short distance near 150M.)
Jumped only fairly, held up towards the rear, waited with until 300M then finished off reasonably well to take 3rd.
Settled down midfield along the fence, held up making the home turn, kept on steadily for modest 4th but always held by leaders.
Pushed along after the start to maintain a midfield position, raced keenly early stages, taken wider 600M racing without cover, kept going well early straight but peaked on its run 200M.
Jumped only fairly, soon outpaced and detached in last, 8Ls to make up 400M, made up some ground in the straight to finish 6th.
Emerged as leader nearing 800M, held the front to 250M before weakening towards the line. (Jockey reminded to ride out to the finish.)
Began well from wide draw, took up running early stages before settling just outside leader, couldn't quicken on straightening and soon outpaced by main rivals.
Jumped on terms, dropped back to race towards the rear, wide into straight before finishing off fairly.
Went forward, vied for early lead before drifting back for cover, couldn't quicken enough on straightening, soon beaten.
Jumped fairly from wide draw then gradually moved up to chase leaders, caught racing 3-wide without cover, checked 250M then drifted out of contention.
Away with them, maintained a midfield position, driven along 450M but didn't respond to riding. (Blood in trachea.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 950M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight, won by a head.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move 500M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out 350M, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Began fairly, raced at rear, 6-1/2L back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to make frame.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, no clear run 200M to 100M, made minor progress thereafter.
Began well from the widest draw, raced prominently on the outside, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider 450M, peaked early in straight, one-paced thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well, took the early lead, headed 950M, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, angled out 450M, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began well, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back on turn, made some progress late but set an impossible task. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross 600M, sat right behind the leader on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, showed good response in straight, took the lead 250M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Bumped start, tracked leaders, 2 wide, carried wider 500M, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 2 wide after passing 550M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, no clear run until 100M, kept on well to make frame without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, angled out 500M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Away well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on the inside, angled out 500M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, peaked 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 450M, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 950M, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, made contact near 500M, very wide turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made no impression thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back, challenged the leader from 500M, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final furlong.

Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 550M, made contact near 500M, no clear run early in straight, showed limited response thereafter, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced at tail, 6 lengths back turning in, showed no response early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 400M, weakened 300M, eased final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well from a high draw, well there on stands rail, given reminders over 300M out, ran on to assert authority over 50m out.
Broke well from the middle draw and soon took up running, held 1L advantage most of the way one off stands rail, no response to winner's late surge and caught about 50M out.
Close up in 1L 3rd, came to challenge under strong pressure inside final 300M but unable to quicken to threaten.
Jumped awkwardly, gradually shifted towards stands rail to race in rear of the field, racing greenly throughout but made significant progress inside final 250M, did best work late.
Jumped well, settled in rear of midfield some 3L off the pace near stands rail, commenced move inside the 300M, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well from the one draw, travelled in prominent positions near the centre of the track, unable to quicken under pressure inside final 250M.
Jumped awkwardly settling about 1L off the pace, came under pressure to hold place inside the 300M but had nothing to give.

Badly bumped at the start, gradually recovered to rear of midfield near the centre of the track, came under pressure to hold place coming onto course proper, hung in a difficult ride inside final 300M.
Jumped awkwardly, badly bumped and unbalanced, recovered steadily to reach within 3L of pace in 8th shortly after coming onto course proper, kept on at the one pace without quickening under pressure.
Not far off the pace in early stages, gradually drifted backward towards 7th just over 2L off the pace onto course proper, faded under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly and had to be straightened, travelled keenly in prominent positions onto the course proper, dropped out under pressure.
Slowly away, tailed off most of the way, went past well-beaten runners closing stages.
Jostled after moderate start settling in rear of midfield, tight between runners and drifted further back over 600M out, made no impression thereafter.
Prominent early stages near the centre of the track, yielded ground noticeably from over 600M out.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, responded well inside 150M.
Sat midfield, traveled okay, made good progress in the Straight, closed off nicely.
Sat handy, raced keenly after the 700M, kept on well to hold 3rd (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, raced greenly, responded nicely over the concluding stages.
Sat towards rear, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, ran on evenly.
Sat rear, traveled okay, one pace to the finish.
Tracked the lead, weakened notably passing 200M, limited response thereafter.
Sat behind midfield, traveled fairly, not much impression made.
Sat worse than midfield, was checked near the 1100M, ran on only fairly.
Sat handy, switched out rounding the Turn, raced greenly, raced wide rounding the Turn, failed to respond in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, settled towards rear, no contention.
Ridden hard to lead, weakened quickly inside 350M, never a threat (See Incident Report).
Tracked leader against rail. Pushed to front off bend and always doing enough to hold runner-up final 200m.
Never far away. Upsides winner 200m out but unable to get past and held final 100m.
Recovered from slow start to track leaders by halfway. Stuck to task after ridden to challenge from 200m out but always held by front two.
Towards rear and work to do off bend after hampered in mid-field. Stayed on despite troubled passage home straight and not fully extended.
In touch with leaders but caught wide. Driven from over 200m out and lost ground.
One paced and unable to get on terms with leaders home straight after racing keenly in mid-field.
Raced in rear. Briefly tight for room when trying to improve between rivals 200m out and never dangerous.
Raced wide in rear. Some headway into mid-field under pressure final 200m but never a threat.
Waited with towards rear. Driven from over 200m out and no headway.
Held up and keen. Only short-lived headway early in straight and well held.
Made running. Headed by winner off bend and weakened quickly final 200m.
Raced wide from high draw. Lost ground quickly off bend and soon well held.
Clean jump, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, commenced move after passing 600M, 4 wide turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced in midfield, 2 wide, a bit closer on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently on the outside, took the lead approaching 800M, led by 1/2L on turn, peaked and headed near 250M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear, 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Commenced well, raced in 3rd, 3/4L back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Jumped with them, took the early lead, headed after passing 1000M, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Out with rest, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead after passing 1000M, headed approaching 800M, 2nd in the middle stages, 1/2L back turning in, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, ran on nicely, battled hard and just won.
Settled midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely, just missed.
Sat towards the rear on the rail, stayed on well.
Sat midfield on the rail, slightly held up early in the Straight, ran on okay.
Sat towards the rear 2 wide, made good progress in the Straight, jumped a mark at 170M, then continue to closed off. (See Incident Report)
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, only one pace when asked.
Caught 3 wide near midfield, ran on ordinarily.
Ridden along to lead, weakened final furlong.
Sat on pace, limited response in the Straight.
Sat last, picked off a few weakened rivals.
Sat behind midfield on the rail, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Sat on pace, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat on pace 3 wide, gave ground in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Improved steadily after moderate start to track race leader along the rail, obtained clear run upon straightening and soon hit the front over 250M out, won comfortably.
Broke well from the one draw to take up running on the rail setting a smart pace, headed by the winner over 250M out but kept on well for 2nd.

Jumped well before quickly taken backward, pulled his way forward steadily to reach rear of midfield 3-wide in 8th over 4L off the pace, ran on steadily while hanging in a difficult ride inside final 200M.

Obtained rails run at the back after first 250M reaching 10th shortly after, snuck up to 7th just some 3L back turning in for home, ran on steadily without threatening inside final 200M. (Tactic questioned)

Crowded and lost ground shortly after start but soon recovered along the rail to reach midfield in 7th within 4L of the pace, obtained clear run shortly after straightening 300M out, ran on steadily under pressure.
Crowded at start losing ground, restrained in rear on rail to straight, shifted towards the centre of track for clear run inside final 200M, ran on steadily without threatening.
Soon taken well behind from a poor draw, obtained 2-wide position at the back passing the 1200M, trailed the field until running on past beaten horses down the centre of the track.
Jumped well from a poor draw and soon taken well back 3-wide, remained similar into straight, made modest progress down the centre of the track without threatening.
Settled in last few, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, baulked for a run in straight until the 300M, produced good late impression closing stages.
Soon taken back to midfield after quick start, raced fiercely from the 1400M when restrained in 7th some 3L back, remained keen onto home turn, unable to sustain effort inside final 100M.
Ridden early and soon picked up to prominent 4th 2-wide travelling keenly at times, became 5th in similar position onto home bend, dropped away quickly inside final 300M.
Travelled in midfield after moderate start travelling keenly at times until the home straight, switched out for a run inside the 300M but unable to make any impression closing stages.
Travelled prominently and wide from a poor draw, improved to share pace 3-wide rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort inside final 300M.

Began well from the widest draw, gradually shifted across to travel alongside race leader in 2nd after the first 200M, became 3rd in similar 2-wide position rounding home bend, folded up quickly inside final 300M.
Jumped on terms, up with early pace before easing to 4th spot, travelled sweetly into straight and quickened up smartly to lead 150M, strode away for an impressive win on debut.
From draw 1 obtained a position ahead of midfield, switched away from fence 500M, worked home steadily in the run home to claim 2nd on debut. Comfortably held by winner.
Vied for early lead before emerging as clear leader 1000M, took them along at good pace, fought well early straight, headed 150M, lost 2nd close home.
Reserved towards the rear 7Ls off the good pace, had some work to do 400M, finished off mildly down the inside to claim 4th.
Went forward to be chasing leader in a race run at good tempo, fought hard to hold his position on straightening, lost 2nd near 200M, kept on one paced under top weight final stages.
Jumped only fairly, recovered to race in midfield, saved ground on inside but had difficulty obtaining clear running 200M before staying on moderately towards the line.
Taken across from wide draw and settled in second half of the field, kept on without threat in the straight but wasn't beaten too far away at the line.
Fast away, vied for early lead before taking a step back to sit in 3rd on settling, couldn't quicken enough in the straight but kept trying until no extra final 100M.
Dropped back to the rear from wide draw, 8Ls off leader middle stages, had big task in hand 400M, made some progress in the run home but never likely.
From the outside barrier caught racing wide no cover in midfield, 4Ls to make up on leader 400M, ran home one paced.
Reserved behind midfield 6Ls away, little change in position heading to home straight, failed to run on.
Caught racing 3-wide towards the rear, wide into straight but couldn't muster the pace to challenge leaders.
Jumped on terms, prominent behind leaders early stages before dropping back to midfield halfway, didn't respond to riding passing 400M, soon drifted out of contention.

Placing: PU
Comment: Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced at the rear early stages, eased down from 1100M and retired from the race. (Jockey concerned with action behind / Lame RH leg.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on strongly to the line, won by 2-1/4L.
Crowded and checked shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Began well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 900M, led by 1-1/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line, finished 3rd.
Began well, took the early lead, headed 900M, a length or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, a bit closer on turn, no daylight early in straight, one-paced thereafter.
Bumped start, tracked leaders on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the outside, 7-1/2L back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final 300M. (Bled.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1/2L back turning in, hit the front 250M, kept on well to hold off the challengers late.

Began smartly from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a head.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, no clear run until approaching final 100M, finished off well to take a place.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run until 250M, finished off well to make frame.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually close home.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide after passing 1100M, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide towards rear, 4 lengths back turning in, angled out early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until near 200M, made minor progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, no clear run early in straight, slightly hampered near 200M, kept on same pace to the line.

Away with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced towards rear of midfield, 4 wide with no cover, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail throughout, never a factor.
