Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 450M, bumped early in straight, finished off strongly to score.
Began well, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out 400M, bumped early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.

Began well, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (Lame right front leg next day.)

Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear in the early stages, 3 wide from 800M, 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide from 850M, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 125M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, sent forward after passing 900M, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, angled out 450M, very wide entering straight and dropped towards rear, made no impression in the run home.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 650M, carried wider 450M, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased final 100M.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, shared lead with rival from 500M, peaked and headed 400M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, dropped to 3rd 650M, peaked on turn, eased early in straight.
Recovered from sluggish start to track pace. Improved to challenge at 200m line and on top final 75m.
Close up throughout against rail. Every chance final 200m but winner too strong.
Raced in mid-field. Under pressure from 300m out and stayed on final 100m to get close.
Tracked pace. Sticking to task when nudged and slightly hampered late on.
Ridden from the off to hold a mid-field position but responded and stayed on final 150m.
Raced in last place until halfway after slow start. Got no room at all when trying to improve up rail final 200m and finished with plenty of running left.
Caught wide throughout in mid-field and one paced home straight.
Waited with towards rear. Making some headway when meeting brief trouble 100m out and never on terms.
Pushed along by halfway after held up and never dangerous.
Raced wide towards rear and no impression under pressure final 250m.
Raced prominently until weakening final 150m.
Made running but weakened quickly once headed 200m out.
Sat worse than midfield on the rail, traveled smoothly, responded nicely when asked.
Settled midfield, traveled comfortably, taken wide rounding the Turn, just missed.
Sat on pace, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Blundered shortly after the start, ridden hard to lead, weakened near the 200M.
Blundered on jumping, became unbalanced traveled fairly, finished off okay.
Sat in front of midfield, was taken wide rounding the Turn, one pace to the finish.
Sat midfield, held up entering the Straight, could not be ridden out when there was no clear run over the concluding stages.
Sat towards rear, traveled fairly, no impression (See Incident Report).
Sat rear, raced rear, limited response when asked.
Settled behind midfield, switched out rounding the Turn, could not finish the race off (See Incident Report).
Shared the lead, crowded entering the Straight, weakened thereafter.
Sat on pace 2 wide, weakened in the Straight.
A bit keen under restraint in rear. Clear run up rail from final turn and improved to challenge over 100m out, coming out on top in close three-way finish.
Raced in mid-field after sluggish start. Briefly crowded when improving over 200m out but every chance final 150m and beaten only narrowly.
Caught wide towards rear of mid-field. Headway to challenge from 200m line and kept on well.
Held up last. Short of room over 200m out when trying to improve and kept on once clear.
Dropped in from outside stall. Kept on in home straight after taken wide but unable to get on terms with leading trio.
Waited with in mid-field. Progress off final bend but tended to hang and no further impression final 150m.
In touch in mid-field. Ridden up to challenge at top of home straight and led briefly but no extra and weakened final 150m.
Tracked leading pair and keen. Every chance until weakening from 100m line, losing several places.
Tracked pace against rail. Well placed top of home straight but weakened from 200m line.
Raced wide throughout and weakened after coming under pressure over 400m out, eased.
Under pressure with 500m to go after racing prominently and lost ground quickly from 200m line, eased.
Keen in front. Headed off final bend and weakened quickly.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, took the lead 900M, headed near 750M, 2nd in the middle stages, hard ridden after turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin. (Blood in trachea.)

Began fairly, raced better than midfield but trapped very wide early, sent forward after entering the back straight, took the lead 750M, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Slowly away, taken back to race 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 100M, ran on well thereafter.
Quickly into stride, showed good speed to take the early lead, headed 900M, positioned a length behind the leader in the middle stages, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear,2 wide, 4-1/2L back turning in, no clear run until final 100M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Stumbled start and made contact, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 6 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, found daylight approaching 150M, made some progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly from a wide draw, in touch, 3 wide, dropped to midfield on turn, very wide into straight, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped on terms, settled midfield 2 wide, stayed on well despite laying in, won going away.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on strongly, always held.
Sat outside the leader, kept on nicely.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, no clear run until 150M, ran home nicely.
Jumped nicely and showed good early speed to lead, weakened final 100M. (See Incident Report)
Sat just behind the leaders, only one pace when asked.
Sat on pace 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Knuckled over badly on jumping, raced in midfield on the rail, closed off ordinarily.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, made no impression.
Sat near the rear, limited response in the Straight.
Sat worse than midfield 2 wide, never a threat. (See Incident Report)
Sat last, never in contention. (See Incident Report)
Niggled along in last few and waited with, lost a stride when tightened passing the 600M, responded well inside final 250M to take command over 100M out, won convincingly.
Soon recovered from sluggish start to travel in 7th some 4L off the pace, commenced move swinging wide into straight, ran on to reach distant 2nd over 100M out.
Settled in prominent 4th swinging wide into straight, ran on to hold every chance until finding no extra 100M out.
Jumped best from the one draw before taken back to track race leader, hampered and unbalanced making the home turn but ran on to hold some chance 200M out, had no more to give inside final 50M.

Towards rear despite niggled along early stages, made steady headway to 6L 8th along back straight, angled out off the rail for a clear run inside the 200M, made some impression near the centre of the track inside final 100M.
Jumped moderately travelling in last few, commenced move out wide rounding home bend and widest into straight, ran on well under strong pressure to be nearest at finish.
Hard ridden from the start from a poor draw to join race leader 2-wide 900M out, hit the front from tiring leader on straightening, unable to sustain effort and overhauled over 100M out.
Bumped at start settling just over 3L back in 6th on rail, gained 5th rounding home bend, angled out for a run making home turn, unable to quicken to challenge and found no extra inside final 100M.
Soon taken well behind from the widest draw, trailed the field until commenced move home bend, saved ground turning in on the inside, found no extra inside final 150M.
Ridden forward to take up running on the rail into back straight, held mainly half a length advantage to home straight, swamped for a placing inside final 150M.
Niggled along towards rear, dropped further back from approaching home bend, never seen with a chance.
Settled some 3L back in 5th 2-wide, became 6th rounding home bend, soon weakened in straight.
In second half of the field early stages, pushed along and moved closer to a midfield spot home turn, kept responding in the straight under pressure to get up close home.
Chased leaders in 4th, closed off well final 300M, fought neck to neck with eventual winner from 150M, just denied.
Sped to the lead, opened up 2L advantage turning home, kept going well only to be caught by first two passing 50M.
Slow to begin, raced towards the rear early stages before improving to midfield home turn, stayed on under big weight to claim modest 4th. Gap to rest.
Jumped on terms, settled ahead of midfield, kept on steadily on straightening but couldn't quicken enough to challenge leaders.
Shifted out abruptly at the start, ridden along to maintain a midfield spot, checked 600M and lost ground, lay out in the straight and proved difficult to fully test. No threat to first four.
Checked shortly after the start, raced towards the rear, plenty to do top of straight, ran past beaten horses only.
Jumped only fairly, ended up racing near last, 9Ls off leader 400M, made some progress in the straight but never a threat to leaders.
Chased leader in a fast run race, lost 2nd nearing 200M then weakened away. (Blood in trachea / Trainer : disadvantaged by rival showing superior pace in early stages.)
Positively ridden early stages, stayed prominent behind leader but gave ground passing 300M.
Soon outpaced, in last spot over 10Ls off the pace, failed to quicken on straightening. Never in the picture.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 400M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly, led last stride.

Made contact shortly after start, positioned 2Ls behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, took the lead 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Moderately away, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place, always just held. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider and made contact 450M, finished off well to make frame, not quite able to challenge.

Made contact shortly after start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some progress early in straight, not enough room 200M to 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 6-1/2L back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, nearest finish.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, angled out 450M, very wide turning in, made minor progress early in straight, short of room and eased final 50M.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made minor progress early in straight, not enough room and eased final 50M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back in the middle stages, still last turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out and made contact 450M, showed some response early in straight, no clear run final 200M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Jumped with them, raced in 3rd, 6 lengths or so back in the middle stages, moved closer on turn, finished off strongly, led near finish.
Out with rest, sent forward to take the lead and set a fast tempo, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner near finish. (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 14 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, still 9 to 10 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 500M, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Began only fairly, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 8 lengths back in the middle stages, moved closer on turn, angled out approaching 450M, kept on evenly in straight.
Shifted out at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, 8 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 2 wide, still well back on turn, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out with rest, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to race in 2nd, peaked on run 400M, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced in midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
From draw 12 maintained a position behind midfield, raced keenly middle stages and got shuffled back on the home turn, quickened up nicely from 350M to get up close home for a pleasing debut victory.
Positively ridden, vied for the lead on inside, 2nd turning for home, kept responding well under pressure in the straight, just no match for winner late.
Jumped only fairly and from a wide barrier was taken back to last in the early stages, over 7Ls to make up 400M, closed off fastest down the outside to go 3rd. Nearest finish.
Went forward on jumping from draw 10, caught 3-wide outside leader first half of the race, opened up a 2L lead 400M, kept going well until no extra and headed 100M out.
Away well enough, restrained to race in midfield along the inside, held up briefly top of the straight before staying on for a non-threatening 5th.
Drifted back to race behind midfield, saved ground on inside, made some progress final 400M but not going the pace to challenge leaders.
Began well, restrained to race in a 3-wide position midfield, shuffled back to near last turning for home, closed off mildly under big weight but could make no impression on first few.
Settled down midfield 4Ls off leader, kept on only fairly in the straight, never a threat to leaders.
Jumped on terms from draw 1, always in touch behind leaders, moved up to 3rd mid-straight, run ended 150M. (Bled.)
Chased leaders, came under pressure to maintain position home turn, soon drifted out of contention on straightening.
Away with them, drifted back to race near last, plenty to do 400M but failed to run on.
Urged along after the start, soon up with leaders, struggled to hold position 500M, weakened rapidly on straightening. (Difficult to load / Unacceptable barrier manners and performance.)
Sat handy on the rail, traveled comfortably, switched out rounding the Turn, made good progress ion the Straight to win.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, responded well inside 200M.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide throughout, kept on okay to hold 3rd.
Shared the lead until 750M, traveled okay, slightly weakened inside 150M.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear, made steady progress, ran on evenly.
Shared the lead until 750M, weakened entering the Straight (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide, one pace to the finish.
Sat midfield, two wide, traveled fairly, minor progress made.
Sat midfield, limited response when asked, no impression.
Sat rear, raced rear, failed to respond (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, steadied when crowded rounding the Turn, never a danger.
Settled worse than midfield, raced wide, weakened passing 100M (Substantial blood in trachea, See Incident Report).
Outpaced early and behind. Headway on bend and sustained run down home straight to lead close home.
Wide early but soon in touch with leaders. Challenged from 200m out and every chance.
Raced prominently. Led from over 200m out until headed and lost two places close home.
Wide throughout from high draw. Chased leaders and kept on from bend but one paced final 50m.
Recovered from slow start to race mid-division. One paced under pressure home straight but passed a few late on.
Some headway off bend after racing in mid-field but no further impression final 100m.
Towards rear before hanging left on bend and getting behind. Still plenty to do 200m out before making late gains on tiring rivals.
Soon outpaced and well behind by halfway. Closed up from over 200m out and passed a few tiring rivals late on.
Settled in mid-field after sluggish start. Some headway off bend but no further impression final 100m.
Raced in touch but unable to pick up for pressure from over 200m out and weakened late on.
Caught three wide as he disputed lead and weakened final 200m.
Disputed lead until weakening over 200m out.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden from 300M, showed very good response, took the lead close home, won by a nose.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead approaching 500M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home, beaten by a narrow margin.
Began smartly from gate 14, sent forward to take the lead, headed approaching 500M, kept on well to take a place.
Began well, raced in midfield on the middle track, kept on well final 400M to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Out with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' rail, moved a bit closer after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced slightly behind midfield, nearer to the middle track, 3-3/4L back at 400M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear on the stands' side, 4 lengths back at 400M, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly and crowded shortly after start, raced towards rear, 4 lengths back at 400M, no clear run until final 50M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 10, raced in midfield on the stands' side, one-paced final 400M.

Out with them, made contact shortly after start, raced in midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped only fairly, raced at rear, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 350M, kept on same pace to the line.
Began well from gate 13, raced prominently on the stands' side, peaked on run 300M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced towards rear, nearer to the middle track, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on the middle track, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, closed off well to score.
Settled midfield 2 wide, ran on nicely, couldn't held off the winner.
Jumped nicely, showed good pace to lead, kept on nicely until weakened final 150M. (See Incident Report)
Sat just behind the leaders early, switched out in the Straight, made good progress early in the Straight, but only one pace final furlong.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, stayed on fairly.
Jumped awkwardly, settled near the rear 3 wide, ran on evenly.
Sat at the rear, made some late ground.
Sat last, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, made no impression
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, weakened in the Straight.
Settled at the rear 3 wide, limited response in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Tracked leader, under pressure from 600M, weakened soon after.
Raced towards the rear, never involved. (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Sat midfield on the rail, never in contention. (Performance unacceptable, must trial)
Ridden forward to be up with the pace briefly before settling one back in 3rd 900M out, soon came to challenge on straightening and hit the front over 200M out.
Jumped fairly before settling some 3L back on rail between 6th and 4th, snuck closer into straight and ran on steadily under pressure in closing stages to snatch 2nd late.
Ridden forward from a poor draw to soon take up running 2-wide, joined by one other rounding home bend and narrowly headed by eventual winner over 200M out, lost 2nd close to home.
Broke well from a middle draw settling mainly some 3L back in 6th, came to challenge from a similar position into straight and fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped well settling in last few, tight when lost position 800M out, went widest turning in for home, made up good ground under pressure near the centre of the track, did best work late.
Jumped fairly from the one draw, niggled along improving gradually to share the pace on rail home bend, unable to sustain effort and weakened out of contention under pressure inside final 200M.
Settled wide towards the rear, one of the widest turning in for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled very wide without cover in midfield from a poor draw, kept on same pace without making any serious impression in home straight.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, ridden along in rear on rail, gained close to pace onto home bend, kept on one pace without quickening in straight.
Ridden along improving steadily to rear of midfield onto home bend when baulked behind runners, switched off heels for a run 350M out, made no impression in the run to the line.
Began well from the widest draw travelling wide without cover in midfield, made headway to reach 2L4th 4-wide around home bend, tired noticeably in straight.
Stumbled badly and lost considerable ground at start, never recovered.
Given a patient ride near the rear, swung wide home turn before running on well to lead near 150M. Always doing enough to hold off the persistent 2nd late.
Restrained to race in mid-division, left racing 3-wide no cover from 800M, quickened up fairly well on straightening to claim lead 250M, gave everything but couldn't hold off winner final stages.
Not hurried after the start, settled in second half of the field and waited with until 500M, tried hard when asked but couldn't match the finishing pace of first two. Held on for 3rd just.
Taken back to last from wide draw, given a waiting ride as usual, had 6Ls to make up 400M, did best work late without troubling first two. Just missed 3rd spot.
From draw stayed prominent behind leaders, poised to strike on straightening but was held up from 350M to 250M. Not able to challenge first two when clear, faded late stages.
Jumped fairly, restrained to a rearward spot 6Ls off the lead, held up for a short distance home turn before running on fairly towards the line.
Contested the early lead but was dropped back to a midfield spot in middle stages, kept on fairly final 400M. Never a winning hope.
Caught wide in the early stages, strode forward to avoid cover additional ground, chased leaders turning for home but failed to pick up, soon no threat to leaders.
Jumped only fairly, stayed in touch with leaders early before dropping back to midfield middle stages, shuffled back to near last 500M, couldn't muster any sort of challenge in the straight.
Jumped only fairly, reserved in midfield and had a ground saving trip to the home straight, held up for clear running 300M-200M but the finishing effort was only fair final stages.
Caught racing wide early stages, slowly improved to race outside leader 900M, couldn't sustain effort mid-straight, weakened away. (Jockey : didn't show its usual early pace.)
Emerged as leader passing 1400M, raced too keenly in the lead and as a result was left without a finishing effort on his first AWT attempt , weakened rapidly final 250M.
Knuckled on jumping, obtained a midfield position but raced wide and without cover for the majority of the event, already beaten top of the straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out 500M, hard ridden after passing 300M, hit the front 100M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide from 600M, took the lead 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M, finished 2nd.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail near 500M, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, made some progress thereafter to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.

Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, 2 wide from 500M, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, finished off evenly.
Away well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped only fairly, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, angled out 600M, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Bumped start, raced at tail, very wide turning in, made no impression in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, wider 550M, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, failed to make any progress thereafter.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, trapped wide in midfield, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced in 3rd, 2 lengths or so back, showed very good response in straight hit the front 250M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out approaching 500M, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, took the early lead, headed near 900M, 2nd on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened final 150M.
Began only fairly, raced at rear, 6-1/2L back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made little progress early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly and made contact, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead near 900M, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened thereafter.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, commenced move 400M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, commenced move 450M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.

Reared as stalls opened and lost ground, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back on turn, angled out 350M, very wide into straight, bumped 300M, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 1 out 1 back, 3 wide turning in, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 350M, no clear run early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 400M, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, made minor progress inside final furlong.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, 3 wide turning in, not enough room near 250M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, 3-1/2L back, 2 wide from 400M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground throughout, no clear run early in straight, weakened quickly final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled towards rear in 7th of strung-out field, commenced move on top of home bend 400M out, ran on under pressure to assert authority close to home.
Settled just better than midfield in 6th or 5th, soon came to challenge on straightening, hit the front briefly 50M out only to be caught shortly afterwards.
Well there, restrained one-out-one-back to 2L 4th into back straight, hit the front under pressure 200M out only to be caught over 50M out,
With leaders early before taken back to 5th on rail into back straight some 3L off the pace, became 6th when pace quickened approaching home bend, kept on for remote 4th.
Began moderately settling wide in last few, widest into straight, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Hard ridden in last few after slow start, settled towards rear on rail in 8th, renewed effort rounding home bend, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Slowly away, remained in last few to home straight, kept on well in the run to the line.
Taken back to last from the widest draw and waited with, trailed the field to straight, ran on well dourly between runners.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground before driven forward steadily to join race leader over 800M out, hit the front over 650M out, held 2L advantage rounding home bend and led until headed over 200M out.

Shared early pace, ceded lead position on rail for cover into back straight, drifted further back to 3L 4th approaching home bend, hung in under pressure early in straight, had no more to give 100M out.
Jumped awkwardly and jockey lost use of iron early, remained in last few throughout and never seen with a chance.
Broke well from a poor draw vying for lead out wide, obtained rails run over 800M out shortly before headed about 650M out, dropped away under pressure quickly inside final 250M.
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, traveled strongly, switched out rounding the Turn, closed off nicely.
Ridden along to lead, traveled comfortably, had every chance.
Settled midfield, raced wide, made forward move passing 900M, made some progress in the Straight (See incident Report).
Sat midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, held up rounding the Turn, not quicken enough (See Incident Report).
Jumped awkwardly, settled in front of midfield, ran on evenly.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled okay, ran on fairly (See incident Report).
Sat midfield, minor progress made in the Straight, no impression.
Sat handy, traveled fairly, limited response when asked.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, one pace to the finish (See incident Report).
Sat rear, traveled only fairly, never a threat.
Settled towards rear, steadied rounding the Turn, could not respond when asked.
Sat handy, gave ground quickly rounding the Turn, failed to respond (Unacceptable Performance, Must BT).
Raced in mid-field. Sustained headway from top of home straight and stayed on strongly final 50m to lead on line.
Tracked pace. Overhauled front-runner late on but headed by winner on line.
Got across from wide draw to make running. Still over two lengths clear 100m out but overhauled close home.
Towards rear of mid-field after bumped at start. Stayed on steadily final 200m.
Stayed on from mid-field but unable to reach leaders.
Held up from wide stall. Last at 200m line before good headway, passing several rivals final 100m.
Raced in last place after sluggish start. Late headway past rivals when short of room and steadied final 40m.
One paced under pressure in home straight after held up and never dangerous.
Raced widest from high draw and no impression under pressure final 200m.
Pushed along in mid-field from halfway and limited impression when briefly short of room 100m out. Lost ground final 50m.
Tracked leader until weakening final 150m.
Weakened from 200m out after racing close up. Eased final 50m.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield, commenced move 450M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, commenced move 450M, took the lead early in straight, headed 150M, kept on well to the line, just beaten by a head,
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Out with rest, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 400M, closed off well to make frame, not quite able to challenge.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out 400M, made some progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear, 9 lengths or so back, still 8 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to be nearest on line.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, a bit closer on turn, 2 wide turning in, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, still well back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped on jumping, raced towards rear on the inside, 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, ran on strongly.
Not the quickest out, settled midfield on the rail, closed off nicely for 2nd.
Sat on pace 2 wide, kept on for 3rd.
Sat outside the leader, kept on until weakened final 50M.
Ridden along to lead, weakened final 100M.
Settled in front of midfield 3 wide, raced keenly, one pace when asked.
Settled worse than midfield 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Settled towards the rear 3 wide, stayed on fairly.
Slow to jumped, settled towards the rear, made no impression.
Sat last, under pressure midway, made minor late ground. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield 2 wide, never a threat.
Settled behind midfield 3 wide, never in contention.
Crowded at start, settled one back in 3rd on rail, ran on under pressure to hit the front 150M out, just held on to the line.
Amongst leaders early stages, gradually taken one-out-one-back onto first bend, commenced move over 400M out and ran on under pressure to hold every chance the length of the straight.
Crowded at start losing ground settling well behind on rail, saved ground turning in for home, ran on well between runners to miss narrowly.
Wide in midfield early stages, slightly worse when 8th rounding first bend and in back straight, came under pressure home bend swinging wide into straight, ran on well to be nearest at finish.

Pressed forward from the widest draw to join the leaders, persevered around the bend to reach 2nd just half a length back, hit the front into home straight only to be headed 150M out, swamped for a placing close to home.
Ducked off runner towards the rail early gradually settling in 5th on rail some 3L off the pace, became 6th in similar position rounding home bend 400M out, kept on steadily without quickening.
Crowded at start losing ground before settling in last few, made no serious impression in home straight.
Ridden prominently early settling in midfield in 6th in back straight, made headway 3-wide rounding home bend, kept on until finding no extra 100M out. (Lame)
Settled 3-wide in last few after beginning from a wide draw, remained in similar position before swinging wider into home straight, ran on past well-beaten horses.
Settled mainly in rear of midfield on rail, saved ground turning in for home, ran home one-paced.
Dipped and tightened at the start gradually settling in last few, never seen with a chance. (Found to have an epiglottic entrapment)
Improved gradually from a poor draw to take up running 1200M out and rails run shortly after, held slender advantage until headed into home straight, weakened noticeably.
From draw 12 caught racing wide no cover chasing leaders, gave instant response when asked 300M, led mid-straight and drew away for a wide margin victory.
Jumped only fairly, patiently ridden in a rearward spot, swung wide into straight before finishing off well to claim 2nd close home. Not reach winner.
Away in line, settled ahead of midfield, ran on mildly inside 300M but never going the pace to challenge winner.
Obtained a midfield position, moved closer to leaders nearing 400M, had every chance on straightening but couldn't quicken enough over final 200M.

Not hurried after the start, held up towards the rear, brought to outside for his challenge but responded only fairly. (Jockey was advised he should ensure that he continues to ride his mounts out to the finish.)
Settled down in midfield, 8th into straight, held up over final 300M and didn't obtain clear running. Not properly tested.
Bumped on jumping, stayed in touch behind leaders, held up for clear running from 300M to 100M, left with too much to do late stages. Inconclusive run.
Quickly away, tracked leader along the fence, held up 300M-200M but the finishing response was only fair over final stages.
Restrained to race behind midfield, swung wide for home and 4Ls to make up top of straight, kept on only fairly.
Chased leader along the 2-path, moved forward vying for the lead passing 400M, run ended 150M and lost several places late. (Jockey concerned the action of his mount over the concluding stages.)
Bumped and became unbalanced after the start, dropped back to last 9Ls off the pace early stages, still last turning for home, failed to muster any sort of challenge.
Began well from draw 1 and soon in front setting the pace, caught inside 300M, weakened rapidly mid-straight to last. (Jockey : didn't appreciate the step-up to Class 3.)
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 500M, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Crowded start, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began smartly, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, showed good response in straight, took the lead approaching 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two close home.
Crowded start, raced slightly better than midfield on outer, commenced move 450M, kept on well in straight to make frame, always just held.
Shifted in at start, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, challenged the leader from 450M, held every chance in straight but unable to sustain effort final 50M.
Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, commenced move 400M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, 1 out 1 back in the middle stages, hard ridden after passing 450M, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.

Made contact shortly after start, raced in midfield early, unbalanced and lost ground 1600M, raced at rear in the middle stages, 4Ls back turning in, no clear run in straight, eased 100M. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Shifted out at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 350M, no clear run early in straight, showed limited response thereafter, eased closing stages.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Shifted out at start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, hard ridden from 300M, took the lead 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Out with rest, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 2 wide from 700M, 3 lengths back turning in, angled out and made contact early in straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the rail, a bit closer on turn, unable to obtain clear run until near 150M, finished off well to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, angled out 500M, 4-1/2L back turning in, bumped near 300M, made good progress thereafter to make frame without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 500M, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped well, tracked leaders, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, angled out and made contact early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.

Made contact with the left side of its barrier on jumping and became unbalanced, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)

Average to begin, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, bumped and crowded near 300M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced wide in mid-field. Quickened to lead 200m out after smooth headway and soon in control, winning very readily.
Got across to race prominently from wide draw. No match for winner from 200m line but stuck to task to hold second.
Still had a lot to do at top of home straight after held up from wide draw. Stayed on well and made up plenty of ground final 250m.
Never far away. Lacked pace of winner from 200m out but stuck to task.
Stayed on from mid-field after briefly short of room over 300m out but lacked pace to challenge winner.
Raced without cover in mid-field and keen. Unable to sustain effort final 150m.
Keen under restraint in rear. Still had plenty do when short of room 300m out and unable to get on terms.
Tracked pace. Pushed along off bend and struggling to quicken when briefly hampered 300m out. No impression after.
Waited with in rear. Troubled passage in home straight after kept to rail and never on terms.
No impression under pressure after racing in mid-field.
Always towards rear and never a factor.
Little impression under pressure after held up.
Made running until headed and weakened 300m out.
Weakened quickly from turn after tracking pace, dropping right away.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled comfortably, made good progress inside 250M, ran on nicely.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled smoothly, responded nicely when hard ridden.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened entering the Straight, had every chance.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, switched out rounding the Turn. Made steady progress over the concluding stages.
Sat towards rear, traveled okay, responded fairly when asked.
Jumped only fairly, sat behind midfield, switched out rounding the Turn, closed off fairly.
Settled handy, two wide, minor progress made (See Incident Report).
Settled midfield, traveled fairly, limited response when asked.
Jumped only fairly, settled behind midfield, no clear run over the concluding stages (See Incident Report).
Got its head up on jumping, settled towards rear, failed to make up ground (Substantial blood in trachea, Must BT, See Incident Report).
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, raced keenly and wide without cover, could not finish the race off (See Incident Report).
Sat towards rear, raced greenly, gave ground quickly.
Sat handy, commenced to race keenly near the 900M, weakened quickly in the Straight.
Raced in mid-field. Short of room and shuffled back 400m out before quickening through to lead 150m out and soon on top, running on strongly.
Waited with towards rear of mid-field and short of room when looking to improve over 300m out. Never a threat to winner but kept on well; final 200m, taking second 50m out.
Held up. Made a rapid move out wide on final bend to lead early in home straight but headed and no extra final 150m.
Raced in mid-field. Lacked pace of winner final 200m but kept on steadily.
In touch with leaders but caught three wide. Driven up to challenge off final bend and every chance until no extra final 150m.
Headway out wide off final turn after racing in mid-field but unable to sustain effort final 150m. Jockey dropped whip 300m out.
Dropped in from high draw. Involved in bumping match with rival early in home straight against rail but some headway until no further impression final 150m.
In rear after slow start. Some headway after short of room early in home straight but never dangerous.
Waited with in rear. Hung right under pressure in home straight and never dangerous.
Chased leader until weakening from 400m out.
Soon recovered from sluggish start to make running. Headed over 300m out and weakened, eased final 100m.
Tracked pace against rail. Hung right under pressure from over 300m out and weakened, eased final 100m.
A bit keen early in prominent position. Weakened quickly off final turn and dropped away.
Began only fairly, raced prominently, 2 wide, 1/2L back turning in, took the lead 300M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until approaching final 100M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to take a place.
Shifted in at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made very good progress early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Taken back to from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run until approaching 200M, made some headway thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, made no impression thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide towards rear, wider turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded start, raced behind midfield on outer, a bit closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, angled out 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide, there to turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Sat just outside the leader, under pressure from 600M, kept on well to score.
Not the quickest out, ridden along early to lead, kept on.
Settled midfield on the rail, angled out in the Straight, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Sat midfield 2 wide, closed off okay.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, under pressure from the 850M, closed off evenly.
Sat behind midfield 2 wide, stayed on fairly.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, made little progress. (See Incident Report)
Sat at the rear 2 wide, picked off a few weakened rivals. (See Incident Report)
Sat on pace 2 wide, weakened in the Straight.
Settled worse than midfield, made no impression.
Sat behind the leaders, limited response in the Straight.
Sat last, never a threat.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, weakened and faded final 300M. (See Incident Report)
Settled near the rear, never in contention.
Broke well in front sharing the pace until ceded advantage while shifting 2-wide about 1000M out, renewed effort entering straight to hit the front shortly afterward, driven clear inside final 150M.
Travelled wide in midfield early stages, taken back to last few about 1100M out, commenced move under pressure from 600M out swinging widest into straight, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Bumped at start settling well behind and waited with, swung wide into straight, ran on well inside final 300M to be nearest at finish.
Well there and gradually shifted across from a poor draw, obtained rails run in front passing the 1000M, led until narrowly headed into straight, swamped for a placing inside final 100M.
Settled in better than midfield sharing 4th most of the way to home straight, tight between runners and checked about 350M out, fought on steadily to the line.

Shared 4th on rail just over 2L off the pace, gained closer to lead when pace steadied home bend, barged his way out for a run 350M out causing interferences, fought on steadily for 4th but demoted to 6th by Stewards.

Soon taken well back from the widest draw and waited with, gained two closer rounding home bend, badly hampered until the 300M after wide into straight, forced to switch again 150M out and did best work late.

Well there from a poor draw and wide without cover early, taken over 2L back for cover from over 1200M out but remained 3-wide sharing 4th around home bend, bumped and unbalanced 350M out, fought on steadily.
Travelled keenly in 2L 5th before drifting to 7th 3-wide 1200M out, over 4-wide into straight and hampered 350M out, kept on steadily to the line.
Settled towards rear from a poor draw, gained closer on rail in slackened pace rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening in straight.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to rear of midfield, drifted towards rear onto home bend, made headway 3-wide from over 600M out, badly bumped twice and unbalanced early in straight, never recovered.
Settled in rear of midfield some 4L off the pace on rail, gained closer while pace slackened around home bend, baulked and switched in for a run over 350M out, one paced in the run to the line.

Slow into stride but soon recovered to join race leaders, tightened and dropped to 3rd 1050M out, 3-wide around home bend and jostled between runners just before forced to steady 350M out, never recovered.
Lacked pace and soon dropped to rear of midfield, found nothing in home straight.
Began well, restrained to race in the 4th spot always in touch with leaders, driven 400M and wrestled the lead near 200M, kept on strongly late stages for an authoritative win.
Settled towards the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, closed off final 400M fastest, took 2nd close home but never got to the winner.
Moved up to chased leader, held 2nd spot from 1600M, went on and took over near 400M, headed mid-straight before losing 2nd close home.
Jumped fairly, caught wide early stages and was steadied to obtain a position with cover near the rear, had some work to do 400M, stayed on to claim 4th near line but posed no threat to first three.
Close up behind leaders early stages, eased back to race in midfield from 1400M, couldn't quicken enough to challenge first three on straightening, kept on mildly to line, lost 4th close home.
Not hurried after the start, waited with in a rearward position 6Ls off the pace, found the line fairly passing 400M and was never a winning hope.

Restrained after the jump, given a waiting ride at the back of the field 7-8Ls off the pace, responded only fairly and made only limited progress from 400M, raced tight late not ridden out near the finish.
Settled down in mid-division, caught wide no cover from 1500M, moved up to 4th at 400M, couldn't sustain run mid-straight and faded.
Obtained a midfield position along the fence, driven 450M but failed to run on.
Soon took up running, set steady pace to the home straight, headed near 400M, soon weakened drifted out of contention.
Jumped well and went forward to track leaders without being pressured to do so, gave way top of the straight then weakened to finish last. (Jockey : intended to ride in a conservative manner.)
Taken back from gate 12, raced behind midfield on the outside, angled out after turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Began well from a wide draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled comfortably on turn, took the lead 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Bumped heavily on jumping and blundered, raced 2 wide behind midfield, a bit closer in the middle stages, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, a bit closer on turn, no clear run early in straight, made some progress thereafter to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began well, sat right behind the leader on the inside, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (A small cut to the left front fetlock.)
Began fairly, taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths back in the middle stages, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began well from gate 14, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 550M, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, there to turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest finish.
Jumped only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 550M, closed off well to take a place.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few close home.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail 800M, angled out 450M, no clear run until final 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Average to begin, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, not enough room until final 200M, kept on same pace to the line.
Blundered shortly after start, raced in midfield, 2 wide, angled out 500M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run until approaching final 50M, made no impression thereafter.
Out with rest, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, no cover from 900M, moved closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved closer 1050M, 2nd in the middle stages, 2 wide, peaked on run 300M, weakened and eased final furlong.
Began well from a wide draw, sat right behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, weakened early in straight.
Began fairly, raced towards rear, 2 wide, difficult to settle throughout, dropped to last 600M, eased final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began awkwardly and made contact, taken back to race at tail, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score. (A cut to the right front leg.)
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 400M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home, nearest finish.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 500M, very wide into straight, kept on same pace in straight.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly and made contact, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, peaked on run 400M, weakened early in straight. (Roarer.)
Jumped only fairly, taken back to last 5-6Ls off leader, still plenty to do top of straight, did best work final 200M, got up last stride.
Ended up leading the field in a slowly run race, kept to task well on straightening, caught by winner near line. (Jockey : not his intention to lead.)
Stayed in touch with leaders along the fence, moved up to 3rd 200M, dug deep late stages and just missed 2nd in a close finish.
From draw 1 moved up to track leader in a slowly run race, poised to strike 300M, ran on steadily to the line but was always held by first 3 late stages.
Restrained to race behind midfield, raced keenly in the middle stages, brought wide top of straight then ran on well under top weight to be nearest at the finish.
Jumped fairly, settled near last further back than intended, raced keenly early stages, briefly held up early straight before closing off the race mildly.
Driven forward, vied for early lead before sitting back in 3rd, couldn't accelerate enough on straightening, well held by leaders final 200M.
Away on terms, taken across to the fence and obtained a position behind midfield, ran home one paced final 300M, never a threat to leaders.
Raced keenly in a position ahead of midfield, unable to run on when placed under pressure passing 300M. (Jockey : unsuited when the pace of the event was run outside of standard.)
From draw 12 caught racing wide no cover in midfield, left behind by rivals from 300M and was soundly beaten.
Sat handy, traveled comfortably, responded nicely when asked.
Settled midfield, traveled okay, slightly held up entering the Straight, ran on well.
Settled midfield, raced wide until 600M, hung in in the Straight, closed off okay.
Taken back and raced rear, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, was checked over the concluding stages (See Incident Report).
Sat in front of midfield, traveled fairly, switched out rounding the Turn, ran on evenly.
Ridden along to lead, traveled okay, was checked and lost running over the concluding stages (See Incident Report).
Settled behind midfield, crowded near the 100M, could not be ridden out.
Shared the lead, raced greenly, closed off fairly.
Sat towards rear, limited response when asked, no impression.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, taken wider entering the Straight, weakened (Lame right fore on the day after racing).
Settled worse than midfield, steadied near 1000M, raced wide from 600M, minor progress made.
Jumped awkwardly, sat towards rear, never a threat.
Keen early and settled towards rear after 300m. Taken wide off bend and came with sustained run to lead close home.
Pressed in front. Saw off that rival at 200m line and stayed in the lead until headed by strong-finishing winner close home.
Held up from wide draw. In last place off turn and finished off well despite twice meeting interference in home straight.
Recovered from slow start to race in mid-field. Kept on but no further impression on leader final 50m.
Dropped in from wide draw and waited with. Kept on up rail but lacked pace to challenge.
Tracked pace until no extra and lost ground final 100m.
In touch with leaders. Unable to quicken for pressure from 200m out.
Raced in mid-field. Pushed along turning in before twice short of room final 200m. Not fully extended.
Wide off turn after racing in mid-field and never dangerous, bumped 150m out.
Soon prominent but caught three wide. Weakened final 200m.
Bumped at start and keen in rear. Very wide off turn and left behind.
Pressed leader until weakening final 200m.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 450M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, angled out 350M, took the lead 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Made contact shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 8-1/2L back turning in, bumped and unbalanced near 300M, made some progress early in straight, no clear run 100M, kept on again final 50M.
Fast into stride, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out approaching 400M, finished off well without threatening.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, no extra final 50M.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths or so back, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made no impression in the run home.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out 450M, bumped early in straight, made no progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed no response early in straight, eased thereafter. (Bled.)
Not the quickest out, ridden along early to lead, travelled comfortably, taken on at 650M, kept on and fought back to win.
Settled midfield 3 wide no cover, challenged and taken the lead at 550M, kept on nicely.
Taken back from the wide barrier, settled towards the rear on the rail, stayed on well.
Sat midfield 2 wide, closed off nicely.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on evenly.
Settled behind the leaders, one pace when asked.
Settled midfield on the rail, limited response in the Straight.
Sat near the rear 2 wide, made some late ground.
Was behind midfield early and caught wide, improved outside the lead, weakened in the Straight.
Settled towards the rear, never a threat.
Sat last, never involved.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, never in contention.
Crowded at start settling in midfield in 6th on rail, commenced move passing the 400M but tightened for a run over 200M out, sustained effort closing stages to snatch victory near the line.

Pressed forward after jockey repositioned his foot in the stirrup to take up running just over 800M out, set a sound pace in the front to straight, held over 1L advantage in straight until weakened and collared in the shadow of post.
Crowded at start settling at the back and waited with, commenced move rounding home bend, shifted off heels for a run over 200M out and finished off the race well.
Soon taken well behind, last into straight, finished off the race strongly inside final 200M, did best work late.
Settled over 2L off the pace in 5th or 4th on rail, in similar position turning in for home, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Broke well from a poor draw settling over 2L off the pace in 4th or 5th, slightly further back rounding home bend, kept on steadily without threatening.
Soon taken back in midfield from the widest draw, steadied for a run upon straightening, kept on well without making any serious impression.
Checked and lost position after moderate start dropping to last few 3-wide, remained wide without cover rounding home bend and the widest into straight, found nothing.
Began well from a poor draw travelling 3-wide without cover in 3rd about 2L oft the pace, soon found no extra after straightening.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start settling in last few on rail, angled off rail for a run entering straight, found nothing.

Amongst leaders after beginning from a wide draw, taken back from brief lead 900M out to settle in 2nd alongside race leader, came under pressure into home straight, hung in and then ducked out 250M out, soon weakened.
Settled in last few, never seen with a chance.
Bustled along after the start, sat 4th on settling, quickened up well from 300M and proved too strong final stages.
Jumped on terms, chased leaders in 3rd, fought hard vying for the lead on straightening, just couldn't match winner's pace final 100M.
Quickly into stride, soon led and took them along at steady pace, continued on well inside 300M, lost lead near 100M but held on well enough for 3rd.
Slow to begin, recovered to race just behind midfield, 5Ls off at 400M, closed off well final 250M to claim 4th near line.
Taken back from outside draw, held up 7Ls back near last on the inside, closed off fairly well final 300M. (Jockey : instructed to ride his mount in a conservative manner from wide draw.)
Settled in second half of the field, bustled along 450M, stayed on without troubling leaders.
From draw 1 obtained an inside spot ahead of midfield, ran home mildly on straightening, no extra closing stages.
From a wide draw made some early use to go forward, 2nd on settling, kept battling in the straight before fading final 100M.
Jumped awkwardly, restrained in mid-division along the 2-path, ran home fairly final 300M. Well held by leaders.
From wide draw switched off to race in last, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, had big task in hand 400M but could only make limited progress in straight. (Jockey : hung in throughout the event.)
Eased back to race near last 7Ls off leader, swung wide into straight but unable to finish off the race. (Trainer : may have been disadvantaged by settling back in the field.)
Jumped awkwardly, unable to slot in and caught racing wide no cover behind midfield, weakened 300M and drifted out of contention.
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, finished off strongly to score by a head.
Crowded start, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Began well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, made good progress thereafter, nearest finish.
Jumped only fairly and was crowded, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide on turn, kept on same pace in straight.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, moved a bit closer after passing 750M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, 4-1/2L back turning in, kept on same pace in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer after passing 750M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
