Began well, in touch, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead near 250M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 2-3/4L back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 550M, 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress, nearest finish.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, 4 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield, 3 wide, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 500M, made no impression in straight.
Bumped start, raced at tail, 8 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Out with rest, positioned 3 wide, 3 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly and made contact with the right side of its barrier, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Fast into stride, tracked leaders, 3 wide, found rail near 1000M, sat right behind the leader in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened 250M, eased final 150M. (Blood in trachea.)

Settled in 7th some 3L off the pace early, drifted further back to 8th over 4L off passing the 1000M, switched out for a clear run entering home straight, responded well to hit the front inside final 150M.
Crowded at start, taken well behind from a poor draw and waited with, commenced move approaching final turn, tight between runners early in straight, finished off the race well inside final 150M.
Settled towards rear of strung-out field after moderate start, commenced move 3-wide home bend swinging one of the widest into straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Niggled along just worse than midfield, lost position home bend dropping to one of the last, renewed effort into straight and ran on well under pressure down the rail to narrowly miss a placing.
Close up in 3rd on rails, baulked for a run early in straight, obtained clear passage over 200M out, fought on steadily without threatening.

Taken back to midfield in 8th early from a poor draw, made headway to reach 3L 6th onto home bend, fought on steadily under pressure from 4-wide into straight, unable to sustain effort closing stages.

Soon came to share the pace from a poor draw settling just outside race leader from the 1100M out, hit the front narrowly upon straightening but unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 100M.
Settled taken back to worse of midfield, baulked for a run a few times in home straight, produced good late impression.
Taken back to last from the widest draw, trailed the field to the 500M, tight between runners early in straight, fought on steadily under pressure inside final 200M.
Close up in joint 4th, held some chance in similar position into straight, gave ground steadily inside final 200M.
Settled well behind from a poor draw, never seen with a chance. (Bled)
Held slender lead to the 350M, dropped quickly out of contention.
Broke well from a poor draw before settling some 3L off the pace in 6th, became 7th rounding home bend, dropped away quickly under pressure inside final 300M.
Close up in joint 4th 3-wide without cover, folded up quickly shortly after turning into straight.
Led, traveled comfortably, made good ground in the Straight, kept on well to win.
Sat handy, traveled nicely, had every chance.
Sat in front midfield, raced keenly in the middle stages, responded nicely when asked.
Sat rear, traveled smoothly, held up entering the Straight, stayed on well.
Jumped only fairly, sat worse than midfield, ran on evenly.
Sat towards rear after crowded, lay in when placed under pressure, ran on okay.
Chased the leader, unbalanced when changing stride entering the Straight, could not be ridden out thereafter.
Sat handy, traveled fairly, weakened in the Straight, did not finish off (See Incident Report).
Settled in behind of midfield, raced wide, ran on fairly (See Incident Report).
Settled midfield, raced greenly, raced tight near the 200M.
Settled in front of midfield, raced wide, failed to respond.
Sat towards rear, switched out rounding the Turn, no impression (See Incident Report).
Tracked leaders. Challenged from 200m out and kept responding to pressure to edge ahead final 50m.
A bit keen early and soon in front. Edged out by winner only late on.
Prominent throughout and held every chance. No extra only final 50m.
Raced in mid-field after awkward start. Kept on but unable to quite reach leaders.
Soon prominent against stand rail. Tended to hang right from over 200m out and one paced.
Jumped awkwardly but quickly recovered to track leaders. Hung right and no extra final 200m.
Lost ground at start after rearing up as stalls opened and raced keenly towards rear of mid-field. One paced final 200m and unable to get on terms with leaders.
Pushed along in mid-field from 400m out and no real impression.
Reared at start and slowly away. Some headway from rear after driven from 400m out but never a threat.
Recovered from sluggish start to race in touch with leaders. Weakened final 200m.
Half reared as stalls opened and raced in rear. Some modest late headway but never a factor.
Fractious in stalls and slowly away. Never out of rear, briefly short of room 200m out.
Raced on the outer in rear and never involved.
Ran green on debut. Hung and dropped away from 300m out.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd early, positioned in 3rd after passing 1200M, 3 wide turning in, took the lead 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, no daylight until approaching 150M, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1000M, 2nd in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, made contact 250M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 4 wide turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 250M, kept on same pace to the line.

Average to begin, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader early, struck on heels and blundered near 1300M, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield in the middle stages, kept on same pace in straight.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at tail, 4 lengths or so back turning in, unable to obtain clear run in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, bumped 1300M, dropped to midfield after passing 1100M, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.

Broke well from a poor draw, prominent in 4th 2-wide early, struck into 1250M out, obtained rails run onto home bend but steadied behind runner when pace slackened, kept on until finding no extra inside final 200M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 3 wide towards rear, checked near 1300M, 6 lengths back in the middle stages, angled out 500M, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, failed to close off in straight.

Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1000M, led by a length in the middle stages, peaked and headed early in straight, weekend final 300M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Sat just behind the leader, switched out rounding the Home Turn, ran on strongly, won comfortably.
Settled midfield on the rail, closed off nicely, no threat to winner.
Raced in midfield 2 wide, travelled keenly, made good ground late.
Sat last, stayed on well for 4th.
Settled in front of midfield on the rail, kept on until weakened final 100M.
Showed good speed to lead, kept on fairly.
Caught 3 wide no cover midfield, ran on ordinarily.
Sat behind midfield on the rail, one pace when asked.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, blundered rounding the Home Turn, made little impression.
Sat towards the rear, made no impression.
Sat one pace, weakened in the Straight.
Settled at the rear, limited response when asked.
Caught 4 wide no cover early before taken back to the rear, never a threat.
Slow to jumped, caught 4 wide no cover, never in contention.
Soon took up running on stands rail holding 1L advantage most of the way, held on well to the line.
Broke well settling close up in 1L 3rd, came under pressure inside the 400M and headed for 2nd passing the 300M, fought back dourly to re-gain 2nd final strides.
Broke well before taken back to track race leader in 3rd on stands rail, commenced move 300M out improving well to reach 2nd briefly only to lose it near the line.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground settling in last few, gradually recovered to just over 2L back in 4th approaching the course proper, ran on under pressure to only narrowly miss a placing.
Held up just over 2L off the pace, came under pressure in similar position approaching the course proper, kept on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly settling in forward of midfield, came under pressure coming onto course proper, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly gradually drifting backward to last few, switched in for a clear run 400M out but unable to quicken under pressure.
Travelled keenly in forward of midfield, gave ground steadily from approaching the course proper. Jockey reported horse hung out throughout a difficult ride.
Always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Prominent briefly steadily dropping back to last few along the rail, tailed-off under pressure inside final 300M.
Broke well and soon in front, quickened to a clear lead 250M then kept on strongly to the line for a comfortable victory.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, 6Ls off the pace middle stages before moving closer passing 600M, ran on well down outside in the straight to take 2nd but couldn't reach winner.
Jumped fairly, asked to go forward chasing leaders, had difficulty obtaining clear running near 300M, tried hard final stages but couldn't get closer to winner final stages.
Blundered on jumping and lost ground, obtained a position behind midfield, brought very wide 700M, briefly went 3rd mid-straight before flattening out late.
Slow to begin, soon improved to race in mid-division, held up for clear running 400-250M before running on well to take 5th. Could do better.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, held up 400-300M behind rivals then closed off fairly when obtaining clear running. Not troubled leaders.
Jumped on terms from draw 1, settled in midfield along the inside, ran home one paced on straightening. Never a threat to leaders.
Reserved in a rearward position 5-6Ls off leaders, taken to wide outside passing 400M, ran home fairly passing tired horses.
From wide draw quickly into stride, pressed leader on outside, run ended passing 300M and faded.
Settled down 3-wide in midfield, in similar position turning home, held up for clear running 400-300M but couldn't make any headway final stages.
From draw 12 unable to obtain a position close to the rail and was obliged to race wide no cover ahead of midfield, couldn't go on final 250M, drifted out of contention.
From wide draw taken back to last, 6Ls to make up 400M but failed to make any progress.
Crowded after the start, obtained a 3-wide spot towards the rear, taken wider 600M and hung out making the home turn, had little left on straightening.
Chased leaders 3-wide, raced without cover for majority of the trip, weakened rapidly final 300M, finished last. (Jockey : raced flat today / Roarer.)

Shifted in at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to the line and scored. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began only fairly and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, cleared 250M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 900M, 2nd in the middle stages, retook the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 900M, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider and made contact 450M, peaked early in straight, kept on same pace to the line.
Began awkwardly, taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Away well, tracked leaders on the outside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, badly hampered by faller near 450M, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 12, raced at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, severely checked near 450M, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider 500M, severely checked 450M, eased thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day.) (See Racing Incidents.)

Placing: FE
Comment: Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 600M, hampered and fell heavily near 450M. (Roarer.) (Lame right hind leg next day.)
Began only fairly, taken back to race towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 950M, 2 wide from 600M, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, finished off well to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Jumped well from gate 10, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear, 2 wide, wider from 600M, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened thereafter. (Roarer.)
Began only fairly and made contact, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, 7-1/2L back turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, dropped towards rear 700M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Began well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 wide from 1000M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, a bit closer in the middle stages, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened final 100M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover from 1000M, 3-1/2L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 2 wide, wider from 700M, 6 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly, led last stride.
Began only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 500M, finished off very strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 400M, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (Dead-heat 3rd.)
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two late. (Dead-heat 3rd.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, found rail near 600M, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight, nearest finish.
Began smartly from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.

Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually close home. (See Racing Incidents)
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, showed limited response in straight, eased close home. (See Racing Incidents)
Began well from gate 9, raced towards rear, 7 lengths back on turn, made no impression in the run home.
Bumped shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 7 lengths back in the middle stages, made no impression in straight.
Made heavy contact with the right side of its barrier on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Shifted out at start, sent forward to race prominently, 1-3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened 250M, eased final 100M.
Started to improve from mid-field on final bend and stayed on to lead on line.
Made running. Responded to pressure from 200m out and headed only on line.
Tracked leader and keen. Challenged and every chance 200m out but no extra final 50m.
Stayed on from mid-field until one paced and no further impression late on.
Held up from wide draw. Kept on at the one pace under pressure from final turn and unable to get on terms with leaders.
Tracked leader until no extra and lost ground final 200m.
Raced in touch with leaders and a bit keen. Moved closer final bend but unable to quicken and weakened final 200m.
Held up in last after sluggish start. Driven and struggling final bend until closing up and passing a few final 150m.
Wide into home straight after racing in mid-field and no impression.
Held up on the outer and never involved after coming widest into home straight.
Raced in touch. Wide off final bend and soon lost ground.
Settled behind midfield, traveled okay, responded nicely when placed under pressure.
Sat towards rear, raced wide, made good process in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Sat handy, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, made steady progress.
Sat worse than midfield, traveled okay, ran on evenly to the line.
Settled towards rear, traveled fairly, one pace to the finish.
Sat midfield, traveled fairly, rider expressed concern about horse's action, did not fully tested (Must BT, See Incident Report).
Slow to jump, sat rear, raced rear, minor progress made in the Straight.
Settled worse than midfield, raced keenly in the early stages, limited response when asked.
Sat handy, raced keenly rounding the Turn, weakened quickly in the Straight.
Tacked the leader, traveled okay, weakened passing 150M.
Settled in front of midfield, traveled fairly, did not make ground.
Ridden along to lead, weakened notably rounding the Turn, faded (Must BT, See Incident Report).
Smooth headway from mid-field off bend and led 100m out. Always doing enough in front.
Raced wide in mid-field. Improved with winner off bend and stayed on to chase that rival home.
Settled in mid-field. Headway from over 200m out and stayed on steadily to make promising debut.
Tracked pace. Hung briefly when driven 400m out but stayed on.
Made running until headed and no extra from 150m out.
Waited with in mid-field. Keeping on but unable to reach leaders when briefly short of room late on.
Held up. Stayed on final 400m but never looked like reaching leaders.
Pressed leader until weakening final 150m.
Tracked leaders. Pushed along off bend and soon weakened.
Drawn wide and held up. Headway from 400m out but unable to sustain and eased final 100m. Bled.
Struggling in rear and detached from over 400m out.
Raced wide in mid-field. Under pressure and struggling from 500m out. Found to be displaying an irregular heart rhythm.
Began only fairly, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed good response in straight, took the lead approaching 100M, kept on very well to the line.

Fast into stride, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1150M, retook the lead 550M, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 100M. (See Racing Incident.)
Moderately away, raced in midfield on rail, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place without threatening the first two.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared after passing 200M, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved closer after passing 1300M, took the lead near 1150M, headed 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually inside final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Began smartly, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide after passing 800M, same margin back on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the outside, 2 wide from 700M, a bit closer on turn, made no impression in straight.
Taken back to race towards rear 3 wide towards rear, hard ridden from 550M, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, hard ridden after passing 600M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.) (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Made contact at start, read at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled towards the rear on the rail, saved every ground, closed off strongly, just got there on the line.
Tracked leader 3 wide, kept on well, just missed.
Settled behind midfield on the rail, held up rounding the Home Turn, ran on strongly for 3rd. (See Incident Report)
Jumped well and led on the rail, kept on until weakened final 150M.
Settled worse than midfield 3 wide, stayed on fairly. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind the leaders, one pace when asked.
Sat on pace 2 wide, kept on only fairly.
Dispute lead 2 wide between horses, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sat midfield on the rail, angled out in the Straight, limited response when asked
Sat last, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Sat in front of midfield 3 wide, weakened in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, never a threat. (Disappointing Performance, must trial) (See Incident Report)
Sat midfield 3 wide, under pressure from 650M, weakened and faded. (Unacceptable Performance, must trial)
Broke well from the one draw and made all kicking some 3L clear into straight, flattered but just held on from others' late challenge closing stages.
Settled better than midfield mainly in 5th some 5L back, finished off the race well to just fail to get up on line.
Chased leader to straight, fought on steadily without threatening while hanging in.
Over 3L back in 3rd on rail, became 4th 5L back when pace quickened on home bend, 5th into straight and fought on steadily to re-gain 4th late.
Settled just worse than midfield, 3-wide rounding home bend, fought on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish despite inconvenienced late.
Not far off to straight, had nothing to give to threaten.
Never better than midfield, found nil in home straight.
Well behind to straight, hampered by faller on the bend, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run to the line.
Hampered at start, travelled wide in last few after beginning from a poor gate, made no further impression while hanging in.
Towards rear, saved ground on rail turning in for home, one paced.
Knuckled over badly at start, always well behind.

Placing: FE
Comment: Apparently injured 650M out and fell.
Pressed forward and crossed to the lead 1200M, set good pace to straight, opened up 2L lead 300M, dug deep closing stages to hold off a late challenge.
From draw 2 went forward to chase leader, well placed to strike 400M, fought hard to line but winner always had enough to hold on.
Jumped only fairly, reserved near last 6-7Ls off leader, brought widest 500M, had plenty to make up top of straight, closed off well to go 3rd near line.
Away well enough from draw 1, reserved in midfield along the fence, fought on steadily on straightening but never able to challenge first two.
Began well, raced in a more forward position than previous starts, caught wide no cover for majority of the race, went 3rd mid-straight but couldn't sustain run late stages.

From wide draw dropped back to race in the last spot 8Ls off the pace, moved up to 11th place 400M but still had plenty to do, had no clear running 300M before finishing off reasonably well to take 6th.
From draw 14 shifted across behind runners in the early stages, raced towards the rear 6Ls back, saved ground throughout but the finishing response final 400M was only fair.
Up with early pace, ended up chasing leaders from 1200M, under pressure to keep up 600M, kept on fairly on straightening and was always held by leaders.
Jumped on terms, couldn't get any closer than 3-wide, chased leaders early before settling down in midfield, ran home one paced final 400M under top weight. Never a threat to leaders.
Jumped only fairly, settled in 2nd half of the field, little change in position turning home, 5Ls to make up but failed to make any progress.
Positively ridden, chased leader from 1200m, hard driven 450M but soon gave ground and dropped out of contention. (Jockey : instructed to hold an on-pace position.)
Jumped awkwardly, settled in mid-division 4-5Ls off the pace early and middle stages, under pressure 650M to hold its position, soon weakened out of contention turning home.
Obtained a 3-wide position in midfield early stages, shuffled back to last making the turn for home and soon left behind by rivals on straightening.
Unable to slot in, caught racing 4-wide from early stages, lost cover 800M and was already gone turning into straight. Eased when no chance.

Bumped start, took the early lead, headed 1150M, positioned 1 out 1 back in the middle stages, angled out 500M, retook the lead 300M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced in midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 750M, 2 lengths or so back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, always just held.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, closed off well to take a place without threatening the first two.
Bumped shortly after start, tracked leaders on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared after passing 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 500M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, not enough room early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run until final 100M, kept on same pace to the line.
Out with rest, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out 600M, 4-1/2L back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 150M.
Jumped awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, no clear run early in straight, steadied near 250M, made no impression thereafter.

Began fairly and made contact, raced prominently but 3 wide early, 2 wide from 900M, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 1150M, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear, 8 lengths back in the middle stages, commenced move 550M, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run in straight, not able to test properly.
Went forward and crossed to the lead 1000M, kept on well when asked 300M, dug deep late and bravely held off the persistent challenge from 2nd and 3rd.

Caught racing 3-wide in midfield from the outside draw, worked into the race well on straightening, quickened up to challenge leaders and came very close to winning. Just denied by a diminishing head.
From draw 13 driven forward to track the pace, launched a strong challenge on leader final 300M, fought hard and came closest at the line. Lost 2nd in a photo.
Began well from draw 7, ended up chasing leaders on the inside, kept trying passing 400M but couldn't match finishing pace of first three final 200M.
Bumped shortly after the start, reserved behind mid-division, brought wide top of the straight, stayed on mildly to the line and was never a winning hope.
Obtained a midfield position along the 2-path, held up making the Home Turn, had every chance final 300M but unable to make progress.
Given a waiting ride in second half of the field, 5Ls to make up top of straight, was held up for clear running 400M-300M before staying on fairly to the line. Never troubled leaders.
Not hurried early stages, drifted back to a 3-wide spot behind midfield, brought wide top of straight but ran on only fairly. (Mucus.)
Close up behind leaders early stages, shuffled back to midfield approaching home turn and raced keenly middle stages, failed to run on early straight, drifted out of contention 250M.

Jumped only fairly and shortly after blundered, settled near last about 6Ls away, lay in in the home straight and had difficulty obtaining clear running near 200M, posed no threat to leaders final stages.

Bumped on jumping, settled down behind midfield along the inside, couldn't muster any sort of challenge in the straight. (Jockey : would appreciate being stepped up in distance for its next race start.)
Jumped awkwardly and ended up racing in the last spot, had task in hand top of straight but failed to run on.
From draw 12 obtained a position ahead of midfield, raced wide and without cover for the majority of the event, had little left passing 400M, weakened away.
Urged along to be chasing leaders, couldn't go on 400M, soon retreated to last and eased down. (Jockey concerned something amiss with his mount in the Home Straight / Irregular heart rhythm.)
Sat handy, traveled smoothly, responded nicely when asked.
Settled midfield, traveled strongly, made good progress in the Straight, had every chance.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, held up on top of the Straight, ran on evenly.
Jumped only fairly, sat towards rear, commenced to improve rounding the Turn, made some ground inside 100M.
Sat in front of midfield, traveled okay, closed off one pace.
Settled handy, traveled fairly, slightly weakened passing 200M.
Sat towards rear, raced on the rail, closed off okay.
Sat behind midfield, traveled fairly, limited when asked.
Sat in front of midfield, raced wide, minor progress made, weakened over the concluding stages.
Sat worse than midfield, weakened inside 300M, no impression.
Sat behind the leader, weakened approaching 250M, could not finish off (See Incident Report).
Ridden along to lead, ran inside standard, weakened notably passing 300M.
Jumped only fairly, sat rear, never a danger.
Sat rear, switched out rounding the Turn, no contention.
Tracked pace. Took narrow lead 100m out and kept responding to hold on.
Three wide tracking pace. Ran on well and every chance from 150m out.
Across from wide stall to make running. No extra after headed 150m out.
Keen in mid-field and had to wait for clear run early in home straight. Ran on once clear but lacked pace to challenge front two.
Held up from high draw. Still plenty to do off bend and ran on without being able to reach leaders.
One paced under pressure from 300m out after racing in mid-field and unable to improve position.
Tracked leaders and keen. No extra final 200m.
Troubled passage up rail early in home straight after racing in mid-field. One paced once clear from 200m out.
Some headway from rear final 200m but never a threat.
A bit keen towards rear of mid-field. Very one paced home straight and no impression.
Held up after briefly tight for room at start. Caught behind rivals 300m out but no impression once clear.
Across to race prominently from high draw. Weakened 200m out and eased.
Slow to get going on debut and held up. Struggling under pressure when hung markedly left 300m out.
Caught wide throughout. Under pressure off bend and soon well held, eased final 200m.
Jumped well from the widest draw, in touch but trapped wide early, 2 wide on turn, hard ridden from 300M, showed very good response, took the lead 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began only fairly, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place, not quite able to challenge.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, a length back turning in, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded and unbalanced shortly after start, raced towards rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start and unbalanced, taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, angled out early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced slightly better than midfield, 3 wide, inconvenienced near 900M, 3-1/2L back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Bumped heavily shortly after start and unbalanced, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept on evenly in straight. (Lost right front plate.)
Jumped only fairly and made contact, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back turning in, angled out early in straight, one-paced in the run home.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on nicely when asked, won comfortably.
Settled midfield 2 wide, held up rounding the Home Turn, closed off nicely.
Taken back from outside barrier, settled last, stayed on.
Raced 3 wide with cover towards the rear, closed off okay.
Settled behind midfield 2 wide, made good ground between horses.
Settled midfield on the rail, closed off fairly.
Sat outside the leader, limited response when asked.
Sat on pace on the rail, one pace when asked.
Jumped well and led, weakened final furlong.
Sat towards the rear 2 wide, raced keenly, didn't run on.
Caught 3 wide no cover behind midfield, weakened in the Straight.
Settled at the rear, never a threat.
Sat behind midfield on the rail, never in contention.
Soon took up running from the one draw, drew 1L 200M out, kept on well under pressure.
Soon recovered along the rail to just over 1L back in 4th after moderate start, fought on steadily in straight to reach 2nd over 100M out.
Broke well from a poor draw settling mainly one-out-one-back in 4th becoming 5th home bend, fought on steadily to only miss 2nd by the narrowest of margins.
Settled worse than midfield in 10th, one of the widest into straight, bumped and unbalanced 400M out, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled towards rear, one of the widest into straight, ran on well down the centre of the track despite shifting ground about 200M out.
Well there alongside race leader, gradually faded under pressure inside final 150M.
Settled mainly 2-wide in midfield, badly unbalanced 400M out, improving when baulked for a run 100M out, unable to make any further impression.
Settled well behind, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Settled in last few, held up for a run on straight until the 300M, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled within 3L of pace in 6th, drifted some 4L back into straight, made no impression inside final 300M. (Mucus in trachea)

Prominent from a poor draw travelling 4-wide without cover, taken some 1L back for cover 3-wide in 7th onto home bend, badly crowded over 400M out and inconvenienced again shortly after, never recovered.
Always well behind, never seen with a chance.
Lost ground at start but soon recovered along the rail to rear of midfield, tightened on top of home bend and baulked for a run early in straight, gradually weakened.
Well there from a poor draw travelling 3-wide without cover, folded up quickly soon after straightening.
Fast into stride and held position just off the lead on settling, moved up stylishly to take lead 350M and was strong through the line under top weight. Held on from fast finishing 2nd late.
Travelled well in midfield along the inside, worked into the race nicely, did best work final 200M to just go under.
Settled ahead of midfield early stages, moved up to chase leader home turn, went 2nd 200M, chased on solidly to be nearest at the line.
In touch, close 5th at 400M, tried hard but lacked a big enough kick, always held by leaders.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground, recovered to race behind midfield, stuck on well from top of straight but could not quite crack the top four.
Jumped only fairly, dropped back to race towards the rear 7Ls back, stayed on final 400M although not troubling leaders. Passable debut.
Taken back from draw 14 and settled near last, some 5Ls to make up 400M but offered little in the run home.
Jumped on terms, reserved in midfield along the 3-path, lacked the turn of foot to capitalise over final 300M, got home only fairly.
Settled midfield but couldn't get closer than 3-wide, couldn't keep going 250M and was easily accounted for.
From a wide draw guided to a 3-wide position towards the rear, 4.5L off the pace 400M, lacked the dash to be competitive.
Began only fairly, moved up to settle in midfield along the 2-path, 3Ls off leader 400M but found little when it mattered.
Jumped only fairly, ended up in last spot 8Ls off the pace, brought to wide outside on straightening but failed to run on.
Sent forward under 10lb claimer, raced keenly in the lead throughout the early stages, headed 350M, compounded under pressure and gave ground.
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders, emptied passing 300M weakened rapidly. (Jockey concerned with his mount's action in the Home Straight when it gave ground / No Vet findings.)

Shifted in at start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd.

Inconvenienced at start, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, bumped and unbalanced near 200M, kept on well to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2nd in the middle stages, 1/2L back turning in, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 50M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, took the lead, travelled keenly in the lead in the early and middle stages, led by 1/2L turning in, peaked and headed 300M, kept on evenly to the line.

Began only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, bumped 200M, crowded near 150M, made minor progress thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made some headway in straight.
Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, angled out 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out after passing 500M, 6 lengths or so back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, 3 wide from 500M, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 250M, weakened final furlong.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, found daylight 250M, finished off very strongly, won by 2-1/4L.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 3 wide, angled out 450M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 125M, ran on evenly to the line.
Out with rest, raced 3 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed 1000M, steadied near 750M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.

Moderately away, raced prominently but trapped wide, slightly taken back after passing 1000M, positioned 3 wide, 2 lengths back in the middle stages, hard ridden from 300M but only showed limited response, ran on evenly to the line.

Made contact and unbalanced shortly after start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 300M, made some progress until approaching final 100M, one-paced thereafter.
Bumped start and blundered, raced 2 wide towards rear, 4 lengths or so back turning in, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, ran on same pace thereafter.
Out in line, positioned 3 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Jumped only fairly, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced prominently but trapped wide, hung out entering straight, weakened early in straight, eased thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Placing: DNF
Comment: Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, went wrong and pulled up 450M. (Bled.) (See Racing Incidents.)

Settled well back 3-wide from a poor draw and waited with, went one of the widest into straight, ran on well to just get up on line.

Ridden positively from the widest draw before settling in 6th in forward of midfield, renewed effort home bend swinging one of the widest into straight, ran on well to hit the front over 100M out only to be caught final strides.

Taken backward to last few from a poor draw, gained slightly closer in slackened pace home bend, ran on between runners to be nearest at finish despite inconvenienced close to home.
Taken back to last few from a poor draw travelling wide without cover, commenced move 650M out reaching 8th some 5L back on top of home bend, made short-lived effort 200M out.
Jumped awkward, pressed forward to track the leader 2-wide, hit the front into straight but unable to sustain effort while hanging in, overhauled inside final 150M.
Settled in midfield on rails, remained similar into straight despite niggled along home bend, saved ground turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Gradually taken back to last few dropping to last over 650M out, ran past well-beaten horses inside final 150M out.
Settled 3-wide without cover in joint 3rd mainly about 2L off the pace, swung wider into straight and found nil.
Jumped best from the one draw, led the field until narrowly headed into straight, dropped away from 2nd quickly inside final 150M.
Crowded at start from a wide draw settling well back on the rail, improved to join backmarkers 750M out, tightened 600M out, saved ground turning in for home, made no further impression.
Settled mainly in joint 3rd 2-wide about 2L off the pace, dropped out tamely on straightening.
Jumped only fairly, sat handy, traveled comfortably, kept on well.
Settled midfield, traveled smoothly, made good progress in the Straight.
Sat towards rear, responded nicely in the Straight, stayed on nicely.
Sat worse than midfield, bumped near the 150M, ran on evenly.
Sat rear, traveled okay, raced tight between 250M to 100M.
Settled in front of midfield, weakened notably near 200M, failed to finish off (See Incident Report).
Sat worse than midfield, traveled fairly, limited response when asked (See Incident Report).
Sat behind midfield, lay in under pressure in the Straight, no impression.
Ridden along to lead, raced keenly, throughout, weakened quickly in the Straight (See Incident Report).
Keen in front and soon leading by 2 lengths. Kicked on again after challenged briefly turning into straight and soon on top, running on strongly.
Tracked leader throughout but unable to challenge that rival final 200m.
Never far away. Chased leading pair off bend and stayed on at the one pace.
Stayed on from mid-field but lacked speed to get near winner.
Raced in mid-field after involved in some early scrimmaging. Stayed on at the one pace final 250m.
Brought widest off bend after held up and never nearer.
Checked briefly at start and waited with in rear. Some headway final 200m but never a threat.
Raced towards rear of mid-field. Driven from 300m out and no real impression.
Tracked pace until weakening from 200m out.
Held up and never a factor. Bled.
Keen in mid-division after involved in some early scrimmaging. Driven and lost ground final 250m.
Raced wide after bumped early. Driven off bend and weakened.
Taken back from gate 9, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly, won by a neck.
Bumped on the hindquarters shortly after start, raced in midfield on the outside, commenced move 400M, finished off strongly, just beaten by a neck.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, a bit closer on turn, angled out 400M, finished off well to make frame.
Out with rest, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (Blood in trachea.)
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually close home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, made little progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually close home.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually inside final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, carried wider 600M, same margin back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the inside, peaked on run 500M, eased early in straight, unacceptable performance. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled behind the leaders on the rail, closed off well and won going away, comfortably
Settled outside the lead, hung out under pressure, ran on okay, no threat to the winner. (See Incident Report)
Jumped nicely and led, kept on nicely.
Jumped on terms, checked at 1000M and lost ground, raced behind midfield on the rail, stayed on well despite the troubled trip
Settled in front of midfield 2 wide, ran on fairly.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, hampered at 150M, still ran on.
Crowded at start and again near the 1000M, midfield 2 wide, made little impression. (Substantial blood)
Sat in front of midfield on the rail, made no ground.
Sat at the rear on the rail, only able to pass weakened rivals.
Caught 3 wide no cover on pace, weakened in the Straight.
Sat at the rear 2 wide, checked near the 150M, never a threat.
Crowded at 1000M, midfield 3 wide, raced keenly never in contention. (Bled)
Travelled well behind and waited with, shifted one of the widest for a clear run into straight, responded well to take command about 100M out.
Began moderately but was able to soon take up running on the rail passing the winning post the first time, led the field until swamped by fast-finishing winner about 100M out, just held on for 2nd.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground settling at the back, trailed the field until commenced move 650M out circling the field 4-wide home bend, carried wider into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled 3-wide in midfield, lost position rounding home bend, tight behind runners early in straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled in midfield on rail, shifted 2-wide for a run turning in for home, one-paced under pressure.
Not far off the pace on rail travelling keenly first bend, saved ground on the inside turning in for home, one-paced without quickening under pressure.

Soon taken across at the back from the widest draw, travelled in last few to straight, snuck up on rail turning in for home, fought on under pressure early in straight, found no extra inside final 100M.
Taken back to last few from a poor draw travelling keenly 3-wide, gained slightly closer early in back straight, very wide around home bend and into straight, fought on steadily while hanging in.
Close up early from a poor draw gradually settling just over 2L back in 4th, restrained in 5th most of back straight, tightened when in a similar position early in home straight, never recovered.
Pressed forward from a poor draw to join race leader onto first bend before settling in 1L 2nd into back straight, dropped out of contention quickly inside final 350M.

Wide in last few early stages, circled the field from first bend to reach 3rd 3-wide 1000M out, remained in a similar position before giving ground steadily on home bend, folded up quickly in straight.

One of the first to jump despite awkwardly but soon retrained to midfield, dropped steadily further back halfway out reaching 9th approaching home bend when inconvenienced, folded up quickly after straightening.
On jumping was badly crowded for room, soon guided to the fence and obtained a run behind mid-division, held up 450M-350M, quickened up nicely when asked and got up just in time in a busy finish.

Prominently ridden, tracked leader from 1300M, poised to strike 300M, fought on under pressure to just go under in a busy finish. (Jockey : lay in in the Home Straight and as a result proved difficult to ride out.)
From wide draw switched off to race in last, 8Ls off the pace home turn, swung widest for home before closing off strongly under top weight to take 3rd. Nearest finish.
Shifted in abruptly on jumping, drifted back to race near last 7Ls back, had some work to do 400M, closed off well to claim 4th. Nearest finish.
Away well from draw 1, soon led and took them along at good pace under 7lb claimer, fought hard to hold the lead on straightening, headed nearing 50M, lost several places close home.
Severely checked on jumping when crowded by a rival, ended up near last, had some work to do top of straight, ran on mildly down the inside but was never close enough to challenge leaders.
Chased leaders in 4th, raced keenly early stages, had every chance turning home but lacked the extra gear to challenge leaders.
Reserved in a position behind midfield, 5Ls off leader middle stages, kept on only fairly final 300M and was never a winning hope.
Taken back from wide draw, raced wide no cover in second half of the field, 6Ls to make up 400M, couldn't muster the pace to challenge.
Settled down in midfield, a little further back than intended, hard pressed from 450M but closed off the race one paced.
Tracked leaders in a race run at good pace, little change in position heading to home turn, couldn't sustain run passing 200M, weakened towards the line.
Maintained a position ahead of midfield, came under pressure 500M, soon gave ground and weakened to last.
Began smartly, raced in 2nd, challenged the leader turning in, hit the front 250M, kept on well to the line, won by a narrow margin.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 400M, very wide turning in, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, 2 wide from 700M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped only fairly, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually close home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, made some progress early in straight, no clear run final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the outside, found rail 800M, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 11, tracked leaders on the outside, no cover throughout, dropped to midfield on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two final 100M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 50M.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground throughout, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 750M, a bit closer on turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped only fairly, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, made no progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, made no progress in the run home.
Made contact at start, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began awkwardly, sent forward to take the lead, peaked and headed 400M, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Tracked leader. Challenged from top of home straight and got on top final 100m.
Never far away and stayed on well for second.
Tracked leader. Led off bend and every chance until headed and no extra final 100m.
Stayed on after racing in touch.
Waited with towards rear. Stayed on but lacked pace to challenge.
Stayed on after held up but unable to get on terms with leaders.
Under pressure in mid-field off bend and stayed on at the one pace.
Pushed along off bend after racing in mid-field and one paced.
In rear after bumped at start. Some headway final 200m but never a danger.
Dropped in behind runners after awkward start from wide stall. Little impression.
Held up from wide draw. Short of room over 200m out and never a factor.
Raced wide throughout and weakened final 250m.
Recovered from awkward start to lead and keen. Headed bend and weakened from 400m line.
Raced wide in mid-field prior to dropping away from bend.
Settled midfield, traveled comfortably, made good progress inside 150M.
Sat handy, traveled okay, ran on evenly.
Sat towards rear, improved after 1500M, raced wide thereafter, lay in rounding the Turn, closed off okay.
Sat handy, held up top of the Straight, ran on fairly well.
Ridden along to lead, slightly weakened after 200M, closed off fairly.
Settled in front of midfield, made the mid race move passing 1400M to share the lead, raced keenly in the middle stages, kept on fairly.
Sat towards rear, raced greenly, one pace to the finish.
Jumped only fairly, settled worse than midfield, limited response in the Straight.
Sat rear, always rear, minor progress made, no impression.
Sat behind midfield, no contention.
Waited with towards rear. Quickened to lead 200m out and soon on top, winning readily.
Raced wide in mid-field. No match for winner final 300m but stayed on to finish clear of rest.
Raced close up and keen. Stuck to task after short of room briefly 300m out but lacked speed to go with front two.
Led early in home straight after racing prominently but no extra once headed 200m out.
No threat to leaders but stayed on at the one pace after racing in mid-field.
Headway and briefly threatened over 200m out after racing in touch but soon no extra.
No extra final 200m after racing in touch with leaders. Finished lame.
Wide in rear from high draw. Some headway from top of home straight but never dangerous.
Short of room over 300m out after racing in mid-field and little impression once clear final 200m.
Only modest headway from rear final 200m and never a threat.
Waited with in rear after sluggish start and no impression under pressure.
Lost ground after slow start and then keen in rear. Carried head awkwardly under pressure and no impression. Bled.
Raced wide from high draw. In touch with leaders off bend but soon weakened.
Across to lead from high draw. Headed over 300m out and weakened quickly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 550M, very wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, no clear run early in straight, cleared approaching 200M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back turning in, taken wide in straight and finished off well to take a place.

Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 700M, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, stayed on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross approaching 700M, 2 wide from 550M, 1/2L back turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, found rail 750M, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, no clear run final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, carried wider 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Made contact at start, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide in midfield, 2 wide in the middle stages, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced in midfield on the inside, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, not enough room 150M, eased thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 150M.
Jumped on terms, ridden along early to led, kept on well to score.
Settled towards the rear 2 wide, stayed on well for 2nd
Sat outside the lead, kept on nicely, won the battle for 3rd.
Caught 3 wide no cover on pace, ran on nicely, just missed 3rd.
Jumped slowly, sat behind midfield on the rail, closed off okay, run peaked final 100M.
Sat midfield 2 wide, held up rounding the Home Turn, made little impression. (See Incident Report)
Sat at the rear, stayed on fairly.
Sat in front of midfield 2 wide, crowded rounding the Home Turn, never ran on. (See Incident Report)
Settled midfield 2 wide, shifted ground rounding the Turn, soon weakened. (See Incident Report)
Sat behind the leaders on the rail, weakened in the Straight.
Caught 4 wide no cover throughout, bumped on the turn and became unbalanced, gave ground in the Straight.
Under pressure since the start, detached midway, never in contention. (See Incident Report)
Settled well behind and waited with, trailed the field around home bend and into straight, responded well down the centre of the track to assert authority closing stages.

Ridden positively from a wide draw before settling for 6th some 3L back 3-wide, further off the pace when leader drew clear home bend, came to challenge in straight holding every chance inside the 200M but found winner too good.
Soon picked up to join race leaders, taken 2L back to 3rd 2-wide inside the 1050M, quickened to hit the front briefly just inside the 300M, made no further impression closing stages.
Gradually settled towards the rear, wide into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well from a poor draw, soon taken back to last few 3-wide with cover, commenced move 600M out on top of home bend, fought on under pressure in straight despite inconvenienced over 300M out.
Soon taken well back trailing the field to home bend, steadied behind runners about 600M out, baulked for run in straight until the 300M, fought on steadily without threatening.

Improved steadily to 3-wide in midfield after the first 300M, steadied and lost position passing the 1000M, came under pressure into straight, kept on under pressure and shifted ground until the 100M.
Broke well but soon taken well back, remained in last few into straight, baulked for a run about 250M out, kept on steadily without quickening.
Travelled keenly not far off the pace in 5th, lost position when crossed about 900M out, some 5L back in 6th rounding home bend, one-paced without quickening in straight.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to rear of midfield in 8th some 5L off the pace, came under pressure home bend, unable to quicken to threaten in straight.
Well there 4-wide from a poor draw, obtained 2-wide one-back position onto home bend, chased leader into straight, kept on before fading inside final 150M.
Began well with leaders, shifted 2L back to 4th passing the 1200M, further off the pace in 5th when race leader drew clear home bend, saved ground turning in but steadily faded in straight.
Settled in forward of midfield on rail after moderate start, inconvenienced 900M out, found nothing in home straight.
Pressed forward from sluggish start to soon take up running, drew some 3L clear in front 700M out while racing keenly around home bend, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 300M.
Moved up to be 2nd on settling, took lead nearing 200M, kicked away late stages for a comfortable victory.
In touch, loomed 300M, tried hard but couldn't get closer to winner in the run home. Lay out under pressure final 200M.
Dropped back to race at the rear 6Ls back, closed off final 400M fastest, just missed 2nd.
Settled in midfield, ran home mildly when driven along inside 400M, never going the pace to challenge first few.
From draw 14 raced along the stand's rail and always in touch with leaders, poised to strike 300M but run ended 100M from home.
Maintained a position behind midfield, made short-lived effort passing 400M, held ground over final stages.
Sent forward under 10lb claimer, raced keenly in the lead, headed near 200M then gave ground final stages. (Jockey : First run in 84 days, would derive benefit from today's performance.)
From draw 1 unable to find cover during the race, settled behind midfield 5Ls back, found less than expected when asked 400M.
Held up in midfield 4Ls off leaders, ran home one-paced. Never dangerous.
Stayed in touch behind leaders until 300M when outpaced. (Jockey : no explanation for the disappointing performance.)
Guided to the stand's rail and obtained a position behind mid-division, couldn't muster the speed to challenge over final 400M.
Reserved behind midfield, failed to run on over final 500M. Never threatened.
Settled near last, niggled long 600M from home but didn't respond to riding. Never in the picture.
Chased leaders, came under pressure halfway, gave ground passing 400M, weakened to last.
Began fairly, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 100M, kept on well to the line and scored by a head.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 600M, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually close home, finished 3rd.
Crowded on jumping, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 12, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, crowded near 800M, 3 wide turning in, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began very awkwardly and made contact, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, tracked leaders on the outside, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced 3 wide in midfield, crowded near 800M, dropped towards rear after passing 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began smartly from gate 13, raced prominently on the outside, travelled well to turn, hard ridden from 350M, finished off strongly, took the lead close home.
Began well, in touch, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on very well in straight, just beaten by a head.
Jumped only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few close home.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-1/2L back turning in, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Began well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, sat a length behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made little progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear, struck heels and blundered near 900M, 5 lengths back turning in, made no impression in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made no impression in straight.
Began only fairly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
